ve some\ndeep bruising in your left thigh',-1),(87194,5,42896,42956,'00:29:47.369','00:29:49.871','and some torn ligaments\nin your left wrist.',-1),(87195,5,42963,43003,'00:29:50.164','00:29:51.831','Nothing serious.',-1),(87196,5,43005,43054,'00:29:51.915','00:29:53.958','So, as soon as we clear\nyour concussion',-1),(87197,5,43057,43097,'00:29:54.042','00:29:55.710','and you feel well enough,\nyou can go home.',-1),(87198,5,43105,43196,'00:29:56.044','00:29:59.839','That may take a day,\nmaybe three. Okay?',-1),(87199,5,43309,43376,'00:30:04.553','00:30:07.346','I won\'t ask too much of you tonight,',-1),(87200,5,43378,43493,'00:30:07.431','00:30:12.226','but as I said, the NTSB is\nrequired to make initial contact.',-1),(87201,5,43529,43605,'00:30:13.729','00:30:16.898','How much do you remember\nabout the flight?',-1),(87202,5,43657,43717,'00:30:19.067','00:30:21.569','I remember...',-1),(87203,5,43761,43833,'00:30:23.405','00:30:26.407','I remember everything up till the crash.',-1),(87204,5,43838,43867,'00:30:26.617','00:30:27.825','Okay.',-1),(87205,5,43869,43917,'00:30:27.910','00:30:29.911','Mr. Whitaker, that\'s fine.',-1),(87206,5,43933,43998,'00:30:30.579','00:30:33.289','I am required\nto inform you that this incident',-1),(87207,5,44001,44041,'00:30:33.415','00:30:35.082','did result in the loss of life.',-1),(87208,5,44082,44126,'00:30:36.752','00:30:38.586','The current information states that',-1),(87209,5,44129,44220,'00:30:38.712','00:30:42.507','of the 102 souls on board, we lost six.',-1),(87210,5,44222,44278,'00:30:42.591','00:30:44.926','Two crew members\nand four passengers.',-1),(87211,5,44286,44336,'00:30:45.260','00:30:47.345','Fifty-nine people\nwere treated and released,',-1),(87212,5,44338,44366,'00:30:47.429','00:30:48.596','37 people remain...',-1),(87213,5,44370,44418,'00:30:48.764','00:30:50.765','Who did we lose on the crew?',-1),(87214,5,44425,44466,'00:30:51.058','00:30:52.767','The two flight attendants,',-1),(87215,5,44468,44551,'00:30:52.851','00:30:56.312','Camelia Satou and Katerina Marquez.',-1),(87216,5,44606,44657,'00:30:58.607','00:31:00.733','The rep from your pilots\' union,',-1),(87217,5,44659,44714,'00:31:00.817','00:31:03.110','Mr. Anderson, will be\nour contact for you.',-1),(87218,5,44716,44788,'00:31:03.195','00:31:06.197','It\'s important that\nyou follow your union\'s guidance',-1),(87219,5,44790,44832,'00:31:06.281','00:31:08.032','on press and media.',-1),(87220,5,44846,44910,'00:31:08.617','00:31:11.285','The pilots\' union works\nclosely with the NTSB.',-1),(87221,5,44927,44982,'00:31:11.995','00:31:14.288','So, I\'m going to head out.',-1),(87222,5,44984,45016,'00:31:14.373','00:31:15.706','I\'ll turn this off.',-1),(87223,5,45018,45071,'00:31:15.791','00:31:17.959','- Good luck, Mr. Whitaker.\n- Thank you.',-1),(87224,5,45359,45427,'00:31:29.972','00:31:32.807','I knew Trina Marquez. She was...',-1),(87225,5,45463,45503,'00:31:34.309','00:31:35.977','We spent some time together.',-1),(87226,5,45511,45571,'00:31:36.311','00:31:38.813','Yeah, apparently,\nshe wasn\'t strapped in.',-1),(87227,5,45595,45664,'00:31:39.815','00:31:42.692','A survivor reported\nshe was assisting a kid.',-1),(87228,5,45679,45735,'00:31:43.318','00:31:45.653','Margaret Thomason, how\'s she doing?',-1),(87229,5,45743,45797,'00:31:45.988','00:31:48.239','Broken collarbone, just, I mean, cuts.',-1),(87230,5,45799,45849,'00:31:48.323','00:31:50.408','I mean, she\'s banged up, but she\'s...',-1),(87231,5,45851,45895,'00:31:50.492','00:31:52.326','She\'s here, too. She\'s fine.',-1),(87232,5,45911,45952,'00:31:52.995','00:31:54.704','And Ken Evans, your copilot,',-1),(87233,5,45955,46032,'00:31:54.830','00:31:58.040','he took a bad shot to the head.',-1),(87234,5,46044,46130,'00:31:58.500','00:32:02.086','And they\'re keeping him in a coma\njust to let the brain swelling go down,',-1),(87235,5,46132,46164,'00:32:02.170','00:32:03.504','but we feel good about him.',-1),(87236,5,46179,46219,'00:32: