:17.870','01:14:19.704','He traded in the crop duster',-1),(87904,5,107068,107133,'01:14:21.207','01:14:23.875','for the old Cessna\nsitting out there in the barn.',-1),(87905,5,107197,107260,'01:14:26.546','01:14:29.172','Flew that damn thing all over the place.',-1),(87906,5,107349,107381,'01:14:32.885','01:14:34.219','He died.',-1),(87907,5,107397,107437,'01:14:34.887','01:14:36.555','I got a divorce and...',-1),(87908,5,107501,107567,'01:14:39.225','01:14:41.977','I\'ve been trying to sell\nthe place ever since.',-1),(87909,5,107620,107660,'01:14:44.188','01:14:45.856','What about your mom?',-1),(87910,5,107676,107701,'01:14:46.524','01:14:47.566','Dead.',-1),(87911,5,107769,107817,'01:14:50.403','01:14:52.404','You? What about your dad?',-1),(87912,5,107821,107893,'01:14:52.572','01:14:55.574','Well, I\'m pretty sure\nhe lives in Colorado.',-1),(87913,5,107897,107924,'01:14:55.741','01:14:56.867','Yeah?',-1),(87914,5,107955,107991,'01:14:58.161','01:14:59.661','No relationship?',-1),(87915,5,108013,108057,'01:15:00.580','01:15:02.414','It was my mom that raised me.',-1),(87916,5,108063,108101,'01:15:02.665','01:15:04.249','She was incredible.',-1),(87917,5,108136,108221,'01:15:05.668','01:15:09.212','She held it together for so long,\nI couldn\'t even tell how sick she was.',-1),(87918,5,108283,108337,'01:15:11.799','01:15:14.050','We spent those last\nseven months together',-1),(87919,5,108339,108385,'01:15:14.135','01:15:16.052','like we were teenagers.',-1),(87920,5,108419,108510,'01:15:17.471','01:15:21.266','We\'d trade stories\nabout boys and whatever.',-1),(87921,5,108599,108645,'01:15:24.979','01:15:26.897','She loved me.',-1),(87922,5,109063,109098,'01:15:44.332','01:15:45.790','My name\'s Trevor.',-1),(87923,5,109116,109156,'01:15:46.500','01:15:48.168','You saved my mom.',-1),(87924,5,109463,109505,'01:16:00.973','01:16:02.724','It\'s great to see you, Whip.',-1),(87925,5,109507,109559,'01:16:02.808','01:16:04.976','It\'s good to see you, too, Margaret.',-1),(87926,5,109688,109732,'01:16:10.358','01:16:12.192','The service was so nice.',-1),(87927,5,109735,109799,'01:16:12.318','01:16:14.986','I mean, all these people\nwho wanted to say goodbye.',-1),(87928,5,109840,109920,'01:16:16.697','01:16:20.033','Trina looked so beautiful in there.\nDidn\'t you think so?',-1),(87929,5,109932,110024,'01:16:20.534','01:16:24.371','I mean, like she was just\ngoing to wake up and smile.',-1),(87930,5,110032,110104,'01:16:24.705','01:16:27.707','I didn\'t go in. I... I just couldn\'t.',-1),(87931,5,110149,110265,'01:16:29.543','01:16:34.381','Trevor, find Daddy, baby.\nHe\'s over there by Mr. Benton.',-1),(87932,5,110437,110496,'01:16:41.555','01:16:44.015','You really should come\nto the counseling group.',-1),(87933,5,110498,110549,'01:16:44.100','01:16:46.226','The union has great people\nfor us to talk to.',-1),(87934,5,110552,110604,'01:16:46.352','01:16:48.520','I can\'t. Really. I...',-1),(87935,5,110629,110659,'01:16:49.563','01:16:50.814','I will.',-1),(87936,5,110756,110796,'01:16:54.860','01:16:56.528','Well...',-1),(87937,5,110829,110876,'01:16:57.905','01:16:59.864','- You take care, okay, Whip?\n- Okay.',-1),(87938,5,110889,110929,'01:17:00.408','01:17:02.075','Listen, Margaret.',-1),(87939,5,110997,111053,'01:17:04.912','01:17:07.247','You know I\'m in the middle of this',-1),(87940,5,111073,111152,'01:17:08.082','01:17:11.334','investigation. The NTSB\nis investigating the crash.',-1),(87941,5,111154,111196,'01:17:11.419','01:17:13.169','Yeah. I\'m gonna talk to them next week.',-1),(87942,5,111198,111273,'01:17:13.254','01:17:16.381','Yeah. Well, I\'m... I\'m a little nervous',-1),(87943,5,111275,111400,'01:17:16.465','01:17:21.678','because I was out the night\nbefore the crash, at dinner.',-1),(87944,5,111402,111431,'01:17:21.762','01:17:22.971','Yeah. With Trina.',-1),(87945,5,111433,111483,'01:17:23.055','01:17:25.140','Right. And I had two glasses of wine,',-1),(87946,5,111485,111545,'01:17:25.224','01:17:27.726','and they\'re probably going to ask you',-1),(87947,5,111550,111591,'01:17:27.935','01:17:29.644','about my condition that morning,',-1),(87948,5,111593,111667,'01:17:29.729','01:17:32.814','or whether you thought\nI had anything to drink.',-1),(87949,5,111758,111785,'01:17:36.610','01:17:37.736','What?',-1),(87950,5,111865,111912,'01:17:41.073','01:17:43.033','I\'ve known you 11 years, Whip.',-1),(87951,5,111914,111940,'01:17:43.117','01:17:44.200','Right.',-1),(87952,5,111942,111995,'01:17:44.285','01:17:46.494','You want to tell me that\nyou and Trina went to dinner',-1),(87953,5,111997,112046,'01:17:46.579','01:17:48.621','- and you had two glasses of wine?\n- No.',-1),(87954,5,112048,112101,'01:17:48.706','01:17:50.915','Sounds like a nice restaurant.\nNow, which one was it?',-1),(87955,5,112104,112175,'01:17:51.000','01:17:53.960','You have to say that it was\nan ordinary day, Margaret.',-1),(87956,5,112177,112204,'01:17:54.045','01:17:55.170','I mean, it was an ordinary day.',-1),(87957,5,112206,112265,'01:17:55.254','01:17:57.714','You know me. I was in shape to fly.',-1),(87958,5,112371,112410,'01:18:02.136','01:18:03.762','You have a problem with saying that?',-1),(87959,5,112463,112503,'01:18:05.973','01:18:07.640','It\'s a lie, Whip.',-1),(87960,5,112508,112592,'01:18:07.850','01:18:11.353','It\'s a lie. Trina told me\nyou two hadn\'t been to sleep.',-1),(87961,5,112594,112716,'01:18:11.437','01:18:16.524','Well, my lack of sleep had nothing to do\nwith that plane falling apart, Margaret.',-1),(87962,5,112718,112753,'01:18:16.609','01:18:18.068','I\'m just trying to get this thing straight.',-1),(87963,5,112755,112824,'01:18:18.152','01:18:21.029','Now you think any other pilot could have\nlanded that plane and saved more lives?',-1),(87964,5,112826,112856,'01:18:21.113','01:18:22.364','I didn\'t say that, Whip.\nI can\'t imagine another...',-1),(87965,5,112858,112882,'01:18:22.448','01:18:23.448','All right, then.',-1),(87966,5,112884,112949,'01:18:23.532','01:18:26.242','Well, imagine your son,\nTrevor, in this church,',-1),(87967,5,112951,112980,'01:18:26.327','01:18:27.535','looking at you in that box.',-1),(87968,5,112982,113030,'01:18:27.620','01:18:29.621','Or my son visiting me in prison. And...',-1),(87969,5,113032,113109,'01:18:29.705','01:18:32.916','- Please, Whip, enough. Enough, Whip.\n- And for the next 40 years...',-1),(87970,5,113112,113171,'01:18:33.000','01:18:35.460','Don\'t you think we\'ve all had enough?',-1),(87971,5,113352,113398,'01:18:43.010','01:18:44.928','I need this, Margaret.',-1),(87972,5,113578,113619,'01:18:52.436','01:18:54.145','What do you want me to say?',-1),(87973,5,113657,113696,'01:18:55.731','01:18:57.357','I just...',-1),(87974,5,113743,113789,'01:18:59.318','01:19:01.236','It was an ordinary day.',-1),(87975,5,113851,113931,'01:19:03.823','01:19:07.158','The storm, after we took off,',-1),(87976,5,113939,113979,'01:19:07.493','01:19:09.160','was very severe.',-1),(87977,5,114015,114083,'01:19:10.663','01:19:13.498','But as far as\nthe flight crew was concerned,',-1),(87978,5,114115,114171,'01:19:14.792','01:19:17.127','it was a perfectly ordinary day.',-1),(87979,5,114684,114724,'01:19:38.524','01:19:40.191','- Hey.\n- Hi.',-1),(87980,5,114792,114822,'01:19:43.028','01:19:44.279','You okay?',-1),(87981,5,114828,114860,'01:19:44.530','01:19:45.864','Yeah, yeah.',-1),(87982,5,114890,114920,'01:19:47.116','01:19:48.366','So?',-1),(87983,5,114925,114979,'01:19:48.576','01:19:50.827','Well, I got through my first day.\nThey didn\'t fire me.',-1),(87984,5,114981,115011,'01:19:50.911','01:19:52.162','- So...\n- Good. Good.',-1),(87985,5,115032,115099,'01:19:53.038','01:19:55.832','And they need someone to work\nthe night shift and they asked me.',-1),(87986,5,115101,115141,'01:19:55.916','01:19:57.542','It\'s time and a half, so...',-1),(87987,5,115200,115231,'01:20:00.004','01:20:01.296','I got a vest.',-1),(87988,5,115253,115286,'01:20:02.214','01:20:03.590','- And a little name tag.\n- Nice.',-1),(87989,5,115288,115312,'01:20:03.674','01:20:04.674','I got you something.',-1),(87990,5,115314,115342,'01:20:04.758','01:20:05.925','- Yeah?\n- Yeah.',-1),(87991,5,115456,115481,'01:20:10.681','01:20:11.723','It\'s a P-51 Mustang.',-1),(87992,5,115484,115509,'01:20:11.849','01:20:12.891','I know it\'s a P-51...',-1),(87993,5,115512,115539,'01:20:13.017','01:20:14.138','Your daddy fly one of those?',-1),(87994,5,115540,115568,'01:20:14.185','01:20:15.351','Yes, he did.',-1),(87995,5,115592,115632,'01:20:16.353','01:20:18.021','It\'s cause for celebration.',-1),(87996,5,115640,115720,'01:20:18.355','01:20:21.691','Oh, well, I promised Sheila that\nI\'d go to this AA meeting now.',-1),(87997,5,115725,115780,'01:20:21.901','01:20:24.194','She\'s my sponsor,\nthe one that\'s been helping me.',-1),(87998,5,115782,115816,'01:20:24.278','01:20:25.695','Can we celebrate tomorrow night?',-1),(87999,5,115828,115853,'01:20:26.197','01:20:27.238','Yeah.',-1),(88000,5,115872,115896,'01:20:28.032','01:20:29.032','Yeah, sure, come on.',-1),(88001,5,116004,116041,'01:20:33.537','01:20:35.079','You know, you could come with me.',-1),(88002,5,116048,116082,'01:20:35.372','01:20:36.789','To the meeting.',-1),(88003,5,116085,116153,'01:20:36.916','01:20:39.709','It\'s an open meeting,\nmeaning that anyone can come.',-1),(88004,5,116165,116201,'01:20:40.211','01:20:41.711','Even you.',-1),(88005,5,116237,116296,'01:20:43.214','01:20:45.673','So the cops got a flashlight\non me behind the dumpster.',-1),(88006,5,116298,116335,'01:20:45.758','01:20:47.300','I\'m wearing nothing\nbut my girlfriend\'s panties,',-1),(88007,5,116338,116401,'01:20:47.426','01:20:50.053','I got vomit all down\nthe front of my chest.',-1),(88008,5,116406,116487,'01:20:50.262','01:20:53.640','And I say to them,\n\"I might have had two beers.\"',-1),(88009,5,116665,116733,'01:21:01.065','01:21:03.900','So that\'s how\nI got the nickname \"Two Beer Barry.\"',-1),(88010,5,116793,116856,'01:21:06.403','01:21:09.030','I\'m getting the stink eye\nfrom Ed over here.',-1),(88011,5,116858,116905,'01:21:09.114','01:21:11.074','Have I gone off format?',-1),(88012,5,116929,116981,'01:21:12.076','01:21:14.244','My name is Barry and I am an alcoholic.',-1),(88013,5,116989,117014,'01:21:14.578','01:21:15.620','Hi, Barry.',-1),(88014,5,117021,117089,'01:21:15.913','01:21:18.748','Are there any other alcoholics present?',-1),(88015,5,117222,117254,'01:21:24.255','01:21:25.588','I always love a meeting where we',-1),(88016,5,117256,117291,'01:21:25.673','01:21:27.131','all have to identify at the top,',-1),(88017,5,117294,117383,'01:21:27.258','01:21:30.969','because it forces me\nto be honest about who I really am.',-1),(88018,5,117418,117479,'01:21:32.429','01:21:34.973','And I never told the truth\nout there, obviously.',-1),(88019,5,117482,117530,'01:21:35.099','01:21:37.100','I lied about everything.',-1),(88020,5,117567,117616,'01:21:38.644','01:21:40.687','I was taught in these rooms\nthat I would never get sober',-1),(88021,5,117619,117687,'01:21:40.813','01:21:43.648','if I kept lying,\nbut that\'s what I was best at.',-1),(88022,5,117743,117793,'01:21:45.985','01:21:48.069','If I knew anything\nin this world it was how to lie,',-1),(88023,5,117795,117842,'01:21:48.153','01:21:50.113','especially about my drinking.',-1),(88024,5,117850,117955,'01:21:50.447','01:21:54.826','But, whatever. I would lie\nabout the name of my dog,',-1),(88025,5,117958,118046,'01:21:54.952','01:21:58.621','I\'d lie about the color of my own hair\nright to your face.',-1),(88026,5,118079,118122,'01:21:59.999','01:22:01.791','And my whole life just became',-1),(88027,5,118141,118204,'01:22:02.543','01:22:05.169','a series of lies strung together by me,',-1),(88028,5,118207,118246,'01:22:05.296','01:22:06.921','- one after the other.\n- I\'m going to go, okay?',-1),(88029,5,118248,118282,'01:22:07.006','01:22:08.423','- Sure.\n- You got a ride home?',-1),(88030,5,118284,118352,'01:22:08.507','01:22:11.342','Yeah. Sheila, she can give\nme a ride. This is Sheila.',-1),(88031,5,118363,118399,'01:22:11.802','01:22:13.303','- How you doing?\n- I\'m Sheila.',-1),(88032,5,118419,118471,'01:22:14.138','01:22:16.306','That my lies would kill me.',-1),(88033,5,118487,118517,'01:22:16.974','01:22:18.224','Left to their own devices,',-1),(88034,5,118520,118595,'01:22:18.350','01:22:21.477','my lies would walk me out that door.',-1),(88035,5,118747,118827,'01:22:27.818','01:22:31.154','Is it safe to say that Captain Whitaker\nremains a bit of a mystery?',-1),(88036,5,118832,118880,'01:22:31.363','01:22:33.364','Those are your words, sir, not mine.',-1),(88037,5,118887,118915,'01:22:33.657','01:22:34.824','I\'ve been speaking to some people',-1),(88038,5,118917,118967,'01:22:34.908','01:22:36.993','who are very close\nto the NTSB investigation.',-1),(88039,5,118972,119032,'01:22:37.202','01:22:39.704','They are confident they will\nsoon be able to determine',-1),(88040,5,119035,119088,'01:22:39.830','01:22:42.040','exactly what brought this plane down.',-1),(88041,5,119095,119128,'01:22:42.333','01:22:43.708','I\'m sure they will, sir.',-1),(88042,5,119153,119213,'01:22:44.710','01:22:47.211','Well, Ken and Vicky Evans,\nthank you both very much.',-1),(88043,5,119220,119268,'01:22:47.504','01:22:49.505','Thank you, sir. And God bless you.',-1),(88044,5,119588,119628,'01:23:02.853','01:23:04.520','How you feeling, Ken?',-1),(88045,5,119688,119720,'01:23:07.024','01:23:08.358','Happy to be alive.',-1),(88046,5,119725,119777,'01:23:08.567','01:23:10.735','Blessed to be alive.',-1),(88047,5,119836,119897,'01:23:13.197','01:23:15.740','I\'m Captain Whitaker. I was flying with...',-1),(88048,5,119900,119932,'01:23:15.866','01:23:17.200','I know who you are.',-1),(88049,5,119969,120032,'01:23:18.744','01:23:21.371','Excuse me. Could you give us\nsome privacy, please?',-1),(88050,5,120049,120078,'01:23:22.081','01:23:23.289','Thank you.',-1),(88051,5,120365