rvice on the plane.',-1),(88647,5,174853,174912,'02:01:25.570','02:01:28.030','Are you aware that\nour investigators found',-1),(88648,5,174914,175000,'02:01:28.114','02:01:31.700','two single service vodka bottles\nin the galley trash bin?',-1),(88649,5,175057,175089,'02:01:34.079','02:01:35.412','Yes, I\'m aware of that.',-1),(88650,5,175121,175177,'02:01:36.748','02:01:39.083','There were five crew members on board',-1),(88651,5,175180,175242,'02:01:39.167','02:01:41.752','that would have had access\nto the beverage trolley.',-1),(88652,5,175250,175296,'02:01:42.087','02:01:44.004','Less than an hour after the accident,',-1),(88653,5,175298,175345,'02:01:44.089','02:01:46.048','blood was taken from each\nof these crew members,',-1),(88654,5,175347,175417,'02:01:46.132','02:01:49.051','yourself, First Officer Evans,',-1),(88655,5,175435,175491,'02:01:49.803','02:01:52.137','Flight Attendant Margaret Thomason,',-1),(88656,5,175506,175574,'02:01:52.764','02:01:55.599','and posthumously from Camelia Satou',-1),(88657,5,175590,175642,'02:01:56.267','02:01:58.435','and Katerina Marquez.',-1),(88658,5,175662,175742,'02:01:59.270','02:02:02.606','Toxicology analysis was performed and',-1),(88659,5,175754,175814,'02:02:03.108','02:02:05.609','three of these tests came back negative,',-1),(88660,5,175816,175886,'02:02:05.694','02:02:08.612','one was disqualified\nfor technical reasons,',-1),(88661,5,175888,175952,'02:02:08.697','02:02:11.365','and one tested positive for alcohol.',-1),(88662,5,175954,176026,'02:02:11.449','02:02:14.451','It registered a .17 blood alcohol level.',-1),(88663,5,176034,176074,'02:02:14.786','02:02:16.453','Are you aware of that?',-1),(88664,5,176090,176142,'02:02:17.122','02:02:19.289','Yeah, I\'m aware of it now.',-1),(88665,5,176305,176369,'02:02:26.047','02:02:28.716','Miss Marquez was not only a colleague,',-1),(88666,5,176371,176440,'02:02:28.800','02:02:31.677','but you knew her outside of work,\nis that correct?',-1),(88667,5,176473,176