','But I\'m here.',-1),(88734,5,183279,183377,'02:07:16.629','02:07:20.716','And I\'ll be here\nfor at least the next four or five years.',-1),(88735,5,183379,183411,'02:07:20.800','02:07:22.134','And that\'s fair.',-1),(88736,5,183499,183563,'02:07:25.805','02:07:28.473','I betrayed the public trust. I did.',-1),(88737,5,183565,183605,'02:07:28.558','02:07:30.225','That\'s how the judge explained it to me.',-1),(88738,5,183607,183667,'02:07:30.310','02:07:32.811','I had betrayed the public trust.',-1),(88739,5,183715,183785,'02:07:34.814','02:07:37.733','The FAA, they took away\nmy pilot\'s license.',-1),(88740,5,183832,183869,'02:07:39.694','02:07:41.236','And that\'s fair.',-1),(88741,5,183889,183977,'02:07:42.071','02:07:45.741','My chances\nof ever flying again are slim to none.',-1),(88742,5,184023,184063,'02:07:47.660','02:07:49.328','And I accept that.',-1),(88743,5,184136,184204,'02:07:52.373','02:07:55.208','I\'ve had a lot of time\nto think about it, all of it.',-1),(88744,5,184249,184305,'02:07:57.045','02:07:59.379','I\'ve been doing some writing.',-1),(88745,5,184349,184453,'02:08:01.215','02:08:05.552','I wrote letters to each of the families\nthat had lost loved ones.',-1),(88746,5,184521,184581,'02:08:08.389','02:08:10.891','Some of them were able\nto hear my apology.',-1),(88747,5,184621,184661,'02:08:12.560','02:08:14.227','Some of them never will.',-1),(88748,5,184701,184761,'02:08:15.897','02:08:18.398','I also apologized to',-1),(88749,5,184793,184905,'02:08:19.734','02:08:24.404','all the people\nthat tried to help me along the way, but I',-1),(88750,5,184936,184988,'02:08:25.698','02:08:27.866','couldn\'t or wouldn\'t listen.',-1),(88751,5,185081,185137,'02:08:31.746','02:08:34.081','People like my wife, you know.',-1),(88752,5,185218,185266,'02:08:37.418','02:08:39.419','My ex-wife and',-1),(88753,5,185362,185394,'02:08:43.424','02:08:44.758','my son.',-1),(88754,5,185478,185554,'02:08:48.262','02:08:51.431','And again, like I said,\nyou kno