feelings about a rock,',-1),(89354,42,64959,65083,'00:45:06.662','00:45:11.792','or a trail, or the road,\nso he\'d tell us to get down, shut up...',-1),(89355,42,65084,65132,'00:45:11.834','00:45:13.836','Get down! Shut up!',-1),(89356,42,65155,65190,'00:45:14.795','00:45:16.255','So we did.',-1),(89357,42,65611,65663,'00:45:33.814','00:45:35.983','Now, I don\'t know much about anything,',-1),(89358,42,65665,65757,'00:45:36.067','00:45:39.904','but I think some of America\'s\nbest young men served in this war.',-1),(89359,42,65759,65824,'00:45:39.987','00:45:42.698','There was Dallas, from Phoenix,',-1),(89360,42,65865,65932,'00:45:44.408','00:45:47.203','Cleveland, he was from Detroit.',-1),(89361,42,65935,65992,'00:45:47.328','00:45:49.705','Hey, Tex. Hey, Tex.',-1),(89362,42,65995,66047,'00:45:49.830','00:45:51.999','Man, what the hell\'s going on?',-1),(89363,42,66049,66154,'00:45:52.083','00:45:56.420','And Tex was... Well, I don\'t remember\nwhere Tex come from.',-1),(89364,42,66156,66193,'00:45:56.504','00:45:58.047','Nothing.',-1),(89365,42,66292,66352,'00:46:02.176','00:46:04.679','Fourth Platoon, on your feet.',-1),(89366,42,66354,66444,'00:46:04.762','00:46:08.516','Still got 10 klicks to go to that river.\nMove out.',-1),(89367,42,66445,66488,'00:46:08.557','00:46:10.351','Come on, move out.',-1),(89368,42,66537,66596,'00:46:12.395','00:46:14.855','Step it up. Look alive out there.',-1),(89369,42,66597,66701,'00:46:14.897','00:46:19.235','The good thing about Vietnam\nis there was always some place to go.',-1),(89370,42,66704,66737,'00:46:19.360','00:46:20.736','Fire in the hole!',-1),(89371,42,66820,66876,'00:46:24.198','00:46:26.534','Gump, check out that hole.',-1),(89372,42,66878,66950,'00:46:26.617','00:46:29.620','And there was always something to do.',-1),(89373,42,66952,67028,'00:46:29.704','00:46:32.873','- Mount them up.\n- Spread out! Cover his back.',-1),(89374,42,67150,67285,'00:46:37.920','00:46:43.551','One day, it started raining,\nand it didn\'t quit for four months.',-1),(89375,42,67309,67378,'00:46:44.552','00:46:47.430','We\'d been through\nevery kind of rain there is:',-1),(89376,42,67381,67442,'00:46:47.555','00:46:50.099','little bitty stinging rain,',-1),(89377,42,67459,67523,'00:46:50.808','00:46:53.477','and big old fat rain,',-1),(89378,42,67534,67599,'00:46:53.936','00:46:56.647','rain that flew in sideways.',-1),(89379,42,67601,67698,'00:46:56.731','00:47:00.776','And sometimes, rain even seemed\nto come straight up from underneath.',-1),(89380,42,67741,67798,'00:47:02.570','00:47:04.947','Shoot, it even rained at night.',-1),(89381,42,67823,67882,'00:47:05.990','00:47:08.451','- Hey, Forrest.\n- Hey, Bubba.',-1),(89382,42,67885,67965,'00:47:08.576','00:47:11.912','I\'m gonna lean up against you.\nYou just lean right back against me.',-1),(89383,42,67966,68058,'00:47:11.954','00:47:15.791','This way, we don\'t have to sleep\nwith our heads in the mud.',-1),(89384,42,68082,68166,'00:47:16.751','00:47:20.254','You know why we a good partnership,\nForrest?',-1),(89385,42,68167,68227,'00:47:20.296','00:47:22.798','\'Cause we be watching out\nfor one another,',-1),(89386,42,68230,68275,'00:47:22.923','00:47:24.800','like brothers and stuff.',-1),(89387,42,68322,68410,'00:47:26.761','00:47:30.431','Hey, Forrest, there\'s something\nI\'ve been thinking about.',-1),(89388,42,68412,68484,'00:47:30.514','00:47:33.517','I got a very important question\nto ask you.',-1),(89389,42,68523,68618,'00:47:35.144','00:47:39.106','How would you like to go\ninto the shrimping business with me?',-1),(89390,42,68646,68686,'00:47:40.274','00:47:41.942','Okay.',-1),(89391,42,68687,68770,'00:47:41.984','00:47:45.446','Man, I tell you what,\nI got it all figured out, too.',-1),(89392,42,68772,68839,'00:47:45.529','00:47:48.324','So many pounds of shrimp\nto pay off the boat,',-1),(89393,42,68842,68922,'00:47:48.449','00:47:51.786','so many pounds for gas,\nwe can just live right on the boat.',-1),(89394,42,68923,68978,'00:47:51.827','00:47:54.121','We ain\'t got to pay no rent.',-1),(89395,42,68980,69030,'00:47:54.205','00:47:56.290','I\'ll be the captain,\nwe can just work it together,',-1),(89396,42,69032,69135,'00:47:56.374','00:48:00.628','split everything right down the middle.\nMan, I\'m telling you, 50-50.',-1),(89397,42,69137,69223,'00:48:00.711','00:48:04.298','And, hey, Forrest,\nall the shrimp you can eat.',-1),(89398,42,69260,69303,'00:48:05.841','00:48:07.635','That\'s a fine idea.',-1),(89399,42,69329,69380,'00:48:08.719','00:48:10.846','Bubba did have a fine idea.',-1),(89400,42,69471,69545,'00:48:14.642','00:48:17.728','I even wrote Jenny\nand told her all about it.',-1),(89401,42,69564,69641,'00:48:18.521','00:48:21.732','I sent her letters,\nnot every day, but almost.',-1),(89402,42,69643,69763,'00:48:21.816','00:48:26.821','I told her what I was doing\nand asked her what she was doing,',-1),(89403,42,69765,69831,'00:48:26.904','00:48:29.657','and told her\nhow I thought about her always,',-1),(89404,42,69863,69935,'00:48:30.991','00:48:33.994','and how I was looking forward\nto getting a letter from her',-1),(89405,42,69936,69996,'00:48:34.036','00:48:36.539','just as soon as she had the time.',-1),(89406,42,70041,70102,'00:48:38.416','00:48:40.918','I\'d always let her know that I was okay.',-1),(89407,42,70133,70257,'00:48:42.211','00:48:47.383','Then, I\'d sign each letter,\n\"Love, Forrest Gump.\"',-1),(89408,42,70613,70704,'00:49:02.231','00:49:06.026','This one day, we was out walking,\nlike always,',-1),(89409,42,70705,70776,'00:49:06.068','00:49:09.029','and then, just like that,',-1),(89410,42,70798,70880,'00:49:09.947','00:49:13.367','somebody turned off the rain\nand the sun come out.',-1),(89411,42,70952,70996,'00:49:16.370','00:49:18.205','Ambush!',-1),(89412,42,71008,71041,'00:49:18.706','00:49:20.082','Take cover!',-1),(89413,42,71129,71157,'00:49:23.711','00:49:24.879','Get down!',-1),(89414,42,71159,71194,'00:49:24.962','00:49:26.422','Get the sixty!',-1),(89415,42,71270,71321,'00:49:29.592','00:49:31.719','Get that pig up here, God damn it!',-1),(89416,42,71322,71373,'00:49:31.760','00:49:33.888','Forrest, you okay?',-1),(89417,42,71450,71513,'00:49:37.099','00:49:39.727','Strongarm! Strongarm!\nBe advised, Strongarm!',-1),(89418,42,71526,71585,'00:49:40.269','00:49:42.730','Medic, we got a man down!',-1),(89419,42,71586,71657,'00:49:42.771','00:49:45.733','Strongarm, this is Leg Lima 6, over!',-1),(89420,42,71674,71754,'00:49:46.442','00:49:49.778','Roger, Strongarm, be advised\nwe have incoming from the tree line',-1),(89421,42,71757,71841,'00:49:49.904','00:49:53.407','at points blue plus two.\nAKs and rockets...',-1),(89422,42,71857,71900,'00:49:54.074','00:49:55.868','Misfire! Misfire!',-1),(89423,42,71957,72005,'00:49:58.245','00:50:00.247','God damn it! Mac!',-1),(89424,42,72028,72111,'00:50:01.207','00:50:04.627','Get that thing...\nFuck it, get it in the tree line!',-1),(89425,42,72134,72162,'00:50:05.586','00:50:06.754','Jesus!',-1),(89426,42,72165,72218,'00:50:06.879','00:50:09.089','My unit is down hard and hurting!',-1),(89427,42,72221,72306,'00:50:09.215','00:50:12.760','Six are pulling back to Blue Line,\nLeg Lima 6 out.',-1),(89428,42,72325,72373,'00:50:13.552','00:50:15.554','Pull back! Pull back!',-1),(89429,42,72374,72425,'00:50:15.596','00:50:17.723','Run! Run, Forrest!',-1),(89430,42,72427,72483,'00:50:17.806','00:50:20.142','- Pull back!\n- Forrest, Forrest!',-1),(89431,42,72486,72549,'00:50:20.267','00:50:22.895','Run, man! Run!',-1),(89432,42,72550,72593,'00:50:22.937','00:50:24.730','Pull back! Run!',-1),(89433,42,72637,72690,'00:50:26.565','00:50:28.776','Run, God damn it, run!',-1),(89434,42,73199,73310,'00:50:49.964','00:50:54.593','Medic! Can I get a medic?',-1),(89435,42,73319,73399,'00:50:54.969','00:50:58.305','I ran and ran, just like Jenny told me to.',-1),(89436,42,73480,73582,'00:51:01.684','00:51:05.938','I ran so far and so fast\nthat pretty soon I was all by myself,',-1),(89437,42,73583,73630,'00:51:05.980','00:51:07.940','which was a bad thing.',-1),(89438,42,73643,73680,'00:51:08.482','00:51:10.025','Bubba!',-1),(89439,42,73731,73822,'00:51:12.152','00:51:15.948','Bubba was my best good friend.\nI had to make sure that he was okay.',-1),(89440,42,73911,73960,'00:51:19.660','00:51:21.704','Any friendlies out there?',-1),(89441,42,73983,74035,'00:51:22.663','00:51:24.832','Yeah, I\'ve got three over here.',-1),(89442,42,74050,74099,'00:51:25.457','00:51:27.459','Where the hell are you?',-1),(89443,42,74113,74145,'00:51:28.043','00:51:29.378','Bubba?',-1),(89444,42,74171,74236,'00:51:30.462','00:51:33.173','And on my way back to find Bubba,',-1),(89445,42,74239,74307,'00:51:33.299','00:51:36.135','well, there was this boy\nlaying on the ground.',-1),(89446,42,74308,74337,'00:51:36.176','00:51:37.386','Tex!',-1),(89447,42,74387,74412,'00:51:39.471','00:51:40.514','Okay.',-1),(89448,42,74413,74508,'00:51:40.556','00:51:44.518','I couldn\'t just let him lay there\nall alone, scared the way he was,',-1),(89449,42,74511,74604,'00:51:44.643','00:51:48.522','so I grabbed him up\nand run him out of there.',-1),(89450,42,74967,75025,'00:52:03.662','00:52:06.081','And every time I went back\nlooking for Bubba,',-1),(89451,42,75028,75113,'00:52:06.206','00:52:09.710','somebody else was saying,\n\"Help me, Forrest. Help me.\"',-1),(89452,42,75297,75342,'00:52:17.384','00:52:19.261','Can\'t hear... Can\'t hear...',-1),(89453,42,75397,75429,'00:52:21.555','00:52:22.890','No sweat, man. Just lay back.',-1),(89454,42,75430,75490,'00:52:22.931','00:52:25.434','You\'ll be okay. You\'ll be okay.',-1),(89455,42,75538,75612,'00:52:27.436','00:52:30.522','I started to get scared\nthat I might never find Bubba.',-1),(89456,42,75613,75644,'00:52:30.564','00:52:31.857','Over.',-1),(89457,42,75645,75725,'00:52:31.899','00:52:35.235','Roger, Strongarm,\nI know my position is danger close.',-1),(89458,42,75726,75770,'00:52:35.277','00:52:37.112','We got Charlie all over this area.',-1),(89459,42,75773,75829,'00:52:37.237','00:52:39.573','I gotta have those fast movers\nin here now. Over.',-1),(89460,42,75830,75912,'00:52:39.615','00:52:43.035','- Six, Strongarm, we want...\n- Lieutenant Dan, Coleman\'s dead!',-1),(89461,42,75913,75942,'00:52:43.077','00:52:44.286','I know he\'s dead!',-1),(89462,42,75945,76013,'00:52:44.411','00:52:47.247','My whole goddamn platoon\nis wiped out!',-1),(89463,42,76016,76050,'00:52:47.373','00:52:48.767','- Leg Lima 6, Leg Lima 6.\n- God damn it!',-1),(89464,42,76050,76117,'00:52:48.791','00:52:51.543','- Copy this transmission. Over.\n- What are you doing?',-1),(89465,42,76118,76198,'00:52:51.585','00:52:54.922','Just leave me here! Get away.\nJust leave me here! Get out!',-1),(89466,42,76201,76257,'00:52:55.047','00:52:57.383','Leg Lima 6, Strongarm.\nHow copy this? Over.',-1),(89467,42,76258,76322,'00:52:57.424','00:53:00.094','God, I said leave me here, God damn it!',-1),(89468,42,76323,76399,'00:53:00.135','00:53:03.305','Leg Lima 6, Leg Lima 6,\nthis is Strongarm, be advised',-1),(89469,42,76402,76450,'00:53:03.430','00:53:05.432','your fast movers\nare inbound at this time, over.',-1),(89470,42,76451,76533,'00:53:05.474','00:53:08.894','Then, it felt like something\njust jumped up and bit me.',-1),(89471,42,76554,76594,'00:53:09.770','00:53:11.438','Something bit me!',-1),(89472,42,76759,76810,'00:53:18.320','00:53:20.447','You chink son of a bitch!',-1),(89473,42,76870,76918,'00:53:22.950','00:53:24.952','I can\'t leave the platoon.',-1),(89474,42,76921,77039,'00:53:25.077','00:53:29.998','I told you to leave me there, Gump.\nForget about me. Get yourself out!',-1),(89475,42,77042,77094,'00:53:30.124','00:53:32.251','Did you hear what I said?',-1),(89476,42,77111,77158,'00:53:32.960','00:53:34.920','God damn it, put me down!',-1),(89477,42,77175,77224,'00:53:35.629','00:53:37.673','Get your ass out of here!',-1),(89478,42,77303,77366,'00:53:40.968','00:53:43.595','I didn