na go home.',-1),(89501,42,80886,80935,'00:56:10.284','00:56:12.327','Bubba was my best good friend.',-1),(89502,42,80958,81067,'00:56:13.287','00:56:17.833','And even I know that ain\'t something\nyou can find just around the corner.',-1),(89503,42,81070,81146,'00:56:17.958','00:56:21.086','Bubba was gonna be\na shrimping boat captain,',-1),(89504,42,81147,81242,'00:56:21.128','00:56:25.090','but instead he died right there\nby that river in Vietnam.',-1),(89505,42,81379,81434,'00:56:30.804','00:56:33.098','That\'s all I have to say about that.',-1),(89506,42,81491,81543,'00:56:35.475','00:56:37.644','It was a bullet, wasn\'t it?',-1),(89507,42,81599,81663,'00:56:39.980','00:56:42.649','- A bullet?\n- That jumped up and bit you.',-1),(89508,42,81720,81771,'00:56:45.027','00:56:47.154','Oh, yes, sir.',-1),(89509,42,81772,81847,'00:56:47.195','00:56:50.324','Bit me directly in the buttocks.',-1),(89510,42,81850,81976,'00:56:50.449','00:56:55.704','They said it was a million-dollar wound,\nbut the Army must keep that money,',-1),(89511,42,81979,82071,'00:56:55.829','00:56:59.666','\'cause I still ain\'t seen a nickel\nof that million dollars.',-1),(89512,42,82092,82176,'00:57:00.500','00:57:04.004','The only good thing\nabout being wounded in the buttocks',-1),(89513,42,82179,82220,'00:57:04.129','00:57:05.839','is the ice cream.',-1),(89514,42,82223,82285,'00:57:05.964','00:57:08.550','They gave me all the ice cream\nI could eat.',-1),(89515,42,82288,82320,'00:57:08.675','00:57:10.010','And guess what?',-1),(89516,42,82321,82396,'00:57:10.052','00:57:13.180','A good friend of mine\nwas in the bed right next door.',-1),(89517,42,82449,82523,'00:57:15.390','00:57:18.477','Lieutenant Dan,\nI got you some ice cream.',-1),(89518,42,82580,82632,'00:57:20.854','00:57:23.023','Lieutenant Dan, ice cream.',-1),(89519,42,82913,82968,'00:57:34.743','00:57:37.037','It\'s time for your bath, Lieutenant.',-1),(89520,42,83173,83205,'00:57:45.545','00:57:46.880','Harper!',-1),(89521,