on?\n- Mr. Hot Wheels.',-1),(89811,42,114989,115076,'01:19:51.245','01:19:54.873','- Who\'s your friend?\n- My name is Forrest, Forrest Gump.',-1),(89812,42,115096,115198,'01:19:55.708','01:19:59.920','This is Cunning Carla\nand Long-Limbs Lenore.',-1),(89813,42,115224,115301,'01:20:01.005','01:20:04.216','So, where you been, baby cakes, huh?\nHaven\'t seen you around lately.',-1),(89814,42,115303,115339,'01:20:04.300','01:20:05.819','You know, you should have\nbeen here for Christmas,',-1),(89815,42,115340,115373,'01:20:05.843','01:20:07.237','\'cause Tommy bought a round\non the house',-1),(89816,42,115374,115410,'01:20:07.261','01:20:08.762','and gave everybody a turkey sandwich.',-1),(89817,42,115412,115485,'01:20:08.846','01:20:11.890','Well, well, I had company.',-1),(89818,42,115506,115594,'01:20:12.766','01:20:16.437','Hey, hey! We was just there.\nThat\'s at Times Square.',-1),(89819,42,115609,115708,'01:20:17.062','01:20:21.191','Don\'t you just love New Year\'s?\nYou get to start all over.',-1),(89820,42,115710,115789,'01:20:21.275','01:20:24.570','- Hey, Lenore...\n- Everybody gets a second chance.',-1),(89821,42,115791,115852,'01:20:24.653','01:20:27.197','It\'s funny,\nbut in the middle of all that fun,',-1),(89822,42,115854,115909,'01:20:27.281','01:20:29.575','I began to think about Jenny,',-1),(89823,42,115931,116038,'01:20:30.492','01:20:34.955','wondering how she was spending\nher New Year\'s night out in California.',-1),(89824,42,116581,116665,'01:20:57.561','01:21:01.065','Eight, seven, six, five,',-1),(89825,42,116668,116751,'01:21:01.190','01:21:04.651','four, three, two, one!',-1),(89826,42,116754,116818,'01:21:04.777','01:21:07.446','Happy New Year!',-1),(89827,42,117214,117279,'01:21:23.921','01:21:26.632','Happy New Year, Lieutenant Dan!',-1),(89828,42,118126,118214,'01:22:01.917','01:22:05.587','What are you, stupid or something?\nWhat\'s your problem?',-1),(89829,42,118230,118264,'01:22:06.255','01:22:07.673','What\'s his problem?',-1),