5:43.134','We can discuss\nmy honorarium',-1),(94849,48,22636,22692,'00:15:43.204','00:15:45.536','over dinner and\nchampagne tonight.',-1),(94850,48,22694,22722,'00:15:45.606','00:15:46.766','Your treat.',-1),(94851,48,22724,22755,'00:15:46.841','00:15:48.138','Yes.',-1),(94852,48,22757,22808,'00:15:48.242','00:15:50.369','My treat.',-1),(94853,48,22885,22937,'00:15:53.548','00:15:55.709','Dr.Jones!\nDr.Jones!',-1),(94854,48,23022,23067,'00:15:59.253','00:16:01.153','Shush! Shush! Shush!',-1),(94855,48,23070,23111,'00:16:01.255','00:16:02.984','Dr.Jones, I am so glad\nyou\'re back.',-1),(94856,48,23113,23144,'00:16:03.057','00:16:04.354','Your mail is on your desk.',-1),(94857,48,23146,23179,'00:16:04.425','00:16:05.824','Here are your\nphone messages.',-1),(94858,48,23181,23218,'00:16:05.893','00:16:07.417','Dr.Jones, you promised...',-1),(94859,48,23219,23252,'00:16:07.495','00:16:08.860','This is your\nappointment schedule,',-1),(94860,48,23254,23302,'00:16:08.930','00:16:10.955','and these term papers still\nhaven\'t been graded.',-1),(94861,48,23304,23348,'00:16:11.032','00:16:12.863','Okay. Irene,\nput everybody\'s name on a list,',-1),(94862,48,23350,23378,'00:16:12.934','00:16:14.094','get the order they arrived...',-1),(94863,48,23380,23407,'00:16:14.202','00:16:15.328','Oh, come on, Dr.Jones.',-1),(94864,48,23409,23435,'00:16:15.403','00:16:16.495','Dr.Jones.',-1),(94865,48,23437,23498,'00:16:16.571','00:16:19.096','...and I\'ll see each\nand every one of them...',-1),(94866,48,23500,23535,'00:16:19.173','00:16:20.640','in turn.',-1),(94867,48,23810,23870,'00:16:32.119','00:16:34.587','\"Venice, Italy.\"',-1),(94868,48,24556,24601,'00:17:03.184','00:17:05.049','Dr.Jones!',-1),(94869,48,24729,24776,'00:17:10.391','00:17:12.359','Dr.Jones?',-1),(94870,48,25156,25232,'00:17:28.175','00:17:31.372','I trust your trip down\nwas comfortable, Dr.Jones.',-1),(94871,48,25234,25305,'00:17:31.445','00:17:34.414','Uh, my men didn\'t alarm you,\nI hope.',-1),(94872,48,25307,25353,'00:17:34.482','00:17:36.416','My name is Donovan.',-1),(94873,48,25355,25381,'00:17:36.484','00:17:37.576','Walter Donovan.',-1),(94874,48,25383,25413,'00:17:37.652','00:17:38.880','I know who you are,\nMr.Donovan.',-1),(94875,48,25414,25446,'00:17:38.953','00:17:40.250','Your contributions\nto the museum',-1),(94876,48,25447,25490,'00:17:40.321','00:17:42.118','over the years have\nbeen extremely generous.',-1),(94877,48,25494,25520,'00:17:42.256','00:17:43.348','Some of the pieces',-1),(94878,48,25522,25566,'00:17:43.424','00:17:45.255','in your collection here\nare very impressive.',-1),(94879,48,25567,25609,'00:17:45.326','00:17:47.055','Well, like yourself,\nDr.Jones,',-1),(94880,48,25611,25654,'00:17:47.128','00:17:48.925','I have a passion\nfor antiquities.',-1),(94881,48,25655,25703,'00:17:48.996','00:17:50.964','Have a look over here.',-1),(94882,48,25752,25811,'00:17:53.000','00:17:55.468','This might interest you.',-1),(94883,48,25860,25907,'00:17:57.505','00:17:59.473','Well, it\'s sandstone.',-1),(94884,48,25908,25947,'00:17:59.540','00:18:01.132','Christian symbol.',-1),(94885,48,25949,25993,'00:18:01.242','00:18:03.073','Early Latin text.',-1),(94886,48,25996,26055,'00:18:03.177','00:18:05.645','Mid-12th century,\nI should think.',-1),(94887,48,26057,26103,'00:18:05.713','00:18:07.647','That was our\nassessment, as well.',-1),(94888,48,26105,26137,'00:18:07.715','00:18:09.080','Where did this come from?',-1),(94889,48,26139,26170,'00:18:09.150','00:18:10.447','My engineers\nunearthed it',-1),(94890,48,26172,26221,'00:18:10.518','00:18:12.577','in the mountain region\nnorth of Ankara',-1),(94891,48,26223,26258,'00:18:12.653','00:18:14.086','while excavating\nfor copper.',-1),(94892,48,26261,26306,'00:18:14.221','00:18:16.121','Can you translate\nthe inscription?',-1),(94893,48,26387,26470,'00:18:19.493','00:18:22.929','\"...who drinks the water\nI shall give him, says the Lord,',-1),(94894,48,26471,26550,'00:18:22.997','00:18:26.262','\"will have a... spring',-1),(94895,48,26552,26635,'00:18:26.334','00:18:29.826','\"inside him welling up\nfor eternal life.',-1),(94896,48,26690,26745,'00:18:32.106','00:18:34.404','\"Let them bring me\nto your holy mountain',-1),(94897,48,26747,26789,'00:18:34.475','00:18:36.238','\"in the place where you dwell.',-1),(94898,48,26791,26817,'00:18:36.310','00:18:37.402','\"Across the desert',-1),(94899,48,26819,26868,'00:18:37.478','00:18:39.503','\"and through the mountain',-1),(94900,48,26869,26918,'00:18:39.580','00:18:41.605','\"to the Canyon\nof the Crescent Moon,',-1),(94901,48,26920,26994,'00:18:41.682','00:18:44.776','to the temple\nwhere the cup that...\"',-1),(94902,48,27076,27130,'00:18:48.189','00:18:50.453','\"Where the cup\nthat holds the blood',-1),(94903,48,27132,27225,'00:18:50.524','00:18:54.392','of Jesus Christ resides\nforever.\"',-1),(94904,48,27227,27315,'00:18:54.462','00:18:58.125','The Holy Grail, Dr.Jones.',-1),(94905,48,27316,27412,'00:18:58.199','00:19:02.192','The chalice used by Christ\nduring the Last Supper.',-1),(94906,48,27414,27492,'00:19:02.269','00:19:05.500','The cup that caught His blood\nat the Crucifixion',-1),(94907,48,27493,27582,'00:19:05.573','00:19:09.270','and was entrusted to\nJoseph of Arimathea.',-1),(94908,48,27584,27630,'00:19:09.343','00:19:11.277','The Arthur legend.',-1),(94909,48,27632,27697,'00:19:11.345','00:19:14.075','I\'ve heard this\nbedtime story before.',-1),(94910,48,27701,27731,'00:19:14.215','00:19:15.477','Eternal life, Dr.Jones!',-1),(94911,48,27733,27789,'00:19:15.549','00:19:17.881','The gift of youth to whoever\ndrinks from the Grail.',-1),(94912,48,27818,27878,'00:19:19.086','00:19:21.611','Now, that\'s a bedtime story\nI\'d like to wake up to.',-1),(94913,48,27880,27905,'00:19:21.689','00:19:22.713','An old man\'s dream.',-1),(94914,48,27906,27947,'00:19:22.790','00:19:24.485','Every man\'s dream,',-1),(94915,48,27949,27997,'00:19:24.558','00:19:26.583','including your\nfather\'s, I believe.',-1),(94916,48,28073,28119,'00:19:29.730','00:19:31.664','Grail lore is his hobby.',-1),(94917,48,28121,28169,'00:19:31.732','00:19:33.723','He\'s a teacher\nof medieval literature.',-1),(94918,48,28171,28223,'00:19:33.801','00:19:35.996','The one the students hope\nthey don\'t get.',-1),(94919,48,28225,28298,'00:19:36.070','00:19:39.096','Walter, you\'re neglecting\nyour guests.',-1),(94920,48,28300,28361,'00:19:39.173','00:19:41.733','Be along in a moment, dear.',-1),(94921,48,28483,28535,'00:19:46.814','00:19:48.975','Hard to resist, isn\'t it?',-1),(94922,48,28537,28617,'00:19:49.049','00:19:52.416','The Holy Grail\'s final resting\nplace described in detail.',-1),(94923,48,28619,28669,'00:19:52.486','00:19:54.579','What good is it?',-1),(94924,48,28671,28719,'00:19:54.655','00:19:56.646','This grail tablet\nspeaks of deserts',-1),(94925,48,28721,28760,'00:19:56.724','00:19:58.351','and mountains and canyons.',-1),(94926,48,28762,28788,'00:19:58.426','00:19:59.518','It\'s pretty vague.',-1),(94927,48,28790,28836,'00:19:59.593','00:20:01.527','Where do you want\nto start looking?',-1),(94928,48,28838,28904,'00:20:01.595','00:20:04.359','Maybe if the tablet were intact,\nyou\'d have something to go on,',-1),(94929,48,28906,28945,'00:20:04.432','00:20:06.059','but the entire top portion\nis missing.',-1),(94930,48,28947,28970,'00:20:06.133','00:20:07.122','Just the same, an attempt',-1),(94931,48,28973,29019,'00:20:07.234','00:20:09.134','to recover the Grail\nis currently underway.',-1),(94932,48,29080,29166,'00:20:11.672','00:20:15.267','Let me tell you another\nbedtime story, Dr.Jones.',-1),(94933,48,29168,29237,'00:20:15.342','00:20:18.243','After the Grail was entrusted\nto Joseph of Arimathea,',-1),(94934,48,29239,29300,'00:20:18.312','00:20:20.872','it disappeared, and was lost\nfor a thousand years',-1),(94935,48,29302,29334,'00:20:20.948','00:20:22.279','before it was found again',-1),(94936,48,29336,29384,'00:20:22.349','00:20:24.340','by three knights\nof the First Crusade.',-1),(94937,48,29386,29422,'00:20:24.418','00:20:25.942','Three brothers, to be exact.',-1),(94938,48,29424,29471,'00:20:26.020','00:20:27.988','I\'ve heard this one, as well.',-1),(94939,48,29473,29564,'00:20:28.055','00:20:31.855','Two of these brothers walked\nout of the desert 150 years',-1),(94940,48,29566,29611,'00:20:31.926','00:20:33.826','after having found the Grail',-1),(94941,48,29613,29683,'00:20:33.894','00:20:36.795','and began the long journey\nback to France,',-1),(94942,48,29684,29733,'00:20:36.864','00:20:38.889','but only one of them made it.',-1),(94943,48,29735,29794,'00:20:38.966','00:20:41.434','And before dying\nof extreme old age,',-1),(94944,48,29796,29847,'00:20:41.502','00:20:43.663','he supposedly imparted\nhis tale',-1),(94945,48,29849,29914,'00:20:43.737','00:20:46.433','to a... to a Franciscan friar,\nI think.',-1),(94946,48,29916,29991,'00:20:46.507','00:20:49.635','Not \"supposedly,\"\nDr.Jones.',-1),(94947,48,29993,30024,'00:20:49.710','00:20:51.041','This is the manuscript',-1),(94948,48,30026,30098,'00:20:51.111','00:20:54.103','in which the friar chronicled\nthe knight\'s story.',-1),(94949,48,30100,30136,'00:20:54.181','00:20:55.705','It doesn\'t reveal',-1),(94950,48,30138,30177,'00:20:55.783','00:20:57.375','the location of the Grail,\nI\'m afraid,',-1),(94951,48,30178,30204,'00:20:57.451','00:20:58.509','but the knight promised',-1),(94952,48,30206,30261,'00:20:58.586','00:21:00.884','that two markers, that had been\nleft behind, would.',-1),(94953,48,30262,30331,'00:21:00.955','00:21:03.822','This tablet is one\nof those markers.',-1),(94954,48,30333,30405,'00:21:03.891','00:21:06.883','It proves\nthe knight\'s story is true.',-1),(94955,48,30407,30456,'00:21:06.961','00:21:09.020','But as you pointed out,\nit\'s incomplete.',-1),(94956,48,30458,30500,'00:21:09.096','00:21:10.859','Now, the second marker\nis entombed',-1),(94957,48,30502,30542,'00:21:10.931','00:21:12.592','with the knight\'s dead brother.',-1),(94958,48,30543,30582,'00:21:12.666','00:21:14.258','Our project leader',-1),(94959,48,30584,30631,'00:21:14.335','00:21:16.326','believes that tomb to be located',-1),(94960,48,30633,30682,'00:21:16.403','00:21:18.428','within the city\nof Venice, Italy.',-1),(94961,48,30732,30791,'00:21:20.508','00:21:22.999','As you can now see,\nDr.Jones,',-1),(94962,48,30793,30867,'00:21:23.077','00:21:26.137','we\'re about\nto complete a great quest',-1),(94963,48,30870,30939,'00:21:26.280','00:21:29.147','that began almost\n2,000 years ago.',-1),(94964,48,30942,30976,'00:21:29.250','00:21:30.683','We\'re only one step away.',-1),(94965,48,30978,31035,'00:21:30.751','00:21:33.151','That\'s usually\nwhen the ground falls out',-1),(94966,48,31038,31077,'00:21:33.254','00:21:34.881','from underneath your feet.',-1),(94967,48,31078,31141,'00:21:34.955','00:21:37.583','You could be more right\nthan you know.',-1),(94968,48,31143,31174,'00:21:37.658','00:21:38.955','Yes?',-1),(94969,48,31176,31232,'00:21:39.026','00:21:41.358','We\'ve hit a snag.',-1),(94970,48,31234,31295,'00:21:41.428','00:21:43.988','Our project leader has vanished,',-1),(94971,48,31297,31347,'00:21:44.064','00:21:46.157','along with all his research.',-1),(94972,48,31350,31380,'00:21:46.267','00:21:47.529','Uh, we received a cable',-1),(94973,48,31382,31426,'00:21:47.601','00:21:49.432','from his colleague,\nDr.Schneider,',-1),(94974,48,31428,31472,'00:21:49.503','00:21:51.368','who has no idea\nof his whereabouts',-1),(94975,48,31474,31506,'00:21:51.438','00:21:52.769','or what\'s become of him.',-1),(94976,48,31508,31593,'00:21:52.840','00:21:56.401','I want you to pick up the trail\nwhere he left off.',-1),(94977,48,31595,31701,'00:21:56.477','00:22:00.880','Find the man,\nand you will find the Grail.',-1),(94978,48,31702,31761,'00:22:00.948','00:22:03.382','You\'ve got\nthe wrong Jones,',-1),(94979,48,31762,31794,'00:22:03.450','00:22:04.781','Mr.Donovan.',-1),(94980,48,31828,31874,'00:22:06.186','00:22:08.120','Why don\'t you try my father?',-1),(94981,48,31876,31922,'00:22:08.188','00:22:10.122','We already have.',-1),(94982,48,31924,31984,'00:22:10.190','00:22:12.681','Your father is the man\nwho has disappeared.',-1),(94983,48,32252,32311,'00:22:23.837','00:22:26.328','Your father and I have been\nfriends since time began.',-1),(94984,48,32313,32344,'00:22:26.407','00:22:27.669','I\'ve watched you grow up, Indy.',-1),(94985,48,32345,32383,'00:22:27.741','00:22:29.333','I\'ve watched\nthe two of you grow apart.',-1),(94986,48,32385,32437,'00:22:29.410','00:22:31.571','I\'ve never seen you this\nconcerned about him before.',-1),(94987,48,32439,32493,'00:22:31.645','00:22:33.909','Dad?',-1),(94988,48,32495,32523,'00:22:33.981','00:22:35.141','He\'s an academic;\na bookworm.',-1),(94989,48,32525,32552,'00:22:35.249','00:22:36.341','He\'s not a field man.',-1),(94990,48,32554,32600,'00:22:36.417','00:22:38.351','Dad? Dad?',-1),(94991,48,32602,32655,'00:22:38.419','00:22:40.649','Dear God.',-1),(94992,48,32708,32782,'00:22:42.856','00:22:45.950','What has the old fool\ngot himself into now?',-1),(94993,48,32784,32831,'00:22:46.026','00:22:47.960','I don\'t know,',-1),(94994,48,32832,32894,'00:22:48.028','00:22:50.622','but whatever it is,\nhe\'s in over his head.',-1),(94995,48,32896,32943,'00:22:50.698','00:22:52.632','Dad?',-1),(94996,48,32944,32985,'00:22:52.700','00:22:54.395','It\'s today\'s mail,',-1),(94997,48,32987,33039,'00:22:54.468','00:22:56.663','and it\'s been opened.',-1),(94998,48,33065,33112,'00:22:57.738','00:22:59.672','Mail.',-1),(94999,48,33113,33160,'00:22:59.740','00:23:01.708','That\'s it, Marcus.',-1),(95000,48,33209,33256,'00:23:03.711','00:23:05.702','Venice, Italy.',-1),(95001,48,33324,33375,'00:23:08.515','00:23:10.642','What is it?',-1),(95002,48,33436,33483,'00:23:13.187','00:23:15.155','It\'s Dad\'s Grail diary.',-1),(95003,48,33526,33565,'00:23:16.924','00:23:18.551','Every clue he followed.',-1),(95004,48,33567,33600,'00:23:18.626','00:23:20.025','Every discovery he made.',-1),(95005,48,33602,33675,'00:23:20.094','00:23:23.154','A complete record of his search\nfor the Holy Grail.',-1),(95006,48,33711,33762,'00:23:24.665','00:23:26.758','This is his whole life.',-1),(95007,48,33764,33816,'00:23:26.834','00:23:29.029','Why would he have\nsent this to me?',-1),(95008,48,33818,33861,'00:23:29.103','00:23:30.900','I don\'t know,',-1),(95009,48,33863,33953,'00:23:30.971','00:23:34.737','but someone must want it\npretty badly.',-1),(95010,48,34155,34218,'00:23:43.150','00:23:45.778','Do you believe, Marcus?',-1),(95011,48,34502,34593,'00:23:57.598','00:24:01.398','Do you believe\nthe Grail actually exists?',-1),(95012,48,34595,34650,'00:24:01.468','00:24:03.766','The search for the Cup of Christ',-1),(95013,48,34652,34724,'00:24:03.837','00:24:06.863','is the search for the divine\nin all of us.',-1),(95014,48,34726,34765,'00:24:06.940','00:24:08.567','But if you want facts, Indy,',-1),(95015,48,34767,34800,'00:24:08.642','00:24:10.041','I\'ve none to give you.',-1),(95016,48,34802,34840,'00:24:10.110','00:24:11.668','At my age, I\'m prepared',-1),(95017,48,34841,34892,'00:24:11.745','00:24:13.838','to take a few\nthings on faith.',-1),(95018,48,35032,35078,'00:24:19.687','00:24:21.621','Call Donovan, Marcus.',-1),(95019,48,35080,35129,'00:24:21.689','00:24:23.748','Tell him I\'ll take\nthat ticket to Venice now.',-1),(95020,48,35188,35242,'00:24:26.193','00:24:28.457','I\'ll tell him\nwe\'ll take two.',-1),(95021,48,35364,35424,'00:24:33.534','00:24:36.002','All right, tell me what\'s going\nto happen when we get to Venice.',-1),(95022,48,35425,35480,'00:24:36.070','00:24:38.334','Don\'t worry, Dr.Schneider\nwill be there to meet you.',-1),(95023,48,35481,35512,'00:24:38.405','00:24:39.667','- Uh, Schneider?\n- I maintain',-1),(95024,48,35513,35553,'00:24:39.740','00:24:41.401','an apartment in Venice.\nIt\'s at your disposal.',-1),(95025,48,35555,35581,'00:24:41.475','00:24:42.567','Oh, well, that\'s good.',-1),(95026,48,35583,35630,'00:24:42.643','00:24:44.611','Thank you.',-1),(95027,48,35655,35701,'00:24:45.646','00:24:47.580','Dr.Jones... good luck.',-1),(95028,48,35703,35745,'00:24:47.648','00:24:49.411','Now be very careful.',-1),(95029,48,35747,35797,'00:24:49.483','00:24:51.576','Don\'t trust anybody.',-1),(95030,48,36604,36630,'00:25:25.185','00:25:26.277','Signora?',-1),(95031,48,36632,36683,'00:25:26.353','00:25:28.480','Signorina?',-1),(95032,48,36828,36875,'00:25:34.528','00:25:36.462','Ah, Venice...',-1),(95033,48,36876,36906,'00:25:36.530','00:25:37.758','Yes.',-1),(95034,48,36907,36967,'00:25:37.831','00:25:40.299','Uh, how will we recognize\nthis Dr.Schneider',-1),(95035,48,36968,36996,'00:25:40.367','00:25:41.527','when we see him?',-1),(95036,48,36998,37044,'00:25:41.602','00:25:43.536','I don\'t know.',-1),(95037,48,37046,37077,'00:25:43.604','00:25:44.901','Maybe he\'ll know us.',-1),(95038,48,37079,37147,'00:25:44.972','00:25:47.805','Dr.Jones?',-1),(95039,48,37149,37175,'00:25:47.875','00:25:48.967','Yes?',-1),(95040,48,37177,37229,'00:25:49.042','00:25:51.237','I knew it was you.',-1),(95041,48,37231,37303,'00:25:51.311','00:25:54.303','You have your father\'s eyes.',-1),(95042,48,37341,37433,'00:25:55.916','00:25:59.716','And my mother\'s ears,\nbut the rest belongs to you.',-1),(95043,48,37434,37509,'00:25:59.787','00:26:02.915','Looks like the best parts have\nalready been spoken for.',-1),(95044,48,37511,37549,'00:26:02.990','00:26:04.548','Marcus Brody?',-1),(95045,48,37551,37590,'00:26:04.625','00:26:06.252','That\'s right.',-1),(95046,48,37591,37622,'00:26:06.326','00:26:07.623','Dr. Elsa Schneider.',-1),(95047,48,37624,37654,'00:26:07.694','00:26:08.922','Oh, how do you do?',-1),(95048,48,37655,37730,'00:26:08.996','00:26:12.090','The last time I saw your father,\nwe were in the library.',-1),(95049,48,37733,37754,'00:26:12.232','00:26:13.096','He was very close',-1),(95050,48,37757,37804,'00:26:13.233','00:26:15.201','to tracking down\nthe knight\'s tomb.',-1),(95051,48,37806,37849,'00:26:15.269','00:26:17.066','I\'ve never seen him so excited.',-1),(95052,48,37851,37894,'00:26:17.137','00:26:18.934','He was as giddy as a schoolboy.',-1),(95053,48,37896,37942,'00:26:19.006','00:26:20.940','Who? Attila\nthe Professor?',-1),(95054,48,37944,37978,'00:26:21.008','00:26:22.441','He was never giddy,',-1),(95055,48,37980,38032,'00:26:22.509','00:26:24.704','even when he was\na schoolboy.',-1),(95056,48,38034,38108,'00:26:24.778','00:26:27.838','Fraulein, will\nyou permit me?',-1),(95057,48,38109,38136,'00:26:27.915','00:26:29.007','I usually don\'t.',-1),(95058,48,38137,38169,'00:26:29.082','00:26:30.413','I usually\ndon\'t, either.',-1),(95059,48,38171,38198,'00:26:30.484','00:26:31.610','In that case,\nI permit you.',-1),(95060,48,38200,38227,'00:26:31.685','00:26:32.811','It would make\nme very happy.',-1),(95061,48,38229,38251,'00:26:32.886','00:26:33.818','But I\'m already sad.',-1),(95062,48,38253,38285,'00:26:33.887','00:26:35.218','By tomorrow,\nit will have faded.',-1),(95063,48,38286,38318,'00:26:35.289','00:26:36.620','Tomorrow I\'ll\nsteal you another.',-1),(95064,48,38320,38351,'00:26:36.690','00:26:37.987','I hate to interrupt you,',-1),(95065,48,38353,38382,'00:26:38.058','00:26:39.286','but the reason\nwe\'re here...',-1),(95066,48,38384,38419,'00:26:39.359','00:26:40.792','Yes. I have something\nto show you.',-1),(95067,48,38420,38464,'00:26:40.861','00:26:42.692','I left your father working\nin the library.',-1),(95068,48,38466,38496,'00:26:42.763','00:26:44.025','He sent me to the map section',-1),(95069,48,38498,38536,'00:26:44.097','00:26:45.689','to fetch an ancient plan\nof the city.',-1),(95070,48,38538,38591,'00:26:45.766','00:26:47.961','When I got back to his table,\nhe\'d gone, with all his papers,',-1),(95071,48,38592,38645,'00:26:48.035','00:26:50.230','except for that scrap,\nwhich I found near his chair.',-1),(95072,48,38647,38694,'00:26:50.304','00:26:52.272','Roman numerals.',-1),(95073,48,38696,38744,'00:26:52.372','00:26:54.363','Here is the library.',-1),(95074,48,38746,38806,'00:26:54.441','00:26:56.932','That doesn\'t look much\nlike a library.',-1),(95075,48,38808,38872,'00:26:57.010','00:26:59.706','Looks like a\nconverted church.',-1),(95076,48,38874,38921,'00:26:59.780','00:27:01.714','In this case,\nit\'s the literal truth.',-1),(95077,48,38922,38967,'00:27:01.782','00:27:03.647','We are on holy ground.',-1),(95078,48,38969,39004,'00:27:03.717','00:27:05.184','These columns over here',-1),(95079,48,39006,39057,'00:27:05.252','00:27:07.379','were brought back\nas spoils of war',-1),(95080,48,39058,39137,'00:27:07.454','00:27:10.719','after the sacking of Byzantium\nduring the Crusades.',-1),(95081,48,39138,39174,'00:27:10.791','00:27:12.258','Now, please excuse me.',-1),(95082,48,39175,39238,'00:27:12.326','00:27:14.954','The library\'s closing\nin a few moments.',-1),(95083,48,39240,39309,'00:27:15.028','00:27:17.895','I\'ll arrange for us\nto stay a little longer.',-1),(95084,48,39383,39464,'00:27:20.968','00:27:24.369','Marcus... I\'ve seen\nthis window before.',-1),(95085,48,39466,39500,'00:27:24.438','00:27:25.871','Where?',-1),(95086,48,39502,39563,'00:27:25.939','00:27:28.464','Right here,\nin Dad\'s diary.',-1),(95087,48,39750,39778,'00:27:36.283','00:27:37.443','You see?',-1),(95088,48,39780,39816,'00:27:37.517','00:27:39.041','Look, Indy.',-1),(95089,48,39818,39866,'00:27:39.119','00:27:41.110','The Roman numerals.',-1),(95090,48,39868,39924,'00:27:41.188','00:27:43.520','Dad was onto something here.',-1),(95091,48,39926,39971,'00:27:43.590','00:27:45.490','Well, now we know\nthe source of the numbers,',-1),(95092,48,39973,40014,'00:27:45.559','00:27:47.288','but we still don\'t know\nwhat they mean.',-1),(95093,48,40016,40068,'00:27:47.361','00:27:49.522','Dad sent me this\ndiary for a reason.',-1),(95094,48,40070,40096,'00:27:49.596','00:27:50.688','Until we find\nout why,',-1),(95095,48,40098,40131,'00:27:50.764','00:27:52.129','I suggest we keep\nit to ourselves.',-1),(95096,48,40133,40159,'00:27:52.232','00:27:53.324','Find something?',-1),(95097,48,40161,40198,'00:27:53.400','00:27:54.958','Uh, yes.\nThree, seven and ten.',-1),(95098,48,40200,40244,'00:27:55.035','00:27:56.866','That window seems\nto be the source',-1),(95099,48,40246,40275,'00:27:56.937','00:27:58.131','of the Roman numerals.',-1),(95100,48,40276,40310,'00:27:58.205','00:27:59.604','My God,\nI must be blind.',-1),(95101,48,40312,40380,'00:27:59.673','00:28:02.540','Dad wasn\'t looking for a book\nabout the knight\'s tomb,',-1),(95102,48,40382,40427,'00:28:02.609','00:28:04.474','he was looking\nfor the tomb itself.',-1),(95103,48,40429,40463,'00:28:04.544','00:28:05.977','Don\'t you get it?',-1),(95104,48,40465,40506,'00:28:06.046','00:28:07.775','The tomb is somewhere\nin the library.',-1),(95105,48,40508,40554,'00:28:07.848','00:28:09.782','You said yourself\nit used to be a church.',-1),(95106,48,40556,40585,'00:28:09.850','00:28:11.078','Look.',-1),(95107,48,40587,40642,'00:28:11.151','00:28:13.449','Three.',-1),(95108,48,40673,40720,'00:28:14.721','00:28:16.689','Three.',-1),(95109,48,40722,40750,'00:28:16.757','00:28:17.917','Seven.',-1),(95110,48,40751,40813,'00:28:17.991','00:28:20.551','Seven. Ten.',-1),(95111,48,40815,40861,'00:28:20.627','00:28:22.562','And ten.',-1),(95112,48,40863,40924,'00:28:22.629','00:28:25.189','Now where\'s the ten?',-1),(95113,48,40926,40987,'00:28:25.265','00:28:27.825','Look around for the ten.',-1),(95114,48,41171,41256,'00:28:35.475','00:28:39.002','Three and seven.',-1),(95115,48,41257,41305,'00:28:39.079','00:28:41.047','Seven and seven',-1),(95116,48,41306,41363,'00:28:41.114','00:28:43.480','and ten.',-1),(95117,48,41826,41874,'00:29:02.769','00:29:04.760','Ten.',-1),(95118,48,41876,41964,'00:29:04.838','00:29:08.501','\"X\" marks the spot.',-1),(95119,48,43345,43369,'00:30:06.066','00:30:07.055','Bingo.',-1),(95120,48,43371,43409,'00:30:07.134','00:30:08.726','You don\'t disappoint,\nDr.Jones.',-1),(95121,48,43411,43450,'00:30:08.802','00:30:10.429','You\'re a great deal\nlike your father.',-1),(95122,48,43452,43491,'00:30:10.504','00:30:12.131','Except he\'s lost,\nand I\'m not.',-1),(95123,48,43493,43519,'00:30:12.239','00:30:13.331','Lower me down.',-1),(95124,48,43765,43812,'00:30:23.550','00:30:25.541','Look after this for me,\nwill you?',-1),(95125,48,44156,44182,'00:30:39.866','00:30:40.924','Come on.',-1),(95126,48,44365,44401,'00:30:48.542','00:30:50.066','Pagan symbols.',-1),(95127,48,44403,44434,'00:30:50.143','00:30:51.440','Fourth or fifth century.',-1),(95128,48,44436,44462,'00:30:51.511','00:30:52.603','Right.',-1),(95129,48,44464,44530,'00:30:52.679','00:30:55.443','600 years before\nthe Crusades.',-1),(95130,48,44532,44589,'00:30:55.515','00:30:57.881','The Christians would have\ndug their own passages',-1),(95131,48,44590,44633,'00:30:57.951','00:30:59.714','and burial chambers\ncenturies later.',-1),(95132,48,44634,44670,'00:30:59.786','00:31:01.276','That\'s right.',-1),(95133,48,44672,44726,'00:31:01.354','00:31:03.618','If there\'s a knight of\nthe First Crusade down here,',-1),(95134,48,44728,44775,'00:31:03.690','00:31:05.658','that\'s where we\'ll find him.',-1),(95135,48,45542,45569,'00:31:37.624','00:31:38.716','What\'s this one?',-1),(95136,48,45595,45619,'00:31:39.793','00:31:40.817','The Ark of the Covenant.',-1),(95137,48,45621,45646,'00:31:40.894','00:31:41.952','Are you sure?',-1),(95138,48,45648,45682,'00:31:42.028','00:31:43.427','Pretty sure.',-1),(95139,48,46105,46138,'00:32:01.047','00:32:02.446','Watch out.',-1),(95140,48,46515,46544,'00:32:18.165','00:32:19.359','It\'s petroleum.',-1),(95141,48,46546,46612,'00:32:19.432','00:32:22.196','I should sink\na well down here and retire.',-1),(95142,48,47010,47045,'00:32:38.785','00:32:40.218','Give me the lighter.',-1),(95143,48,47289,47327,'00:32:50.397','00:32:51.989','Oh, rats.',-1),(95144,48,47329,47354,'00:32:52.065','00:32:53.089','Ugh!',-1),(95145,48,47710,47752,'00:33:07.948','00:33:09.677','Come on.',-1),(95146,48,48920,48951,'00:33:58.365','00:33:59.662','Come here.',-1),(95147,48,49138,49192,'00:34:07.440','00:34:09.704','Look, it...',-1),(95148,48,49194,49220,'00:34:09.776','00:34:10.868','it must be one of these.',-1),(95149,48,49222,49250,'00:34:10.944','00:34:12.104','Look at the artistry',-1),(95150,48,49253,49338,'00:34:12.212','00:34:15.773','of these carvings,\nand the scrollwork.',-1),(95151,48,49703,49759,'00:34:30.997','00:34:33.329','It\'s this one.',-1),(95152,48,50122,50163,'00:34:48.448','00:34:50.143','This is it.',-1),(95153,48,50166,50198,'00:34:50.250','00:34:51.615','We found it.',-1),(95154,48,50255,50281,'00:34:53.987','00:34:55.045','Look.',-1),(95155,48,50320,50368,'00:34:56.690','00:34:58.681','The engraving on the shield,',-1),(95156,48,50370,50444,'00:34:58.758','00:35:01.852','it\'s the same\nas on the Grail tablet.',-1),(95157,48,50480,50524,'00:35:03.363','00:35:05.194','The shield is the second marker.',-1),(95158,48,50526,50562,'00:35:05.265','00:35:06.755','What\'s that?',-1),(95159,48,50563,50610,'00:35:06.833','00:35:08.767','It\'s a rubbing',-1),(95160,48,50612,50682,'00:35:08.835','00:35:11.770','Dad made\nof the Grail tablet.',-1),(95161,48,50684,50745,'00:35:11.838','00:35:14.398','Just like your father--\ngiddy as a schoolboy.',-1),(95162,48,50772,50808,'00:35:15.508','00:35:17.032','Wouldn\'t it be wonderful',-1),(95163,48,50810,50860,'00:35:17.110','00:35:19.169','if he were here now\nto see this?',-1),(95164,48,50897,50948,'00:35:20.747','00:35:22.874','He never would have\nmade it past the rats.',-1),(95165,48,50950,50978,'00:35:22.949','00:35:24.109','He hates rats.',-1),(95166,48,50982,51036,'00:35:24.250','00:35:26.514','He\'s scared to death of them.',-1),(95167,48,51540,51573,'00:35:47.540','00:35:48.905','Get back!',-1),(95168,48,51575,51612,'00:35:48.975','00:35:50.533','Back against the wall.',-1),(95169,48,51727,51746,'00:35:55.315','00:35:56.111','Quick! Under it!',-1),(95170,48,51748,51781,'00:35:56.182','00:35:57.547','Air pocket!',-1),(95171,48,51916,51950,'00:36:03.189','00:36:04.622','Don\'t wander off.',-1),(95172,48,51952,51977,'00:36:04.691','00:36:05.715','What?',-1),(95173,48,51979,52008,'00:36:05.792','00:36:07.020','What?!',-1),(95174,48,52462,52502,'00:36:25.945','00:36:27.606','I think I\'ve found\na way out.',-1),(95175,48,52504,52539,'00:36:27.680','00:36:29.147','Deep breath.',-1),(95176,48,52955,53007,'00:36:46.466','00:36:48.627','Ah, Venice.',-1),(95177,48,53775,53806,'00:37:20.633','00:37:21.930','Whoa!',-1),(95178,48,54596,54644,'00:37:54.834','00:37:56.859','Are you crazy?!\nDon\'t go between them!',-1),(95179,48,54646,54716,'00:37:56.936','00:37:59.837','Go between them?\nAre you crazy?!',-1),(95180,48,54978,55013,'00:38:10.750','00:38:12.240','I said go around!',-1),(95181,48,55015,55057,'00:38:12.318','00:38:14.081','You said\ngo between them!',-1),(95182,48,55060,55112,'00:38:14.187','00:38:16.348','I said,\ndon\'t go between them!',-1),(95183,48,56623,56653,'00:39:19.319','00:39:20.581','No!',-1),(95184,48,56780,56829,'00:39:25.858','00:39:27.883','Why are you\ntrying to kill us?',-1),(95185,48,56831,56868,'00:39:27.961','00:39:29.519','Because you\'re looking\nfor the Holy Grail.',-1),(95186,48,56870,56923,'00:39:29.596','00:39:31.826','My father was looking\nfor the Holy Grail.',-1),(95187,48,56925,56952,'00:39:31.898','00:39:33.024','Did you kill him too?',-1),(95188,48,56954,56976,'00:39:33.099','00:39:34.031','No.',-1),(95189,48,56978,57019,'00:39:34.100','00:39:35.829','Where is he?',-1),(95190,48,57021,57080,'00:39:35.902','00:39:38.370','Talk or you\'re dead.',-1),(95191,48,57082,57120,'00:39:38.438','00:39:40.030','Damn it, tell me!',-1),(95192,48,57122,57152,'00:39:40.106','00:39:41.334','Tell me!',-1),(95193,48,57153,57216,'00:39:41.407','00:39:44.035','If you don\'t let go, Dr.Jones,\nwe\'ll both die.',-1),(95194,48,57218,57266,'00:39:44.110','00:39:46.101','Then we\'ll die.',-1),(95195,48,57269,57341,'00:39:46.245','00:39:49.214','My soul is prepared.\nHow\'s yours?',-1),(95196,48,57381,57418,'00:39:50.883','00:39:52.441','This is your last chance.',-1),(95197,48,57420,57492,'00:39:52.518','00:39:55.510','No, Dr.Jones, it\'s yours.',-1),(95198,48,57865,57933,'00:40:11.070','00:40:13.903','All right, where\'s my father?',-1),(95199,48,57935,58001,'00:40:13.973','00:40:16.737','If you let me go,\nI will tell you where he is.',-1),(95200,48,58003,58048,'00:40:16.809','00:40:18.674','Who are you?',-1),(95201,48,58049,58096,'00:40:18.745','00:40:20.679','My name is Kazim.',-1),(95202,48,58097,58133,'00:40:20.747','00:40:22.237','And why were you\ntrying to kill me?',-1),(95203,48,58135,58177,'00:40:22.315','00:40:24.044','The secret of the Grail',-1),(95204,48,58178,58234,'00:40:24.117','00:40:26.449','has been safe\nfor a thousand years,',-1),(95205,48,58236,58282,'00:40:26.519','00:40:28.419','and for all that time,',-1),(95206,48,58283,58342,'00:40:28.488','00:40:30.956','the Brotherhood of\nthe Cruciform Sword',-1),(95207,48,58344,58459,'00:40:31.024','00:40:35.825','have been prepared\nto do anything to keep it safe.',-1),(95208,48,58491,58538,'00:40:37.163','00:40:39.097','Let me off\nat this jetty.',-1),(95209,48,58613,58718,'00:40:42.235','00:40:46.604','Ask yourself, why do you\nseek the Cup of Christ?',-1),(95210,48,58720,58800,'00:40:46.673','00:40:50.006','Is it for His glory,\nor for yours?',-1),(95211,48,58801,58864,'00:40:50.076','00:40:52.704','I didn\'t come\nfor the Cup of Christ.',-1),(95212,48,58866,58912,'00:40:52.779','00:40:54.679','I came to find my father.',-1),(95213,48,58913,58995,'00:40:54.747','00:40:58.148','In that case,\nGod be with you in your quest.',-1),(95214,48,58997,59066,'00:40:58.217','00:41:01.084','Your father is being held\nin the Castle of Brunwald,',-1),(95215,48,59067,59124,'00:41:01.154','00:41:03.520','on the Austrian-German border.',-1),(95216,48,59334,59367,'00:41:12.265','00:41:13.630','How\'s the head?',-1),(95217,48,59368,59434,'00:41:13.700','00:41:16.430','It\'s better,\nnow I\'ve seen this.',-1),(95218,48,59436,59490,'00:41:16.502','00:41:18.766','It\'s the name of a city.',-1),(95219,48,59492,59529,'00:41:18.838','00:41:20.396','\"Alexandretta\"?',-1),(95220,48,59560,59593,'00:41:21.674','00:41:23.073','Hmm...',-1),(95221,48,59595,59640,'00:41:23.142','00:41:25.007','The knights of the First Crusade',-1),(95222,48,59641,59718,'00:41:25.078','00:41:28.275','laid siege to the city\nof Alexandretta for over a year.',-1),(95223,48,59720,59783,'00:41:28.347','00:41:30.975','The entire city was destroyed.',-1),(95224,48,59831,59920,'00:41:32.985','00:41:36.682','The present city of Iskenderun\nis built on its ruins.',-1),(95225,48,59966,60021,'00:41:38.624','00:41:40.888','Marcus, you remember\nwhat the Grail tablet said:',-1),(95226,48,60023,60082,'00:41:40.960','00:41:43.428','\"Across the desert\nand through the mountain',-1),(95227,48,60083,60134,'00:41:43.496','00:41:45.623','to the Canyon\nof the Crescent Moon.\"',-1),(95228,48,60208,60259,'00:41:48.668','00:41:50.795','But where exactly?',-1),(95229,48,60260,60300,'00:41:50.870','00:41:52.531','Your father would know.',-1),(95230,48,60302,60324,'00:41:52.605','00:41:53.537','Mm.',-1),(95231,48,60326,60384,'00:41:53.606','00:41:56.040','Your father did know.',-1),(95232,48,60386,60423,'00:41:56.109','00:41:57.633','Look. He made a map.',-1),(95233,48,60425,60467,'00:41:57.710','00:41:59.473','He must have\npieced it together',-1),(95234,48,60469,60501,'00:41:59.545','00:42:00.876','from clues\nscattered through',-1),(95235,48,60502,60545,'00:42:00.947','00:42:02.744','the whole history\nof the Grail quest.',-1),(95236,48,60547,60574,'00:42:02.815','00:42:03.941','A map with no names.',-1),(95237,48,60576,60616,'00:42:04.016','00:42:05.677','Now, he knew there\nwas a city',-1),(95238,48,60618,60658,'00:42:05.752','00:42:07.447','with an oasis\ndue east, here.',-1),(95239,48,60660,60684,'00:42:07.520','00:42:08.509','He knew the course',-1),(95240,48,60686,60729,'00:42:08.588','00:42:10.385','turned south through\nthe desert to a river,',-1),(95241,48,60730,60774,'00:42:10.456','00:42:12.287','and the river led\ninto the mountains, here.',-1),(95242,48,60776,60811,'00:42:12.358','00:42:13.825','Straight to the canyon.',-1),(95243,48,60813,60872,'00:42:13.893','00:42:16.361','He knew everything\nexcept where to begin,',-1),(95244,48,60874,60913,'00:42:16.429','00:42:18.056','the name of the city.',-1),(95245,48,60960,60998,'00:42:20.032','00:42:21.590','Alexandretta.',-1),(95246,48,61000,61023,'00:42:21.667','00:42:22.656','Now we know.',-1),(95247,48,61025,61059,'00:42:22.735','00:42:24.134','Yes. Now we know.',-1),(95248,48,61062,61095,'00:42:24.270','00:42:25.635','Marcus, get hold of Sallah.',-1),(95249,48,61096,61130,'00:42:25.705','00:42:27.104','Tell him to meet you\nin Iskenderun.',-1),(95250,48,61132,61155,'00:42:27.173','00:42:28.140','What about you?',-1),(95251,48,61156,61190,'00:42:28.207','00:42:29.606','I\'m going after Dad.',-1),(95252,48,61703,61751,'00:42:50.997','00:42:52.965','Elsa?',-1),(95253,48,61875,61945,'00:42:58.137','00:43:01.072','Elsa? Elsa?',-1),(95254,48,61947,61990,'00:43:01.140','00:43:02.937','Oh! Oh...',-1),(95255,48,62190,62221,'00:43:11.284','00:43:12.581','My room...',-1),(95256,48,62223,62265,'00:43:12.652','00:43:14.415','Mine, too.',-1),(95257,48,62267,62310,'00:43:14.487','00:43:16.250','What were they\nlooking for?',-1),(95258,48,62311,62346,'00:43:16.322','00:43:17.789','This.',-1),(95259,48,62348,62384,'00:43:17.857','00:43:19.347','The Grail diary?',-1),(95260,48,62386,62422,'00:43:19.425','00:43:20.949','Uh-huh.',-1),(95261,48,62424,62467,'00:43:21.027','00:43:22.824','You had it?',-1),(95262,48,62469,62513,'00:43:22.895','00:43:24.726','You didn\'t trust me.',-1),(95263,48,62515,62562,'00:43:24.797','00:43:26.788','I didn\'t know you.',-1),(95264,48,62564,62633,'00:43:26.866','00:43:29.733','At least I let you tag along.',-1),(95265,48,62635,62663,'00:43:29.802','00:43:30.996','Oh, yes.',-1),(95266,48,62665,62733,'00:43:31.070','00:43:33.903','Give them a flower,\nand they\'ll follow you anywhere.',-1),(95267,48,62767,62815,'00:43:35.308','00:43:37.299','Knock it off. You\'re not mad.',-1),(95268,48,62817,62852,'00:43:37.376','00:43:38.843','No?',-1),(95269,48,62853,62907,'00:43:38.911','00:43:41.141','No. You like\nthe way I do things.',-1),(95270,48,62909,62982,'00:43:41.247','00:43:44.273','It\'s lucky I don\'t do\nthings the same way.',-1),(95271,48,62984,63047,'00:43:44.350','00:43:46.978','You\'d still be standing\nat the Venice pier!',-1),(95272,48,63049,63109,'00:43:47.053','00:43:49.578','Look, what do you think\nis going on here?',-1),(95273,48,63111,63184,'00:43:49.655','00:43:52.681','Since I met you,\nI\'ve nearly been incinerated,',-1),(95274,48,63186,63253,'00:43:52.758','00:43:55.556','drowned, shot at,\nand chopped into fish bait.',-1),(95275,48,63255,63315,'00:43:55.628','00:43:58.153','We\'re caught in the middle\nof something sinister here.',-1),(95276,48,63317,63380,'00:43:58.231','00:44:00.859','My guess is Dad found out\nmore than he was looking for.',-1),(95277,48,63382,63404,'00:44:00.933','00:44:01.865','And until I\'m sure,',-1),(95278,48,63406,63443,'00:44:01.934','00:44:03.492','I\'m going to\ncontinue to do things',-1),(95279,48,63445,63488,'00:44:03.569','00:44:05.366','the way I think\nthey should be done.',-1),(95280,48,63571,63648,'00:44:08.808','00:44:12.005','How dare you kiss me!',-1),(95281,48,63777,63857,'00:44:17.383','00:44:20.716','Leave me alone.\nI don\'t like fast women.',-1),(95282,48,63858,63894,'00:44:20.786','00:44:22.253','And I hate...',-1),(95283,48,63895,63977,'00:44:22.321','00:44:25.722','arrogant men.',-1),(95284,48,64204,64240,'00:44:35.167','00:44:36.691','Ah, Venice.',-1),(95285,48,65010,65066,'00:45:08.768','00:45:11.100','What do you know\nabout this place?',-1),(95286,48,65068,65150,'00:45:11.203','00:45:14.604','I know the Brunwalds\nare famous art collectors.',-1),(95287,48,65191,65230,'00:45:16.309','00:45:17.936','What are you going to do?',-1),(95288,48,65232,65258,'00:45:18.010','00:45:19.102','Don\'t know.',-1),(95289,48,65260,65291,'00:45:19.178','00:45:20.475','I\'ll think of something.',-1),(95290,48,65481,65513,'00:45:28.387','00:45:29.718','Yes?',-1),(95291,48,65514,65554,'00:45:29.789','00:45:31.450','And not before time!',-1),(95292,48,65556,65581,'00:45:31.524','00:45:32.582','Did you intend to leave us',-1),(95293,48,65583,65615,'00:45:32.658','00:45:33.989','standing on\nthe doorstep all day?',-1),(95294,48,65617,65640,'00:45:34.060','00:45:35.027','We\'re drenched!',-1),(95295,48,65682,65733,'00:45:36.762','00:45:38.889','Now look, I\'ve gone\nand caught a sniffle.',-1),(95296,48,65735,65761,'00:45:38.965','00:45:40.057','Are you expected?',-1),(95297,48,65763,65819,'00:45:40.132','00:45:42.464','Do not take that tone\nwith me, my good man.',-1),(95298,48,65820,65869,'00:45:42.535','00:45:44.560','Now buttle off\nand tell Baron Brunwald',-1),(95299,48,65871,65946,'00:45:44.637','00:45:47.765','that Lord Clarence MacDonald\nand his lovely assistant...',-1),(95300,48,65978,66032,'00:45:49.108','00:45:51.372','...are here to view\nthe tapestries.',-1),(95301,48,66034,66060,'00:45:51.444','00:45:52.502','Tapestries?',-1),(95302,48,66061,66102,'00:45:52.578','00:45:54.273','Dear me,\nthe man is dense.',-1),(95303,48,66104,66147,'00:45:54.347','00:45:56.144','This is a castle,\nisn\'t it?',-1),(95304,48,66149,66183,'00:45:56.215','00:45:57.648','There are tapestries?',-1),(95305,48,66185,66235,'00:45:57.717','00:45:59.810','This is a castle,',-1),(95306,48,66237,66299,'00:45:59.885','00:46:02.479','and we have\nmany tapestries.',-1),(95307,48,66301,66360,'00:46:02.555','00:46:05.023','But if you are\na Scottish lord,',-1),(95308,48,66362,66432,'00:46:05.091','00:46:08.026','then I am Mickey Mouse!',-1),(95309,48,66434,66484,