,-1),(95692,48,106355,106402,'01:13:51.481','01:13:53.449','I was the next man.',-1),(95693,48,106404,106431,'01:13:53.517','01:13:54.643','Oh.',-1),(95694,48,106460,106498,'01:13:55.853','01:13:57.445','Of course. Well...',-1),(95695,48,106500,106560,'01:13:57.521','01:14:00.012','Ships that pass\nin the night.',-1),(95696,48,106562,106644,'01:14:00.090','01:14:03.526','Do you remember the last time\nwe had a quiet drink, hmm?',-1),(95697,48,106693,106725,'01:14:05.562','01:14:06.893','I had a milkshake.',-1),(95698,48,106727,106773,'01:14:06.964','01:14:08.898','Hmm?',-1),(95699,48,106775,106827,'01:14:08.966','01:14:11.161','What did we\ntalk about?',-1),(95700,48,106829,106877,'01:14:11.235','01:14:13.226','We didn\'t talk.',-1),(95701,48,106880,106936,'01:14:13.337','01:14:15.703','We never talked.',-1),(95702,48,106938,107054,'01:14:15.772','01:14:20.607','Do I detect\na rebuke?',-1),(95703,48,107056,107103,'01:14:20.677','01:14:22.645','A regret.',-1),(95704,48,107105,107140,'01:14:22.713','01:14:24.203','It was just the two of us, Dad.',-1),(95705,48,107142,107180,'01:14:24.281','01:14:25.839','It was a lonely way to grow up.',-1),(95706,48,107181,107209,'01:14:25.916','01:14:27.042','For you, too.',-1),(95707,48,107210,107253,'01:14:27.117','01:14:28.880','If you\'d been an ordinary,\naverage father,',-1),(95708,48,107254,107309,'01:14:28.952','01:14:31.216','like the other guys\' dads,\nyou\'d have understood that.',-1),(95709,48,107310,107385,'01:14:31.288','01:14:34.382','Actually, I was\na wonderful father.',-1),(95710,48,107386,107434,'01:14:34.458','01:14:36.426','When?',-1),(95711,48,107435,107480,'01:14:36.493','01:14:38.358','Did I ever tell\nyou to eat up?',-1),(95712,48,107482,107520,'01:14:38.428','01:14:40.020','Go to bed?\nWash your ears?',-1),(95713,48,107522,107558,'01:14:40.097','01:14:41.621','Do your homework? No.',-1),(95714,48,107560,107603,'01:14:41.698','01:14:43.495','I respected\nyour privacy,',-1),(95715,48,107605,107659,'01:14:43.567','01:14:45.831','and I taught\nyou self-reliance.',-1),(95716,48,107661,107686,'01:14:45.903','01:14:46.927','What you taught me was',-1),(95717,48,107688,107723,'01:14:47.004','01:14:48.471','that I was\nless important to you',-1),(95718,48,107724,107758,'01:14:48.538','01:14:49.937','than people\nwho\'d been dead',-1),(95719,48,107760,107797,'01:14:50.007','01:14:51.565','for 500 years\nin another country.',-1),(95720,48,107799,107841,'01:14:51.642','01:14:53.405','And I learned it so well',-1),(95721,48,107843,107910,'01:14:53.477','01:14:56.275','that we\'ve hardly spoken\nfor 20 years.',-1),(95722,48,107912,107966,'01:14:56.346','01:14:58.610','You left just when you\nwere becoming interesting.',-1),(95723,48,107968,108003,'01:14:58.682','01:15:00.149','Unbelievable.',-1),(95724,48,108005,108030,'01:15:00.217','01:15:01.275','Dad, how can you...?',-1),(95725,48,108033,108057,'01:15:01.385','01:15:02.409','Very well.',-1),(95726,48,108059,108118,'01:15:02.486','01:15:04.920','I\'m here now.',-1),(95727,48,108119,108168,'01:15:04.988','01:15:07.013','What do you want\nto talk about?',-1),(95728,48,108170,108197,'01:15:07.090','01:15:08.216','Hmm?',-1),(95729,48,108200,108258,'01:15:08.358','01:15:10.758','Well, I...',-1),(95730,48,108305,108346,'01:15:12.729','01:15:14.424','Uh...',-1),(95731,48,108436,108491,'01:15:18.201','01:15:20.465','I can\'t think of anything.',-1),(95732,48,108492,108542,'01:15:20.537','01:15:22.596','Then what are\nyou complaining about?',-1),(95733,48,108581,108629,'01:15:24.241','01:15:26.209','Look, we have work to do.',-1),(95734,48,108669,108715,'01:15:27.878','01:15:29.812','When we get to\nAlexandretta,',-1),(95735,48,108717,108772,'01:15:29.880','01:15:32.178','we will face\nthree challenges.',-1),(95736,48,108773,108820,'01:15:32.249','01:15:34.183','The first,',-1),(95737,48,108822,108858,'01:15:34.251','01:15:35.775','\"The Breath of God.',-1),(95738,48,108860,108914,'01:15:35.852','01:15:38.116','Only the penitent\nman will pass.\"',-1),(95739,48,108916,108946,'01:15:38.188','01:15:39.450','Second,',-1),(95740,48,108948,108978,'01:15:39.523','01:15:40.785','\"The Word of God.',-1),(95741,48,108980,109066,'01:15:40.857','01:15:44.418','Only in the footsteps\nof God will he proceed.\"',-1),(95742,48,109067,109094,'01:15:44.494','01:15:45.586','Third,',-1),(95743,48,109095,109131,'01:15:45.662','01:15:47.152','\"The Path of God.',-1),(95744,48,109133,109182,'01:15:47.230','01:15:49.255','\"Only in the leap\nfrom the lion\'s head',-1),(95745,48,109183,109245,'01:15:49.333','01:15:51.893','will he prove his worth.\"',-1),(95746,48,109296,109344,'01:15:54.004','01:15:56.029','What does that mean?',-1),(95747,48,109346,109392,'01:15:56.106','01:15:58.040','I don\'t know.',-1),(95748,48,109394,109428,'01:15:58.108','01:15:59.541','We\'ll find out.',-1),(95749,48,109585,109657,'01:16:06.049','01:16:09.075','We\'re turning around.',-1),(95750,48,109659,109718,'01:16:09.152','01:16:11.586','They\'re taking us back\nto Germany.',-1),(95751,48,109863,109918,'01:16:17.661','01:16:19.925','Well, I thought\nit would take them a lot longer',-1),(95752,48,109919,109951,'01:16:19.997','01:16:21.328','to figure out\nthe radio was dead.',-1),(95753,48,109953,110000,'01:16:21.398','01:16:23.366','Come on, Dad. Move!',-1),(95754,48,110089,110144,'01:16:27.070','01:16:29.368','Come on, Dad. Come on!',-1),(95755,48,110479,110530,'01:16:43.320','01:16:45.447','I didn\'t know you\ncould fly a plane.',-1),(95756,48,110532,110560,'01:16:45.522','01:16:46.682','Fly, yes.',-1),(95757,48,110614,110669,'01:16:48.925','01:16:51.223','Land, no.',-1),(95758,48,111234,111285,'01:17:14.751','01:17:16.912','Dad, you\'re going to have\nto use the machine gun.',-1),(95759,48,111287,111340,'01:17:16.987','01:17:19.182','Get it ready.',-1),(95760,48,111342,111399,'01:17:19.256','01:17:21.656','Eleven o\'clock!',-1),(95761,48,111401,111455,'01:17:21.725','01:17:23.989','Dad, eleven o\'clock!',-1),(95762,48,111481,111540,'01:17:25.062','01:17:27.530','What happens at eleven o\'clock?',-1),(95763,48,111542,111589,'01:17:27.597','01:17:29.565','Twelve, eleven, ten.',-1),(95764,48,111591,111638,'01:17:29.633','01:17:31.601','Eleven o\'clock, fire!',-1),(95765,48,112274,112323,'01:17:58.095','01:18:00.154','Dad, are we hit?!',-1),(95766,48,112325,112374,'01:18:00.230','01:18:02.255','More or less.',-1),(95767,48,112375,112420,'01:18:02.332','01:18:04.197','Son, I\'m sorry.',-1),(95768,48,112424,112474,'01:18:04.334','01:18:06.427','They got us.',-1),(95769,48,112521,112545,'01:18:08.405','01:18:09.394','Hang on, Dad.',-1),(95770,48,112547,112577,'01:18:09.473','01:18:10.735','We\'re going in!',-1),(95771,48,112882,112909,'01:18:23.420','01:18:24.546','Nice landing.',-1),(95772,48,112910,112959,'01:18:24.621','01:18:26.646','Thanks.',-1),(95773,48,113305,113341,'01:18:41.071','01:18:42.561','Those people are\ntrying to kill us!',-1),(95774,48,113343,113369,'01:18:42.639','01:18:43.731','I know, Dad!',-1),(95775,48,113371,113404,'01:18:43.807','01:18:45.172','Well.',-1),(95776,48,113405,113453,'01:18:45.242','01:18:47.233','It\'s a new\nexperience for me.',-1),(95777,48,113455,113516,'01:18:47.310','01:18:49.870','It happens to me all the time.',-1),(95778,48,114248,114295,'01:19:20.343','01:19:22.311','This is intolerable!',-1),(95779,48,114328,114361,'01:19:23.680','01:19:25.045','This could be close.',-1),(95780,48,114560,114621,'01:19:33.356','01:19:35.916','Faster, boy! Faster!',-1),(95781,48,114997,115054,'01:19:51.575','01:19:53.941','Well, they don\'t come\nany closer than that!',-1),(95782,48,115434,115502,'01:20:09.759','01:20:12.592','Dad, he\'s coming back!',-1),(95783,48,116619,116680,'01:20:59.142','01:21:01.702','I suddenly\nremembered my Charlemagne.',-1),(95784,48,116682,116752,'01:21:01.778','01:21:04.679','\"Let my armies be the rocks\nand the trees',-1),(95785,48,116753,116805,'01:21:04.748','01:21:06.909','and the birds in the sky.\"',-1),(95786,48,117226,117255,'01:21:24.434','01:21:25.628','These pages are taken',-1),(95787,48,117256,117316,'01:21:25.702','01:21:28.193','from Professor Jones\'\ndiary, Your Highness,',-1),(95788,48,117318,117349,'01:21:28.271','01:21:29.568','and they include a map',-1),(95789,48,117351,117417,'01:21:29.639','01:21:32.403','that pinpoints the exact\nlocation of the Grail.',-1),(95790,48,117419,117481,'01:21:32.475','01:21:35.069','As you can see, the Grail\nis all but in our hands.',-1),(95791,48,117483,117510,'01:21:35.145','01:21:36.271','However, Your Highness,',-1),(95792,48,117513,117562,'01:21:36.379','01:21:38.438','we would not think\nof crossing your soil',-1),(95793,48,117564,117594,'01:21:38.515','01:21:39.777','without your permission,',-1),(95794,48,117596,117649,'01:21:39.849','01:21:42.079','nor of removing the\nGrail from your borders',-1),(95795,48,117651,117722,'01:21:42.152','01:21:45.121','without suitable\ncompensation.',-1),(95796,48,117776,117827,'01:21:47.357','01:21:49.484','What have you brought?',-1),(95797,48,118022,118080,'01:21:57.600','01:22:00.000','Precious valuables,\nYour Highness,',-1),(95798,48,118081,118152,'01:22:00.070','01:22:03.005','donated by some\nof the finest families',-1),(95799,48,118153,118203,'01:22:03.073','01:22:05.132','in all of Germany.',-1),(95800,48,118279,118311,'01:22:08.311','01:22:09.642','Ah!',-1),(95801,48,118313,118384,'01:22:09.713','01:22:12.682','Rolls-Royce\nPhantom Two.',-1),(95802,48,118385,118421,'01:22:12.749','01:22:14.239','Four-point-three liter,',-1),(95803,48,118423,118484,'01:22:14.317','01:22:16.842','30 horsepower,\nsix-cylinder engine,',-1),(95804,48,118486,118549,'01:22:16.920','01:22:19.582','with Stromberg\ndowndraft carburetor.',-1),(95805,48,118551,118636,'01:22:19.656','01:22:23.183','Can go from zero to\n100 kilometers an hour',-1),(95806,48,118638,118694,'01:22:23.259','01:22:25.591','in 12.5 seconds.',-1),(95807,48,118695,118747,'01:22:25.662','01:22:27.823','And I even\nlike the color.',-1),(95808,48,118749,118831,'01:22:27.897','01:22:31.298','The keys are in the ignition,\nYour Highness.',-1),(95809,48,118862,118922,'01:22:32.602','01:22:35.093','You shall have\ncamels, horses,',-1),(95810,48,118924,118970,'01:22:35.171','01:22:37.105','an armed escort, provisions,',-1),(95811,48,118972,119018,'01:22:37.173','01:22:39.107','desert vehicles',-1),(95812,48,119020,119048,'01:22:39.175','01:22:40.369','and tanks.',-1),(95813,48,119050,119097,'01:22:40.443','01:22:42.411','You\'re welcome.',-1),(95814,48,119471,119506,'01:22:57.994','01:22:59.427','We have no time to lose.',-1),(95815,48,119507,119570,'01:22:59.496','01:23:02.124','Indiana Jones\nand his father have escaped.',-1),(95816,48,119636,119682,'01:23:04.868','01:23:06.768','We go this way.',-1),(95817,48,119684,119721,'01:23:06.836','01:23:08.394','Get that camel\nout of the way.',-1),(95818,48,119780,119822,'01:23:10.874','01:23:12.603','What happened\nto Marcus, Sallah?',-1),(95819,48,119824,119893,'01:23:12.675','01:23:15.542','Ah, they set out across\nthe desert this afternoon.',-1),(95820,48,119894,119962,'01:23:15.612','01:23:18.445','I believe they took\nMr.Brody with them.',-1),(95821,48,119997,120063,'01:23:19.883','01:23:22.647','Now they have the map.',-1),(95822,48,120065,120128,'01:23:22.719','01:23:25.347','And in this sort of race,',-1),(95823,48,120130,120208,'01:23:25.422','01:23:28.687','there\'s no silver medal\nfor finishing second.',-1),(95824,48,120732,120797,'01:23:50.513','01:23:53.243','Care to wet your\nwhistle, Marcus?',-1),(95825,48,120799,120846,'01:23:53.316','01:23:55.284','I\'d rather spit\nin your face.',-1),(95826,48,120850,120900,'01:23:55.418','01:23:57.511','But as I haven\'t\ngot any spit...',-1),(95827,48,120964,121019,'01:24:00.190','01:24:02.488','Must be within\nthree or four miles.',-1),(95828,48,121021,121086,'01:24:02.559','01:24:05.289','Otherwise we are\noff the map.',-1),(95829,48,121129,121195,'01:24:07.063','01:24:09.793','Well, Marcus,\nwe are on the brink',-1),(95830,48,121196,121247,'01:24:09.866','01:24:11.993','of the recovery\nof the greatest artifact',-1),(95831,48,121249,121283,'01:24:12.068','01:24:13.467','in the history\nof mankind.',-1),(95832,48,121284,121344,'01:24:13.536','01:24:16.027','You\'re meddling with powers',-1),(95833,48,121346,121415,'01:24:16.105','01:24:18.972','you cannot\npossibly comprehend.',-1),(95834,48,121543,121606,'01:24:24.314','01:24:26.942','Ah, I see Brody.',-1),(95835,48,121608,121667,'01:24:27.016','01:24:29.484','He seems okay.',-1),(95836,48,121737,121775,'01:24:32.388','01:24:33.980','They\'ve got a tank.',-1),(95837,48,121919,121958,'01:24:39.996','01:24:41.588','Six-pound gun.',-1),(95838,48,121959,122001,'01:24:41.664','01:24:43.393','What do you think\nyou\'re doing there?',-1),(95839,48,122003,122025,'01:24:43.466','01:24:44.398','Get down!',-1),(95840,48,122027,122089,'01:24:44.467','01:24:47.061','Dad, we\'re well out of range.',-1),(95841,48,122332,122378,'01:24:57.180','01:24:59.114','That car belonged\nto my brother-in-law.',-1),(95842,48,122380,122410,'01:24:59.182','01:25:00.444','Come on, come on!',-1),(95843,48,122412,122458,'01:25:00.517','01:25:02.417','I can\'t see anyone up there.',-1),(95844,48,122459,122501,'01:25:02.485','01:25:04.214','Maybe it wasn\'t\neven Jones.',-1),(95845,48,122502,122540,'01:25:04.287','01:25:05.845','No, it is him,\nall right.',-1),(95846,48,122542,122582,'01:25:05.922','01:25:07.617','He\'s here somewhere.',-1),(95847,48,122584,122650,'01:25:07.690','01:25:10.420','Put Brody in the tank.',-1),(95848,48,122835,122896,'01:25:18.134','01:25:20.694','Well, in this sun,',-1),(95849,48,122898,122953,'01:25:20.770','01:25:23.068','without transportation,\nthey\'re as good as dead.',-1),(95850,48,123185,123225,'01:25:32.715','01:25:34.376','It\'s Jones, all right.',-1),(95851,48,123325,123361,'01:25:38.555','01:25:40.045','Now, who are\nall these people?',-1),(95852,48,123362,123385,'01:25:40.123','01:25:41.055','Who cares?',-1),(95853,48,123386,123433,'01:25:41.124','01:25:43.058','As long as they\'re\nkeeping Donovan busy.',-1),(95854,48,123435,123478,'01:25:43.126','01:25:44.923','Dad, you stay here\nwhile Sallah and I',-1),(95855,48,123479,123529,'01:25:44.994','01:25:47.053','organize some transportation.',-1),(95856,48,124118,124157,'01:26:11.588','01:26:13.215','I\'m going after those horses.',-1),(95857,48,124158,124181,'01:26:13.289','01:26:14.221','I\'ll take the camels.',-1),(95858,48,124184,124207,'01:26:14.357','01:26:15.324','I don\'t need camels.',-1),(95859,48,124209,124231,'01:26:15.391','01:26:16.323','But, Indy...',-1),(95860,48,124233,124259,'01:26:16.392','01:26:17.484','No camels.',-1),(95861,48,124520,124556,'01:26:28.371','01:26:29.838','Who is he?',-1),(95862,48,124599,124669,'01:26:31.641','01:26:34.576','A messenger from God.',-1),(95863,48,124671,124728,'01:26:34.644','01:26:37.010','For the unrighteous,',-1),(95864,48,124729,124834,'01:26:37.080','01:26:41.449','the Cup of Life\nholds everlasting damnation.',-1),(95865,48,125276,125300,'01:26:59.869','01:27:00.836','Marcus!',-1),(95866,48,125324,125350,'01:27:01.871','01:27:02.929','Oh.',-1),(95867,48,125352,125427,'01:27:03.006','01:27:06.134','\"Genius of the Restoration...\"',-1),(95868,48,125429,125500,'01:27:06.209','01:27:09.201','\"Aid our own resuscitation.\"',-1),(95869,48,125502,125532,'01:27:09.278','01:27:10.540','Henry, what are you\ndoing here?',-1),(95870,48,125534,125567,'01:27:10.613','01:27:11.978','It\'s a rescue, old boy.\nCome on.',-1),(95871,48,125721,125749,'01:27:18.388','01:27:19.582','Search him.',-1),(95872,48,125751,125805,'01:27:19.656','01:27:21.886','What is in this book?',-1),(95873,48,125806,125892,'01:27:21.958','01:27:25.519','That miserable\nlittle diary of yours.',-1),(95874,48,125894,125946,'01:27:25.595','01:27:27.756','We have the map.\nThe book is useless.',-1),(95875,48,125947,126026,'01:27:27.830','01:27:31.095','And yet you come all the way\nback to Berlin to get it.',-1),(95876,4