imal.',-1),(99160,16,97736,97811,'01:07:52.370','01:07:55.498','- Well, that\'s a little unfair.\n<i>- No, what\'s unfair...</i>',-1),(99161,16,97813,97892,'01:07:55.573','01:07:58.872','is that Conor hasn\'t slept in two weeks\nbecause of that dog\'s barking...',-1),(99162,16,97894,97952,'01:07:58.943','01:08:01.343','that Patrick gets\nknocked down twice a day...',-1),(99163,16,97953,98000,'01:08:01.413','01:08:03.347','<i>that I can\'t even think straight.</i>',-1),(99164,16,98001,98049,'01:08:03.415','01:08:05.406','God forbid there\'s\na hint of thunder.',-1),(99165,16,98051,98098,'01:08:05.483','01:08:07.417','- Just don\'t!\n- Just calm down for a second.',-1),(99166,16,98099,98172,'01:08:07.485','01:08:10.511','I know that it\'s been a rough couple of\nmonths with the new baby and everything.',-1),(99167,16,98174,98250,'01:08:10.588','01:08:13.785','I understand that.\nBut I was talking with Arnie.',-1),(99168,16,98252,98299,'01:08:13.858','01:08:15.792','- And postpartum dep-\n- Don\'t you dare.',-1),(99169,16,98300,98392,'01:08:15.860','01:08:19.694','I am not depressed.\nI am exhausted.',-1),(99170,16,98394,98454,'01:08:19.764','01:08:22.289','<i>I\'m not angry because of some condition.</i>',-1),(99171,16,98456,98519,'01:08:22.367','01:08:24.961','I can\'t even go out\nfor an hour without the kids...',-1),(99172,16,98520,98592,'01:08:25.036','01:08:28.005','because every babysitter in this\nneighborhood is terrified of Marley.',-1),(99173,16,98593,98672,'01:08:28.072','01:08:31.371','I know that, but you were the one that\nsaid you didn\'t wanna work anymore.',-1),(99174,16,98674,98721,'01:08:31.443','01:08:33.411','<i>- We can get help-</i>\n- I don\'t need any help!',-1),(99175,16,98723,98769,'01:08:33.478','01:08:35.412','- That makes it hard.\n- Just get rid of the dog!',-1),(99176,16,98771,98824,'01:08:35.480','01:08:37.675','- That\'s not gonna happen obviously.\n- Please keep your voice down.',-1),(99177,16,98825,98898,'01:08:37.749','01:08:40.775','- Me keep my voice down?\n- Just do it. Just get rid of the dog!',-1),(99178,16,98900,98947,'01:08:40.852','01:08:42.820','Everybody gets rid of their dogs.\nIt\'s just a dog.',-1),(99179,16,98949,99025,'01:08:42.887','01:08:46.050','And I\'m just a husband. You gonna\nget rid of me when I misbehave?',-1),(99180,16,99026,99073,'01:08:46.124','01:08:48.058','- I\'ve thought about it.\n- Well, that makes two of us.',-1),(99181,16,99075,99132,'01:08:48.126','01:08:50.526','- What do you have to complain about?\n- What do I-',-1),(99182,16,99134,99206,'01:08:50.595','01:08:53.621','- Because you\'re such a joy to be around?\n- You\'re such a jerk.',-1),(99183,16,99208,99277,'01:08:53.698','01:08:56.565','So nice to walk in the door,\nfeel like you\'re joining a chain gang.',-1),(99184,16,99279,99314,'01:08:56.634','01:08:58.124','<i>Just a jerk!</i>',-1),(99185,16,99399,99477,'01:09:01.639','01:09:04.904','Stop it! It\'s your fault.',-1),(99186,16,99479,99554,'01:09:04.976','01:09:08.104','- You gotta be kidding me?\n- Nope.',-1),(99187,16,99556,99636,'01:09:08.179','01:09:11.512','<i>Just for a couple of days\ntill things cool down at home.</i>',-1),(99188,16,99694,99742,'01:09:13.952','01:09:15.920','A couple days will be all right.',-1),(99189,16,99743,99802,'01:09:15.987','01:09:18.421','You guys know each other.\nYou\'ll be comfortable.',-1),(99190,16,99803,99905,'01:09:18.490','01:09:22.722','- Want a beer?\n- No, I\'m fine. Thanks. Are you moving?',-1),(99191,16,99907,99970,'01:09:22.794','01:09:25.456','- Yeah.\n<i>- Where?</i>',-1),(99192,16,99972,100020,'01:09:25.530','01:09:27.521','New York.',-1),(99193,16,100022,100114,'01:09:27.599','01:09:31.433','<i>The Gray Lady came a-courtin\'.</i>',-1),(99194,16,100116,100185,'01:09:31.503','01:09:34.404','The <i>Times</i> offered you\na permanent job?',-1),(99195,16,100187,100252,'01:09:34.472','01:09:37.202','I gave Arnie my notice last week.',-1),(99196,16,100254,100329,'01:09:37.275','01:09:40.403','- You didn\'t say anything.\n<i>- I know. I\'m sorry.</i>',-1),(99197,16,100331,100465,'01:09:40.478','01:09:46.075','I just- It all happened so fast,\nI\'m not even used to the idea yet.',-1),(99198,16,100467,100557,'01:09:46.150','01:09:49.916','That\'s great. The <i>New York Times.</i>',-1),(99199,16,100559,100625,'01:09:49.988','01:09:52.718','It\'s what we always dreamed of.',-1),(99200,16,100707,100802,'01:09:56.160','01:10:00.096','Well, congratulations.\nI mean, you deserve it.',-1),(99201,16,100803,100886,'01:10:00.164','01:10:03.622','- Yeah.\n- Thanks for looking after Marley.',-1),(99202,16,100888,100945,'01:10:03.701','01:10:06.067','- Yeah.\n- He\'s eating your briefcase right now.',-1),(99203,16,100947,101011,'01:10:06.137','01:10:08.799','- Shit!\n<i>- Marley. Marley, no.</i>',-1),(99204,16,101012,101104,'01:10:08.873','01:10:12.707','- Two days, John. I\'m serious.\n- Sorry.',-1),(99205,16,101193,101261,'01:10:16.381','01:10:19.214','Sorry. I didn\'t mean to wake you.',-1),(99206,16,101262,101307,'01:10:19.284','01:10:21.149','I wasn\'t, uh, sleeping.',-1),(99207,16,101373,101467,'01:10:23.888','01:10:27.824','<i>- Where\'s Marley?</i>\n- Sebastian\'s gonna watch him for a few days.',-1),(99208,16,101469,101535,'01:10:27.892','01:10:30.656','Mm-hmm. I\'d love to see that.',-1),(99209,16,101537,101662,'01:10:30.728','01:10:35.927','<i>Just until I can find\na more permanent home.</i>',-1),(99210,16,101700,101785,'01:10:37.502','01:10:41.063','- This is his permanent home, John.\n- Mmm.',-1),(99211,16,101787,101835,'01:10:41.139','01:10:43.130','<i>Marley\'s not going anywhere.</i>\n<i>Honey, I\'m sorry.</i>',-1),(99212,16,101836,101901,'01:10:43.207','01:10:45.903','I just got overwhelmed.',-1),(99213,16,101903,102020,'01:10:45.977','01:10:50.846','<i>- No one tells you how hard this is all gonna be.</i>\n- Which part?',-1),(99214,16,102021,102096,'01:10:50.915','01:10:54.009','All of it:',-1),(99215,16,102098,102173,'01:10:54.085','01:10:57.248','Marriage, being a parent.',-1),(99216,16,102175,102266,'01:10:57.322','01:11:01.122','<i>It\'s the hardest job in the world</i>\n<i>and nobody prepares you for that.</i>',-1),(99217,16,102268,102339,'01:11:01.192','01:11:04.161','Nobody tells you how much\nyou have to give up.',-1),(99218,16,102341,102452,'01:11:04.228','01:11:08.858','I feel like they do tell you,\nbut you don\'t listen...',-1),(99219,16,102454,102530,'01:11:08.933','01:11:12.096','or you think, \"Ah, they\'re just miserable.\"',-1),(99220,16,102642,102728,'01:11:16.774','01:11:20.335','I\'ve given up so much\nof what made me who I am.',-1),(99221,16,102761,102808,'01:11:21.713','01:11:23.681','But I can\'t say that because...',-1),(99222,16,102809,102877,'01:11:23.748','01:11:26.581','I\'m a very bad person if I say that.',-1),(99223,16,102925,102985,'01:11:28.553','01:11:31.044','But I feel it. I really do.',-1),(99224,16,102986,103093,'01:11:31.122','01:11:35.582','I feel it sometimes. I just-',-1),(99225,16,103095,103148,'01:11:35.660','01:11:37.855','I just want you to know that.',-1),(99226,16,103150,103243,'01:11:37.929','01:11:41.797','I do know that.\nAnd you can say it. I say it.',-1),(99227,16,103244,103319,'01:11:41.866','01:11:44.994','But I did make a choice.',-1),(99228,16,103321,103436,'01:11:45.069','01:11:49.870','I made a choice, and even\nif it\'s harder than I thought...',-1),(99229,16,103438,103487,'01:11:49.941','01:11:51.966','I don\'t regret it.',-1),(99230,16,103489,103540,'01:11:52.043','01:11:54.170','- Are you sure?\n- I am very sure.',-1),(99231,16,103541,103628,'01:11:54.245','01:11:57.874','\'Cause it kinda has like a\n\"there\'s no place like home\" feeling to it.',-1),(99232,16,103630,103726,'01:11:57.949','01:12:01.942','I just think these things are gonna happen\nand we\'re gonna get through them.',-1),(99233,16,103728,103824,'01:12:02.020','01:12:06.013','- And we\'ll just do it together.\n- Together.',-1),(99234,16,103888,104017,'01:12:08.693','01:12:14.063','- Getting rid of Marley is not gonna fix anything.\n- No.',-1),(99235,16,104019,104127,'01:12:14.132','01:12:18.660','And getting rid of you\nisn\'t gonna fix anything either.',-1),(99236,16,104129,104176,'01:12:18.736','01:12:20.670','- Can I ask you a favor?\n- Yes.',-1),(99237,16,104177,104241,'01:12:20.738','01:12:23.400','No more kids for a while.',-1),(99238,16,104243,104310,'01:12:23.474','01:12:26.272','Absolutely. Deal.',-1),(99239,16,104407,104506,'01:12:30.314','01:12:34.444','Hi, guys.',-1),(99240,16,104508,104568,'01:12:34.519','01:12:37.010','All right, say hello to Colleen.',-1),(99241,16,104570,104630,'01:12:37.088','01:12:39.613','- Daddy says her name is Whoops.\n- No, I-',-1),(99242,16,104632,104700,'01:12:39.691','01:12:42.524','<i>- Patrick said that.</i>\n- What?',-1),(99243,16,104702,104766,'01:12:42.593','01:12:45.289','- Why did you say that?\n- I was just kidding around.',-1),(99244,16,104768,104823,'01:12:45.363','01:12:47.627','- It was kind of a secret, guys.\n- Over here.',-1),(99245,16,104972,105046,'01:12:53.838','01:12:56.932','The old pro moves back.\nHe looks for a little separation.',-1),(99246,16,105048,105102,'01:12:57.008','01:12:59.272','Gets an assist from Colleen.',-1),(99247,16,105104,105167,'01:12:59.343','01:13:01.971','Nice shot, Dad!',-1),(99248,16,105169,105228,'01:13:02.046','01:13:04.537','Nice shot? Come on. Conor?',-1),(99249,16,105230,105293,'01:13:04.615','01:13:07.209','- Extraordinary.\n- Yeah. Again.',-1),(99250,16,105294,105366,'01:13:07.285','01:13:10.277','Wait. Let me get this. I\'ll be back.',-1),(99251,16,105368,105453,'01:13:10.354','01:13:13.881','<i>- All right.</i>\n- The knees are shot.',-1),(99252,16,105489,105538,'01:13:15.393','01:13:17.452','- Hello?\n- John Grogan?',-1),(99253,16,105540,105588,'01:13:17.528','01:13:19.519','Yes, it is.',-1),(99254,16,105590,105683,'01:13:19.597','01:13:23.499','- Gil Lawford from the <i>Philadelphia Inquirer.</i>\n- Uh, yeah, yeah.',-1),(99255,16,105732,105791,'01:13:25.536','01:13:27.970','Hi. How are you?\nThanks for getting back to me.',-1),(99256,16,105817,105908,'01:13:29.073','01:13:32.839','Oh! Hey, who was that on the phone?',-1),(99257,16,105909,105955,'01:13:32.910','01:13:34.810','The <i>Philadelphia Inquirer.</i>',-1),(99258,16,105957,106046,'01:13:34.879','01:13:38.610','I sent the editor some clips\na while back and he wants to meet.',-1),(99259,16,106048,106154,'01:13:38.683','01:13:43.120','- What\'s a while back?\n- He was down here on vacation a month ago.',-1),(99260,16,106156,106232,'01:13:43.187','01:13:46.350','And he read my stuff.\nAnd we kind of had lunch.',-1),(99261,16,106234,106322,'01:13:46.424','01:13:50.087','- How do you kind of have lunch?\n<i>- I didn\'t think anything was gonna come of it.</i>',-1),(99262,16,106323,106367,'01:13:50.161','01:13:51.992','<i>Okay.</i>',-1),(99263,16,106369,106439,'01:13:52.063','01:13:54.998','- But?\n<i>- They offered me a job.</i>',-1),(99264,16,106441,106506,'01:13:55.066','01:13:57.762','I mean, I have an interview.',-1),(99265,16,106508,106586,'01:13:57.835','01:14:01.100','- As, like, a columnist or-\n- As a reporter.',-1),(99266,16,106588,106647,'01:14:01.172','01:14:03.663','<i>As a reporter?</i>\n<i>Well, what did you say?</i>',-1),(99267,16,106649,106739,'01:14:03.741','01:14:07.472','<i>I said, \"Thank you very much,</i>\n<i>but I\'m happy here. \"</i>',-1),(99268,16,106741,106832,'01:14:07.545','01:14:11.345','<i> \"Never have I heard someone</i>\n<i>piss and moan as much as John Grogan.</i>',-1),(99269,16,106833,106884,'01:14:11.415','01:14:13.508','If he doesn\'t like it here,\nhe should move.\"',-1),(99270,16,106886,106949,'01:14:13.584','01:14:16.212','That\'s part of my job\nis to get a response.',-1),(99271,16,106950,107023,'01:14:16.287','01:14:19.313','- I\'m glad to see a little blood\nflowing from these people.\n- No.',-1),(99272,16,107025,107119,'01:14:19.390','01:14:23.292','- There\'s a recurring theme here.\n- Recurring theme is we got a lot\nof cranks in Broward County.',-1),(99273,16,107120,107187,'01:14:23.361','01:14:26.125','- That\'s what I\'m up against.\n- But what I\'m trying to say, with all due respect...',-1),(99274,16,107188,107235,'01:14:26.197','01:14:28.131','is that you are one of them!',-1),(99275,16,107236,107299,'01:14:28.199','01:14:30.793','I\'m a commentator.\nEveryone wants me to act...',-1),(99276,16,107300,107349,'01:14:30.868','01:14:32.893','<i>like everything\'s great,</i>\n<i>when there are issues.</i>',-1),(99277,16,107351,107447,'01:14:32.970','01:14:36.997','<i>There\'s overcrowding, there\'s crime,</i>\n<i>there\'s racial tensions.</i>',-1),(99278,16,107449,107536,'01:14:37.074','01:14:40.669','Every time you turn around there\'s a new\nsky rise going up even uglier than the one-',-1),(99279,16,107537,107625,'01:14:40.745','01:14:44.408','That goes on all over the world.\nIt\'s not Florida. It\'s you. What\'s wrong?',-1),(99280,16,107627,107748,'01:14:44.482','01:14:49.510','Nothing\'s wrong. Everyone wants to think,\n\"Oh, he\'s turning 40. He\'s become a curmudgeon.\"',-1),(99281,16,107750,107826,'01:14:49.587','01:14:52.750','That\'s not it. Maybe-',-1),(99282,16,107827,107918,'01:14:52.824','01:14:56.590','I don\'t know. Maybe I\'m sick of my column.',-1),(99283,16,107919,108011,'01:14:56.661','01:15:00.495','I don\'t- I don\'t find the things\nI\'m saying that interesting.',-1),(99284,16,108013,108094,'01:15:00.565','01:15:03.932','<i>John. John, you\'re the comic voice\nof south Florida.</i>',-1),(99285,16,108096,108145,'01:15:04.001','01:15:06.060','You\'re a national treasure,\nfor God\'s sakes.',-1),(99286,16,108147,108240,'01:15:06.137','01:15:10.039','- Maybe a regional treasure.\n- Well, a municipal treasure for sure.',-1),(99287,16,108242,108311,'01:15:10.107','01:15:12.974','<i>- Thank you.</i>\n- Listen. Take a vacation.\nGo away for a couple weeks.',-1),(99288,16,108313,108376,'01:15:13.044','01:15:15.706','- Take a month off.\n- Go where?',-1),(99289,16,1