 the prisons.',-1),(103708,45,9085,9166,'00:06:18.545','00:06:21.922','Your mother\'s Barbara, your father\'s Cliff...',-1),(103709,45,9170,9263,'00:06:22.090','00:06:25.968','- He has electric trains.\n- Really?',-1),(103710,45,9267,9337,'00:06:26.136','00:06:29.055','Am I what they had in mind?',-1),(103711,45,9341,9443,'00:06:29.222','00:06:33.476','Walter, they\'re gonna love you!',-1),(103712,45,9503,9625,'00:06:35.979','00:06:41.067','Everybody, Annie has an announcement.',-1),(103713,45,9629,9719,'00:06:41.234','00:06:44.987','Walter and I are engaged.',-1),(103714,45,9830,9916,'00:06:49.618','00:06:53.204','Thank you. Thank you.',-1),(103715,45,10046,10107,'00:06:58.585','00:07:01.128','Congratulations, Walter.',-1),(103716,45,10149,10200,'00:07:02.881','00:07:05.007','Bless you!',-1),(103717,45,10239,10360,'00:07:06.635','00:07:11.680','- Are you all right?\n- Maybe it\'s the flowers.',-1),(103718,45,10364,10468,'00:07:11.848','00:07:16.185','- We\'ll move them.\n- No! I feel terrible, sneezing now.',-1),(103719,45,10472,10594,'00:07:16.353','00:07:21.440','- This is a very important moment.\n- He\'s allergic to everything.',-1),(103720,45,10598,10682,'00:07:21.608','00:07:25.111','Bees.\nI\'m allergic to bees.',-1),(103721,45,10686,10824,'00:07:25.278','00:07:31.033','He\'s allergic to all bees.\nWe have to take adrenalin with us.',-1),(103722,45,10828,10983,'00:07:31.201','00:07:37.665','- If he eats just a bit of a nut...\n- My head swells, and I drop dead.',-1),(103723,45,10987,11089,'00:07:37.833','00:07:42.044','- It\'s the same with him and bees.\n- We had salmon at our wedding.',-1),(103724,45,11093,11232,'00:07:42.212','00:07:48.008','- A wedding without salmon is...\n- I\'m not allergic to salmon.',-1),(103725,45,11236,11296,'00:07:48.176','00:07:50.678','But you never know.',-1),(103726,45,11300,11399,'00:07:50.846','00:07:54.974','- You never know.\n- He wasn\'t always allergic to bees.',-1),(103727,45,11403,11578,'00:07:55.142','00:08:02.439','