nah.\nHow old are you?',-1),(103800,45,20007,20081,'00:13:53.666','00:13:56.710','- I\'m eight.\n- You\'re up late.',-1),(103801,45,20085,20222,'00:13:56.878','00:14:02.591','- It\'s not so late in Seattle.\n- You\'re right. What\'s your wish?',-1),(103802,45,20226,20362,'00:14:02.759','00:14:08.430','- My dad needs a new wife.\n- You don\'t like the one he has?',-1),(103803,45,20366,20462,'00:14:08.598','00:14:12.601','- He doesn\'t have one.\n- Where\'s your mum?',-1),(103804,45,20466,20602,'00:14:12.769','00:14:18.440','- She died.\n- Well, who can believe this?',-1),(103805,45,20606,20745,'00:14:18.608','00:14:24.404','- I\'ve been sad, but Dad\'s worse.\n- Have you talked to him about it?',-1),(103806,45,20749,20879,'00:14:24.572','00:14:29.993','No, that makes him sadder.',-1),(103807,45,20883,20948,'00:14:30.161','00:14:32.871','Jonah, is your dad home?',-1),(103808,45,20952,21065,'00:14:33.039','00:14:37.709','- Is he busy?\n- No, he\'s out on the deck.',-1),(103809,45,21069,21145,'00:14:37.877','00:14:41.046','Can\'t you ask him to talk to me?',-1),(103810,45,21149,21290,'00:14:41.214','00:14:47.094','- Wretched woman! Hang up, Jonah!\n- No, he\'d kill me.',-1),(103811,45,21294,21410,'00:14:47.262','00:14:52.099','He won\'t be angry when he hears\nhow concerned you are about him.',-1),(103812,45,21414,21540,'00:14:52.267','00:14:57.521','- Want to bet?\n- If he yells, you lose a fan.',-1),(103813,45,21591,21728,'00:14:59.649','00:15:05.362','Dad, there\'s someone on the phone for you.',-1),(103814,45,21800,21861,'00:15:08.366','00:15:10.909','His name is Sam.',-1),(103815,45,21865,22000,'00:15:11.077','00:15:16.707','If you\'ve just tuned in, tonight\'s\ntopic is wishes and dreams.',-1),(103816,45,22004,22089,'00:15:16.874','00:15:20.377','We have a listener from Seattle.',-1),(103817,45,22093,22183,'00:15:20.545','00:15:24.298','Sam, this is Dr. Fieldstone\non Network America.',-1),(103818,45,22205,22313,'00:15:25.216','00:15:29.720','What are you selling?\nMicro-hibachis or knives?',-1),(103819,45,22317,22441,'00:15:29.887','00:15:35.058','Neither. I want to help.\nYour son asked me for advice.',-1),(103820,45,22445,22568,'00:15:35.226','00:15:40.355','- He wants to find you a new wife.\n- Who is this?',-1),(103821,45,22572,22707,'00:15:40.523','00:15:46.153','Dr. Fieldstone of Network America.\nYou are on the air.',-1),(103822,45,22711,22815,'00:15:46.321','00:15:50.657','- You called a radio station?\n- Sam, are you there?',-1),(103823,45,22819,22959,'00:15:50.825','00:15:56.663','- Yes.\n- You mourn your wife\'s death.',-1),(103824,45,22963,23048,'00:15:56.831','00:16:00.334','Your son is worried about you.',-1),(103825,45,23052,23162,'00:16:00.501','00:16:05.088','Get out here.\nI won\'t go through this alone.',-1),(103826,45,23166,23266,'00:16:05.256','00:16:09.426','It\'s hard for him to talk to you about this.',-1),(103827,45,23270,23384,'00:16:09.594','00:16:14.348','If we talk about it,\nmaybe Jonah will feel better.',-1),(103828,45,23388,23514,'00:16:14.515','00:16:19.770','- Talk to her. She\'s a doctor.\n- Her first name could be Doctor.',-1),(103829,45,23518,23686,'00:16:19.937','00:16:26.943','- Please.\n- Sam, it\'s his Christmas wish.',-1),(103830,45,23690,23755,'00:16:27.111','00:16:29.821','- Okay.\n- Good.',-1),(103831,45,23759,23885,'00:16:29.989','00:16:35.243','I know this is difficult.\nWhen did your wife die?',-1),(103832,45,23910,24043,'00:16:36.287','00:16:41.833','- About a year and a half ago.\n- Have you had any relationships?',-1),(103833,45,24064,24169,'00:16:42.669','00:16:47.047','- No.\n- Why not?',-1),(103834,45,24215,24309,'00:16:48.966','00:16:52.886','- Marcia... or Dr. Fieldstone?\n- Dr. Marcia.',-1),(103835,45,24313,24461,'00:16:53.054','00:16:59.226','- I don\'t mean to be rude...\n- I don\'t want to pry...',-1),(103836,45,24465,24642,'00:16:59.394','00:17:06.775','- Sure you do.\n- Go on, Sam. I\'m listening.',-1),(103837,45,24646,24772,'00:17:06.943','00:17:12.197','We had 