),(103857,45,27389,27462,'00:19:01.224','00:19:04.267','- Yes?\n- Tea, with the bag out.',-1),(103858,45,27466,27638,'00:19:04.435','00:19:11.608','- Maybe I\'ll just go up to Seattle.\n- Don\'t open his refrigerator.',-1),(103859,45,27642,27772,'00:19:11.776','00:19:17.197','Men don\'t cover food, and they\nleave it in there till it walks out.',-1),(103860,45,27776,27904,'00:19:17.365','00:19:22.702','I wouldn\'t kick him out of bed\nfor eating crackers. Sixty five cents.',-1),(103861,45,27908,28070,'00:19:22.870','00:19:29.584','We\'ll take a call before we talk to\nSleepless. Go ahead, Tennessee.',-1),(103862,45,28075,28186,'00:19:29.794','00:19:34.422','I\'d like to have his address.',-1),(103863,45,28190,28283,'00:19:34.590','00:19:38.468','Honey, get in line.',-1),(103864,45,28311,28438,'00:19:39.637','00:19:44.933','- If I could ask you a question...\n- Go ahead.',-1),(103865,45,28442,28541,'00:19:45.101','00:19:49.229','People who truly loved are likely to love again.',-1),(103866,45,28545,28697,'00:19:49.397','00:19:55.735','Sam, could you love anybody\nas much as you loved your wife?',-1),(103867,45,28724,28827,'00:19:56.863','00:20:01.157','Well, that\'s hard to imagine.',-1),(103868,45,28831,28906,'00:20:01.325','00:20:04.452','What are you going to do?',-1),(103869,45,28910,29084,'00:20:04.620','00:20:11.835','Get out of bed every morning\nand breathe in and out all day long.',-1),(103870,45,29088,29284,'00:20:12.003','00:20:20.176','And after a while I won\'t have to\nremind myself to do it.',-1),(103871,45,29338,29525,'00:20:22.430','00:20:30.228','And then after a while I won\'t\nremember how perfect things were.',-1),(103872,45,29530,29632,'00:20:30.438','00:20:34.691','Why was your wife so special?',-1),(103873,45,29636,29719,'00:20:34.859','00:20:38.320','How long is your program?',-1),(103874,45,29779,29885,'00:20:40.823','00:20:45.243','It was a million little things.',-1),(103875,45,29889,30001,'00:20:45.411','00:20:50.081','When you added them up, it meant\nwe were meant for each other.',-1),(103876,45,30005,30111,'00:20:50.249','00:20:54.628','I knew it the very first time I touched her.',-1),(103877,45,30115,30257,'00:20:54.795','00:21:00.717','It was like coming home,\nonly to no home I\'d ever known.',-1),(103878,45,30261,30340,'00:21:00.885','00:21:04.179','I was just taking her hand...',-1),(103879,45,30344,30455,'00:21:04.347','00:21:08.975','...to help her out of a car.\nAnd I knew it.',-1),(103880,45,30486,30595,'00:21:10.269','00:21:14.814','- It was like... magic.\n- Magic.',-1),(103881,45,30614,30751,'00:21:15.608','00:21:21.321','It\'s time to wrap it up.\nI\'m Dr. Marcia Fieldstone.',-1),(103882,45,30755,30859,'00:21:21.489','00:21:25.825','To all my listeners,\na magical and Merry Christmas.',-1),(103883,45,30863,31037,'00:21:25.993','00:21:33.249','And Sleepless in Seattle,\ncall and tell us how it\'s going.',-1),(103884,45,31042,31080,'00:21:33.417','00:21:35.000','You can count on it.',-1),(103885,45,31082,31136,'00:21:35.086','00:21:37.337','<font color=\"#7F7F7F\"> Ray Charles: <i>\"Over The Rainbow\"</i></font>',-1),(103886,45,31209,31434,'00:21:40.383','00:21:49.766',' <i>I know</i> \n <i>Somewhere over the rainbow</i> ',-1),(103887,45,31490,31611,'00:21:52.103','00:21:57.148',' <i>The blue birds fly</i> ',-1),(103888,45,31709,31763,'00:22:01.237','00:22:03.488',' <i>Birds fly</i> ',-1),(103889,45,31802,31874,'00:22:05.116','00:22:08.118',' <i>Over the rainbow</i> ',-1),(103890,45,31912,31984,'00:22:09.704','00:22:12.704',' <i>Why then, oh why can\'t I?</i> ',-1),(103891,45,32271,32388,'00:22:24.635','00:22:29.514','He sells the best soup ever and\nhe is the meanest man in America.',-1),(103892,45,32392,32504,'00:22:29.682','00:22:34.352','- I feel strongly about this.\n- Do it.',-1),(103893,45,32508,32570,'00:22:34.520','00:22:37.105','New Year\'s Eve. I won\'t write it.',-1),(103894,45,32574,32676,'00:22:37.273','00:22:41.526','Listen: \"Phone service\nwas tied up Christmas Eve...