.',-1),(104204,45,77980,78091,'00:54:09.204','00:54:13.833','I\'m an excellent third baseman,\nand let me tell you...',-1),(104205,45,78096,78212,'00:54:14.001','00:54:18.838','...Robinson was the best. We must\nagree on this. I\'m from Baltimore.\"',-1),(104206,45,78216,78342,'00:54:19.006','00:54:24.260','She likes Brooks Robinson.\nSo do you. It\'s a sign.',-1),(104207,45,78346,78457,'00:54:24.428','00:54:29.057','Come here. I\'ll show you a sign.',-1),(104208,45,78522,78673,'00:54:31.769','00:54:38.066','Where\'s Seattle?\nAnd Baltimore? Right there!',-1),(104209,45,78677,78803,'00:54:38.233','00:54:43.488','There\'s like 26 states between\nhere and there. That\'s a sign.',-1),(104210,45,78807,78928,'00:54:43.656','00:54:48.701','I\'m out of here. Goodbye.\nI love you.',-1),(104211,45,78998,79108,'00:54:51.622','00:54:56.167','Clarise, did you move your car?',-1),(104212,45,79289,79411,'00:55:03.717','00:55:08.805','- Thanks, Derrick. I\'ll have...\n- White wine spritzer?',-1),(104213,45,79415,79497,'00:55:08.973','00:55:12.392','- And you, sir?\n- I\'m fine.',-1),(104214,45,79501,79621,'00:55:12.559','00:55:17.563','- You look good.\n- So do you.',-1),(104215,45,79698,79773,'00:55:20.776','00:55:23.903','I thought you\'d never call me.',-1),(104216,45,79777,79856,'00:55:24.071','00:55:27.365','I really wanted you to.',-1),(104217,45,79860,80001,'00:55:27.533','00:55:33.413','Mr. Baldwin, phone call for you.',-1),(104218,45,80161,80288,'00:55:40.045','00:55:45.341','Dad, can we go to New York for Valentine\'s Day?',-1),(104219,45,80292,80436,'00:55:45.509','00:55:51.514','Annie Reed wants to meet us at the\ntop of the Empire State Building.',-1),(104220,45,80440,80608,'00:55:51.682','00:55:58.688','Jonah, have you fallen down?\nHas Clarise been strangled?',-1),(104221,45,80612,80686,'00:55:58.856','00:56:01.941','- No.\n- Is that the reason you\'re calling?',-1),(104222,45,80690,80818,'00:56:02.109','00:56:07.447','We can get cheap tickets from Jessica\'s parent