ood for a whole year!',-1),(104262,45,88116,88224,'01:01:11.501','01:01:16.005','It\'s good that your father\'s dating.\nIt\'s just hard on you.',-1),(104263,45,88228,88333,'01:01:16.173','01:01:20.551','You think you want it,\nbut when it happens, it scares you.',-1),(104264,45,88337,88468,'01:01:20.719','01:01:26.182','Shouldn\'t your father decide\nwhether someone is right for him?',-1),(104265,45,88472,88527,'01:01:26.350','01:01:28.642','He\'s not sane enough.',-1),(104266,45,88531,88672,'01:01:28.810','01:01:34.690','He\'s kissing her on the lips.\nMy dad\'s been captured by a \'ho!',-1),(104267,45,88676,88789,'01:01:34.858','01:01:39.570','Calm down. Tomorrow,\nwhen you\'re having breakfast...',-1),(104268,45,88793,88934,'01:01:39.738','01:01:45.618','...tell him how you feel.\nDon\'t keep it inside.',-1),(104269,45,89043,89154,'01:01:50.165','01:01:54.752','Miss Scarlett. In the broom closet.\nWith the radio.',-1),(104270,45,89158,89291,'01:01:54.920','01:02:00.466','Walter, you scared me.\nDon\'t ever do that again.',-1),(104271,45,89360,89474,'01:02:03.345','01:02:08.099','- I saw a black widow.\n- You scared me and Victoria.',-1),(104272,45,89478,89597,'01:02:08.266','01:02:13.229','- It was right there.\n- Next time I want you to say:',-1),(104273,45,89601,89704,'01:02:13.397','01:02:17.691','\"Dad, I see a poisonous insect.\"',-1),(104274,45,89708,89791,'01:02:17.859','01:02:21.320','And I\'ll deal with it. Don\'t scream.',-1),(104275,45,89795,89903,'01:02:21.488','01:02:25.991','Becky thought Rick was on the radio.',-1),(104276,45,89907,90049,'01:02:26.159','01:02:32.081','It turned out the guy lived\nin Duluth. Where\'s Duluth?',-1),(104277,45,90053,90161,'01:02:32.249','01:02:36.710','- That doesn\'t make any sense.\n- I know. No sense at all.',-1),(104278,45,90165,90302,'01:02:36.878','01:02:42.591','- Thank God my life is in place.\n- Duluth? That\'s in North Dakota.',-1),(104279,45,90646,90764,'01:02:56.940','01:03:01.861','- Great letter. Write t