ed\nthis movie too many times.',-1),(104356,45,104831,104990,'01:12:47.989','01:12:54.619','From the minute I heard that program\nI\'ve been a complete jerk.',-1),(104357,45,104994,105087,'01:12:54.787','01:12:58.665','- You\'re not a jerk.\n- Thank you. An idiot!',-1),(104358,45,105091,105230,'01:12:58.833','01:13:04.588','- You don\'t know who she was.\n- I have a picture of her.',-1),(104359,45,105234,105386,'01:13:04.756','01:13:11.094','The detective sent it to me.\nSee, that\'s what she looks like.',-1),(104360,45,105407,105530,'01:13:11.971','01:13:17.100','- It\'s her back.\n- It\'s her and he\'s crazy about her.',-1),(104361,45,105534,105652,'01:13:17.268','01:13:22.189','What\'s this?\nIt\'s from Seattle.',-1),(104362,45,105821,105886,'01:13:29.238','01:13:31.948','Becky.',-1),(104363,45,105912,105995,'01:13:33.034','01:13:36.495','So I mailed your letter.',-1),(104364,45,106012,106158,'01:13:37.205','01:13:43.251','\"Dear Annie. Thanks for your letter.\nYou sound neat.',-1),(104365,45,106237,106389,'01:13:46.547','01:13:52.886','We\'re excited about meeting you\nin New York and seeing if we are...',-1),(104366,45,106393,106472,'01:13:53.054','01:13:56.348','...M-F-E-O.',-1),(104367,45,106476,106577,'01:13:56.516','01:14:00.727','See you soon.\nSleepless in Seattle.\"',-1),(104368,45,106581,106648,'01:14:00.895','01:14:03.688','M-F-E-O?',-1),(104369,45,106721,106808,'01:14:06.734','01:14:10.362','Made for each other.',-1),(104370,45,106812,106888,'01:14:10.530','01:14:13.698','It\'s cute. Like a little clue.',-1),(104371,45,106998,107079,'01:14:18.287','01:14:21.665','So he can\'t write. Big deal.',-1),(104372,45,107083,107220,'01:14:21.833','01:14:27.504','Verbal ability is overrated in guys.\nOur need for it leads to trouble.',-1),(104373,45,107224,107345,'01:14:27.672','01:14:32.717','- I\'m going to run back to Walter.\n- And the letter?',-1),(104374,45,107349,107464,'01:14:32.885','01:14:37.681','It was written before I went\nout there. Before the \'ho.',-1),(104375,45,107527,107695,'01:14:40.309','01:14:47.315','But she didn\'t look like a \'ho.\nShe looked like one of our friends.',-1),(104376,45,107784,107923,'01:14:51.028','01:14:56.825','- You saw her in the airport too?\n- It was like I knew her.',-1),(104377,45,107927,108057,'01:14:56.993','01:15:02.414','- Like a dj-vu?\n- It was very dj-vu-ish.',-1),(104378,45,108061,108198,'01:15:02.582','01:15:08.253','- At least you\'re seeing people.\n- Well, only one.',-1),(104379,45,108202,108301,'01:15:08.421','01:15:12.549','- Victoria.\n- You don\'t like her?',-1),(104380,45,108305,108432,'01:15:12.717','01:15:18.013','- She laughs like a hyena.\n- Is this true?',-1),(104381,45,108436,108536,'01:15:18.181','01:15:22.350','Sort of. Tell them what you did.',-1),(104382,45,108540,108618,'01:15:22.518','01:15:25.770','Tell them about the radio show.',-1),(104383,45,108622,108712,'01:15:25.938','01:15:29.691','Christmas Eve he calls a radio show.',-1),(104384,45,108716,108881,'01:15:29.859','01:15:36.740','- And tells them I need a new wife.\n- That\'s so sweet.',-1),(104385,45,108885,108983,'01:15:36.908','01:15:40.994','Now he\'s obsessed with a woman who wrote me.',-1),(104386,45,108987,109049,'01:15:41.162','01:15:43.747','She wants to meet me on top of Empire State.',-1),(104387,45,109054,109112,'01:15:43.956','01:15:46.374','On Valentines Day.',-1),(104388,45,109117,109252,'01:15:46.542','01:15:52.172','It\'s like that movie.\nAn Affair to Remember.',-1),(104389,45,109256,109378,'01:15:52.340','01:15:57.427','Cary Grant and Deborah Kerr.\nIs that \"car\" or \"cur\"?',-1),(104390,45,109458,109596,'01:16:00.765','01:16:06.519','They were to meet at the Empire\nState, but she got hit by a taxi.',-1),(104391,45,109600,109717,'01:16:06.687','01:16:11.566','He waited and waited.\nAnd it was raining.',-1),(104392,45,109721,109876,'01:16:11.734','01:16:18.198','Then she\'s too proud to tell him that she\'s...',-1),(104393,45,109933,110074,'01:16:20.576','01:16:26.456'