:00.633','I cried over The Dirty Dozen.\nJim Brown throwing the grenades.',-1),(104412,45,112339,112474,'01:18:00.801','01:18:06.431','Richard Jaeckel and Lee Marvin\non top of a tank dressed like Nazis.',-1),(104413,45,112515,112683,'01:18:08.142','01:18:15.148','Trini Lopez... breaks his neck\nwhen they\'re parachuting.',-1),(104414,45,112687,112803,'01:18:15.316','01:18:20.153','Richard Jaeckel had on a shiny\nhelmet, because he was an MP.',-1),(104415,45,112807,112921,'01:18:20.321','01:18:25.075','Please, no more.\nGod, I love that movie.',-1),(104416,45,113123,113236,'01:18:33.459','01:18:38.171','- This is the best movie I ever saw.\n- What\'s so great about it?',-1),(104417,45,113240,113352,'01:18:38.339','01:18:43.009','- You have to find her.\n- How much would it cost to go?',-1),(104418,45,113356,113468,'01:18:43.177','01:18:47.847','Nobody knows.\nIt changes practically every day.',-1),(104419,45,113472,113551,'01:18:48.015','01:18:51.309','- How much money do you have?\n- 80 dollars.',-1),(104420,45,113555,113699,'01:18:51.477','01:18:57.482','- I have 42. That\'ll cover cabs.\n- How would I get there?',-1),(104421,45,113703,113841,'01:18:57.650','01:19:03.405','I have to drop these tickets off.\nCan you keep an eye on things?',-1),(104422,45,114089,114169,'01:19:13.749','01:19:17.043','- Window seat or aisle?\n- Window.',-1),(104423,45,114173,114288,'01:19:17.211','01:19:22.006','You want a fruit plate?\nI\'d rather die than eat airplane food.',-1),(104424,45,114292,114395,'01:19:22.174','01:19:26.469','I\'ll write you\'re 12.\nThat way you can fly unaccompanied.',-1),(104425,45,114399,114557,'01:19:26.637','01:19:33.226','- Who\'d believe I\'m 12?\n- They\'ll believe the computer.',-1),(104426,45,114561,114692,'01:19:33.394','01:19:38.857','I\'ll say you\'re short for your age,\nbut that they shouldn\'t mention it.',-1),(104427,45,114696,114750,'01:19:39.024','01:19:41.276','Great idea!',-1),(104428,45,114759,114787,'01:19:41.652','01:19:42.819','<fon