48.740','- <i>Come on. Go.</i>\n- <i>Jacob?</i>',-1),(104625,20,9812,9880,'00:06:48.860','00:06:51.700','Go, go!',-1),(104626,20,9882,9946,'00:06:51.780','00:06:54.450','<i>Come on, come on!</i>',-1),(104627,20,9948,10004,'00:06:54.530','00:06:56.870','- Yes!\n- Jacob, dinner.',-1),(104628,20,10170,10199,'00:07:03.780','00:07:04.960','Have you finished your homework?',-1),(104629,20,10202,10276,'00:07:05.090','00:07:08.170','- Yes. You just killed me.\n- Good. Now that you\'re dead,',-1),(104630,20,10278,10335,'00:07:08.260','00:07:10.630','you can shut that off\nand come down for dinner.',-1),(104631,20,10338,10402,'00:07:10.760','00:07:13.430','- Did you order pepperoni tonight?\n- Nope. Are these clean?',-1),(104632,20,10405,10456,'00:07:13.550','00:07:15.680','- <i>Yeah.</i>\n- We\'ve had pizza twice this week,',-1),(104633,20,10458,10503,'00:07:15.760','00:07:17.640','so I made you a proper meal tonight...',-1),(104634,20,10506,10574,'00:07:17.770','00:07:20.600','- with vegetables.\n- <i>Vegetables?</i>',-1),(104635,20,10600,10637,'00:07:21.690','00:07:23.230','Stop being such a stepmom.',-1),(104636,20,10701,10749,'00:07:25.900','00:07:27.900','Where\'d you get this?',-1),(104637,20,10787,10825,'00:07:29.490','00:07:31.070','It was Dad\'s.',-1),(104638,20,10827,10892,'00:07:31.150','00:07:33.860','Yeah, I know. Where was it?',-1),(104639,20,10894,11009,'00:07:33.950','00:07:38.740','I found it in the downstairs bathroom.\nIt\'s mine now.',-1),(104640,20,11058,11087,'00:07:40.750','00:07:41.960','Okay.',-1),(104641,20,11089,11130,'00:07:42.080','00:07:43.790','Okay.',-1),(104642,20,11134,11202,'00:07:43.920','00:07:46.790','- Come on. I said please shut that off.\n- <i>You didn\'t say \"please.\"</i>',-1),(104643,20,11205,11248,'00:07:46.880','00:07:48.670','- Jacob.\n- Helen.',-1),(104644,20,11437,11483,'00:07:56.550','00:07:58.470','- Hello?\n- <i>Helen Benson?</i>',-1),(104645,20,11485,11539,'00:07:58.560','00:08:00.810','- Yes.\n- <i>Dr. Helen Benson?</i>'