g with us, Dr. Benson.\n- Helen?',-1),(104666,20,13077,13138,'00:09:04.910','00:09:07.420','Jacob, grab your coat.\nYou\'re gonna stay at Isabel\'s.',-1),(104667,20,13206,13252,'00:09:10.290','00:09:12.170','<i>Attention, Bravo.\nPrepare to move out. Over.</i>',-1),(104668,20,13288,13328,'00:09:13.700','00:09:15.340','It\'s gonna be okay.',-1),(104669,20,13330,13379,'00:09:15.420','00:09:17.470','Dr. Benson, there isn\'t much time.',-1),(104670,20,13464,13546,'00:09:21.010','00:09:24.430','Okay, we\'ve got her. Let\'s go.',-1),(104671,20,14005,14070,'00:09:43.580','00:09:46.250','Two stoplights down, then left,\nthere\'s an on-ramp for the highway.',-1),(104672,20,14072,14109,'00:09:46.370','00:09:47.910','- Do you see it?\n- This must be a mistake.',-1),(104673,20,14112,14189,'00:09:48.000','00:09:51.210','Helen Benson.\nSocial security number: 51-48-7843?',-1),(104674,20,14192,14230,'00:09:51.340','00:09:52.920','- <i>Yeah.</i>\n- It\'s no mistake.',-1),(104675,20,14232,14278,'00:09:53.000','00:09:54.920','- What is this about?\n- Everything will be explained.',-1),(104676,20,14281,14358,'00:09:55.050','00:09:58.260','- Stop the car. Can you stop the car, please?\n- Ma\'am--',-1),(104677,20,14360,14410,'00:09:58.340','00:10:00.430','<i>I am not under arrest. You can\'t do this.</i>',-1),(104678,20,14413,14478,'00:10:00.550','00:10:03.260','- This is a matter of national security. You\'re just gonna--\n- National security?',-1),(104679,20,14480,14526,'00:10:03.350','00:10:05.270','That just means whatever you want it to mean.',-1),(104680,20,14528,14581,'00:10:05.350','00:10:07.560','I\'m just asking you to tell me\nwhy I\'m needed,',-1),(104681,20,14584,14650,'00:10:07.690','00:10:10.440','- or to let me go.\n- I can\'t tell you why you\'re needed, because I don\'t know.',-1),(104682,20,14653,14719,'00:10:10.560','00:10:13.320','- But I know they need you, and I know it\'s urgent.\n- How do you know that?',-1),(104683,20,14858,14906,'00:10:19.110','00:10:21.110','Where are all the cars?',-1),(104684,20,14909,14973,'00:10:21.240','00:10:23.910','- They shut down the highway.\n- They shut it down?',-1),(104685,20,14976,15036,'00:10:24.040','00:10:26.540','- For what?\n- For us.',-1),(104686,20,15985,16040,'00:11:06.080','00:11:08.370','I was driving up my driveway--',-1),(104687,20,16042,16098,'00:11:08.450','00:11:10.790','<i>I was on the computer--</i>',-1),(104688,20,16139,16221,'00:11:12.460','00:11:15.880','- Hi. I\'m Yusef.\n- Helen.',-1),(104689,20,16223,16299,'00:11:15.960','00:11:19.130','Helen, do you have any idea\nwhy this is happening to us?',-1),(104690,20,16302,16348,'00:11:19.260','00:11:21.170','- No.\n- <i>Well, think.</i>',-1),(104691,20,16350,16416,'00:11:21.260','00:11:24.010','- What do we have in common?\n- What do you do for a living, Yusef?',-1),(104692,20,16418,16457,'00:11:24.100','00:11:25.710','- I\'m a nuclear physicist.\n- I\'m an astronomer.',-1),(104693,20,16457,16507,'00:11:25.740','00:11:27.810','- Geologist.\n- I\'m an astrobiologist.',-1),(104694,20,16508,16531,'00:11:27.840','00:11:28.820','Fossil record study?',-1),(104695,20,16533,16601,'00:11:28.890','00:11:31.730','No. Microbiology.\nTheories of life beyond Earth.',-1),(104696,20,16604,16661,'00:11:31.850','00:11:34.230','- All right, so we\'re all scientists.\n- No, not me.',-1),(104697,20,16663,16731,'00:11:34.310','00:11:37.150','- I\'m a civil engineer.\n- <i>Put it all together, and what do you get?</i>',-1),(104698,20,16733,16788,'00:11:37.230','00:11:39.530','I\'ve participated in government mobilizations\nlike this before.',-1),(104699,20,16790,16840,'00:11:39.610','00:11:41.700','War games in preparations for certain scenarios.',-1),(104700,20,16843,16898,'00:11:41.820','00:11:44.110','- Is that what you think this is?\n- No.',-1),(104701,20,16900,16967,'00:11:44.200','00:11:46.990','Whatever it is, it\'s not a game.',-1),(104702,20,17263,17355,'00:11:59.300','00:12:03.130','<i>No! Keep those vehicles moving! Let\'s go!</i>',-1),(104703,20,17835,17881,'00:12:23.150','00:12:25.070','<i>Your attention, please!</i>',-1),(104704,20,17883,17962,'00:12:25.160','00:12:28.450','<i>Make your way directly across the courtyard\nto the main barracks.</i>',-1),(104705,20,17964,18032,'00:12:28.530','00:12:31.370','<i>Leave all your cell phones\nand cameras here.</i>',-1),(104706,20,18034,18132,'00:12:31.450','00:12:35.500','I repeat: cell phones and cameras\nare not allowed inside.',-1),(104707,20,18133,18184,'00:12:35.580','00:12:37.670','Leave any cell phones and cameras here.',-1),(104708,20,18186,18244,'00:12:37.750','00:12:40.170','<i>Helen!\nWill you bring her up?</i>',-1),(104709,20,18246,18317,'00:12:40.250','00:12:43.210','<i>Ladies and gentlemen, you need to give up\nyour cell phones and your cameras.</i>',-1),(104710,20,18320,18366,'00:12:43.340','00:12:45.260','- <i>Your attention, please!</i>\n- Thank you.',-1),(104711,20,18368,18429,'00:12:45.340','00:12:47.890','<i>Make your way directly across the courtyard\nto the main barracks.</i>',-1),(104712,20,18432,18465,'00:12:48.010','00:12:49.390','- <i>Helen.</i>\n- Hi, Michael.',-1),(104713,20,18468,18514,'00:12:49.510','00:12:51.430','- Been a long time.\n- Are you behind all this?',-1),(104714,20,18516,18575,'00:12:51.520','00:12:53.980','- Yes. I\'m glad you came.\n- It\'s not like I had a choice.',-1),(104715,20,18577,18653,'00:12:54.060','00:12:57.230','Sorry about that.\nI had you put on the vital list.',-1),(104716,20,18656,18722,'00:12:57.350','00:13:00.110','- I thought it was important to have you a part of this team.\n- Why?',-1),(104717,20,18724,18787,'00:13:00.190','00:13:02.820','I\'ve been keeping up with the work\nthat you\'ve been doing with Professor Barnhardt.',-1),(104718,20,18789,18835,'00:13:02.900','00:13:04.820','What does it have to do with this?',-1),(104719,20,18837,18884,'00:13:04.900','00:13:06.860','I\'ll have to crash-brief you\nin the conference room.',-1),(104720,20,18996,19064,'00:13:11.540','00:13:14.370','Object 07-493...',-1),(104721,20,19067,19169,'00:13:14.460','00:13:18.710','<i>was first spotted just beyond Jupiter\'s orbit\nby the Spaceguard Program.</i>',-1),(104722,20,19170,19274,'00:13:18.790','00:13:23.090','<i>It was notable for the fact\nthat it was not moving in an asteroidal ellipse,</i>',-1),(104723,20,19276,19347,'00:13:23.170','00:13:26.130','but rather, it had a hyperbolic orbit...',-1),(104724,20,19349,19431,'00:13:26.220','00:13:29.640','and was shooting through our solar system.',-1),(104725,20,19433,19573,'00:13:29.720','00:13:35.560','The object is moving at speeds of up to\nthree times 10 to the seventh meters per second.',-1),(104726,20,19575,19699,'00:13:35.640','00:13:40.810','<i>At first, it was projected to pass\nmillions of miles outside of Earth\'s orbit.</i>',-1),(104727,20,19701,19747,'00:13:40.900','00:13:42.820','However, we soon discovered that...',-1),(104728,20,19749,19833,'00:13:42.900','00:13:46.400','the object was not following\na gravitationally free fall trajectory.',-1),(104729,20,19835,19900,'00:13:46.490','00:13:49.200','As such,',-1),(104730,20,19902,19978,'00:13:49.280','00:13:52.450','its path was recalculated.',-1),(104731,20,20082,20164,'00:13:56.750','00:14:00.170','It was at this time a crisis response team\nwas activated...',-1),(104732,20,20166,20222,'00:14:00.250','00:14:02.590','and everything you see around you\nwas set in motion.',-1),(104733,20,20333,20382,'00:14:07.220','00:14:09.260','Can we launch a missile to intercept it?',-1),(104734,20,20384,20458,'00:14:09.340','00:14:12.430','<i>The military\'s attempting to do just that.\nIn fact, they may launch several.</i>',-1),(104735,20,20460,20540,'00:14:12.510','00:14:15.850','But given the speed at which\nthis object is moving,',-1),(104736,20,20542,20629,'00:14:15.930','00:14:19.560','our chances of success are slim at best.',-1),(104737,20,20632,20719,'00:14:19.690','00:14:23.310','- Why don\'t they evacuate the area?\n- <i>We simply do not have enough time.</i>',-1),(104738,20,20721,20801,'00:14:23.400','00:14:26.730','The affected area contains\nsome eight million inhabitants.',-1),(104739,20,20803,20882,'00:14:26.820','00:14:30.110','The best we can do is to plan for the aftermath.',-1),(104740,20,20884,20926,'00:14:30.200','00:14:31.950','How long do we have?',-1),(104741,20,21036,21072,'00:14:36.500','00:14:38.000','Seventy-eight minutes.',-1),(104742,20,21156,21228,'00:14:41.540','00:14:44.540','<i>Hey, what did the cops want anyway?</i>',-1),(104743,20,21231,21306,'00:14:44.630','00:14:47.760','Well, there\'s gonna be...',-1),(104744,20,21308,21383,'00:14:47.840','00:14:50.970','a big storm tonight.',-1),(104745,20,21385,21431,'00:14:51.050','00:14:52.970','And...',-1),(104746,20,21433,21484,'00:14:53.050','00:14:55.180','they needed some scientists to help out.',-1),(104747,20,21486,21537,'00:14:55.260','00:14:57.390','You know with...',-1),(104748,20,21539,21586,'00:14:57.470','00:14:59.430','planning stuff.',-1),(104749,20,21588,21635,'00:14:59.520','00:15:01.480','So, um,',-1),(104750,20,21679,21751,'00:15:03.310','00:15:06.320','pretty soon, you\'re all gonna go down\nto the basement, okay?',-1),(104751,20,21754,21833,'00:15:06.440','00:15:09.740','- I already told Isabel.\n- <i>I haven\'t seen anything on TV about--</i>',-1),(104752,20,21835,21891,'00:15:09.820','00:15:12.160','Jacob, just--',-1),(104753,20,21893,21965,'00:15:12.240','00:15:15.240','just do it, all right?',-1),(104754,20,21967,22015,'00:15:15.330','00:15:17.330','<i>All right. I should go.</i>',-1),(104755,20,22017,22063,'00:15:17.410','00:15:19.330','Wait. Um, can we talk...',-1),(104756,20,22065,22133,'00:15:19.410','00:15:22.210','just a little bit longer?',-1),(104757,20,22134,22206,'00:15:22.290','00:15:25.250','<i>We\'re having dinner now.\nI really should go.</i>',-1),(104758,20,22238,22300,'00:15:26.590','00:15:29.170','You know, I love you very much.',-1),(104759,20,22302,22358,'00:15:29.260','00:15:31.590','<i>Okay. Bye, Helen.</i>',-1),(104760,20,22551,22599,'00:15:39.640','00:15:41.640','Is that a cell phone?',-1),(104761,20,22678,22724,'00:15:44.940','00:15:46.860','Can I borrow it?',-1),(104762,20,22936,23009,'00:15:55.700','00:15:58.740','What are the odds of an asteroid\nmaking impact on Manhattan?',-1),(104763,20,23011,23091,'00:15:58.830','00:16:02.160','- Astronomical. Plus, there\'s no light signature.\n- Then it can\'t be an asteroid.',-1),(104764,20,23094,23160,'00:16:02.290','00:16:05.040','- A primordial black hole, perhaps.\n- You know what that would mean?',-1),(104765,20,23163,23211,'00:16:05.130','00:16:07.130','Whatever it is, if this object is moving...',-1),(104766,20,23213,23298,'00:16:07.210','00:16:10.760','at three times 10 to the seventh meters per second,\nthere will be no aftermath.',-1),(104767,20,23300,23435,'00:16:10.840','00:16:16.470','If they can\'t stop it before it hits,\nthere will be nothing left but dust.',-1),(104768,20,23437,23523,'00:16:16.550','00:16:20.140','It will sterilize the Earth.\nThis is all theater.',-1),(104769,20,23525,23576,'00:16:20.220','00:16:22.350','They\'re sayin\' we lost launch capabilities.',-1),(104770,20,23578,23633,'00:16:22.430','00:16:24.730','<i>What does that even mean?</i>',-1),(104771,20,23635,23699,'00:16:24.810','00:16:27.480','- The missile\'s disabled.\n- Disabled by what?',-1),(104772,20,23702,23750,'00:16:27.610','00:16:29.610','- They don\'t know.\n- <i>But they can restore it, right?</i>',-1),(104773,20,23752,23806,'00:16:29.690','00:16:31.940','There\'s a fallback! They have to launch!',-1),(104774,20,24002,24045,'00:16:40.120','00:16:41.910','Object impact in seven.',-1),(104775,20,24048,24093,'00:16:42.040','00:16:43.910','- <i>Our Father, who art in heaven, hallowed be thy name.</i>\n- Six. Five.',-1),(104776,20,24096,24131,'00:16:44.040','00:16:45.460','- Thy kingdom come, thy will be done,\n- <i>Four.</i>',-1),(104777,20,24132,24191,'00:16:45.540','00:16:47.960','- <i>on Earth as it is in heaven.</i>\n- <i>Three. Two.</i>',-1),(104778,20,24194,24254,'00:16:48.090','00:16:50.590','<i>One.</i>',-1),(104779,20,24392,24442,'00:16:56.340','00:16:58.430','Where is it?',-1),(104780,20,24445,24488,'00:16:58.550','00:17:00.350','- Could they have made a mistake?\n- <i>Wait!</i>',-1),(104781,20,24490,24580,'00:17:00.430','00:17:04.180','Roger that.\nThey\'re saying the object\'s still on its approach.',-1),(104782,20,24582,24632,'00:17:04.270','00:17:06.350','Well, then where is it?',-1),(104783,20,24635,24710,'00:17:06.480','00:17:09.610','- <i>It\'s slowing down.</i>\n- I see it.',-1),(104784,20,27803,27908,'00:19:18.490','00:19:22.860','Radiation levels are slightly elevated,\nbut it\'s not dangerous.',-1),(104785,20,27911,27984,'00:19:22.990','00:19:26.030','I\'m getting a lot of electrostatic interference.',-1),(104786,20,27986,28030,'00:19:26.120','00:19:27.950','Yeah, me too.',-1),(104787,20,28080,28132,'00:19:30.040','00:19:32.170','Did you feel that?',-1),(104788,20,28159,28198,'00:19:33.330','00:19:34.920','Feel what?',-1),(104789,20,28270,28318,'00:19:37.920','00:19:39.920','I feel it.',-1),(104790,20,28437,28486,'00:19:44.890','00:19:46.930','It\'s close.',-1),(104791,20,30054,30109,'00:20:52.250','00:20:54.580','Checkmate 0-6. Who has tactical command here?',-1),(104792,20,30112,30192,'00:20:54.670','00:20:58.040','This is 29-17. I need to know\nwho has jurisdiction on this site.',-1),(104793,20,31264,31323,'00:21:42.670','00:21:45.130','<i>Checkmate 0-3, this is Gator 2-3.</i>',-1),(104794,20,31325,31384,'00:21:45.220','00:21:47.680','<i>We\'re blind here.</i>',-1),(104795,20,31386,31464,'00:21:47.760','00:21:51.010','<i>Checkmate 0-6, actual.\nDo you copy? Over.</i>',-1),(104796,20,31510,31567,'00:21:52.930','00:21:55.310','<i>What the hell is that thing?</i>',-1),(104797,20,31570,31675,'00:21:55.430','00:21:59.810','<i>I need the rules of engagement now!</i>',-1),(104798,20,31677,31774,'00:21:59.900','00:22:03.940','<i>Target is advancing.\nRepeat: Target is advancing.</i>',-1),(104799,20,31929,31996,'00:22:10.410','00:22:13.200','<i>Sniper team leaders, come back.</i>',-1),(104800,20,32108,32195,'00:22:17.870','00:22:21.460','- <i>Do not fire!</i>\n- <i>It\'s coming right at us!</i>',-1),(104801,20,32198,32284,'00:22:21.590','00:22:25.170','- <i>Hold your fire! Hold your fire!</i>\n- <i>Do we engage?</i>',-1),(104802,20,32287,32346,'00:22:25.300','00:22:27.760','- <i>Do not fire!</i>\n- <i>Fire! Fire!</i>',-1),(104803,20,32435,32518,'00:22:31.470','00:22:34.930','- Cease fire!\n- All stations, cease fire! Cease fire!',-1),(104804,20,32520,32563,'00:22:35.020','00:22:36.810','Don\'t shoot! Do not shoot!',-1),(104805,20,32754,32809,'00:22:44.780','00:22:47.070','We need a medic!',-1),(104806,20,34052,34131,'00:23:38.870','00:23:42.160','<i>Klaatu, barada, nikto.</i>',-1),(104807,20,34868,34944,'00:24:12.860','00:24:16.030','We need that D.N.A. swab.\nD.N.A. swab now!',-1),(104808,20,34947,34996,'00:24:16.160','00:24:18.200','- It\'s soaking through.\n- <i>What\'s the O2, stat?</i>',-1),(104809,20,34998,35061,'00:24:18.290','00:24:20.910','Get me the O2, stat!',-1),(104810,20,35093,35138,'00:24:22.210','00:24:24.120','Go. No one else.',-1),(104811,20,35267,35321,'00:24:29.460','00:24:31.710','Let\'s go!',-1),(104812,20,35407,35478,'00:24:35.300','00:24:38.260','<i>What am I supposed to do now?\nDo I start an I.V.?</i>',-1),(104813,20,35480,35550,'00:24:38.350','00:24:41.270','No. We don\'t know its physiology.\nFor all we know, the fluids may kill it.',-1),(104814,20,35552,35632,'00:24:41.350','00:24:44.690','- <i>What do I do? What do I do?</i>\n- Its blood is red. It must have hemoglobin.',-1),(104815,20,35635,35703,'00:24:44.810','00:24:47.650','- Okay, she\'s right. Start the drip.\n- Okay. I can\'t find a vein.',-1),(104816,20,35705,35762,'00:24:47.730','00:24:50.110','- It doesn\'t have any veins.\n- Look for a central line site then.',-1),(104817,20,35764,35814,'00:24:50.190','00:24:52.280','<i>It\'s going into cardiac arrest. Defib?</i>',-1),(104818,20,35816,35887,'00:24:52.360','00:24:55.320','- Yeah. Get in there now. Go! Go!\n- Clear!',-1),(104819,20,35938,35984,'00:24:57.450','00:24:59.370','- <i>Are you okay?</i>\n- The monitor shorted out.',-1),(104820,20,35986,36041,'00:24:59.450','00:25:01.740','Heart rate is stabilizing. It\'s stabilizing.',-1),(104821,20,36043,36104,'00:25:01.830','00:25:04.370','<i>What now? What now?</i>',-1),(104822,20,36159,36210,'00:25:06.630','00:25:08.750','Do you have a surgeon?',-1),(104823,20,36257,36372,'00:25:10.710','00:25:15.510','Normally for a gunshot,\nwe\'d be using a general anesthetic.',-1),(104824,20,36374,36464,'00:25:15.590','00:25:19.350','But as we don\'t know\nhow the patient will react,',-1),(104825,20,36466,36585,'00:25:19.430','00:25:24.390','I have opted for a local.',-1),(104826,20,36627,36714,'00:25:26.140','00:25:29.770','I\'m making the first incision... now.',-1),(104827,20,36808,36863,'00:25:33.690','00:25:35.990','No explosions.',-1),(104828,20,36865,36939,'00:25:36.070','00:25:39.160','<i>So far, so good.</i>',-1),(104829,20,36941,36993,'00:25:39.240','00:25:41.410','Pale flesh.',-1),(104830,20,36995,37041,'00:25:41.490','00:25:43.410','The texture--',-1),(104831,20,37044,37116,'00:25:43.500','00:25:46.540','Something akin to--\nWhat?',-1),(104832,20,37118,37185,'00:25:46.620','00:25:49.380','Whale blubber.',-1),(104833,20,37187,37233,'00:25:49.460','00:25:51.380','I\'m taking a specimen now.',-1),(104834,20,37235,37357,'00:25:51.460','00:25:56.550','Let\'s pack that on ice and chopper it\nto a genomics lab for D.N.A. mapping.',-1),(104835,20,37359,37405,'00:25:56.630','00:25:58.550','I\'d like a sample of that as well.',-1),(104836,20,37407,37468,'00:25:58.640','00:26:01.180','<i>I am entering the wound.</i>',-1),(104837,20,37498,37566,'00:26:02.430','00:26:05.270','And--',-1),(104838,20,37568,37616,'00:26:05.350','00:26:07.350','My God.',-1),(104839,20,37649,37701,'00:26:08.730','00:26:10.900','What is this? I\'m-I\'m sorry.',-1),(104840,20,37703,37759,'00:26:10.980','00:26:13.320','I\'m-I\'m a little taken aback.',-1),(104841,20,37762,37808,'00:26:13.440','00:26:15.360','- <i>What\'s wrong?</i>\n- <i>Nothing\'s wrong.</i>',-1),(104842,20,37810,37898,'00:26:15.440','00:26:19.110','That\'s the thing. It\'s all so familiar.',-1),(104843,20,37900,37964,'00:26:19.200','00:26:21.870','The outer layer of the flesh\nis exotic, it\'s strange,',-1),(104844,20,37966,38026,'00:26:21.950','00:26:24.450','<i>but as I go deeper,</i>',-1),(104845,20,38028,38095,'00:26:24.540','00:26:27.330','<i>there\'s muscle, vein, nerve, bone.</i>',-1),(104846,20,38122,38167,'00:26:28.420','00:26:30.330','<i>I\'m extracting...</i>',-1),(104847,20,38170,38220,'00:26:30.420','00:26:32.500','the bullet.',-1),(104848,20,38355,38397,'00:26:38.130','00:26:39.880','This gray flesh,',-1),(104849,20,38399,38508,'00:26:39.970','00:26:44.510','it seems to be just falling away.',-1),(104850,20,38510,38605,'00:26:44.600','00:26:48.560','It\'s-- It\'s removing itself.',-1),(104851,20,38639,38704,'00:26:49.980','00:26:52.690','I think I need to keep extracting it.',-1),(104852,20,38730,38788,'00:26:53.770','00:26:56.190','<i>Yes. Continue.</i>',-1),(104853,20,38813,38868,'00:26:57.240','00:26:59.530','Can you explain any of this?',-1),(104854,20,40176,40257,'00:27:54.000','00:27:57.380','It\'s dreaming.',-1),(104855,20,40259,40305,'00:27:57.460','00:27:59.380','Any signs of neural activity?',-1),(104856,20,40307,40397,'00:27:59.460','00:28:03.220','<i>It lit up the F.M.R.I.\nlike Times Square.</i>',-1),(104857,20,40475,40541,'00:28:06.470','00:28:09.220','Get help.',-1),(104858,20,40543,40615,'00:28:09.310','00:28:12.310','Code white. Subject is conscious.',-1),(104859,20,40651,40699,'00:28:13.810','00:28:15.810','Help!',-1),(104860,20,40853,40920,'00:28:22.240','00:28:25.030','It\'s looking at you.\nTry saying something to it.',-1),(104861,20,40923,41006,'00:28:25.160','00:28:28.620','My name is Dr. Helen Benson.',-1),(104862,20,41032,41078,'00:28:29.700','00:28:31.620','We\'re trying to help you.',-1),(104863,20,41081,41138,'00:28:31.710','00:28:34.120','You have nothing to fear from us.',-1),(104864,20,41141,41236,'00:28:34.210','00:28:38.170','Help you. Nothing to fear.',-1),(104865,20,41290,41360,'00:28:40.420','00:28:43.340','<i>Global markets are panicked\nin early trading this morning...</i>',-1),(104866,20,41362,41419,'00:28:43.430','00:28:45.800','<i>in response to the crisis in Central Park.</i>',-1),(104867,20,41421,41516,'00:28:45.890','00:28:49.850','<i>Trading has been halted on the New York Stock Exchange,\nthe Nikkei and the Hang Seng...</i>',-1),(104868,20,41518,41569,'00:28:49.930','00:28:52.060','<i>as Manhattan prepares for a massive evacuation.</i>',-1),(104869,20,41571,41691,'00:28:52.140','00:28:57.150','<i>In other cities around the world,\npeople are voluntarily evacuating population centers,</i>',-1),(104870,20,41693,41741,'00:28:57.230','00:28:59.230','<i>fearing that the sphere in Central Park...</i>',-1),(104871,20,41743,41793,'00:28:59.320','00:29:01.400','<i>may be the vanguard\nof an impending alien invasion.</i>',-1),(104872,20,41795,41841,'00:29:01.480','00:29:03.400','<i>The president and the vice president...</i>',-1),(104873,20,41843,41895,'00:29:03.490','00:29:05.650','<i>have been taken to separate\nand secure locations.</i>',-1),(104874,20,41897,41951,'00:29:05.740','00:29:07.990','Until this situation has some kind of resolve,',-1),(104875,20,41953,42003,'00:29:08.070','00:29:10.160','I am the eyes and the ears of the presidency.',-1),(104876,20,42029,42092,'00:29:11.240','00:29:13.870','- So, what do we know?\n- Madam Secretary,',-1),(104877,20,42095,42163,'00:29:13.960','00:29:16.830','we lost contact with one of our D.S.C.S.-3\nlistening satellites...',-1),(104878,20,42167,42231,'00:29:16.960','00:29:19.630','- orbiting Earth.\n- What is that image?',-1),(104879,20,42234,42316,'00:29:19.750','00:29:23.170','- Are you saying the sphere in Central Park isn\'t the only one?\n- In fact, we have intelligence...',-1),(104880,20,42318,42384,'00:29:23.260','00:29:26.010','that smaller spheres have landed\nat other locations around the world.',-1),(104881,20,42386,42438,'00:29:26.090','00:29:28.260','Do we have briefings on that?\nAnd where are these spheres right now?',-1),(104882,20,42440,42523,'00:29:28.340','00:29:31.810','- How is that even possible?\n- I think we\'re asking the wrong questions.',-1),(104883,20,42525,42581,'00:29:31.890','00:29:34.220','What questions should we be asking?',-1),(104884,20,42583,42646,'00:29:34.310','00:29:36.940','Well, let\'s start with this.\nWhere is our satellite?',-1),(104885,20,42649,42717,'00:29:37.060','00:29:39.900','- We lost contact with it.\n- In the scheme of things,',-1),(104886,20,42719,42767,'00:29:39.980','00:29:41.980','the loss of one satellite\nisn\'t necessarily our concern.',-1),(104887,20,42769,42850,'00:29:42.070','00:29:45.440','D.S.C.S.-3 stands for\nDefense Systems Communications Satellite.',-1),(104888,20,42852,42906,'00:29:45.530','00:29:47.780','Remember what it communicates with?',-1),(104889,20,42908,42975,'00:29:47.860','00:29:50.660','They were able to access our defense mainframe\nvia that satellite.',-1),(104890,20,42977,43065,'00:29:50.740','00:29:54.410','That\'s how they temporarily shut down\nour missile defenses and entered our airspace.',-1),(104891,20,43068,43134,'00:29:54.540','00:29:57.250','- <i>We have changed all the codes.</i>\n- And on top of that,',-1),(104892,20,43135,43216,'00:29:57.330','00:30:00.670','there is a vast amount of vital intelligence\non that mainframe.',-1),(104893,20,43218,43263,'00:30:00.750','00:30:02.630','They know everything about us now.',-1),(104894,20,43266,43343,'00:30:02.750','00:30:05.960','- And we know nothing about them.\n- Almost nothing.',-1),(104895,20,43345,43399,'00:30:06.050','00:30:08.300','The fact that they chose\nto disable our defenses tells us...',-1),(104896,20,43401,43456,'00:30:08.380','00:30:10.680','something about their intentions.',-1),(104897,20,43549,43612,'00:30:14.560','00:30:17.180','Madam Secretary,\nwe brought in several specialists...',-1),(104898,20,43614,43670,'00:30:17.270','00:30:19.600','to analyze the tissue samples\nwe harvested from the being.',-1),(104899,20,43672,43720,'00:30:19.690','00:30:21.690','This is our chief geneticist,\nDr. Hideo Ikegawa.',-1),(104900,20,43722,43796,'00:30:21.770','00:30:24.860','This is our chief astrobiologist,\nDr. Helen Benson.',-1),(104901,20,43798,43855,'00:30:24.940','00:30:27.320','- Hello.\n- <i>Doctor?</i>',-1),(104902,20,43857,43909,'00:30:27.400','00:30:29.570','The being is in a nascent state.',-1),(104903,20,43911,44015,'00:30:29.660','00:30:33.990','The D.N.A. samples we\'ve taken seem to represent\nthree distinct life forms.',-1),(104904,20,44017,44063,'00:30:34.080','00:30:35.990','Three different D.N.A. types?',-1),(104905,20,44065,44129,'00:30:36.080','00:30:38.710','<i>Yes, including the being\'s brain.</i>',-1),(104906,20,44130,44208,'00:30:38.790','00:30:42.040','The body tissue is human,\nas far as we can tell.',-1),(104907,20,44211,44296,'00:30:42.130','00:30:45.670','The gray flesh encasing it\nis organic material.',-1),(104908,20,44298,44347,'00:30:45.760','00:30:47.800','Some kind of bioengineered space suit.',-1),(104909,20,44349,44432,'00:30:47.880','00:30:51.340','What it resembles, oddly enough,\nis placental tissue.',-1),(104910,20,44434,44512,'00:30:51.430','00:30:54.680','Which makes sense, given that placenta\'s\na life-support system.',-1),(104911,20,44514,44569,'00:30:54.760','00:30:57.060','And that basically, in order to survive\nin our environment,',-1),(104912,20,44571,44618,'00:30:57.140','00:30:59.100','the being had to be born here...',-1),(104913,20,44620,44676,'00:30:59.190','00:31:01.520','in its human form.',-1),(104914,20,44678,44771,'00:31:01.600','00:31:05.480','They must\'ve come here in the past\nand obtained a D.N.A. sample from a human subject.',-1),(104915,20,44773,44821,'00:31:05.570','00:31:07.570','Now, since that birth,',-1),(104916,20,44823,44887,'00:31:07.650','00:31:10.320','the being has grown exponentially.',-1),(104917,20,44889,44955,'00:31:10.410','00:31:13.160','This is one hour after surgery.',-1),(104918,20,44957,44998,'00:31:13.240','00:31:14.950','<i>Three hours.</i>',-1),(104919,20,45048,45097,'00:31:17.000','00:31:19.080','- Six hours.\n- How much can you tell us about it...',-1),(104920,20,45101,45186,'00:31:19.210','00:31:22.790','- by decoding its D.N.A.?\n- <i>Um, you don\'t understand.</i>',-1),(104921,20,45189,45252,'00:31:22.880','00:31:25.500','These are the Dead Sea Scrolls.\nGeneticists...',-1),(104922,20,45255,45323,'00:31:25.630','00:31:28.460','- are gonna be studying this code for generations.\n- No, they aren\'t.',-1),(104923,20,45325,45441,'00:31:28.550','00:31:33.390','This code is the property of the U.S. government.\nIts very existence is classified.',-1),(104924,20,45443,45491,'00:31:33.470','00:31:35.470','I wanna see it.',-1),(104925,20,45757,45802,'00:31:46.570','00:31:48.440','Water.',-1),(104926,20,45805,45892,'00:31:48.570','00:31:52.200','- Bring him up.\n- Does it actually speak our language,',-1),(104927,20,45894,45951,'00:31:52.280','00:31:54.660','or does it just parrot what it\'s heard?',-1),(104928,20,45953,46015,'00:31:54.740','00:31:57.330','No, it seems to already understand our language.',-1),(104929,20,46017,46074,'00:31:57.410','00:31:59.750','<i>They\'ve compromised our satellites.\nThey know everything about us.</i>',-1),(104930,20,46075,46129,'00:31:59.830','00:32:02.080','Mr. Driscoll.',-1),(104931,20,46753,46799,'00:32:28.070','00:32:29.980','<i>My name is Regina Jackson.</i>',-1),(104932,20,46801,46900,'00:32:30.070','00:32:34.200','I\'m the secretary of defense\nof the United States of America.',-1),(104933,20,46952,47017,'00:32:36.370','00:32:39.080','This body will take some getting used to.',-1),(104934,20,47167,47244,'00:32:45.330','00:32:48.500','I\'ve been sent here to determine who\nor what you represent...',-1),(104935,20,47246,47303,'00:32:48.590','00:32:50.960','and what your intentions are.',-1),(104936,20,47333,47394,'00:32:52.220','00:32:54.760','It feels unreal to me.',-1),(104937,20,47455,47501,'00:32:57.300','00:32:59.220','Alien.',-1),(104938,20,47573,47624,'00:33:02.230','00:33:04.350','It\'ll take time to adapt.',-1),(104939,20,47649,47722,'00:33:05.400','00:33:08.440','What were you... before you were human?',-1),(104940,20,47808,47854,'00:33:12.030','00:33:13.940','Different.',-1),(104941,20,47856,47902,'00:33:14.030','00:33:15.950','Different how?',-1),(104942,20,47929,47989,'00:33:17.070','00:33:19.570','It would only frighten you.',-1),(104943,20,48039,48128,'00:33:21.660','00:33:25.370','- Do you have a name?\n- Klaatu.',-1),(104944,20,48186,48243,'00:33:27.750','00:33:30.130','Do you represent a civilization?',-1),(104945,20,48314,48375,'00:33:33.090','00:33:35.630','I represent a group of civilizations.',-1),(104946,20,48377,48482,'00:33:35.720','00:33:40.100','- Where is this group of civilizations?\n- All around you.',-1),(104947,20,48484,48553,'00:33:40.180','00:33:43.060','<i>What is your purpose in coming here?</i>',-1),(104948,20,48555,48655,'00:33:43.140','00:33:47.310','There is a gathering of world leaders\nnot far from here.',-1),(104949,20,48657,48708,'00:33:47.400','00:33:49.520','I will explain my purpose to them.',-1),(104950,20,48710,48784,'00:33:49.610','00:33:52.690','I\'m afraid that\'s not possible.',-1),(104951,20,48786,48854,'00:33:52.780','00:33:55.610','Perhaps you should explain yourself\nto me instead.',-1),(104952,20,48856,48928,'00:33:55.700','00:33:58.700','Do you speak for the entire human race?',-1),(104953,20,48930,48998,'00:33:58.780','00:34:01.620','I speak for the president of the United States.',-1),(104954,20,49074,49122,'00:34:04.790','00:34:06.750','<i>Now, please, tell me.</i>',-1),(104955,20,49123,49182,'00:34:06.830','00:34:09.290','Why have you come to our planet?',-1),(104956,20,49239,49297,'00:34:11.630','00:34:14.050','- Your planet?\n- Yes.',-1),(104957,20,49299,49348,'00:34:14.130','00:34:16.170','This is our planet.',-1),(104958,20,49402,49453,'00:34:18.430','00:34:20.550','No. It is not.',-1),(104959,20,49478,49569,'00:34:21.600','00:34:25.390','We\'ve decided to sedate him\nand move him to a more secure location.',-1),(104960,20,49571,49633,'00:34:25.480','00:34:28.060','- Are you going to interrogate him?\n- That\'s a possibility.',-1),(104961,20,49635,49706,'00:34:28.140','00:34:31.100','Madam Secretary, as scientists,\nwe can\'t consent to this.',-1),(104962,20,49708,49772,'00:34:31.190','00:34:33.860','He says he wants to speak to the U.N.',-1),(104963,20,49774,49851,'00:34:33.940','00:34:37.150','History has lessons to teach us\nabout first encounters...',-1),(104964,20,49853,49899,'00:34:37.240','00:34:39.150','between civilizations.',-1),(104965,20,49901,49994,'00:34:39.240','00:34:43.120','As a rule, the less-advanced civilization\nis either exterminated or enslaved.',-1),(104966,20,49996,50061,'00:34:43.200','00:34:45.910','I\'m thinking of Pizarro and the Incas,',-1),(104967,20,50064,50148,'00:34:46.000','00:34:49.540','Columbus and the Native Americans,\nand the list goes on.',-1),(104968,20,50150,50214,'00:34:49.620','00:34:52.290','Unfortunately, in this case,',-1),(104969,20,50217,50262,'00:34:52.380','00:34:54.290','the less-advanced civilization is us.',-1),(104970,20,50265,50356,'00:34:54.380','00:34:58.170','This is a representative\nof an extraterrestrial civilization.',-1),(104971,20,50358,50435,'00:34:58.260','00:35:01.470','This is the most important discovery\nin the history of mankind.',-1),(104972,20,50437,50502,'00:35:01.550','00:35:04.260','It may well be the last discovery\nin the history of mankind.',-1),(104973,20,50504,50586,'00:35:04.350','00:35:07.770','<i>We need to know what they\'re planning,\nand we need to know now.</i>',-1),(104974,20,50588,50675,'00:35:07.850','00:35:11.480','<i>So you wanna drug him?\nInterrogate him? I\'m sorry.</i>',-1),(104975,20,50678,50768,'00:35:11.600','00:35:15.360','- We won\'t do that. You understand?\n- I understand completely.',-1),(104976,20,50770,50848,'00:35:15.440','00:35:18.690','Of course, if you won\'t do it,\nwe\'ll have to call in someone who will.',-1),(104977,20,50850,50913,'00:35:18.780','00:35:21.400','<i>Well, I\'m sure you can find\nsomeone who will help you with--</i>',-1),(104978,20,50915,51001,'00:35:21.490','00:35:25.080','- I\'ll do it.\n- Helen.',-1),(104979,20,51027,51085,'00:35:26.160','00:35:28.580','I\'ll do it.',-1),(104980,20,51658,51704,'00:35:52.440','00:35:54.350','That won\'t be necessary, Doctor.',-1),(104981,20,51706,51797,'00:35:54.440','00:35:58.230','We\'ve already prepared the solution for you.',-1),(104982,20,51841,51893,'00:36:00.070','00:36:02.240','I just need a syringe.',-1),(104983,20,52141,52188,'00:36:12.580','00:36:14.500','<i>I want to apologize to you.</i>',-1),(104984,20,52189,52264,'00:36:14.580','00:36:17.670','<i>It seems we got off to a bad start.</i>',-1),(104985,20,52267,52333,'00:36:17.800','00:36:20.550','- It seems we did.\n- We\'re going to transport you...',-1),(104986,20,52335,52401,'00:36:20.630','00:36:23.380','to a different facility\nfor better medical care.',-1),(104987,20,52403,52441,'00:36:23.470','00:36:25.050','No, you are not.',-1),(104988,20,52443,52494,'00:36:25.140','00:36:27.260','Excuse me?',-1),(104989,20,52497,52572,'00:36:27.390','00:36:30.520','- I am leaving.\n- I can\'t allow you to do that.',-1),(104990,20,52574,52683,'00:36:30.600','00:36:35.150','- It is not up to you.\n- <i>This is a military installation.</i>',-1),(104991,20,52685,52762,'00:36:35.230','00:36:38.440','<i>You\'re surrounded by hundreds of soldiers.\nThere\'s no leaving here.</i>',-1),(104992,20,52764,52808,'00:36:38.520','00:36:40.360','I have done nothing wrong.',-1),(104993,20,52810,52866,'00:36:40.440','00:36:42.780','You invaded our airspace.',-1),(104994,20,52868,52976,'00:36:42.860','00:36:47.370','That... automaton that emerged from the sphere,\nit attacked our troops.',-1),(104995,20,52978,53026,'00:36:47.450','00:36:49.450','It acted to defend me.',-1),(104996,20,53028,53090,'00:36:49.540','00:36:52.120','It activates in the presence of violence.',-1),(104997,20,53093,53156,'00:36:52.210','00:36:54.870','Dr. Benson, please.',-1),(104998,20,53650,53698,'00:37:15.440','00:37:17.440','Run.',-1),(104999,20,53745,53793,'00:37:19.400','00:37:21.400','It\'s done.',-1),(105000,20,53832,53871,'00:37:23.030','00:37:24.650','If you\'ll come with us, ma\'am.',-1),(105001,20,54440,54492,'00:37:48.340','00:37:50.510','Keep moving, please.',-1),(105002,20,55681,55753,'00:38:40.060','00:38:43.060','I\'m going to ask you\na series of control questions.',-1),(105003,20,55866,55978,'00:38:47.780','00:38:52.450','Are you currently in a seated position?',-1),(105004,20,55980,56018,'00:38:52.530','00:38:54.120','Yes.',-1),(105005,20,56020,56075,'00:38:54.200','00:38:56.490','Are you human?',-1),(105006,20,56112,56184,'00:38:58.000','00:39:01.000','My body is.',-1),(105007,20,56185,56258,'00:39:01.080','00:39:04.090','Do you feel pain?',-1),(105008,20,56260,56319,'00:39:04.170','00:39:06.630','My body does.',-1),(105009,20,56431,56493,'00:39:11.300','00:39:13.890','Are you aware of an impending attack...',-1),(105010,20,56495,56559,'00:39:13.970','00:39:16.640','on the planet Earth?',-1),(105011,20,56633,56679,'00:39:19.730','00:39:21.640','You should let me go.',-1),(105012,20,56842,56892,'00:39:28.440','00:39:30.530','I\'ll repeat the question.',-1),(105013,20,57519,57589,'00:39:56.640','00:39:59.560','What gate did you use to enter this base?',-1),(105014,20,57592,57675,'00:39:59.680','00:40:03.140','- East loading door.\n- How do I get there?',-1),(105015,20,57677,57757,'00:40:03.230','00:40:06.560','100 yards left from the back of this building.',-1),(105016,20,57759,57815,'00:40:06.650','00:40:08.980','Is there a security code?',-1),(105017,20,57853,57926,'00:40:10.570','00:40:13.610','Four-four-bravo-three-zero.',-1),(105018,20,57928,57983,'00:40:13.700','00:40:15.990','What size is that suit?',-1),(105019,20,57986,58057,'00:40:16.120','00:40:19.080','- Forty-two long.\n- Take it off.',-1),(105020,20,59013,59106,'00:40:58.910','00:41:02.750','<i>Attention. All security personnel,\nreport to your designated posts.</i>',-1),(105021,20,59107,59197,'00:41:02.830','00:41:06.580','<i>All civilian personnel\nreport to Operations immediately.</i>',-1),(105022,20,59415,59461,'00:41:15.630','00:41:17.550','I\'m leaving you now.',-1),(105023,20,59463,59505,'00:41:17.640','00:41:19.390','No.',-1),(105024,20,60180,60227,'00:41:47.500','00:41:49.460','<i>Put every arm of the government--</i>',-1),(105025,20,60228,60313,'00:41:49.540','00:41:53.050','<i>military, law enforcement, federal, state and local--\non high alert.</i>',-1),(105026,20,60316,60384,'00:41:53.170','00:41:56.010','- If the media gets word that we\'ve lost the being--\n- Use a cover story.',-1),(105027,20,60386,60472,'00:41:56.090','00:41:59.680','We can\'t risk a panic.\nCall him an escaped convict.',-1),(105028,20,60474,60553,'00:41:59.760','00:42:03.060','Use every surveillance satellite,\nevery drone aircraft,',-1),(105029,20,60555,60593,'00:42:03.140','00:42:04.720','<i>every freeway camera.</i>',-1),(105030,20,60595,60651,'00:42:04.810','00:42:07.140','<i>Use every resource we\'ve got.</i>',-1),(105031,20,60798,60852,'00:42:13.280','00:42:15.530','<i>Attention: All scheduled trains...</i>',-1),(105032,20,60854,60960,'00:42:15.610','00:42:20.030','<i>into and out of Penn Station\nto Manhattan are canceled...</i>',-1),(105033,20,60962,61051,'00:42:20.120','00:42:23.830','<i>due to the security perimeter\nin Central Park.</i>',-1),(105034,20,61394,61445,'00:42:38.090','00:42:40.220','Excuse me. Excuse me.',-1),(105035,20,61536,61620,'00:42:44.010','00:42:47.520','<i>We are committed to providing you\nwith quality service.</i>',-1),(105036,20,61622,61674,'00:42:47.600','00:42:49.770','<i>Thank you.</i>',-1),(105037,20,61801,61868,'00:42:55.070','00:42:57.860','<i>We ask that our passengers\nremain calm and orderly...</i>',-1),(105038,20,61870,61929,'00:42:57.950','00:43:00.410','<i>during these difficult circumstances.</i>',-1),(105039,20,62058,62170,'00:43:05.790','00:43:10.420','<i>Any disturbance will be subject\nto immediate arrest by transit police.</i>',-1),(105040,20,62172,62217,'00:43:10.500','00:43:12.380','Let\'s go.',-1),(105041,20,62220,62272,'00:43:12.500','00:43:14.670','- Back off.\n- Don\'t push me!',-1),(105042,20,62275,62325,'00:43:14.800','00:43:16.880','- <i>Look, I\'m warning you.\n- <i>I don\'t--</i>',-1),(105043,20,62327,62398,'00:43:16.970','00:43:19.920','- <i>Just give me the ticket!</i>\n- <i>I\'m not giving you anything. Just--</i>',-1),(105044,20,62400,62522,'00:43:20.010','00:43:25.100','Give me the--\nWhat\'s the matter with you?',-1),(105045,20,62728,62795,'00:43:33.690','00:43:36.480','- Hey!\n- Go and get him.',-1),(105046,20,62851,62922,'00:43:38.820','00:43:41.780','- <i>We have a man down.</i>\n- <i>Unrest is causing leaders around the world...</i>',-1),(105047,20,62924,63003,'00:43:41.860','00:43:45.160','<i>to criticize the U.S. response\nto the arrival of the spheres.</i>',-1),(105048,20,63005,63051,'00:43:45.240','00:43:47.160','<i>Reactions from both national...</i>',-1),(105049,20,63053,63126,'00:43:47.240','00:43:50.290','<i>and international religious communities\nhave been varied.</i>',-1),(105050,20,63128,63198,'00:43:50.370','00:43:53.290','<i>While some have responded with hope and measured optimism,\nmost religious communities...</i>',-1),(105051,20,63201,63269,'00:43:53.380','00:43:56.210','<i>have considered recent events\nto be apocalyptic.</i>',-1),(105052,20,63271,63355,'00:43:56.300','00:43:59.800','<i>At gatherings and prayer vigils\nin virtually every major city,</i>',-1),(105053,20,63357,63410,'00:43:59.880','00:44:02.090','<i>many see the arrival\nof the Central Park sphere...</i>',-1),(105054,20,63412,63487,'00:44:02.180','00:44:05.300','<i>as a sign of a new era,\nor perhaps even the end of the world.</i>',-1),(105055,20,64018,64081,'00:44:27.450','00:44:30.080','<i>Leaders around the world are protesting\nthe U.S.\'s decision...</i>',-1),(105056,20,64083,64170,'00:44:30.160','00:44:33.790','<i>to deny foreign scientists\nfull access to the being.</i>',-1),(105057,20,64172,64218,'00:44:33.870','00:44:35.790','<i>Have you done your homework?</i>',-1),(105058,20,64221,64296,'00:44:35.880','00:44:39.000','School\'s canceled on account of the aliens.',-1),(105059,20,64299,64349,'00:44:39.130','00:44:41.210','- <i>They say it\'s an invasion.</i>\n- Well, they\'re wrong.',-1),(105060,20,64351,64414,'00:44:41.300','00:44:43.930','- What makes you so sure?\n- I just know.',-1),(105061,20,64417,64469,'00:44:44.050','00:44:46.220','Don\'t get that!',-1),(105062,20,64472,64525,'00:44:46.350','00:44:48.550','- Jacob!\n- Hello?',-1),(105063,20,64527,64607,'00:44:48.640','00:44:51.970','- <i>May I speak to Dr. Helen Benson, please?</i>\n- It\'s for you.',-1),(105064,20,64677,64720,'00:44:54.900','00:44:56.690','Hello?',-1),(105065,20,64722,64782,'00:44:56.770','00:44:59.270','- <i>Dr. Helen Benson?</i>\n- Yes.',-1),(105066,20,64784,64831,'00:44:59.360','00:45:01.320','<i>I\'m calling from Newark Penn Station.</i>',-1),(105067,20,64833,64886,'00:45:01.400','00:45:03.610','I\'ve got your patient here.',-1),(105068,20,64888,64972,'00:45:03.700','00:45:07.200','Oh. Um, sorry.\nI think there\'s been a mistake.',-1),(105069,20,64974,65028,'00:45:07.280','00:45:09.530','<i>Um, I\'m not that kind of a doctor.</i>',-1),(105070,20,65030,65083,'00:45:09.620','00:45:11.830','<i>Hold-Hold on a second.</i>',-1),(105071,20,65085,65144,'00:45:11.910','00:45:14.370','<i>He says you got his medicine.</i>',-1),(105072,20,65147,65226,'00:45:14.460','00:45:17.790','I\'ll be right there.',-1),(105073,20,65406,65451,'00:45:25.260','00:45:27.140','<i>Attention, all passengers.</i>',-1),(105074,20,65454,65518,'00:45:27.260','00:45:29.930','Excuse me!',-1),(105075,20,65520,65597,'00:45:30.010','00:45:33.220','Excuse me. I\'m sorry. Somebody called me.\nMy name\'s Dr. Benson.',-1),(105076,20,65599,65649,'00:45:33.310','00:45:35.390','Good. He\'s over there.\nHe\'s your problem now.',-1),(105077,20,65651,65726,'00:45:35.480','00:45:38.600','<i>Go ahead, take him. He\'s your problem.</i>',-1),(105078,20,65855,65937,'00:45:43.990','00:45:47.410','<i>I need my bag!</i>',-1),(105079,20,65939,66006,'00:45:47.490','00:45:50.280','<i>It\'s a black bag.</i>',-1),(105080,20,66008,66110,'00:45:50.370','00:45:54.620','<i>Evacuation registration point\nlocated two blocks this way.</i>',-1),(105081,20,66113,66169,'00:45:54.710','00:45:57.080','You know, I took a huge risk\nback at the hospital.',-1),(105082,20,66173,66252,'00:45:57.210','00:46:00.500','Did I make a mistake?',-1),(105083,20,66254,66329,'00:46:00.590','00:46:03.710','Are you a friend to us?',-1),(105084,20,66331,66384,'00:46:03.800','00:46:06.010','I\'m a friend to the Earth.',-1),(105085,20,66456,66532,'00:46:09.010','00:46:12.180','<i>Let\'s keep it steady, folks.\nLet\'s keep going forward.</i>',-1),(105086,20,66700,66767,'00:46:19.190','00:46:21.980','- Hello.\n- Hi.',-1),(105087,20,66769,66855,'00:46:22.070','00:46:25.650','Okay. Now what?',-1),(105088,20,66857,66904,'00:46:25.740','00:46:27.700','Drive.',-1),(105089,20,67306,67354,'00:46:44.420','00:46:46.420','Look in your pocket.',-1),(105090,20,67417,67465,'00:46:49.050','00:46:51.050','Your inside pocket.',-1),(105091,20,68189,68250,'00:47:21.210','00:47:23.750','Turn left.',-1),(105092,20,68614,68692,'00:47:38.930','00:47:42.190','<i>Striker two-eight-two-niner,\ndescend and maintain 2,000...</i>',-1),(105093,20,68694,68743,'00:47:42.270','00:47:44.310','<i>to establish the vectors\nto the target area.</i>',-1),(105094,20,68745,68810,'00:47:44.400','00:47:47.110','Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.',-1),(105095,20,68812,68877,'00:47:47.190','00:47:49.900','All right, everybody, we got our mission!',-1),(105096,20,68879,68950,'00:47:49.990','00:47:52.950','All right. Target acquired and confirmed, sir.\nWe are locked on.',-1),(105097,20,68952,69024,'00:47:53.030','00:47:56.030','<i>Madam Secretary,\nthey\'re sending in the drones.</i>',-1),(105098,20,69026,69076,'00:47:56.120','00:47:58.200','Bring in the reapers! We are go!',-1),(105099,20,69078,69155,'00:47:58.290','00:48:01.460','- Roger that. Descending to 1,200.\n- Let\'s light this thing up.',-1),(105100,20,69317,69372,'00:48:08.210','00:48:10.510','<i>That\'s affirmative. In motion now.</i>',-1),(105101,20,69374,69481,'00:48:10.590','00:48:15.050','- <i>Ground forces have been activated.</i>\n- Arm your Sidewinder missiles.',-1),(105102,20,69483,69560,'00:48:15.140','00:48:18.350','<i>Roger that, Colonel.\nSidewinder missiles armed.</i>',-1),(105103,20,69757,69843,'00:48:26.570','00:48:30.150','- He\'s activating.\n- Fire! Fire, fire!',-1),(105104,20,69961,70003,'00:48:35.070','00:48:36.820','- Missiles intercepted!\n- Get out of there!',-1),(105105,20,70006,70088,'00:48:36.950','00:48:40.370','- <i>Withdraw and realign for another sortie.</i>\n- <i>Negative!</i>',-1),(105106,20,70090,70157,'00:48:40.450','00:48:43.210','I\'ve lost link! I\'ve lost control!',-1),(105107,20,70216,70257,'00:48:45.670','00:48:47.380','Who\'s in control of the aircraft then?',-1),(105108,20,70299,70393,'00:48:49.130','00:48:53.050','<i>Striker 2-8 headed for \"R\" perimeter.\nI am out of control!</i>',-1),(105109,20,70640,70693,'00:49:03.350','00:49:05.560','Anyone got any other ideas?',-1),(105110,20,70698,70791,'00:49:05.770','00:49:09.650','<i>Why are people running?</i>',-1),(105111,20,70793,70867,'00:49:09.730','00:49:12.820','We should stay and fight.',-1),(105112,20,70869,70926,'00:49:12.900','00:49:15.280','They didn\'t come here to hurt us.',-1),(105113,20,70928,71014,'00:49:15.360','00:49:18.950','Well, we should kill \'em anyway,\njust to make sure.',-1),(105114,20,71016,71064,'00:49:19.030','00:49:21.040','- <i>Don\'t say that.</i>\n- <i>That\'s what Dad would\'ve done.</i>',-1),(105115,20,71103,71191,'00:49:22.660','00:49:26.330','- I think he would\'ve looked for a different way.\n- He would\'ve fought.',-1),(105116,20,71220,71266,'00:49:27.500','00:49:29.420','I like to think I knew him pretty well.',-1),(105117,20,71268,71325,'00:49:29.500','00:49:31.880','I knew him too, longer than you.',-1),(105118,20,71365,71439,'00:49:33.550','00:49:36.630','- What do you think?\n- Of what?',-1),(105119,20,71441,71505,'00:49:36.720','00:49:39.390','Should people run,\nor should we stay and fight?',-1),(105120,20,71530,71603,'00:49:40.430','00:49:43.470','- Neither.\n- <i>What should we do then?</i>',-1),(105121,20,71605,71652,'00:49:43.560','00:49:45.520','There\'s nothing you can do.',-1),(105122,20,71695,71789,'00:49:47.310','00:49:51.230','This is it. Pull in here.',-1),(105123,20,72009,72057,'00:50:00.410','00:50:02.410','McDonald\'s?',-1),(105124,20,72094,72139,'00:50:03.950','00:50:05.830','Where are you going?',-1),(105125,20,72143,72226,'00:50:05.960','00:50:09.420','- <i>Jacob, where are you going?</i>\n- To the bathroom.',-1),(105126,20,72318,72366,'00:50:13.260','00:50:15.260','Where is the boy\'s father?',-1),(105127,20,72418,72463,'00:50:17.430','00:50:19.300','He\'s dead.',-1),(105128,20,72466,72555,'00:50:19.430','00:50:23.140','- How did he die?\n- He was in the army.',-1),(105129,20,72557,72638,'00:50:23.220','00:50:26.600','So the boy wishes his soldier father were here...',-1),(105130,20,72640,72694,'00:50:26.690','00:50:28.940','to rescue the world from the aliens?',-1),(105131,20,72696,72784,'00:50:29.020','00:50:32.690','The boy wishes his father were here\nfor a lot of reasons,',-1),(105132,20,72786,72842,'00:50:32.770','00:50:35.110','aliens being the least of them.',-1),(105133,20,72909,72972,'00:50:37.900','00:50:40.530','He wasn\'t even that kind of a soldier.',-1),(105134,20,72974,73083,'00:50:40.620','00:50:45.160','He was an engineer.\nHe went over there to build,',-1),(105135,20,73086,73158,'00:50:45.290','00:50:48.290','- not to fight.\n- And his mother?',-1),(105136,20,73212,73262,'00:50:50.500','00:50:52.590','She died when he was a baby.',-1),(105137,20,73299,73410,'00:50:54.130','00:50:58.760','I married his father, and... a year ago,\nhe was killed.',-1),(105138,20,73497,73543,'00:51:02.390','00:51:04.310','Why did you come here?',-1),(105139,20,73580,73636,'00:51:05.850','00:51:08.180','I came to save the Earth.',-1),(105140,20,73663,73762,'00:51:09.310','00:51:13.440','- From what?\n- He\'s here.',-1),(105141,20,73931,74012,'00:51:20.490','00:51:23.870','<i>And number 44. Forty-four\'s ready.</i>',-1),(105142,20,74016,74087,'00:51:24.030','00:51:26.990','Your tea, Grandfather.',-1),(105143,20,74089,74137,'00:51:27.080','00:51:29.080','Thank you.',-1),(105144,20,74404,74458,'00:51:40.180','00:51:42.430','Are you one of them?',-1),(105145,20,74460,74517,'00:51:42.510','00:51:44.890','One of who?',-1),(105146,20,74519,74581,'00:51:44.970','00:51:47.560','No. Never mind. Sorry.',-1),(105147,20,74614,74674,'00:51:48.930','00:51:51.440','You\'ve been out of contact\nfor a long time.',-1),(105148,20,74676,74735,'00:51:51.520','00:51:53.980','I had a dangerous assignment.',-1),(105149,20,74752,74804,'00:51:54.690','00:51:56.860','This is hostile territory.',-1),(105150,20,74806,74842,'00:51:56.940','00:51:58.440','I\'ve noticed.',-1),(105151,20,74844,74922,'00:51:58.530','00:52:01.780','I was hoping I could reason with them.',-1),(105152,20,74924,75005,'00:52:01.860','00:52:05.240','I\'m afraid they are not a reasonable race.',-1),(105153,20,75033,75130,'00:52:06.410','00:52:10.450','I\'ve been living amongst them\nfor seventy years now.',-1),(105154,20,75132,75176,'00:52:10.540','00:52:12.370','I know them well.',-1),(105155,20,75208,75237,'00:52:13.670','00:52:14.880','And?',-1),(105156,20,75239,75318,'00:52:14.960','00:52:18.250','Any attempt to intercede with them\nwould be futile.',-1),(105157,20,75320,75381,'00:52:18.340','00:52:20.880','They are destructive,',-1),(105158,20,75398,75449,'00:52:21.590','00:52:23.720','and they won\'t change.',-1),(105159,20,75481,75567,'00:52:25.050','00:52:28.640','Is that your official report?',-1),(105160,20,75569,75695,'00:52:28.720','00:52:33.980','The tragedy is, they know\nwhat\'s going to become of them.',-1),(105161,20,75738,75774,'00:52:35.770','00:52:37.270','They sense it.',-1),(105162,20,75776,75876,'00:52:37.360','00:52:41.530','But they can\'t seem to do anything about it.',-1),(105163,20,76008,76093,'00:52:47.030','00:52:50.580','It\'s decided then.',-1),(105164,20,76095,76172,'00:52:50.660','00:52:53.870','I\'ll begin the process as soon as possible.',-1),(105165,20,76175,76252,'00:52:53.960','00:52:57.170','We should make preparations\nfor our departure.',-1),(105166,20,76254,76310,'00:52:57.250','00:52:59.590','I\'m staying.',-1),(105167,20,76312,76364,'00:52:59.670','00:53:01.840','<i>You can\'t stay here.</i>',-1),(105168,20,76366,76420,'00:53:01.920','00:53:04.180','I can, and I will.',-1),(105169,20,76422,76472,'00:53:04.260','00:53:06.340','If you stay, you\'ll die.',-1),(105170,20,76474,76536,'00:53:06.430','00:53:09.010','<i>I know.</i>',-1),(105171,20,76538,76591,'00:53:09.100','00:53:11.310','<i>This is my home now.</i>',-1),(105172,20,76630,76705,'00:53:12.930','00:53:16.060','You yourself called them a destructive race.',-1),(105173,20,76707,76764,'00:53:16.150','00:53:18.520','<i>That\'s true.</i>',-1),(105174,20,76766,76868,'00:53:18.610','00:53:22.860','<i>But still, there is another side.</i>',-1),(105175,20,76870,76954,'00:53:22.940','00:53:26.450','You see, I-- I love them.',-1),(105176,20,77005,77103,'00:53:28.580','00:53:32.660','This is a very strange thing.',-1),(105177,20,77106,77189,'00:53:32.750','00:53:36.210','I-I-I can\'t find a way to explain it to you.',-1),(105178,20,77190,77243,'00:53:36.290','00:53:38.460','For many years, I--',-1),(105179,20,77244,77324,'00:53:38.540','00:53:41.840','I cursed my luck for being sent here.',-1),(105180,20,77326,77418,'00:53:41.920','00:53:45.760','Human life is difficult.',-1),(105181,20,77420,77524,'00:53:45.840','00:53:50.180','But as this life is coming to an end,',-1),(105182,20,77526,77626,'00:53:50.260','00:53:54.430','I consider myself lucky...\nto have lived it.',-1),(105183,20,77728,77774,'00:53:58.690','00:54:00.610','<i>Copy that, Base.</i>',-1),(105184,20,77776,77840,'00:54:00.690','00:54:03.360','No sudden movements, no aggressive actions.',-1),(105185,20,77842,77913,'00:54:03.440','00:54:06.400','No matter what happens, no gunfire.',-1),(105186,20,77915,77983,'00:54:06.490','00:54:09.320','Track is in place, sir.\nContainment panels are in position.',-1),(105187,20,77986,78047,'00:54:09.450','00:54:11.990','- We\'re ready on your order.\n- On my command,',-1),(105188,20,78082,78127,'00:54:13.450','00:54:15.330','move the panels into place.',-1),(105189,20,78131,78169,'00:54:15.460','00:54:17.080','- Three.\n- <i>Three.</i>',-1),(105190,20,78173,78202,'00:54:17.210','00:54:18.420','- Two.\n- <i>Two.</i>',-1),(105191,20,78204,78237,'00:54:18.500','00:54:19.880','One.',-1),(105192,20,78239,78300,'00:54:19.960','00:54:22.540','<i>Synchronize established.\nI.S.I. ready to copy.</i>',-1),(105193,20,78510,78570,'00:54:31.260','00:54:33.760','<i>Containment panels are secure.</i>',-1),(105194,20,78573,78680,'00:54:33.890','00:54:38.350','<i>And... we\'re still here.</i>',-1),(105195,20,78836,78898,'00:54:44.860','00:54:47.440','<i>911. What\'s your emergency?</i>',-1),(105196,20,78900,78969,'00:54:47.530','00:54:50.410','<i>The escaped convict they showed on the news,\nI just saw the guy at the gas station.</i>',-1),(105197,20,78972,79018,'00:54:50.530','00:54:52.450','- <i>Can you describe him?</i>\n- <i>He was in a little car.</i>',-1),(105198,20,79020,79080,'00:54:52.530','00:54:55.040','<i>911. What is your emergency.</i>',-1),(105199,20,79082,79130,'00:54:55.120','00:54:57.120','<i>I just saw that wanted man\nover by the McDonald\'s.</i>',-1),(105200,20,79133,79177,'00:54:57.210','00:54:59.080','<i>Can you give me\na description of the car?</i>',-1),(105201,20,79181,79248,'00:54:59.210','00:55:02.000','- <i>A silver four-door with a woman and a kid.</i>\n- <i>I need three units...</i>',-1),(105202,20,79251,79302,'00:55:02.130','00:55:04.250','- <i>to look for a silver Honda near Ochada orchard.</i>\n- <i>Unit one responding.</i>',-1),(105203,20,79305,79394,'00:55:04.380','00:55:08.090','- <i>We are patrolling the orchards off I-67.</i>\n- <i>HP-28 to follow up.</i>',-1),(105204,20,79396,79453,'00:55:08.170','00:55:10.550','This is it.',-1),(105205,20,79455,79508,'00:55:10.640','00:55:12.850','Stop here.',-1),(105206,20,79510,79579,'00:55:12.930','00:55:15.810','Should--',-1),(105207,20,79685,79754,'00:55:20.230','00:55:23.110','Uh, Helen, who is this guy?',-1),(105208,20,79757,79809,'00:55:23.230','00:55:25.400','- <i>A friend.</i>\n- What kind of friend?',-1),(105209,20,79875,79951,'00:55:28.150','00:55:31.320','Scootch over. He\'s a work friend.',-1),(105210,20,79987,80070,'00:55:32.820','00:55:36.290','- What\'s his name?\n- Klaatu.',-1),(105211,20,80073,80112,'00:55:36.410','00:55:38.000','- Klaatu?\n- Yeah.',-1),(105212,20,80113,80173,'00:55:38.080','00:55:40.580','What kind of name is that?',-1),(105213,20,80176,80236,'00:55:40.670','00:55:43.170','It\'s foreign, I think.',-1),(105214,20,80238,80308,'00:55:43.290','00:55:46.170','I never heard you talk about him before.',-1),(105215,20,80310,80372,'00:55:46.250','00:55:48.840','Well, I haven\'t known him for very long.',-1),(105216,20,80374,80436,'00:55:48.920','00:55:51.510','We\'re just giving him a ride.',-1),(105217,20,80438,80511,'00:55:51.590','00:55:54.640','Where?',-1),(105218,20,80514,80573,'00:55:54.760','00:55:57.220','- Here.\n- The forest?',-1),(105219,20,80705,80757,'00:56:02.730','00:56:04.900','Stay here.\nI want you to lock the door, okay?',-1),(105220,20,80759,80828,'00:56:04.980','00:56:07.860','And don\'t open it for anyone but me.',-1),(105221,20,80830,80878,'00:56:07.940','00:56:09.940','I\'m serious.',-1),(105222,20,84653,84719,'00:58:47.230','00:58:49.980','Helen, what\'s going on?',-1),(105223,20,84863,84919,'00:58:55.990','00:58:58.320','<i>We\'re getting images of these spheres\nfrom all over the world.</i>',-1),(105224,20,84922,85002,'00:58:58.450','00:59:01.780','- Okavango, Gobi, Baku.\n- Which of our agencies gathered this intel?',-1),(105225,20,85004,85050,'00:59:01.870','00:59:03.780','Ma\'am, none of them.\nWe pulled these off the Internet.',-1),(105226,20,85218,85310,'00:59:10.790','00:59:14.590','Is that... them?',-1),(105227,20,85312,85346,'00:59:14.670','00:59:16.090','No.',-1),(105228,20,85348,85442,'00:59:16.170','00:59:20.090','It\'s us.\nThose are ordinary cephalopods.',-1),(105229,20,85475,85523,'00:59:21.470','00:59:23.470','Squid. Octopus.',-1),(105230,20,85575,85673,'00:59:25.640','00:59:29.730','<i>I don\'t like him. He\'s weird, and--</i>',-1),(105231,20,85676,85775,'00:59:29.850','00:59:33.980','- Why are we driving him around anyway?\n- Um--',-1),(105232,20,85823,85861,'00:59:35.980','00:59:37.570','It\'s complicated.',-1),(105233,20,85863,85920,'00:59:37.650','00:59:40.030','Is he comin\' home with us?',-1),(105234,20,85922,85988,'00:59:40.110','00:59:42.860','No. No.',-1),(105235,20,85990,86083,'00:59:42.950','00:59:46.830','Well, what if you decide you like him,\nand he wants to move in?',-1),(105236,20,86085,86134,'00:59:46.910','00:59:48.950','No, it\'s not like that.\nGod, no!',-1),(105237,20,86136,86183,'00:59:49.040','00:59:50.960','Listen to me.',-1),(105238,20,86184,86242,'00:59:51.040','00:59:53.420','No one is moving in.\nYou don\'t understand.',-1),(105239,20,86244,86347,'00:59:53.540','00:59:57.800','- Whatever. You wait for him. I\'m goin\' home.\n- Jacob.',-1),(105240,20,86462,86594,'01:00:02.590','01:00:08.100','Jacob!',-1),(105241,20,86596,86663,'01:00:08.180','01:00:10.980','What is the matter with you?',-1),(105242,20,87485,87536,'01:00:45.220','01:00:47.350','<i>These spheres now appear to be leaving...</i>',-1),(105243,20,87538,87586,'01:00:47.430','01:00:49.430','<i>in the same mysterious manner as they came.</i>',-1),(105244,20,87588,87649,'01:00:49.520','01:00:52.060','<i>Hopefully, this mass exodus\nwill bring an end to the panic and unrest...</i>',-1),(105245,20,87651,87691,'01:00:52.140','01:00:53.810','<i>we\'ve been seeing around the world.</i>',-1),(105246,20,87693,87743,'01:00:53.900','01:00:55.980','<i>The only sphere that\ndoesn\'t appear to be leaving...</i>',-1),(105247,20,87745,87792,'01:00:56.060','01:00:58.020','<i>is the giant sphere in Central Park.</i>',-1),(105248,20,87826,87875,'01:00:59.440','01:01:01.490','You think we scared \'em off?',-1),(105249,20,87899,87950,'01:01:02.490','01:01:04.610','They\'re not afraid of us.',-1),(105250,20,88253,88299,'01:01:17.210','01:01:19.130','I need to get back to the city.',-1),(105251,20,88301,88360,'01:01:19.210','01:01:21.670','Not until you tell me what\'s going on.',-1),(105252,20,88362,88426,'01:01:21.760','01:01:24.420','- Did you do that?\n- Yes.',-1),(105253,20,88429,88531,'01:01:24.550','01:01:28.800','- <i>Jacob, get in the car.</i>\n- He\'s one of them.',-1),(105254,20,88533,88570,'01:01:28.890','01:01:30.430','Please, get in the car.',-1),(105255,20,88605,88660,'01:01:31.890','01:01:34.180','Get in the car.',-1),(105256,20,88928,88974,'01:01:45.360','01:01:47.280','I need to know what\'s happening.',-1),(105257,20,89001,89055,'01:01:48.410','01:01:50.660','This planet is dying.',-1),(105258,20,89057,89104,'01:01:50.740','01:01:52.700','The human race is killing it.',-1),(105259,20,89106,89162,'01:01:52.790','01:01:55.120','So you\'ve come here to help us?',-1),(105260,20,89189,89239,'01:01:56.210','01:01:58.330','No, I didn\'t.',-1),(105261,20,89299,89343,'01:02:00.800','01:02:02.630','You said you came to save us.',-1),(105262,20,89345,89407,'01:02:02.710','01:02:05.300','I said I came to save the Earth.',-1),(105263,20,89409,89492,'01:02:05.380','01:02:08.840','You came to save the Earth...',-1),(105264,20,89494,89561,'01:02:08.930','01:02:11.720','from us.',-1),(105265,20,89563,89644,'01:02:11.810','01:02:15.180','You came to save the Earth from us?',-1),(105266,20,89646,89726,'01:02:15.270','01:02:18.600','We can\'t risk the survival of this planet\nfor the sake of one species.',-1),(105267,20,89729,89814,'01:02:18.730','01:02:22.270','- What are you saying?\n- If the Earth dies, you die.',-1),(105268,20,89816,89890,'01:02:22.360','01:02:25.440','If you die, the Earth survives.',-1),(105269,20,89892,89955,'01:02:25.530','01:02:28.160','There are only a handful of planets\nin the cosmos...',-1),(105270,20,89957,90013,'01:02:28.240','01:02:30.570','that are capable of supporting complex life.',-1),(105271,20,90015,90095,'01:02:30.660','01:02:33.990','- You can\'t do this.\n- This one can\'t be allowed to perish.',-1),(105272,20,90097,90175,'01:02:34.080','01:02:37.330','We can change.\nWe can still turn things around.',-1),(105273,20,90178,90235,'01:02:37.420','01:02:39.830','We\'ve watched, we\'ve waited\nand hoped that you would change.',-1),(105274,20,90239,90273,'01:02:39.960','01:02:41.380','- Please.\n- It\'s reached the tipping point.',-1),(105275,20,90276,90315,'01:02:41.500','01:02:43.130','- We have to act.\n- Please!',-1),(105276,20,90317,90390,'01:02:43.210','01:02:46.260','We\'ll undo the damage you\'ve done\nand give the Earth a chance to begin again.',-1),(105277,20,90392,90452,'01:02:46.340','01:02:48.840','Don\'t do this.',-1),(105278,20,90454,90514,'01:02:48.930','01:02:51.430','Please! We could change.',-1),(105279,20,90516,90568,'01:02:51.510','01:02:53.680','<i>We can change.</i>',-1),(105280,20,90570,90695,'01:02:53.770','01:02:58.980','The decision is made.\nThe process has begun.',-1),(105281,20,90698,90791,'01:02:59.100','01:03:02.980','Oh, God.',-1),(105282,20,90940,90998,'01:03:09.200','01:03:11.620','<i>Adam 85 confirming.</i>',-1),(105283,20,91000,91047,'01:03:11.700','01:03:13.660','<i>10-4, Central.</i>',-1),(105284,20,91180,91225,'01:03:19.170','01:03:21.080','It won\'t make any difference, Helen.',-1),(105285,20,91228,91276,'01:03:21.170','01:03:23.170','Even if they arrest me,',-1),(105286,20,91278,91366,'01:03:23.250','01:03:26.920','even if they kill me,\nthe process will continue.',-1),(105287,20,91368,91453,'01:03:27.010','01:03:30.550','Both of you, hands on the car, right now!',-1),(105288,20,91455,91494,'01:03:30.640','01:03:32.260','Is that a child in the car?',-1),(105289,20,91497,91581,'01:03:32.390','01:03:35.890','- Yes.\n- <i>This is HP-28.</i>',-1),(105290,20,91583,91665,'01:03:35.970','01:03:39.390','I\'m on I-67.\nI have the F.B.I. suspect in custody,',-1),(105291,20,91667,91723,'01:03:39.480','01:03:41.810','along with one adult female\nand one child.',-1),(105292,20,91725,91789,'01:03:41.900','01:03:44.560','- <i>Awaiting instructions.</i>\n- <i>7-0-140. Roger.</i>',-1),(105293,20,91791,91846,'01:03:44.650','01:03:46.940','Tell the child to get out of the car.',-1),(105294,20,91849,91923,'01:03:47.070','01:03:50.150','- <i>Get the kid out of the car!</i>\n- Honey, come on.',-1),(105295,20,91964,92016,'01:03:51.860','01:03:54.030','<i>Okay, you two, over there.</i>',-1),(105296,20,92018,92064,'01:03:54.120','01:03:56.030','<i>You, I\'m not gonna tell you again.</i>',-1),(105297,20,92066,92121,'01:03:56.120','01:03:58.410','- Hands on the car.\n- Please don\'t hurt him.',-1),(105298,20,92124,92206,'01:03:58.500','01:04:01.920','- I\'m not gonna hurt him, so long as he--\n- I wasn\'t talking to you.',-1),(105299,20,92250,92298,'01:04:03.750','01:04:05.790','The pain will only last a moment.',-1),(105300,20,92618,92712,'01:04:19.100','01:04:23.020','You killed him! You killed him!',-1),(105301,20,92715,92777,'01:04:23.150','01:04:25.730','- Jacob. Jacob!\n- Let me finish.',-1),(105302,20,92779,92851,'01:04:25.820','01:04:28.820','- You killed him! You killed him!\n- Shh. Shh. Come here.',-1),(105303,20,92854,92935,'01:04:28.940','01:04:32.320','- You killed him!\n- All right. Sit down.',-1),(105304,20,92937,92992,'01:04:32.410','01:04:34.700','- <i>He killed him!</i>\n- <i>Shh!</i>',-1),(105305,20,92994,93042,'01:04:34.780','01:04:36.780','<i>He killed him!</i>',-1),(105306,20,94015,94063,'01:05:17.330','01:05:19.330','He\'ll be all right.',-1),(105307,20,94146,94230,'01:05:22.750','01:05:26.250','I don\'t understand.',-1),(105308,20,94231,94339,'01:05:26.330','01:05:30.800','You\'re gonna kill us all,\nbut you saved him.',-1),(105309,20,94341,94401,'01:05:30.880','01:05:33.380','He was an obstacle.\nI meant him no harm.',-1),(105310,20,94450,94547,'01:05:35.430','01:05:39.470','You could stop this, couldn\'t you,\nif you wanted to?',-1),(105311,20,94549,94643,'01:05:39.560','01:05:43.480','I tried to reason with you.\nI tried to speak with your leaders.',-1),(105312,20,94645,94694,'01:05:43.560','01:05:45.600','Those aren\'t our leaders.',-1),(105313,20,94696,94758,'01:05:45.690','01:05:48.270','You wanna speak to one of our leaders,\nI\'ll take you to one.',-1),(105314,20,94760,94820,'01:05:48.360','01:05:50.860','<i>Let me take you.</i>',-1),(105315,20,94953,95000,'01:05:56.410','01:05:58.370','Get in the car.',-1),(105316,20,95040,95109,'01:06:00.030','01:06:02.910','Maybe they were just collecting specimens\nfrom our planet.',-1),(105317,20,95112,95157,'01:06:03.000','01:06:04.910','It\'s not our planet.',-1),(105318,20,95160,95221,'01:06:05.000','01:06:07.580','That what he said to me in the hospital.',-1),(105319,20,95313,95368,'01:06:11.380','01:06:13.670','An ark.',-1),(105320,20,95371,95439,'01:06:13.800','01:06:16.630','- <i>Excuse me?</i>\n- It\'s an ark.',-1),(105321,20,95441,95488,'01:06:16.720','01:06:18.680','So are all the other spheres.',-1),(105322,20,95490,95550,'01:06:18.760','01:06:21.260','They\'re saving as many species\nas they can.',-1),(105323,20,95553,95694,'01:06:21.390','01:06:27.270','- If the sphere is an ark, then what comes next is--\n- The flood.',-1),(105324,20,96235,96284,'01:06:49.830','01:06:51.840','Karl, we\'re here.',-1),(105325,20,96374,96426,'01:06:55.590','01:06:57.760','Okay, let\'s get you settled.',-1),(105326,20,96639,96690,'01:07:06.640','01:07:08.770','<i>That\'s a Nobel Prize.</i>',-1),(105327,20,96692,96792,'01:07:08.850','01:07:13.020','<i>He won it for his work\nin biological altruism.</i>',-1),(105328,20,96794,96867,'01:07:13.110','01:07:16.150','Probably still be in his desk drawer\nif I hadn\'t gotten it framed for him.',-1),(105329,20,96946,97018,'01:07:19.450','01:07:22.450','- You tired?\n- Just a little.',-1),(105330,20,97060,97141,'01:07:24.200','01:07:27.580','Close, but no.',-1),(105331,20,97280,97332,'01:07:33.340','01:07:35.500','I wouldn\'t--',-1),(105332,20,97334,97384,'01:07:35.590','01:07:37.670','He won\'t mind.',-1),(105333,20,97510,97595,'01:07:42.930','01:07:46.470','He\'s one of them.\nYou shouldn\'t be helping him.',-1),(105334,20,97597,97645,'01:07:46.560','01:07:48.560','We should stop him.',-1),(105335,20,97761,97874,'01:07:53.400','01:07:58.110','For just this once,\nI need you to trust me.',-1),(105336,20,98896,98959,'01:08:40.690','01:08:43.320','Is it possible?',-1),(105337,20,99314,99393,'01:08:58.090','01:09:01.380','I have so many questions to ask you.',-1),(105338,20,99731,99772,'01:09:15.480','01:09:17.190','It\'s Bach.',-1),(105339,20,99854,99900,'01:09:20.610','01:09:22.530','It\'s beautiful.',-1),(105340,20,99902,99965,'01:09:22.610','01:09:25.240','So we\'re not so different after all.',-1),(105341,20,100009,100078,'01:09:27.070','01:09:29.950','I wish that were true.',-1),(105342,20,100152,100218,'01:09:33.040','01:09:35.790','<i>So is it a machine, or a living thing?</i>',-1),(105343,20,100222,100295,'01:09:35.920','01:09:38.960','- It\'s both. Or... neither.\n- What do you mean, neither?',-1),(105344,20,100296,100362,'01:09:39.040','01:09:41.750','It seems to be some sort of\nsilicone-based hybrid.',-1),(105345,20,100364,100445,'01:09:41.840','01:09:45.220','We\'re calling it GORT--\nGenetically Organized Robotic Technology.',-1),(105346,20,100447,100495,'01:09:45.300','01:09:47.300','Oh, the military and their acronyms.',-1),(105347,20,100497,100548,'01:09:47.390','01:09:49.510','We\'ve used every diagnostic method available--',-1),(105348,20,100550,100602,'01:09:49.600','01:09:51.760','M.R.I., thermal imaging, PET scan.',-1),(105349,20,100604,100664,'01:09:51.850','01:09:54.350','But it was impervious.\nSo we attempted...',-1),(105350,20,100666,100717,'01:09:54.440','01:09:56.560','a robotically-assisted exploration\nusing a diamond drill.',-1),(105351,20,100720,100766,'01:09:56.690','01:09:58.610','- And?\n- The drill bit fractured.',-1),(105352,20,100768,100814,'01:09:58.690','01:10:00.610','It\'ll take 24 hours to fix it robotically.',-1),(105353,20,101872,101933,'01:10:44.690','01:10:47.240','Colonel, we don\'t have 24 hours.',-1),(105354,20,101935,102004,'01:10:47.320','01:10:50.200','Send somebody in there\nto fix that drill.',-1),(105355,20,102009,102078,'01:10:50.410','01:10:53.280','<i>Food and fuel hoarding\nhave led to shortages,</i>',-1),(105356,20,102080,102151,'01:10:53.370','01:10:56.330','<i>which erupted into looting incidents\nthroughout Asia and South America.</i>',-1),(105357,20,102153,102197,'01:10:56.410','01:10:58.210','<i>Outbreaks of rioting...</i>',-1),(105358,20,102198,102286,'01:10:58.290','01:11:01.920','<i>and unrest in such cities\nas Guangdong, China, London and Chicago...</i>',-1),(105359,20,102288,102420,'01:11:02.000','01:11:07.510','<i>due to the shortages of such basic commodities\nas fuel, food and drinking water.</i>',-1),(105360,20,102422,102490,'01:11:07.590','01:11:10.430','<i>Many point to the Central Park sphere as--</i>',-1),(105361,20,102492,102554,'01:11:10.510','01:11:13.100','<i>Amidst the chaos in the\nNew York-NewJersey areas,</i>',-1),(105362,20,102556,102675,'01:11:13.180','01:11:18.140','<i>local police are looking for an escaped convict\nwhose name is not being released.</i>',-1),(105363,20,102677,102768,'01:11:18.230','01:11:22.020','<i>Authorities believe that he is\na significant threat to the public...</i>',-1),(105364,20,102770,102852,'01:11:22.110','01:11:25.530','<i>and are asking for any information\nthat could lead to his capture.</i>',-1),(105365,20,102854,102947,'01:11:25.610','01:11:29.490','<i>If you have seen this man,\nplease contact the number on your screen below.</i>',-1),(105366,20,102949,103052,'01:11:29.570','01:11:33.870','There must be alternatives.\nYou must have some technology that can solve our problem.',-1),(105367,20,103054,103113,'01:11:33.950','01:11:36.410','Your problem is not technology.',-1),(105368,20,103116,103146,'01:11:36.500','01:11:37.790','The problem is you.',-1),(105369,20,103148,103242,'01:11:37.870','01:11:41.790','- You lack the will to change.\n- Then help us change.',-1),(105370,20,103245,103290,'01:11:41.880','01:11:43.790','I cannot change your nature.',-1),(105371,20,103293,103347,'01:11:43.880','01:11:46.130','You treat the world\nas you treat each other.',-1),(105372,20,103349,103451,'01:11:46.210','01:11:50.470','But every civilization reaches\na crisis point eventually.',-1),(105373,20,103454,103544,'01:11:50.590','01:11:54.350','- <i>Most of them don\'t make it.</i>\n- Yours did. How?',-1),(105374,20,103546,103624,'01:11:54.430','01:11:57.680','Our sun was dying.\nWe had to evolve in order to survive.',-1),(105375,20,103626,103699,'01:11:57.770','01:12:00.810','So it was only when your world\nwas threatened with destruction...',-1),(105376,20,103701,103749,'01:12:00.890','01:12:02.900','that you became what you are now.',-1),(105377,20,103752,103823,'01:12:03.020','01:12:05.980','- Yes.\n- Well, that\'s where we are.',-1),(105378,20,103825,103899,'01:12:06.070','01:12:09.150','You say we\'re on the brink of destruction,\nand you\'re right.',-1),(105379,20,103901,103965,'01:12:09.240','01:12:11.900','But it\'s only on the brink...',-1),(105380,20,103967,104016,'01:12:11.990','01:12:14.030','that people find the will to change.',-1),(105381,20,104018,104090,'01:12:14.120','01:12:17.120','Only at the precipice do we evolve.',-1),(105382,20,104124,104172,'01:12:18.540','01:12:20.500','<i>This is our moment.</i>',-1),(105383,20,104173,104253,'01:12:20.580','01:12:23.880','<i>Don\'t take it from us.\nWe are close to an answer.</i>',-1),(105384,20,104405,104453,'01:12:30.220','01:12:32.220','What\'s wrong?',-1),(105385,20,104897,105000,'01:12:50.740','01:12:55.030','Jacob. Can you get your boots on?',-1),(105386,20,105002,105056,'01:12:55.120','01:12:57.370','He can\'t get caught.',-1),(105387,20,105059,105113,'01:12:57.490','01:12:59.740','- What do I do?\n- Change his mind.',-1),(105388,20,105115,105183,'01:12:59.830','01:13:02.660','Not with reason, but with yourself.',-1),(105389,20,105469,105521,'01:13:14.550','01:13:16.720','<i>It\'s too late for that.</i>',-1),(105390,20,106236,106298,'01:13:46.500','01:13:49.090','Jacob!',-1),(105391,20,106300,106351,'01:13:49.170','01:13:51.300','Down here! He\'s here!',-1),(105392,20,106353,106405,'01:13:51.380','01:13:53.550','- Down here! Down here!\n- What are you doing?',-1),(105393,20,106408,106454,'01:13:53.670','01:13:55.590','- He\'s here!\n- What are you doing?',-1),(105394,20,106456,106544,'01:13:55.680','01:13:59.350','- I\'m trying to help them! That\'s why I called them.\n- What?',-1),(105395,20,106547,106599,'01:13:59.470','01:14:01.640','- I told them where we are.\n- Jacob, you didn\'t!',-1),(105396,20,106601,106646,'01:14:01.720','01:14:03.600','We shouldn\'t be helping him.',-1),(105397,20,106648,106708,'01:14:03.680','01:14:06.190','Jacob, I\'m trying to help us.',-1),(105398,20,106710,106766,'01:14:06.270','01:14:08.600','We should kill him!\nThat\'s what Dad would\'ve done.',-1),(105399,20,106768,106815,'01:14:08.690','01:14:10.650','You fight me on everything.\nOn everything!',-1),(105400,20,106818,106897,'01:14:10.770','01:14:14.070','- If my dad were here--\n- But he isn\'t here! He\'s gone!',-1),(105401,20,107034,107100,'01:14:19.780','01:14:22.540','Jacob--',-1),(105402,20,107144,107227,'01:14:24.370','01:14:27.830','<i>We\'ve extracted the female.\nReturning to base.</i>',-1),(105403,20,107450,107548,'01:14:37.090','01:14:41.180','- <i>Got a visual on the male.</i>\n- <i>Yeah, I see him.</i>',-1),(105404,20,107550,107642,'01:14:41.260','01:14:45.100','<i>Yep. Got it. Target acquired.\nPermission to engage.</i>',-1),(105405,20,107684,107731,'01:14:46.850','01:14:48.810','<i>You are clear to engage.</i>',-1),(105406,20,107734,107813,'01:14:48.940','01:14:52.230','- <i>You are go to take out the target.</i>\n- <i>Roger that.</i>',-1),(105407,20,108748,108825,'01:15:31.190','01:15:34.400','Please don\'t hurt me!',-1),(105408,20,109034,109081,'01:15:43.120','01:15:45.080','Thanks.',-1),(105409,20,109247,109299,'01:15:51.960','01:15:54.130','I don\'t know where we are.',-1),(105410,20,109455,109515,'01:16:00.630','01:16:03.140','Can you help me get home?',-1),(105411,20,109641,109680,'01:16:08.390','01:16:10.020','This way.',-1),(105412,20,110684,110775,'01:16:51.850','01:16:55.650','- He\'s come here to exterminate us, hasn\'t he?\n- You can\'t stop him.',-1),(105413,20,110777,110837,'01:16:55.730','01:16:58.230','The only chance we have is\nif he changes his mind.',-1),(105414,20,110839,110892,'01:16:58.320','01:17:00.530','You have to let me talk to him.',-1),(105415,20,110894,110940,'01:17:00.610','01:17:02.530','What makes you think he\'ll listen to you?',-1),(105416,20,110942,110988,'01:17:02.610','01:17:04.530','I don\'t know that he will.',-1),(105417,20,110990,111066,'01:17:04.620','01:17:07.780','But I think he trusts me,\nand I don\'t think he wants to do this.',-1),(105418,20,111068,111113,'01:17:07.870','01:17:09.740','We have the situation under control.',-1),(105419,20,111115,111176,'01:17:09.830','01:17:12.370','Madam Secretary, General Quinn\nneeds to see you in the briefing room.',-1),(105420,20,111180,111281,'01:17:12.500','01:17:16.710','- He says it\'s urgent.\n- You\'re not in control.',-1),(105421,20,111317,111358,'01:17:18.210','01:17:19.920','You don\'t know what he\'s capable of!',-1),(105422,20,111360,111465,'01:17:20.010','01:17:24.380','<i>But she didn\'t do anything wrong.\nSo they should let her go, right?</i>',-1),(105423,20,111510,111573,'01:17:26.260','01:17:28.890','You\'re afraid you\'re going\nto be left alone.',-1),(105424,20,111575,111682,'01:17:28.970','01:17:33.430','I already am alone. Helen\'s just someone\nthat was stuck with me when my dad died.',-1),(105425,20,111684,111732,'01:17:33.520','01:17:35.520','You know?',-1),(105426,20,111770,111869,'01:17:37.110','01:17:41.230','Oh. I forgot. You\'re an alien.\nYou don\'t understand anything.',-1),(105427,20,112025,112072,'01:17:47.740','01:17:49.700','<i>We\'re good to go.</i>',-1),(105428,20,112317,112363,'01:17:59.880','01:18:01.800','Hold it.',-1),(105429,20,112411,112477,'01:18:03.800','01:18:06.550','Your sleeve.',-1),(105430,20,112502,112549,'01:18:07.590','01:18:09.550','<i>Oh.</i>',-1),(105431,20,112588,112634,'01:18:11.180','01:18:13.100','<i>Let-Let me out!</i>',-1),(105432,20,112659,112705,'01:18:14.140','01:18:16.060','- Open the air lock.\n- No.',-1),(105433,20,112707,112738,'01:18:16.140','01:18:17.440','- <i>Open the door!</i>\n- Then we have to flash.',-1),(105434,20,112741,112790,'01:18:17.560','01:18:19.610','- Our protocol--\n- I decide what protocol is.',-1),(105435,20,112792,112857,'01:18:19.690','01:18:22.400','<i>Open the door! Let me out!</i>',-1),(105436,20,112860,112901,'01:18:22.530','01:18:24.240','- <i>Let me out!</i>\n- Reset the drill.',-1),(105437,20,112903,112942,'01:18:24.320','01:18:25.950','<i>Open it!</i>',-1),(105438,20,112944,112994,'01:18:26.030','01:18:28.110','I said, reset the drill.',-1),(105439,20,112996,113083,'01:18:28.200','01:18:31.830','<i>Let me out! Let me out!\nOpen the door!</i>',-1),(105440,20,113085,113137,'01:18:31.910','01:18:34.080','<i>Let me out!</i>',-1),(105441,20,113320,113360,'01:18:41.670','01:18:43.340','Sir, the restraints!',-1),(105442,20,114626,114714,'01:19:36.100','01:19:39.770','Open the door!',-1),(105443,20,114716,114772,'01:19:39.850','01:19:42.190','Open the door!',-1),(105444,20,114774,114844,'01:19:42.270','01:19:45.190','This facility has been sealed.',-1),(105445,20,114886,114932,'01:19:46.940','01:19:48.860','No one leaves.',-1),(105446,20,115350,115412,'01:20:06.250','01:20:08.840','We\'ve lost contact with the flash chamber, sir.',-1),(105447,20,115718,115754,'01:20:21.600','01:20:23.100','Whiskey task force, engage!',-1),(105448,20,116330,116385,'01:20:47.090','01:20:49.380','- <i>Were there any survivors?</i>\n- No.',-1),(105449,20,116387,116454,'01:20:49.460','01:20:52.260','As you know, at 0524 hours,',-1),(105450,20,116456,116515,'01:20:52.340','01:20:54.800','our pilots launched a salvo\nof Sidewinder air-to-air missiles...',-1),(105451,20,116518,116570,'01:20:54.930','01:20:57.100','- into the heart of the mass.\n- And?',-1),(105452,20,116572,116628,'01:20:57.180','01:20:59.520','Every strike made it larger.',-1),(105453,20,116630,116693,'01:20:59.600','01:21:02.230','<i>And this mass--\nWhere is it heading?</i>',-1),(105454,20,116695,116739,'01:21:02.310','01:21:04.140','Everywhere.',-1),(105455,20,117931,117992,'01:21:53.820','01:21:56.360','Dr. Benson.',-1),(105456,20,117994,118061,'01:21:56.450','01:21:59.240','Madam Secretary, please.',-1),(105457,20,118063,118152,'01:21:59.330','01:22:03.000','I don\'t wanna die here in this room\nwithout seeing my son one more time.',-1),(105458,20,118194,118241,'01:22:04.790','01:22:06.710','Do you really think you can persuade him?',-1),(105459,20,118242,118312,'01:22:06.790','01:22:09.670','I think you should let me try.',-1),(105460,20,118419,118493,'01:22:14.130','01:22:17.220','Go on, then.\nBut I make you no promises.',-1),(105461,20,118495,118549,'01:22:17.300','01:22:19.550','I still answer to the president.',-1),(105462,20,118552,118620,'01:22:19.680','01:22:22.510','- You\'re on your own.\n- No, she\'s not. I\'ll go with you.',-1),(105463,20,118682,118740,'01:22:25.100','01:22:27.520','- Good luck.\n- Thank you.',-1),(105464,20,119272,119318,'01:22:49.670','01:22:51.590','It doesn\'t work.',-1),(105465,20,119501,119557,'01:22:59.220','01:23:01.550','Go ahead.',-1),(105466,20,119718,119792,'01:23:08.270','01:23:11.360','It\'s me. Are you okay?',-1),(105467,20,119825,119909,'01:23:12.730','01:23:16.240','I\'m fine. He\'s right here.',-1),(105468,20,119947,119996,'01:23:17.820','01:23:19.860','She wants to talk to you.',-1),(105469,20,120038,120084,'01:23:21.620','01:23:23.530','Yes.',-1),(105470,20,120086,120154,'01:23:23.620','01:23:26.450','I need to get back to the city.',-1),(105471,20,120157,120210,'01:23:26.580','01:23:28.790','- Yes.\n- Tell her I know where we can meet her.',-1),(105472,20,120553,120599,'01:23:43.050','01:23:44.970','I told Helen we should kill you.',-1),(105473,20,120644,120691,'01:23:46.850','01:23:48.810','Yes, I heard that.',-1),(105474,20,120693,120738,'01:23:48.890','01:23:50.770','I didn\'t mean it, though.',-1),(105475,20,120741,120802,'01:23:50.900','01:23:53.440','- You didn\'t?\n- Well, not anymore.',-1),(105476,20,120974,121019,'01:24:00.610','01:24:02.490','So what\'s gonna happen to us?',-1),(105477,20,121099,121170,'01:24:05.830','01:24:08.790','I was just wondering the same thing.',-1),(105478,20,121369,121445,'01:24:17.050','01:24:20.220','- End of the world!\n- Good luck!',-1),(105479,20,121447,121493,'01:24:20.300','01:24:22.220','This is it.',-1),(105480,20,121495,121546,'01:24:22.300','01:24:24.430','This is where we\'re supposed to meet her.',-1),(105481,20,121548,121596,'01:24:24.510','01:24:26.510','Come on!',-1),(105482,20,121803,121851,'01:24:35.150','01:24:37.150','Hurry up. It\'s this way.',-1),(105483,20,122629,122674,'01:25:09.560','01:25:11.430','You can do this,',-1),(105484,20,122676,122742,'01:25:11.520','01:25:14.270','<i>just like with the trooper.</i>',-1),(105485,20,122781,122828,'01:25:15.900','01:25:17.860','There are some things I can\'t do.',-1),(105486,20,122830,122887,'01:25:17.940','01:25:20.320','But you have powers.',-1),(105487,20,122943,122989,'01:25:22.650','01:25:24.570','I\'m sorry.',-1),(105488,20,123044,123177,'01:25:26.870','01:25:32.410','Please.',-1),(105489,20,123222,123321,'01:25:34.250','01:25:38.380','Jacob, nothing ever truly dies.',-1),(105490,20,123323,123411,'01:25:38.460','01:25:42.130','The universe wastes nothing.\nEverything is simply...',-1),(105491,20,123413,123460,'01:25:42.220','01:25:44.170','transformed.',-1),(105492,20,123510,123565,'01:25:46.260','01:25:48.550','Just leave me alone.',-1),(105493,20,124607,124670,'01:26:31.970','01:26:34.600','- It\'s not fair.\n- No.',-1),(105494,20,124672,124737,'01:26:34.680','01:26:37.390','No, it isn\'t fair.',-1),(105495,20,124739,124825,'01:26:37.480','01:26:41.060','He left me alone.',-1),(105496,20,124827,124920,'01:26:41.150','01:26:45.030','Oh, baby. You\'re not alone.',-1),(105497,20,124922,125033,'01:26:45.110','01:26:49.740','And he didn\'t leave you.\nI see him in you...',-1),(105498,20,125035,125093,'01:26:49.820','01:26:52.240','all the time.',-1),(105499,20,125095,125141,'01:26:52.330','01:26:54.240','All the time.',-1),(105500,20,125143,125223,'01:26:54.330','01:26:57.660','Sometimes, it\'s hard for me to bear.',-1),(105501,20,125254,125307,'01:26:58.920','01:27:01.130','You miss him too?',-1),(105502,20,125331,125380,'01:27:02.130','01:27:04.170','So much.',-1),(105503,20,125443,125572,'01:27:06.800','01:27:12.180','I\'m sorry.',-1),(105504,20,125574,125612,'01:27:12.260','01:27:13.850','Okay.',-1),(105505,20,126304,126350,'01:27:42.670','01:27:44.590','<i>It\'s all right.</i>',-1),(105506,20,126352,126396,'01:27:44.670','01:27:46.510','He\'s here to help.',-1),(105507,20,126492,126540,'01:27:50.510','01:27:52.510','There\'s another side to you.',-1),(105508,20,126627,126699,'01:27:56.140','01:27:59.140','I feel it now.',-1),(105509,20,127042,127108,'01:28:13.450','01:28:16.200','Is that how it ends?',-1),(105510,20,127170,127208,'01:28:18.790','01:28:20.370','Yes.',-1),(105511,20,127211,127281,'01:28:20.460','01:28:23.380','You can\'t stop it?',-1),(105512,20,127307,127356,'01:28:24.460','01:28:26.500','I don\'t know.',-1),(105513,20,127464,127549,'01:28:31.010','01:28:34.550','It would come at a price...\nto you and your way of life.',-1),(105514,20,127551,127598,'01:28:34.640','01:28:36.600','But we can change.',-1),(105515,20,127600,127646,'01:28:36.680','01:28:38.600','You know that now.',-1),(105516,20,127648,127753,'01:28:38.680','01:28:43.060','Please. Please, just give us a chance.',-1),(105517,20,127815,127922,'01:28:45.650','01:28:50.110','I\'ll try. I must get back to the city.',-1),(105518,20,128374,128481,'01:29:08.920','01:29:13.380','<i>Of course, Mr. President,\nI understand the situation.</i>',-1),(105519,20,128483,128564,'01:29:13.470','01:29:16.850','But with all due respect, sir,\nany further military action...',-1),(105520,20,128566,128612,'01:29:16.930','01:29:18.850','will only make things worse.',-1),(105521,20,128614,128694,'01:29:18.930','01:29:22.270','I believe we may still be able\nto open a dialogue--',-1),(105522,20,128838,128905,'01:29:28.270','01:29:31.070','Yes, Mr. President. As you wish, sir.',-1),(105523,20,128907,128958,'01:29:31.150','01:29:33.280','Thank you.',-1),(105524,20,129619,129727,'01:30:00.810','01:30:05.310','- Checkpoint.\n- We can\'t stop. There isn\'t time.',-1),(105525,20,130012,130059,'01:30:17.200','01:30:19.160','Lincoln Bravo One to Lincoln Bravo Two.',-1),(105526,20,130061,130145,'01:30:19.240','01:30:22.740','<i>A black S.U.V. crashed our checkpoint with the s