he victim,</i>',-1),(105594,7,5389,5444,'00:03:44.560','00:03:46.847','<i>the brave journalist going\nup against the bad guy.</i>',-1),(105595,7,5448,5511,'00:03:47.000','00:03:49.653','<i>I don\'t know why malicious\nintent couldn\'t be proven.</i>',-1),(105596,7,5511,5546,'00:03:49.654','00:03:51.085','When you call a\nguy a criminal...',-1),(105597,7,5549,5590,'00:03:51.240','00:03:52.924','<i>If you want to\nsay these things...</i>',-1),(105598,7,5593,5635,'00:03:53.080','00:03:54.809','<i>Mikael Blomkvist\nlikes publicity.</i>',-1),(105599,7,5640,5710,'00:03:55.000','00:03:57.924','<i>There\'s really no greater\ndisgrace for a journalist than libel.</i>',-1),(105600,7,5713,5793,'00:03:58.080','00:04:01.402','<i>... was found guilty\ntoday on 16 counts of aggravated libel.</i>',-1),(105601,7,5797,5880,'00:04:01.560','00:04:05.007','Can I get that sandwich there?\nAnd a black coffee.',-1),(105602,7,5883,5954,'00:04:05.160','00:04:08.084','<i>In an article published earlier\nthis year, Blomkvist claimed,</i>',-1),(105603,7,5957,6035,'00:04:08.240','00:04:11.483','<i>Wennerstrm, founder and president\nof the Wennerstrm Group,</i>',-1),(105604,7,6039,6126,'00:04:11.640','00:04:15.281','<i>used state funds intended for\nindustrial development in Poland</i>',-1),(105605,7,6131,6201,'00:04:15.480','00:04:18.404','<i>in an arms deal with the\nright-wing Ustae in Croatia.</i>',-1),(105606,7,6205,6276,'00:04:18.560','00:04:21.530','<i>I have nothing against Mr. Blomkvist.\nHe\'s a fine journalist,</i>',-1),(105607,7,6280,6335,'00:04:21.680','00:04:23.967','<i>who I don\'t believe\nis guided by malice.</i>',-1),(105608,7,6338,6388,'00:04:24.120','00:04:26.202','<i>But what he wrote\nwas inaccurate.</i>',-1),(105609,7,6392,6455,'00:04:26.360','00:04:28.966','<i>And inaccuracies can\'t\ngo unanswered.</i>',-1),(105610,7,6459,6538,'00:04:29.160','00:04:32.448','<i>All journalists have to\naccept, like the rest of us,</i>',-1),(105611,7,6542,6615,'00:04:32.600','00:04:35.649','<i>actions have consequences.</i>',-1),(105612,7,6619,6660,'00:04:35.800','00:04:37.529','<i>Blomkvist\nwas ordered to pay</i>',-1),(105613,7,6664,6727,'00:04:37.680','00:04:40.331','<i>600,000 Swedish kronor in\ndamages and all court costs.</i>',-1),(105614,7,6731,6813,'00:04:40.480','00:04:43.882','Can I get a packet of\nMarlboro Red and a lighter?',-1),(105615,7,7545,7585,'00:05:14.400','00:05:16.050','Tsk. Yeah.',-1),(105616,7,7802,7864,'00:05:25.120','00:05:27.691','Where have you been?\nWalking. Thinking.',-1),(105617,7,7868,7904,'00:05:27.840','00:05:29.365','Smoking? Yeah. Just one.',-1),(105618,7,8075,8125,'00:05:36.480','00:05:38.562','TV4 called.\nI told them no statement',-1),(105619,7,8129,8183,'00:05:38.720','00:05:40.961','until we\'ve read the\njudgment in its entirety.',-1),(105620,7,8186,8241,'00:05:41.120','00:05:43.407','Well, I have. Anyone else?',-1),(105621,7,8245,8290,'00:05:43.560','00:05:45.449','Everyone who wants to\nsee you humiliated.',-1),(105622,7,8294,8353,'00:05:45.600','00:05:48.046','Been on the phone all morning?\nI\'m as much to blame.',-1),(105623,7,8357,8411,'00:05:48.240','00:05:50.481','You are? You wrote it?\nI read it. I ran it.',-1),(105624,7,8415,8467,'00:05:50.640','00:05:52.802','Not the same.\nOur credibility isn\'t dead yet.',-1),(105625,7,8471,8510,'00:05:52.960','00:05:54.610','Mine is.',-1),(105626,7,8580,8618,'00:05:57.520','00:05:59.090','I\'m tired.',-1),(105627,7,8634,8710,'00:05:59.760','00:06:02.923','I\'m gonna go home, crawl\nunder the duvet for a week.',-1),(105628,7,8811,8875,'00:06:07.160','00:06:09.811','I\'ll call Greger, tell\nhim I\'m not coming home.',-1),(105629,7,8879,8908,'00:06:09.960','00:06:11.200','Thank you.',-1),(105630,7,8999,9049,'00:06:14.960','00:06:17.042','It\'s possible we\ncould wait forever.',-1),(105631,7,9052,9143,'00:06:17.200','00:06:20.966','You called her and spoke to her?\nI\'m afraid that doesn\'t mean much.',-1),(105632,7,9229,9308,'00:06:24.560','00:06:27.848','<i>No one here particularly\nlikes her.</i>',-1),(105633,7,9312,9368,'00:06:28.000','00:06:30.367','I find it\'s much better\nif she works from home.',-1),(105634,7,9379,9437,'00:06:30.800','00:06:33.246','But you told her I\nwanted to meet with her.',-1),(105635,7,9441,9506,'00:06:33.400','00:06:36.085','I\'ve told her many times I\nprefer her not to meet clients.',-1),(105636,7,9538,9585,'00:06:37.440','00:06:39.408','<i>- You like her?\n- Very much.</i>',-1),(105637,7,9589,9667,'00:06:39.560','00:06:42.803','<i>She\'s one of the best investigators I\nhave, as you saw from her report.</i>',-1),(105638,7,9672,9762,'00:06:43.000','00:06:46.766','But? I\'m concerned\nyou won\'t like her.',-1),(105639,7,9766,9806,'00:06:46.920','00:06:48.604','Mm. She\'s different.',-1),(105640,7,9811,9839,'00:06:48.800','00:06:49.961','In what way?',-1),(105641,7,9864,9890,'00:06:51.040','00:06:52.087','In every way.',-1),(105642,7,10035,10083,'00:06:58.160','00:07:00.128','<i>Miss Salander is here.</i>',-1),(105643,7,10225,10260,'00:07:06.080','00:07:07.525','Lisbeth.',-1),(105644,7,10264,10318,'00:07:07.680','00:07:09.921','Mr. Dirch Frode.',-1),(105645,7,10321,10366,'00:07:10.080','00:07:11.923','How do you do?',-1),(105646,7,10637,10676,'00:07:23.240','00:07:24.844','Something wrong with the report?',-1),(105647,7,10680,10717,'00:07:25.000','00:07:26.570','No, it was\nquite thorough.',-1),(105648,7,10721,10791,'00:07:26.720','00:07:29.644','But I\'m also interested\nin what\'s not in it.',-1),(105649,7,10796,10868,'00:07:29.840','00:07:32.844','There\'s nothing not in it.\nYour opinion of him isn\'t.',-1),(105650,7,10878,10964,'00:07:33.280','00:07:36.841','I\'m not paid to give my opinion.\nSo you don\'t have one?',-1),(105651,7,11049,11087,'00:07:40.400','00:07:41.970','He\'s clean, in my opinion.',-1),(105652,7,11090,11152,'00:07:42.120','00:07:44.691','You mean he\'s hygienic?',-1),(105653,7,11162,11252,'00:07:45.120','00:07:48.841','He\'s who he presents himself to be.\nIn his business, that\'s an asset.',-1),(105654,7,11256,11331,'00:07:49.000','00:07:52.129','Well, there\'s less in his asset\ncolumn after his conviction today.',-1),(105655,7,11335,11379,'00:07:52.320','00:07:54.163','True. He made a fool of himself.',-1),(105656,7,11383,11419,'00:07:54.320','00:07:55.810','If it happened that way.',-1),(105657,7,11423,11471,'00:07:55.960','00:07:57.962','Are you suggesting\nthat he was set up?',-1),(105658,7,11494,11537,'00:07:58.920','00:08:00.729','That was never part\nof my assignment.',-1),(105659,7,11541,11582,'00:08:00.880','00:08:02.609','But you\'re right.',-1),(105660,7,11586,11647,'00:08:02.760','00:08:05.331','He did make a fool of\nhimself professionally.',-1),(105661,7,11651,11732,'00:08:05.480','00:08:08.848','How much of a fool did he\nmake of himself financially?',-1),(105662,7,11736,11801,'00:08:09.000','00:08:11.731','The judgment will just\nabout empty his savings.',-1),(105663,7,11806,11833,'00:08:11.920','00:08:13.046','Moment.',-1),(105664,7,11853,11912,'00:08:13.880','00:08:16.360','Your report is light\nin another area.',-1),(105665,7,11916,11957,'00:08:16.520','00:08:18.249','His personal life.',-1),(105666,7,11961,12005,'00:08:18.400','00:08:20.243','Anything you chose\nnot to disclose?',-1),(105667,7,12036,12073,'00:08:21.520','00:08:23.045','Nothing that\nwarranted inclusion.',-1),(105668,7,12076,12118,'00:08:23.200','00:08:24.929','Does that mean yes or no?',-1),(105669,7,12121,12221,'00:08:25.080','00:08:29.210','I think what Miss Salander means, and\nI agree, is that everyone has a right',-1),(105670,7,12225,12301,'00:08:29.400','00:08:32.563','to a certain amount of privacy,\neven if they\'re being investigated.',-1),(105671,7,12305,12369,'00:08:32.720','00:08:35.405','Not in this case.\nI need to know anything about him',-1),(105672,7,12373,12460,'00:08:35.560','00:08:39.167','I might find unsavory,\neven if she doesn\'t.',-1),(105673,7,12548,12600,'00:08:42.840','00:08:45.002','He\'s had a longstanding\nsexual relationship',-1),(105674,7,12603,12701,'00:08:45.160','00:08:49.245','with his co-editor of the magazine.\nIt wrecked his marriage but not hers.',-1),(105675,7,12705,12759,'00:08:49.400','00:08:51.641','Sometimes he performs\ncunnilingus.',-1),(105676,7,12764,12819,'00:08:51.840','00:08:54.161','Not often enough, in my opinion.',-1),(105677,7,12840,12887,'00:08:55.000','00:08:56.968','No, you\'re right not\nto include that.',-1),(105678,7,12890,12923,'00:08:57.120','00:08:58.485','I know.',-1),(105679,7,14268,14340,'00:09:54.520','00:09:57.524','You needed a better attorney.\nYou needed your sister.',-1),(105680,7,14344,14375,'00:09:57.680','00:09:58.966','She offered. He declined.',-1),(105681,7,14379,14416,'00:09:59.160','00:10:00.685','As she hoped. Never a good idea.',-1),(105682,7,14420,14479,'00:10:00.840','00:10:03.320','Mixing family and business.\nI would\'ve lost anyway.',-1),(105683,7,14483,14568,'00:10:03.480','00:10:07.007','It wasn\'t about Mikael.\nIt was about Wennerstrm sending a message',-1),(105684,7,14571,14647,'00:10:07.160','00:10:10.323','to the press and the FSA,\nsaying, \"Don\'t ask questions.\"',-1),(105685,7,14653,14678,'00:10:10.560','00:10:11.607','Cheer up.',-1),(105686,7,14780,14804,'00:10:15.840','00:10:16.841','Dad.',-1),(105687,7,14808,14868,'00:10:17.000','00:10:19.526','Nilla, you don\'t have\nto worry about me.',-1),(105688,7,14873,14915,'00:10:19.720','00:10:21.484','Mom\'s worried. About me?',-1),(105689,7,14937,14968,'00:10:22.400','00:10:23.686','About the money.',-1),(105690,7,16547,16577,'00:11:29.480','00:11:30.720','Good evening.',-1),(105691,7,16651,16709,'00:11:33.800','00:11:36.246','Nilla? What are you doing?',-1),(105692,7,16713,16740,'00:11:36.400','00:11:37.526','Nothing.',-1),(105693,7,16744,16773,'00:11:37.680','00:11:38.886','Are you serious?',-1),(105694,7,16776,16862,'00:11:39.040','00:11:42.601','I don\'t wanna talk about it\nsince I know you won\'t approve.',-1),(105695,7,16867,16893,'00:11:42.800','00:11:43.881','Of, um...?',-1),(105696,7,16905,16937,'00:11:44.400','00:11:45.731','Nilla. Light of Life.',-1),(105697,7,16941,16973,'00:11:45.880','00:11:47.245','Light of what?',-1),(105698,7,17193,17224,'00:11:56.400','00:11:57.686','<i>Herr Blomkvist.</i>',-1),(105699,7,17228,17260,'00:11:57.840','00:11:59.171','<i>Yea h. Forgive me for intruding</i>',-1),(105700,7,17264,17315,'00:11:59.360','00:12:01.488','<i>on Christmas.\nMy name is Dirch Frode.</i>',-1),(105701,7,17319,17414,'00:12:01.640','00:12:05.611','I\'m an attorney. I represent Henrik Vanger.\nPerhaps you\'ve heard of him?',-1),(105702,7,17418,17445,'00:12:05.760','00:12:06.886','Yeah, of course I have.',-1),(105703,7,17449,17507,'00:12:07.080','00:12:09.481','<i>He\'d love to talk to you\nabout a private matter.</i>',-1),(105704,7,17511,17584,'00:12:09.640','00:12:12.689','This is an awkward moment.',-1),(105705,7,17588,17663,'00:12:12.840','00:12:15.969','<i>Oh, I\'m sorry. I\'m about to sit\ndown to a Christmas dinner myself.</i>',-1),(105706,7,17666,17716,'00:12:16.120','00:12:18.202','No, that\'s not exactly\nwhat I meant.',-1),(105707,7,17720,17778,'00:12:18.360','00:12:20.761','You\'re referring to your\nrecent legal problems.',-1),(105708,7,17782,17827,'00:12:20.920','00:12:22.809','That has provided us\nwith much amusement.',-1),(105709,7,17831,17855,'00:12:22.960','00:12:23.961','I\'m sorry?',-1),(105710,7,17858,17921,'00:12:24.120','00:12:26.726','<i>Herr Vanger has little love\nfor Herr Wennerstrm either.</i>',-1),(105711,7,17925,17986,'00:12:26.880','00:12:29.451','Have him call me.\nBut he would love to speak to you',-1),(105712,7,17991,18053,'00:12:29.640','00:12:32.211','in person, if possible.\nUp north.',-1),(105713,7,18056,18104,'00:12:32.360','00:12:34.362','<i>In Hedestad.\nThat\'s not gonna be possible.</i>',-1),(105714,7,18109,18177,'00:12:34.560','00:12:37.404','<i>Herr Blomkvist, he\'s far too old\nto go to Stockholm. Please.</i>',-1),(105715,7,18181,18234,'00:12:37.560','00:12:39.767','Be so kind as to consider.',-1),(105716,7,18238,18305,'00:12:39.920','00:12:42.730','<i>Hedestad is lovely\nin the winter.</i>',-1),(105717,7,18309,18406,'00:12:42.880','00:12:46.930','I\'ll call you back on this number.\nOkay?',-1),(105718,7,18726,18791,'00:13:00.280','00:13:02.965','Usually when I wake up in\na cold bed it\'s at home.',-1),(105719,7,18794,18837,'00:13:03.120','00:13:04.884','I\'m sorry. What are you doing?',-1),(105720,7,18840,18913,'00:13:05.040','00:13:08.044','I\'m writing a press release.\nSaying?',-1),(105721,7,18990,19049,'00:13:11.280','00:13:13.726','You\'re taking over as\npublisher, you\'re very sorry',-1),(105722,7,19053,19108,'00:13:13.880','00:13:16.167','for any nuisance Mr\n. Wennerstrm was caused,',-1),(105723,7,19111,19184,'00:13:16.320','00:13:19.369','and I can\'t be reached for comment.\nAre you giving up?',-1),(105724,7,19188,19219,'00:13:19.520','00:13:20.806','Stepping aside.',-1),(105725,7,19227,19269,'00:13:21.160','00:13:22.889','This makes me sick.',-1),(105726,7,20137,20196,'00:13:59.080','00:14:01.526','- First time in Hedestad?\n- And the last.',-1),(105727,7,20200,20257,'00:14:01.680','00:14:04.047','Oh, don\'t say that.\nIt\'s lovely in the spring.',-1),(105728,7,20260,20327,'00:14:04.200','00:14:06.965','You said it would be\nlovely in the winter.',-1),(105729,7,20330,20378,'00:14:07.120','00:14:09.088','Well, this is unseasonable.',-1),(105730,7,20382,20443,'00:14:09.280','00:14:11.806','Well, I\'ll be on the 4:30\ntrain back to Stockholm.',-1),(105731,7,20447,20477,'00:14:11.960','00:14:13.246','Unless we get snowed in.',-1),(105732,7,20499,20526,'00:14:14.160','00:14:15.286','I\'m joking...',-1),(105733,7,20530,20599,'00:14:15.440','00:14:18.330','You\'ll be home tonight,\nif that\'s what you wish.',-1),(105734,7,21556,21582,'00:14:58.200','00:14:59.281','Welcome.',-1),(105735,7,21587,21612,'00:14:59.480','00:15:00.527','Come inside.',-1),(105736,7,21635,21675,'00:15:01.480','00:15:03.130','It\'s warm.',-1),(105737,7,21680,21713,'00:15:03.360','00:15:04.725','How do you do?',-1),(105738,7,21867,21904,'00:15:11.160','00:15:12.685','So,',-1),(105739,7,21935,21968,'00:15:13.960','00:15:15.371','what do you know about me?',-1),(105740,7,21983,22057,'00:15:15.960','00:15:19.043','You used to run one of the largest\nindustrial firms in the country.',-1),(105741,7,22060,22119,'00:15:19.200','00:15:21.646','\"Used to.\" That\'s correct.\nOh, I didn\'t mean that.',-1),(105742,7,22123,22166,'00:15:21.800','00:15:23.609','Should I stay? No.',-1),(105743,7,22178,22256,'00:15:24.120','00:15:27.363','My grandfather forged the tracks',-1),(105744,7,22260,22312,'00:15:27.520','00:15:29.682','that the 4:30 train\nwill take you home on.',-1),(105745,7,22326,22374,'00:15:30.280','00:15:32.282','We stitched this\ncountry together.',-1),(105746,7,22378,22491,'00:15:32.440','00:15:37.162','We made the steel, milled the\nlumber that built modern Sweden.',-1),(105747,7,22495,22573,'00:15:37.320','00:15:40.563','And what do you think our most\nprofitable product now is?',-1),(105748,7,22577,22608,'00:15:40.720','00:15:42.006','Fertilizer. Heh, heh.',-1),(105749,7,22611,22678,'00:15:42.160','00:15:44.925','I\'m not obsessed by the declining\nhealth of the company.',-1),(105750,7,22681,22744,'00:15:45.080','00:15:47.686','But I am with the\nsettling of accounts.',-1),(105751,7,22749,22804,'00:15:47.880','00:15:50.201','And the clock is ticking.\nI need your help.',-1),(105752,7,22808,22843,'00:15:50.360','00:15:51.805','I\'m... Doing what?',-1),(105753,7,22847,22905,'00:15:51.960','00:15:54.406','Officially, assisting\nwith my memoirs.',-1),(105754,7,22911,23020,'00:15:54.640','00:15:59.168','But what you\'ll really be doing',-1),(105755,7,23023,23120,'00:15:59.320','00:16:03.370','is solving a mystery by\ndoing what you do so well.',-1),(105756,7,23125,23183,'00:16:03.560','00:16:05.961','Your recent legal\nmishap notwithstanding.',-1),(105757,7,23186,23292,'00:16:06.120','00:16:10.523','You will be investigating\nthieves, misers, bullies,',-1),(105758,7,23296,23429,'00:16:10.680','00:16:16.210','the most detestable collection of\npeople that you will ever meet.',-1),(105759,7,23435,23469,'00:16:16.480','00:16:17.891','My family.',-1),(105760,7,23640,23718,'00:16:25.040','00:16:28.283','Would you like to sit?\nI could possibly clear a place if necessary.',-1),(105761,7,23722,23774,'00:16:28.440','00:16:30.602','Did you make it?\nHave you something for me?',-1),(105762,7,23859,23964,'00:16:34.160','00:16:38.529','I am on welfare, I do not administer it.\nThis is not enough.',-1),(105763,7,23969,24120,'00:16:38.720','00:16:45.001','<i> Only one thing left to do I\ncan hurt someone like you </i>',-1),(105764,7,24138,24233,'00:16:45.760','00:16:49.731','<i> Tear you out For all\nto see these lies N</i>',-1),(105765,7,24237,24269,'00:16:49.880','00:16:51.211','No, thank you.',-1),(105766,7,24344,24374,'00:16:54.360','00:16:55.600','This <i>is</i> Harriet.',-1),(105767,7,24412,24480,'00:16:57.200','00:17:00.010','The granddaughter of\nmy brother Richard.',-1),(105768,7,24493,24565,'00:17:00.560','00:17:03.564','Richard was a Nazi\nof the first order,',-1),(105769,7,24573,24700,'00:17:03.880','00:17:09.205','joining the Nationalist Socialist\nFreedom League when he was 17.',-1),(105770,7,24704,24815,'00:17:09.360','00:17:13.968','Isn\'t it interesting how fascists always\nsteal the word \"freedom\"? Heh, heh.',-1),(105771,7,24865,24956,'00:17:16.080','00:17:19.846','Oh, the 4:30. Yes, I know. Okay.',-1),(105772,7,24960,25076,'00:17:20.000','00:17:24.847','Anyway, Richard died a martyr\nto the Nazi cause in 1940.',-1),(105773,7,25080,25143,'00:17:25.000','00:17:27.651','Missed all the real excitement.',-1),(105774,7,25152,25251,'00:17:28.000','00:17:32.130','But not the opportunity to regularly\nbeat his wife, Margareta,',-1),(105775,7,25255,25297,'00:17:32.320','00:17:34.049','and their son, Gottfried.',-1),(105776,7,25301,25342,'00:17:34.240','00:17:35.924','Now, Gottfried,\nHarriet\'s father,',-1),(105777,7,25345,25411,'00:17:36.080','00:17:38.811','was what they used to\ncall a good-time Charlie.',-1),(105778,7,25415,25478,'00:17:38.960','00:17:41.611','They still call them that.\nDo they? Okay.',-1),(105779,7,25482,25539,'00:17:41.760','00:17:44.161','He was a charmer, a\nladies\' man and a drunk.',-1),(105780,7,25543,25614,'00:17:44.320','00:17:47.290','In other words, a born salesman.\nWhich he did for the company,',-1),(105781,7,25618,25684,'00:17:47.440','00:17:50.171','traveling around and taking\nclients out to dinner.',-1),(105782,7,25687,25743,'00:17:50.320','00:17:52.641','Well, somebody\'s gotta do it.\nThat\'s right.',-1),(105783,7,25748,25820,'00:17:52.840','00:17:55.844','Anyway, ahem, he died in 1965.',-1),(105784,7,25824,25872,'00:17:56.000','00:17:58.002','Drowned, drunk,\nhere on the island.',-1),(105785,7,25875,25982,'00:17:58.160','00:18:02.609','His wife, Isabella, who had been pretty\nmuch useless as a parent before,',-1),(105786,7,25986,26043,'00:18:02.760','00:18:05.127','became even more so\nafter his death,',-1),(105787,7,26046,26111,'00:18:05.280','00:18:07.965','which is when I began\nlooking after the children.',-1),(105788,7,26114,26186,'00:18:08.120','00:18:11.124','Martin, who runs Vanger\nIndustries, now that I\'m retired.',-1),(105789,7,26190,26230,'00:18:11.280','00:18:12.930','That\'s right, I Googled him.',-1),(105790,7,26233,26262,'00:18:13.080','00:18:14.286','And Harriet.',-1),(105791,7,26289,26386,'00:18:15.400','00:18:19.450','Ah. She was bright, curious,',-1),(105792,7,26399,26469,'00:18:19.960','00:18:22.884','a winning combination\nin any person.',-1),(105793,7,26483,26555,'00:18:23.480','00:18:26.484','And beautiful. Yeah.',-1),(105794,7,26588,26632,'00:18:27.840','00:18:29.683','Something happened to her?',-1),(105795,7,26636,26689,'00:18:29.840','00:18:32.081','Someone in the family\nmurdered Harriet,',-1),(105796,7,26706,26753,'00:18:32.760','00:18:34.728','and for the past 40 years,',-1),(105797,7,26758,26812,'00:18:34.920','00:18:37.207','has been trying to\ndrive me insane.',-1),(105798,7,26864,26938,'00:18:39.360','00:18:42.443','<i>It was\nSeptember 24th, 1966.</i>',-1),(105799,7,26943,26985,'00:18:42.640','00:18:44.404','A Saturday.',-1),(105800,7,26990,27030,'00:18:44.600','00:18:46.284','Harriet was 16.',-1),(105801,7,27036,27062,'00:18:46.520','00:18:47.601','My brothers',-1),(105802,7,27066,27165,'00:18:47.760','00:18:51.890','<i>and their wives and their children and\ngrandchildren were all gathered here</i>',-1),(105803,7,27168,27242,'00:18:52.040','00:18:55.089','<i>for our loathsome annual\nboard meeting and dinner.</i>',-1),(105804,7,27245,27343,'00:18:55.240','00:18:59.325','<i>It was also the day the yacht\nclub held their autumn parade.</i>',-1),(105805,7,27347,27423,'00:18:59.480','00:19:02.643','<i>Harriet, with one or two school\nfriends, went into town to see it.</i>',-1),(105806,7,27427,27501,'00:19:02.800','00:19:05.883','She returned a\nlittle after 2:00.',-1),(105807,7,27505,27599,'00:19:06.080','00:19:09.971','<i>She came into the parlor.\nShe asked if she could talk to me.</i>',-1),(105808,7,27602,27656,'00:19:10.120','00:19:12.361','I honestly don\'t remember\nwhat I was doing',-1),(105809,7,27660,27705,'00:19:12.520','00:19:14.409','that I thought was\nmore important,',-1),(105810,7,27709,27768,'00:19:14.560','00:19:17.040','<i>but I told her to give\nme a few minutes.</i>',-1),(105811,7,27810,27925,'00:19:18.760','00:19:23.561','It was during those few minutes\nthat something else occurred.',-1),(105812,7,27992,28075,'00:19:26.360','00:19:29.807','<i>The accident had nothing\nto do with Harriet,</i>',-1),(105813,7,28079,28106,'00:19:29.960','00:19:31.086','and yet everything.',-1),(105814,7,28129,28206,'00:19:32.080','00:19:35.289','<i>Heh. It was chaos as everybody\nput down what they were doing.</i>',-1),(105815,7,28211,28267,'00:19:35.480','00:19:37.801','<i>Police, ambulance, fire brigade,</i>',-1),(105816,7,28271,28365,'00:19:37.960','00:19:41.885','<i>reporters, photographers, onlookers\nall quickly arrived from town</i>',-1),(105817,7,28368,28477,'00:19:42.040','00:19:46.568','<i>just as we on the island, the family,\nhurried to the bridge from our side.</i>',-1),(105818,7,28481,28515,'00:19:46.720','00:19:48.165','<i>The driver of the car,</i>',-1),(105819,7,28519,28557,'00:19:48.320','00:19:49.890','a man named Aronsson,',-1),(105820,7,28561,28617,'00:19:50.080','00:19:52.401','<i>was pinned and severely injured.</i>',-1),(105821,7,28621,28691,'00:19:52.560','00:19:55.484','<i>We tried desperately to pry\nhim loose with our hands</i>',-1),(105822,7,28695,28752,'00:19:55.640','00:19:58.041','<i>since metal tools might spark.</i>',-1),(105823,7,28785,28875,'00:19:59.400','00:20:03.166','<i>It was an hour after the crash\nthat Harriet was in the kitchen.</i>',-1),(105824,7,28879,28930,'00:20:03.320','00:20:05.448','Anna herself saw her.',-1),(105825,7,29030,29147,'00:20:09.600','00:20:14.481','<i>Well, we finally got poor Aronsson out\nof his car and off to the hospital.</i>',-1),(105826,7,29160,29235,'00:20:15.000','00:20:18.163','<i>Just as we from our side</i>',-1),(105827,7,29240,29312,'00:20:18.360','00:20:21.364','<i>slowly drifted back\nto the house.</i>',-1),(105828,7,29359,29413,'00:20:23.320','00:20:25.561','<i>The sun was down, the\nexcitement over.</i>',-1),(105829,7,29422,29473,'00:20:25.920','00:20:28.082','<i>We sat down to dinner.</i>',-1),(105830,7,29477,29516,'00:20:28.240','00:20:29.844','<i>It was then that I noticed.</i>',-1),(105831,7,29528,29563,'00:20:30.360','00:20:31.805','<i>Harriet wasn\'t there.</i>',-1),(105832,7,29592,29640,'00:20:33.040','00:20:35.008','<i>And she wasn\'t there\nthe next morning.</i>',-1),(105833,7,29662,29687,'00:20:35.920','00:20:36.967','<i>Or the next.</i>',-1),(105834,7,29704,29738,'00:20:37.680','00:20:39.091','Or the next 40 years.',-1),(105835,7,29827,29868,'00:20:42.800','00:20:44.529','<i>What was she going to tell me?</i>',-1),(105836,7,29873,29951,'00:20:44.720','00:20:47.963','Why didn\'t I make time for her?\nWhy didn\'t I listen?',-1),(105837,7,29954,30036,'00:20:48.120','00:20:51.522','And she couldn\'t have just run away?\nNo. Not without being seen.',-1),(105838,7,30040,30079,'00:20:51.680','00:20:53.330','The firemen stayed out all night',-1),(105839,7,30084,30131,'00:20:53.520','00:20:55.488','<i>on the bridge pumping\nup gasoline.</i>',-1),(105840,7,30135,30203,'00:20:55.640','00:20:58.484','<i>No one swam across\nor took a boat.</i>',-1),(105841,7,30207,30272,'00:20:58.640','00:21:01.371','All the boats were still\ntied up on this side Sunday.',-1),(105842,7,30276,30339,'00:21:01.520','00:21:04.126','Believe me, I checked.',-1),(105843,7,30388,30434,'00:21:06.200','00:21:08.123','She couldn\'t have\njust fallen and drowned?',-1),(105844,7,30438,30553,'00:21:08.280','00:21:13.047','No. The currents aren\'t strong here.\nAnything that falls in the water turns up.',-1),(105845,7,30556,30587,'00:21:13.200','00:21:14.486','Like her father.',-1),(105846,7,30591,30648,'00:21:14.640','00:21:17.041','His body didn\'t drift\nmore than 10 meters',-1),(105847,7,30652,30710,'00:21:17.200','00:21:19.601','when he drowned the year before.',-1),(105848,7,30714,30790,'00:21:19.760','00:21:22.923','Oh, no. Someone killed her.',-1),(105849,7,30793,30857,'00:21:23.080','00:21:25.731','Someone on the island that day.',-1),(105850,7,30861,30909,'00:21:25.880','00:21:27.882','Someone close enough to know',-1),(105851,7,30912,31018,'00:21:28.040','00:21:32.443','what she used to give me\neach year on my birthday.',-1),(105852,7,31065,31117,'00:21:34.400','00:21:36.562','Those are from her.',-1),(105853,7,31128,31212,'00:21:37.040','00:21:40.522','And the rest, from her killer.',-1),(105854,7,31521,31552,'00:21:53.400','00:21:54.686','Who knows about these?',-1),(105855,7,31556,31640,'00:21:54.840','00:21:58.367','There\'s me, the\npolice, the killer,',-1),(105856,7,31649,31674,'00:21:58.720','00:21:59.767','and now you.',-1),(105857,7,31891,31949,'00:22:08.800','00:22:11.246','<i>After the police\ninvestigation evaporated,</i>',-1),(105858,7,31953,32021,'00:22:11.400','00:22:14.210','<i>I kept at it, studying all\nthe information there was.</i>',-1),(105859,7,32033,32126,'00:22:14.720','00:22:18.611','I have spent half my life examining\nthe events of a single day.',-1),(105860,7,32130,32182,'00:22:18.760','00:22:20.922','I understand your frustration,',-1),(105861,7,32185,32254,'00:22:21.080','00:22:23.924','but what you\'re asking me to\ndo, it\'s a waste of money.',-1),(105862,7,32257,32333,'00:22:24.080','00:22:27.243','But we haven\'t discussed your fee.\nWe don\'t need to.',-1),(105863,7,32337,32372,'00:22:27.400','00:22:28.845','Thank you.',-1),(105864,7,32376,32463,'00:22:29.000','00:22:32.641','I can\'t find something you\'ve\nbeen unable to find in 40 years.',-1),(105865,7,32467,32559,'00:22:32.800','00:22:36.646','You don\'t know that.\nYou have a very keen investigative mind.',-1),(105866,7,32575,32609,'00:22:37.320','00:22:38.731','Here\'s what I propose:',-1),(105867,7,32613,32655,'00:22:38.880','00:22:40.644','You come stay on the island.',-1),(105868,7,32659,32737,'00:22:40.800','00:22:44.043','I have a nice little cottage\nby the water you can use.',-1),(105869,7,32740,32786,'00:22:44.200','00:22:46.123','You study the\nmaterial I send you.',-1),(105870,7,32790,32844,'00:22:46.280','00:22:48.521','You find something I\'ve\nmissed or you don\'t.',-1),(105871,7,32849,32923,'00:22:48.720','00:22:51.803','What you\'re asking me to do is set\naside my life and career for...',-1),(105872,7,32927,32976,'00:22:51.960','00:22:54.008','Think of this as a\nwell-deserved holiday.',-1),(105873,7,32979,33089,'00:22:54.160','00:22:58.722','A way of avoiding all those people that\nyou might want to avoid right now.',-1),(105874,7,33093,33154,'00:22:58.880','00:23:01.451','As for compensation, I\'ll\npay you double your salary',-1),(105875,7,33158,33198,'00:23:01.600','00:23:03.284','for as many months as it takes.',-1),(105876,7,33203,33270,'00:23:03.480','00:23:06.290','Quadruple it if you solve the mystery.\nHerr Vanger...',-1),(105877,7,33274,33326,'00:23:06.440','00:23:08.602','I\'m not done.\nI will throw in one more thing,',-1),(105878,7,33330,33382,'00:23:08.760','00:23:10.922','even though you\'re a\nterrible negotiator.',-1),(105879,7,33385,33448,'00:23:11.080','00:23:13.686','It\'s something you want\nmore than anything else,',-1),(105880,7,33452,33535,'00:23:13.840','00:23:17.322','and it can\'t be bought at any price.\nSo let me give it to you.',-1),(105881,7,33552,33622,'00:23:18.040','00:23:20.930','Hans-Erik Wennerstrm.',-1),(105882,7,33643,33698,'00:23:21.800','00:23:24.121','He began his career\nworking for me,',-1),(105883,7,33702,33791,'00:23:24.280','00:23:27.966','and I have followed it with\ninterest, shall we say, ever since.',-1),(105884,7,33863,33896,'00:23:30.960','00:23:32.371','You were right about him.',-1),(105885,7,33917,33968,'00:23:33.240','00:23:35.368','You just couldn\'t prove it.',-1),(105886,7,34703,34784,'00:24:05.960','00:24:09.362','We\'re in the middle of the worst crisis\never, and you\'re writing a memoir.',-1),(105887,7,34788,34876,'00:24:09.520','00:24:13.206','You fired me. I need something to do.\nYou fired you.',-1),(105888,7,34927,34977,'00:24:15.320','00:24:17.402','I need you here, not\nthe North Pole.',-1),(105889,7,34982,35040,'00:24:17.600','00:24:20.001','Mikael, you know what this\nis going to look like.',-1),(105890,7,35043,35093,'00:24:20.160','00:24:22.242','Like I\'ve been gutted.\nI\'m running away. I am.',-1),(105891,7,35097,35166,'00:24:22.400','00:24:25.290','Wennerstrm wants to see me wave\na white flag, not a red flag.',-1),(105892,7,35171,35247,'00:24:25.480','00:24:28.643','If it looks like there\'s a problem\nbetween us, it\'ll satisfy him.',-1),(105893,7,35251,35283,'00:24:28.800','00:24:30.165','There is a problem between us.',-1),(105894,7,35288,35350,'00:24:30.360','00:24:32.931','He won\'t be satisfied\nuntil he shuts us down.',-1),(105895,7,35365,35459,'00:24:33.560','00:24:37.485','You\'re leaving me to fight him alone.\nIt\'s four hours by train.',-1),(105896,7,35585,35639,'00:24:42.720','00:24:44.961','It\'s not the North Pole.',-1),(105897,7,36637,36675,'00:25:26.560','00:25:28.164','Hey, hey...',-1),(105898,7,38057,38132,'00:26:25.720','00:26:28.849','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(105899,7,38384,38467,'00:26:39.360','00:26:42.807','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(105900,7,38615,38651,'00:26:48.960','00:26:50.485','What?',-1),(105901,7,38663,38691,'00:26:50.960','00:26:52.166','Some milk?',-1),(105902,7,39147,39229,'00:27:11.160','00:27:14.562','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(105903,7,39276,39338,'00:27:16.520','00:27:19.091','Oh, yeah. These as well.',-1),(105904,7,40242,40275,'00:27:56.760','00:27:58.125','You\'re Mr. Palmgren\'s daughter?',-1),(105905,7,40279,40321,'00:27:58.320','00:28:00.049','His ward.\nHe doesn\'t have a daughter.',-1),(105906,7,40367,40402,'00:28:01.960','00:28:03.450','Please.',-1),(105907,7,40436,40500,'00:28:04.840','00:28:07.525','He\'s had severe\ncerebral hemorrhaging,',-1),(105908,7,40504,40589,'00:28:07.680','00:28:11.241','<i>either from the fall itself or from\na stroke that led to the fall.</i>',-1),(105909,7,40594,40639,'00:28:11.440','00:28:13.329','<i>His blood pressure\nis still high.</i>',-1),(105910,7,40643,40715,'00:28:13.480','00:28:16.484','<i>I\'m hopeful he\'ll regain consciousness,\nbut that\'s not assured.</i>',-1),(105911,7,40719,40775,'00:28:16.640','00:28:18.961','<i>And it\'s possible,\neven if he does,</i>',-1),(105912,7,40778,40846,'00:28:19.120','00:28:21.930','<i>that there will be\nneurological damage.</i>',-1),(105913,7,41361,41405,'00:28:43.400','00:28:45.209','Oh, jeez.',-1),(105914,7,41532,41574,'00:28:50.520','00:28:52.284','Hi. I\'m Gunnar.',-1),(105915,7,41601,41626,'00:28:53.400','00:28:54.447','The caretaker.',-1),(105916,7,41630,41687,'00:28:54.600','00:28:56.967','Oh, hey, Gunnar. Come in. Okay.',-1),(105917,7,41796,41860,'00:29:01.520','00:29:04.171','You want to put it in there?\nOkay.',-1),(105918,7,42053,42095,'00:29:12.240','00:29:13.969','You\'re an author.',-1),(105919,7,42098,42196,'00:29:14.120','00:29:18.205','Well, I\'m doing a\nbiography of Herr Vanger.',-1),(105920,7,42206,42238,'00:29:18.600','00:29:19.931','Oh.',-1),(105921,7,42241,42319,'00:29:20.080','00:29:23.323','I saw you on television.\nThat\'s unfortunate.',-1),(105922,7,42323,42366,'00:29:23.480','00:29:25.289','Bit of trouble, I guess.',-1),(105923,7,42388,42450,'00:29:26.200','00:29:28.771','No jail time though.\nThat\'s good. No.',-1),(105924,7,42467,42526,'00:29:29.480','00:29:31.926','Cost you a lot of\nmoney though, yeah?',-1),(105925,7,42573,42606,'00:29:33.880','00:29:35.291','There.',-1),(105926,7,42682,42792,'00:29:38.440','00:29:43.002','The entire island\nis owned by my family.',-1),(105927,7,42829,42953,'00:29:44.560','00:29:49.726','Your closest neighbor\nis my brother Harald,',-1),(105928,7,42974,43030,'00:29:50.600','00:29:52.921','another Nazi, if\nyou can believe.',-1),(105929,7,43033,43071,'00:29:53.080','00:29:54.650','Two in the family.',-1),(105930,7,43075,43175,'00:29:54.800','00:29:58.964','Oh, yes, he\'s quite\ndetestable, to put it nicely.',-1),(105931,7,43178,43261,'00:29:59.120','00:30:02.567','But you\'ll probably never see him.\nHe\'s a recluse.',-1),(105932,7,43265,43332,'00:30:02.720','00:30:05.530','He was there that day?\nIndeed, he was.',-1),(105933,7,43336,43419,'00:30:05.680','00:30:09.162','His daughter, Cecilia,\nlives over there.',-1),(105934,7,43432,43464,'00:30:09.680','00:30:11.011','They don\'t speak.',-1),(105935,7,43468,43517,'00:30:11.200','00:30:13.248','Does anybody speak to\nanybody on this island?',-1),(105936,7,43521,43598,'00:30:13.400','00:30:16.609','Ha, ha. Actually, Isabella,\nHarriet\'s mother, who lives there,',-1),(105937,7,43602,43695,'00:30:16.760','00:30:20.651','she speaks to Harald, which is one\nof the reasons I don\'t speak to her.',-1),(105938,7,43699,43726,'00:30:20.800','00:30:21.926','Right.',-1),(105939,7,43729,43806,'00:30:22.080','00:30:25.289','Cecilia\'s brother, Birger,\nlives over there.',-1),(105940,7,43810,43850,'00:30:25.440','00:30:27.090','Who doesn\'t he speak to?',-1),(105941,7,43853,43880,'00:30:27.240','00:30:28.366','You, probably.',-1),(105942,7,43884,43969,'00:30:28.520','00:30:32.047','But you wouldn\'t want him to.\nHe can be just as unpleasant as Harald.',-1),(105943,7,43972,44016,'00:30:32.200','00:30:34.009','Quickly losing track\nof who\'s who here.',-1),(105944,7,44019,44091,'00:30:34.160','00:30:37.164','Ho-ho-ho.\nHow you\'ll wish it were always so.',-1),(105945,7,44095,44190,'00:30:37.320','00:30:41.291','Soon you will know us all only\ntoo well, with my apologies.',-1),(105946,7,44197,44319,'00:30:41.560','00:30:46.646','Now, out there, my grandnephew\nMartin\'s house, Harriet\'s brother.',-1),(105947,7,44323,44357,'00:30:46.800','00:30:48.211','Who speaks to him?',-1),(105948,7,44360,44441,'00:30:48.360','00:30:51.728','I speak to him. He runs the company\nnow, as I think I told you.',-1),(105949,7,44494,44582,'00:30:53.920','00:30:57.606','Oh. Someone\'s shooting his dinner.\nGunnar, probably.',-1),(105950,7,44586,44619,'00:30:57.760','00:30:59.125','Oh, yes, I met him earlier.',-1),(105951,7,44622,44709,'00:30:59.280','00:31:02.887','He was 19 when\nHarriet disappeared.',-1),(105952,7,44723,44765,'00:31:03.480','00:31:05.209','Well, he lives over there.',-1),(105953,7,44814,44853,'00:31:07.280','00:31:08.884','And you live there. Sorry?',-1),(105954,7,44856,44893,'00:31:09.040','00:31:10.565','Your house.',-1),(105955,7,44931,45000,'00:31:12.160','00:31:15.004','Oh. Ha. Oh, yes.',-1),(105956,7,45013,45053,'00:31:15.560','00:31:17.244','Yes, you\'re right.',-1),(105957,7,45057,45098,'00:31:17.400','00:31:19.084','The man who hires the detective',-1),(105958,7,45101,45181,'00:31:19.240','00:31:22.562','should always be kept\non the suspects list.',-1),(105959,7,46443,46483,'00:32:15.160','00:32:16.810','Her mother.',-1),(105960,7,47176,47231,'00:32:45.680','00:32:47.967','But what about the search?\nPlease.',-1),(105961,7,47258,47328,'00:32:49.120','00:32:52.010','Please. I beg you.',-1),(105962,7,48078,48163,'00:33:23.280','00:33:26.807','<i>The fact that I never\nfound a body was not surprising.</i>',-1),(105963,7,48167,48237,'00:33:26.960','00:33:29.884','<i>You can\'t dig up\nan entire island.</i>',-1),(105964,7,48266,48320,'00:33:31.120','00:33:33.361','But neither could I\nfind the motive.',-1),(105965,7,48324,48388,'00:33:33.520','00:33:36.205','Was it spontaneous?\nWas it calculated?',-1),(105966,7,48392,48449,'00:33:36.360','00:33:38.727','Did she know something\nsomeone wished she didn\'t?',-1),(105967,7,48453,48538,'00:33:38.880','00:33:42.441','Was it about business?\nBusiness? Well, she was 16.',-1),(105968,7,48542,48584,'00:33:42.600','00:33:44.364','And very bright.',-1),(105969,7,48588,48654,'00:33:44.520','00:33:47.251','Henrik told me and many others\nhe could easily see her',-1),(105970,7,48657,48698,'00:33:47.400','00:33:49.084','running the company one day.',-1),(105971,7,48711,48775,'00:33:49.640','00:33:52.325','She was with some friends\nthat day at a parade.',-1),(105972,7,48779,48868,'00:33:52.480','00:33:56.201','She told them she was feeling unwell.\nShe left early.',-1),(105973,7,48872,48957,'00:33:56.360','00:33:59.887','But they also told me she\nkept secrets from them too.',-1),(105974,7,48964,49047,'00:34:00.200','00:34:03.647','The main thing I learned was that\nteenage girls are complicated.',-1),(105975,7,49051,49106,'00:34:03.800','00:34:06.087','I have one. Oh, then you know.',-1),(105976,7,49112,49187,'00:34:06.360','00:34:09.489','I wanted to, uh, ahem,',-1),(105977,7,49191,49234,'00:34:09.640','00:34:11.449','ask you about this.',-1),(105978,7,49298,49361,'00:34:14.120','00:34:16.726','She received that from\nHenrik the Christmas before.',-1),(105979,7,49420,49492,'00:34:19.200','00:34:22.170','I\'ve studied it more\ntimes than I can say.',-1),(105980,7,49524,49557,'00:34:23.520','00:34:24.885','I know every page of it.',-1),(105981,7,49561,49617,'00:34:25.080','00:34:27.401','It\'s the last page I was curious about.\nAs was I.',-1),(105982,7,49621,49715,'00:34:27.560','00:34:31.485','It\'s a list of names, numbers and\nit must have some significance.',-1),(105983,7,49719,49755,'00:34:31.640','00:34:33.130','All local phone numbers.',-1),(105984,7,49758,49813,'00:34:33.280','00:34:35.567','The first belonged\nto a woman, Margot,',-1),(105985,7,49818,49888,'00:34:35.760','00:34:38.684','whose mother was Magda, who\ndenied knowing Harriet.',-1),(105986,7,49892,49965,'00:34:38.840','00:34:41.889','The fourth, R.L., belonged\nto Rosmarie Larsson,',-1),(105987,7,49968,50062,'00:34:42.040','00:34:45.931','an elderly woman who\ndied some years before.',-1),(105988,7,50065,50171,'00:34:46.080','00:34:50.483','The other three were not connected\nin any way that I could find.',-1),(105989,7,50185,50263,'00:34:51.080','00:34:54.323','I reminded you of things you\'d\nrather forget, and I\'m sorry.',-1),(105990,7,50268,50316,'00:34:54.520','00:34:56.522','I can\'t forget.',-1),(105991,7,50349,50391,'00:34:57.880','00:34:59.644','It\'s my Rebecka case.',-1),(105992,7,50411,50445,'00:35:00.480','00:35:01.891','Uh, I don\'t know what that is.',-1),(105993,7,50461,50574,'00:35:02.560','00:35:07.282','Every policeman has at least one\nunsolved case to obsess over.',-1),(105994,7,50592,50651,'00:35:08.040','00:35:10.486','Back then we had an\nOfficer Torstensson.',-1),(105995,7,50655,50724,'00:35:10.640','00:35:13.530','Year after year, he kept going\nback to this Rebecka case.',-1),(105996,7,50728,50807,'00:35:13.680','00:35:16.968','Taking out the files,\nstudying them over and over.',-1),(105997,7,50810,50860,'00:35:17.120','00:35:19.168','We were young.\nWe laughed at him.',-1),(105998,7,50863,50910,'00:35:19.320','00:35:21.288','And that was also a\nmissing-girl case?',-1),(105999,7,50914,50980,'00:35:21.440','00:35:24.205','No, no, no, that\'s not\nwhy I mention it.',-1),(106000,7,50984,51054,'00:35:24.360','00:35:27.284','I\'m talking about the\nsoul of a policeman.',-1),(106001,7,51068,51137,'00:35:27.840','00:35:30.730','<i>Poor old Torstensson\nnever solved it.</i>',-1),(106002,7,51141,51197,'00:35:30.880','00:35:33.247','<i>And he never let it go.</i>',-1),(106003,7,51369,51416,'00:35:40.400','00:35:42.368','So how\'s Mr.\nPalmgren doing?',-1),(106004,7,51428,51496,'00:35:42.840','00:35:45.684','I heard he had a stroke\nof some kind? Huh?',-1),(106005,7,51500,51525,'00:35:45.840','00:35:46.887','It\'s terrible.',-1),(106006,7,51556,51626,'00:35:48.200','00:35:51.124','Now, what exactly do you do\nat this security company?',-1),(106007,7,51630,51673,'00:35:51.280','00:35:53.044','Make coffee, sort mail.',-1),(106008,7,51676,51717,'00:35:53.200','00:35:54.884','But not full-time.',-1),(106009,7,51729,51770,'00:35:55.400','00:35:57.084','Not even part-time consistently.',-1),(106010,7,51773,51892,'00:35:57.240','00:36:02.201','They somehow got along without\ncoffee or mail in July and August?',-1),(106011,7,52005,52057,'00:36:06.880','00:36:09.042','How much do you make there?\nEnough.',-1),(106012,7,52099,52125,'00:36:10.800','00:36:11.881','How much is your rent?',-1),(106013,7,52128,52165,'00:36:12.040','00:36:13.565','<i>I Pay my rent.</i>',-1),(106014,7,52252,52297,'00:36:17.200','00:36:19.043','And when was the last\ntime you were late?',-1),(106015,7,52300,52325,'00:36:19.200','00:36:20.247','Never.',-1),(106016,7,52356,52439,'00:36:21.520','00:36:24.967','You think that thing through your\neyebrow makes you attractive?',-1),(106017,7,52495,52521,'00:36:27.320','00:36:28.401','Here\'s the problem.',-1),(106018,7,52562,52634,'00:36:30.120','00:36:33.090','There\'s a discrepancy\nbetween the obligation',-1),(106019,7,52637,52736,'00:36:33.240','00:36:37.370','of Mr. Palmgren\'s guardianship and\nthe management of your finances.',-1),(106020,7,52740,52818,'00:36:37.520','00:36:40.763','There\'s no discrepancy.\nIt was clear I could manage my own finances.',-1),(106021,7,52822,52849,'00:36:40.920','00:36:42.046','That is not clear to me.',-1),(106022,7,52852,52905,'00:36:42.200','00:36:44.407','I\'m not a child.\nYou are not. But you were.',-1),(106023,7,52909,52962,'00:36:44.560','00:36:46.767','And between then and now,\nyou were committed',-1),(106024,7,52966,53034,'00:36:46.920','00:36:49.764','to the locked ward of St.\nStefan\'s where you continued',-1),(106025,7,53038,53089,'00:36:49.920','00:36:52.048','to display violent aggression.',-1),(106026,7,53106,53170,'00:36:52.760','00:36:55.445','And you failed to adapt\nto four foster homes,',-1),(106027,7,53174,53254,'00:36:55.600','00:36:58.922','arrested twice for intoxication,\ntwice for narcotics,',-1),(106028,7,53257,53355,'00:36:59.080','00:37:03.130','again for assault, smashing\na bottle into a man\'s face.',-1),(106029,7,53359,53414,'00:37:03.320','00:37:05.607','And it\'s not even that long ago.',-1),(106030,7,53418,53523,'00:37:05.760','00:37:10.129','You may have conned Mr. Palmgren\ninto thinking that you have changed,',-1),(106031,7,53526,53570,'00:37:10.280','00:37:12.123','but when I\'m looking at this,',-1),(106032,7,53574,53670,'00:37:12.280','00:37:16.251','not to mention the way\nyou\'re looking at me now,',-1),(106033,7,53673,53717,'00:37:16.400','00:37:18.209','I don\'t think you have.',-1),(106034,7,53727,53791,'00:37:18.640','00:37:21.325','So the good old Mr\n. Palmgren days are over.',-1),(106035,7,53795,53867,'00:37:21.480','00:37:24.484','Starting now, you will be\ngiven a monthly allowance.',-1),(106036,7,53871,53927,'00:37:24.640','00:37:26.961','You\'ll provide me with\nreceipts for your expenses.',-1),(106037,7,53930,54007,'00:37:27.120','00:37:30.329','If the numbers don\'t balance, I assume\nthe difference is going to drugs.',-1),(106038,7,54011,54056,'00:37:30.480','00:37:32.369','I\'ve taken care of\nmyself since I was 10.',-1),(106039,7,54061,54096,'00:37:32.560','00:37:34.005','The state has taken care of you.',-1),(106040,7,54099,54165,'00:37:34.160','00:37:36.891','Miss Salander, please, look\nat me, this is important.',-1),(106041,7,54168,54249,'00:37:37.040','00:37:40.408','Since your behavior is\nelaborately documented in here,',-1),(106042,7,54254,54315,'00:37:40.600','00:37:43.126','it will shock no one if\nI chose an alternative',-1),(106043,7,54319,54400,'00:37:43.320','00:37:46.688','to the very lenient arrangement\nI have just outlined.',-1),(106044,7,54459,54559,'00:37:49.160','00:37:53.324','Would you prefer\ninstitutionalization?',-1),(106045,7,55061,55087,'00:38:14.240','00:38:15.321','Yes.',-1),(106046,7,55092,55130,'00:38:15.520','00:38:17.090','I\'m Liv. Oh, hi.',-1),(106047,7,55133,55173,'00:38:17.240','00:38:18.890','We\'re going to the same place.\nHop in.',-1),(106048,7,55176,55210,'00:38:19.040','00:38:20.451','Oh, good, thank you.',-1),(106049,7,55409,55485,'00:38:28.720','00:38:31.883','I found him at death\'s\ndoor, halfway up the hill.',-1),(106050,7,55491,55561,'00:38:32.160','00:38:35.050','I\'m afraid I\'m a little out of shape.\nIt\'s a climb for anyone.',-1),(106051,7,55564,55622,'00:38:35.200','00:38:37.601','- I should\'ve warned you. Come in.\n- Thank you, Martin.',-1),(106052,7,55626,55664,'00:38:37.760','00:38:39.364','Henrik says\ngreat things about you.',-1),(106053,7,55668,55775,'00:38:39.520','00:38:43.969','- Mmm. Martin? Smells wonderful.\n- No. Leave your shoes on.',-1),(106054,7,55778,55808,'00:38:44.120','00:38:45.360','What are we drinking?',-1),(106055,7,55812,55852,'00:38:45.520','00:38:47.204','What a place.\nLook at that view.',-1),(106056,7,55856,55941,'00:38:47.360','00:38:50.887','I used to work in the company\'s\npetrochemical division in Gteborg.',-1),(106057,7,55944,55982,'00:38:51.040','00:38:52.610','When it was sold,\nI went with it.',-1),(106058,7,55986,56017,'00:38:52.760','00:38:54.046','A dark day.',-1),(106059,7,56024,56103,'00:38:54.360','00:38:57.648','I live in Hong Kong, but come\nback to Stockholm for family events.',-1),(106060,7,56107,56164,'00:38:57.800','00:39:00.201','And I drive up to spend a\ncouple of days with Martin.',-1),(106061,7,56169,56251,'00:39:00.400','00:39:03.802','It\'s just the moose steak she wants.\nWho can blame her? It\'s wonderful.',-1),(106062,7,56307,56378,'00:39:06.160','00:39:09.084','Something\'s left open.\nDo you like this wine,',-1),(106063,7,56382,56473,'00:39:09.280','00:39:13.046','or you want to try something else?\nNo, no, it\'s fine.',-1),(106064,7,56579,56629,'00:39:17.480','00:39:19.562','You\'re writing a book\nnow, Martin said.',-1),(106065,7,56633,56696,'00:39:19.720','00:39:22.371','Henrik\'s biography. I love Henrik.\nHe\'s fascinating.',-1),(106066,7,56700,56732,'00:39:22.520','00:39:23.851','Martin too.',-1),(106067,7,56736,56813,'00:39:24.000','00:39:27.209','Together they are the\nold Sweden and the new.',-1),(106068,7,56816,56846,'00:39:27.360','00:39:28.600','Yes, they are.',-1),(106069,7,56889,56946,'00:39:30.400','00:39:32.767','You know about Harriet, right?',-1),(106070,7,56967,57010,'00:39:33.640','00:39:35.449','You don\'t? Yes, I do.',-1),(106071,7,57038,57130,'00:39:36.600','00:39:40.446','The family doesn\'t want to talk about it,\nbut it can\'t be swept under the rug.',-1),(106072,7,57134,57180,'00:39:40.600','00:39:42.523','What can\'t? Harriet.',-1),(106073,7,57188,57217,'00:39:42.840','00:39:44.080','We can talk about it later.',-1),(106074,7,57221,57290,'00:39:44.240','00:39:47.084','Uh... We can talk about it now.',-1),(106075,7,57298,57348,'00:39:47.440','00:39:49.522','Liv knows everything\nabout my crazy family.',-1),(106076,7,57352,57411,'00:39:49.680','00:39:52.160','That\'s why she\'ll never marry me.\nThat\'s one reason.',-1),(106077,7,57415,57463,'00:39:52.320','00:39:54.322','I don\'t want to read\nabout that in the book.',-1),(106078,7,57467,57522,'00:39:54.480','00:39:56.767','Everything else is fine.\nHarriet certainly.',-1),(106079,7,57533,57619,'00:39:57.240','00:40:00.801','You know, everything\nchanged after that.',-1),(106080,7,57624,57679,'00:40:01.000','00:40:03.321','Not just the family, but\nthe company as well.',-1),(106081,7,57683,57733,'00:40:03.480','00:40:05.562','How so?\nWe\'re not Ericsson or Nordea.',-1),(106082,7,57737,57821,'00:40:05.720','00:40:09.247','But we\'re still the largest\nfamily-owned company in the country.',-1),(106083,7,57827,57878,'00:40:09.480','00:40:11.608','At our height we had\n40,000 employees.',-1),(106084,7,57883,57912,'00:40:11.800','00:40:13.040','We have half of that now.',-1),(106085,7,57916,58011,'00:40:13.200','00:40:17.125','And that downward slide began\nafter my sister\'s death.',-1),(106086,7,58100,58175,'00:40:20.840','00:40:23.969','It broke Henrik\'s\nentrepreneurial spirit',-1),(106087,7,58183,58209,'00:40:24.320','00:40:25.401','and his heart.',-1),(106088,7,58230,58295,'00:40:26.280','00:40:28.965','- Uh... You were here that day?\n- I came in later,',-1),(106089,7,58298,58365,'00:40:29.120','00:40:31.885','after the accident on the\nbridge, with the 4:30 train.',-1),(106090,7,58368,58440,'00:40:32.040','00:40:35.010','I know it well. A terrible day.',-1),(106091,7,58489,58530,'00:40:37.080','00:40:38.764','And the days after, you know?',-1),(106092,7,58534,58637,'00:40:38.920','00:40:43.209','Searching, not finding.\nEven worse.',-1),(106093,7,58657,58752,'00:40:44.080','00:40:48.005','This event, Mikael, it has to\nhave a big part in your book.',-1),(106094,7,59297,59359,'00:41:10.720','00:41:13.326','I got a call from\nsocial welfare.',-1),(106095,7,59376,59431,'00:41:14.040','00:41:16.327','I\'ve been assigned\na new guardian.',-1),(106096,7,60945,60978,'00:42:19.400','00:42:20.765','Hi. Hello.',-1),(106097,7,60982,61040,'00:42:20.920','00:42:23.366','I thought I\'d come\nover and say hello.',-1),(106098,7,61045,61130,'00:42:23.560','00:42:27.087','I\'m Cecilia. Oh, yes.\nPlease, come in.',-1),(106099,7,61209,61258,'00:42:30.400','00:42:32.448','Can I get you some coffee?',-1),(106100,7,61262,61317,'00:42:32.600','00:42:34.887','No, thank you.',-1),(106101,7,61542,61652,'00:42:44.280','00:42:48.842','We are all uncomfortable with the\nidea of a chronicle of our family.',-1),(106102,7,61656,61723,'00:42:49.040','00:42:51.805','It\'s not about the family.\nIt\'s about Henrik and the company.',-1),(106103,7,61730,61756,'00:42:52.120','00:42:53.201','Like I said.',-1),(106104,7,61793,61867,'00:42:54.720','00:42:57.803','It\'s not my intention to present\na malicious portrait of anyone.',-1),(106105,7,61871,61909,'00:42:57.960','00:42:59.564','Unlike the one\nthat landed you in court.',-1),(106106,7,61914,61991,'00:42:59.760','00:43:02.969','Unlike that one, yes.',-1),(106107,7,61998,62074,'00:43:03.280','00:43:06.443','So you\'re not really here to find\nout what happened to Harriet.',-1),(106108,7,62079,62171,'00:43:06.640','00:43:10.486','I can\'t ignore such a dramatic event,\nbut, no, that\'s by no means my focus.',-1),(106109,7,62175,62222,'00:43:10.640','00:43:12.608','Those boxes that Gunnar\ncarted down here,',-1),(106110,7,62226,62331,'00:43:12.760','00:43:17.129','which are where, in the closet now?\nThose weren\'t Henrik\'s investigation?',-1),(106111,7,62339,62468,'00:43:17.480','00:43:22.850','I wonder sometimes who\'s crazier, my\nNazi father or my obsessed uncle.',-1),(106112,7,62472,62511,'00:43:23.000','00:43:24.650','Since we\'re talking about her,',-1),(106113,7,62515,62568,'00:43:24.800','00:43:27.007','since you brought her\nup, what was she like?',-1),(106114,7,62571,62599,'00:43:27.160','00:43:28.321','What was Harriet like?',-1),(106115,7,62603,62667,'00:43:28.480','00:43:31.165','I\'m sure Henrik has told you.\nHe was my 