261,101338,'01:10:19.240','01:10:22.449','I haven\'t been around enough to\nreally know what\'s going on with you.',-1),(106362,7,101401,101510,'01:10:25.080','01:10:29.608','And I apologize for that.\nBut I\'d never want you not to tell me something',-1),(106363,7,101514,101571,'01:10:29.760','01:10:32.127','because you think I might\nnot want to hear it.',-1),(106364,7,101594,101634,'01:10:33.120','01:10:34.770','That\'s what I\'m doing.',-1),(106365,7,101666,101704,'01:10:36.120','01:10:37.690','<i>It should\'ve\nbeen me visiting you.</i>',-1),(106366,7,101708,101753,'01:10:37.840','01:10:39.729','I\'m sorry It\'s okay.',-1),(106367,7,101758,101808,'01:10:39.920','01:10:42.002','It was nice seeing you.',-1),(106368,7,101818,101852,'01:10:42.440','01:10:43.851','BYE-bye',-1),(106369,7,101861,101894,'01:10:44.240','01:10:45.605','I\'ll see you. Yeah.',-1),(106370,7,101899,101931,'01:10:45.800','01:10:47.131','Thanks.',-1),(106371,7,102000,102047,'01:10:50.000','01:10:51.968','Oh, don\'t go too hard\non the Catholics.',-1),(106372,7,102050,102098,'01:10:52.120','01:10:54.088','The what?\nThe article you\'re writing.',-1),(106373,7,102101,102153,'01:10:54.240','01:10:56.402','Oh, I\'m not writing an\narticle about Catholics.',-1),(106374,7,102158,102226,'01:10:56.600','01:10:59.444','The Bible quotes by your desk.',-1),(106375,7,102235,102266,'01:10:59.800','01:11:01.086','<i>I love you.</i>',-1),(106376,7,103168,103227,'01:11:38.680','01:11:41.160','<i>A woman who is\na medium or a sorcerer</i>',-1),(106377,7,103231,103307,'01:11:41.320','01:11:44.483','<i>shall be put to\ndeath by stoning.</i>',-1),(106378,7,103322,103380,'01:11:45.120','01:11:47.521','<i>If a dove is the\nsinner\'s offering,</i>',-1),(106379,7,103384,103469,'01:11:47.680','01:11:51.241','<i>the priest shall wring off\nits head, cleave its wings,</i>',-1),(106380,7,103474,103520,'01:11:51.440','01:11:53.363','<i>and burn it upon the altar.</i>',-1),(106381,7,103581,103657,'01:11:55.880','01:11:59.043','<i>Hello?</i>\nDetective Morell, it\'s Mikael Blomkvist.',-1),(106382,7,103660,103693,'01:11:59.200','01:12:00.565','<i>Yes, hello. How are you?</i>',-1),(106383,7,103697,103760,'01:12:00.720','01:12:03.371','<i>Not still freezing in Hedestad,\nI hope, for your sake.</i>',-1),(106384,7,103764,103835,'01:12:03.520','01:12:06.490','You know that Rebecka\ncase you mentioned.',-1),(106385,7,103839,103877,'01:12:06.640','01:12:08.244','<i>Would you recall her last name?</i>',-1),(106386,7,103882,103945,'01:12:08.440','01:12:11.046','Of course I do.\nBut what has that to do with anything?',-1),(106387,7,103948,104044,'01:12:11.200','01:12:15.171','<i>Nothing, probably. Jacobsson.\nRebecka Jacobsson.</i>',-1),(106388,7,104085,104119,'01:12:16.880','01:12:18.325','<i>And how was she killed?</i>',-1),(106389,7,104124,104168,'01:12:18.520','01:12:20.363','She was decapitated.',-1),(106390,7,104173,104232,'01:12:20.560','01:12:23.040','<i>Her arms were cutoff\nand she was burned.</i>',-1),(106391,7,104236,104284,'01:12:23.200','01:12:25.168','<i>But all that happened\nin the 1940s.</i>',-1),(106392,7,104354,104407,'01:12:28.120','01:12:30.327','What have you found?\nI have to call you back.',-1),(106393,7,104411,104437,'01:12:30.480','01:12:31.561','<i>Why..?</i>',-1),(106394,7,104754,104790,'01:12:44.760','01:12:46.285','Is it Henrik?\nYeah, we were talking.',-1),(106395,7,104794,104834,'01:12:46.440','01:12:48.124','He rubbed his arm,\nthen he collapsed.',-1),(106396,7,104838,104906,'01:12:48.280','01:12:51.090','Think he\'s gonna be okay?\nI honestly don\'t know.',-1),(106397,7,104909,104953,'01:12:51.240','01:12:53.083','You go. Talk to you later.\nI\'m sorry.',-1),(106398,7,105235,105260,'01:13:04.800','01:13:05.847','Evening.',-1),(106399,7,105314,105366,'01:13:08.120','01:13:10.282','So how is he?',-1),(106400,7,105370,105430,'01:13:10.440','01:13:12.920','Well, the good news\nis he survived.',-1),(106401,7,105442,105481,'01:13:13.440','01:13:15.044','How he does now,\nwe\'ll have to see.',-1),(106402,7,105498,105558,'01:13:15.760','01:13:18.286','He\'s in intensive care. Right.',-1),(106403,7,105574,105610,'01:13:18.920','01:13:20.445','Oh, uh...',-1),(106404,7,105617,105672,'01:13:20.720','01:13:23.041','May I have one of those?\nYou want a sandwich?',-1),(106405,7,105677,105749,'01:13:23.240','01:13:26.244','Small Scotch. Uh, sure.',-1),(106406,7,105846,105883,'01:13:30.280','01:13:31.805','Thank you.',-1),(106407,7,105887,105979,'01:13:31.960','01:13:35.806','Um, I hate to be indelicate, but\nHenrik promised me something',-1),(106408,7,105983,106036,'01:13:35.960','01:13:38.167','when I agreed to do\nthis Yeah, Wennerstrm',-1),(106409,7,106039,106110,'01:13:38.320','01:13:41.290','I need to know what he has on him.\nNow. In case, um...',-1),(106410,7,106114,106150,'01:13:41.440','01:13:42.930','In case he dies?',-1),(106411,7,106153,106222,'01:13:43.080','01:13:45.924','Well, that is indelicate.\nAnd I apologize.',-1),(106412,7,106225,106287,'01:13:46.080','01:13:48.651','I don\'t know what he has on\nhim, if you\'re asking me.',-1),(106413,7,106291,106394,'01:13:48.800','01:13:53.089','And he can\'t tell you in the\ncondition he\'s in, so...',-1),(106414,7,106411,106507,'01:13:53.800','01:13:57.805','We also didn\'t discuss who I\'d report\nto if something should happen to him.',-1),(106415,7,106511,106555,'01:13:57.960','01:13:59.803','Oh, well, you\'d report\nto me, of course.',-1),(106416,7,106575,106655,'01:14:00.640','01:14:03.962','But we both know that nothing\'s\ngoing to come of this, don\'t we?',-1),(106417,7,106675,106758,'01:14:04.800','01:14:08.282','No. No, we don\'t know that.\nWhat do you mean?',-1),(106418,7,106786,106847,'01:14:09.440','01:14:11.966','I may have found something.\nYou\'re joking.',-1),(106419,7,106861,106887,'01:14:12.560','01:14:13.641','What have you found?',-1),(106420,7,106913,106996,'01:14:14.720','01:14:18.167','The last time I reported on something\nwithout being absolutely sure,',-1),(106421,7,106999,107043,'01:14:18.320','01:14:20.163','I lost my life savings.',-1),(106422,7,107057,107119,'01:14:20.720','01:14:23.326','I need a research assistant.\nCan you authorize that?',-1),(106423,7,107124,107200,'01:14:23.520','01:14:26.683','Yes. Do you have one in mind?',-1),(106424,7,107204,107256,'01:14:26.840','01:14:29.002','I can find someone.\nI know an excellent one.',-1),(106425,7,107259,107300,'01:14:29.160','01:14:30.844','She did the background\ncheck on you.',-1),(106426,7,107304,107328,'01:14:31.000','01:14:32.001','The what?',-1),(106427,7,107331,107394,'01:14:32.160','01:14:34.766','Well, you don\'t think\nwe can hire just anyone',-1),(106428,7,107398,107448,'01:14:34.920','01:14:37.002','without doing a\nbackground check.',-1),(106429,7,107467,107499,'01:14:37.800','01:14:39.165','I want to read that.',-1),(106430,7,107513,107587,'01:14:39.720','01:14:42.803','Herr Frode was kind enough to\nshare your report with me.',-1),(106431,7,107591,107645,'01:14:42.960','01:14:45.247','The investigator\'s name.\nThat is her name, yes?',-1),(106432,7,107671,107765,'01:14:46.320','01:14:50.211','See, I can\'t find any record of\nher, and I\'m pretty good at that.',-1),(106433,7,107776,107854,'01:14:50.680','01:14:53.923','Would it matter what her name is?\nIf I wanted to speak to her, yes.',-1),(106434,7,107858,107906,'01:14:54.120','01:14:56.122','It\'s against policy You sure?',-1),(106435,7,107910,107960,'01:14:56.280','01:14:58.362','Just like your sources.\nYou understand.',-1),(106436,7,107964,107988,'01:14:58.520','01:14:59.521','Okay. Ahem.',-1),(106437,7,108016,108071,'01:15:00.680','01:15:02.967','Here\'s a name for you.',-1),(106438,7,108074,108100,'01:15:03.120','01:15:04.201','My sister.',-1),(106439,7,108104,108144,'01:15:04.360','01:15:06.010','She\'s also my lawyer.',-1),(106440,7,108147,108181,'01:15:06.160','01:15:07.571','She\'ll be contacting you.',-1),(106441,7,108185,108273,'01:15:07.720','01:15:11.406','There are things in here that can\nonly have come from one place.',-1),(106442,7,108353,108448,'01:15:14.720','01:15:18.691','The reason you can find no record of\nher is because her records are sealed.',-1),(106443,7,108452,108536,'01:15:18.840','01:15:22.367','She\'s a ward of the state.\nWhat\'s that gotta do with anything?',-1),(106444,7,108560,108597,'01:15:23.360','01:15:24.885','She\'s had a rough life.',-1),(106445,7,108629,108702,'01:15:26.240','01:15:29.289','Can we please not\nmake it any rougher?',-1),(106446,7,110406,110448,'01:16:40.280','01:16:42.009','Who is it?',-1),(106447,7,110452,110495,'01:16:42.200','01:16:43.964','It\'s Mikael Blomkvist.',-1),(106448,7,110603,110657,'01:16:48.480','01:16:50.721','Actually, I\'m not really up yet.\nMay I come in?',-1),(106449,7,110661,110695,'01:16:50.880','01:16:52.325','Please?',-1),(106450,7,110853,110935,'01:16:58.880','01:17:02.327','Hi. You and I need to talk.\nI\'ve got us some breakf...',-1),(106451,7,110947,111000,'01:17:02.800','01:17:05.041','I\'m sorry, I didn\'t realize\nyou had some company.',-1),(106452,7,111005,111049,'01:17:05.240','01:17:07.049','Who do you think you are?',-1),(106453,7,111056,111124,'01:17:07.360','01:17:10.170','I\'m the guy you know better\nthan my closest friends do.',-1),(106454,7,111183,111264,'01:17:12.640','01:17:16.008','Why don\'t you put some clothes\non, get rid of your girlfriend.',-1),(106455,7,111267,111295,'01:17:16.160','01:17:17.321','We need to talk.',-1),(106456,7,111532,111581,'01:17:27.200','01:17:29.248','I\'m sorry, you have to go.',-1),(106457,7,111585,111627,'01:17:29.400','01:17:31.129','Okay.',-1),(106458,7,111987,112036,'01:17:46.160','01:17:48.208','Do you need me to stay?',-1),(106459,7,112053,112078,'01:17:48.880','01:17:49.927','No.',-1),(106460,7,112251,112297,'01:17:57.160','01:17:59.049','Bye. Bye.',-1),(106461,7,112465,112491,'01:18:06.080','01:18:07.161','Bye.',-1),(106462,7,112495,112520,'01:18:07.320','01:18:08.367','Sorry. It\'s okay.',-1),(106463,7,112681,112739,'01:18:15.080','01:18:17.481','I guess I must have alarmed\nyou, turning up like that.',-1),(106464,7,112743,112799,'01:18:17.640','01:18:19.961','If you touch me, I\'ll\nmore than alarm you.',-1),(106465,7,112802,112838,'01:18:20.120','01:18:21.610','That won\'t be necessary.',-1),(106466,7,112866,112933,'01:18:22.760','01:18:25.570','Your report, very detailed.',-1),(106467,7,112938,113010,'01:18:25.760','01:18:28.764','But for me, it wasn\'t very entertaining.\nIt wasn\'t meant to be.',-1),(106468,7,113014,113078,'01:18:28.920','01:18:31.605','When I write about people, I\ntry to entertain the reader.',-1),(106469,7,113082,113130,'01:18:31.760','01:18:33.762','Wennerstrm wasn\'t\nentertained much.',-1),(106470,7,113212,113308,'01:18:37.200','01:18:41.171','Uh, your boss, Armansky,',-1),(106471,7,113312,113394,'01:18:41.360','01:18:44.762','yeah, he tells me you only\ndo jobs that interest you,',-1),(106472,7,113398,113458,'01:18:44.920','01:18:47.446','so I suppose I\nshould be flattered.',-1),(106473,7,113476,113518,'01:18:48.200','01:18:49.929','You gonna sit down?',-1),(106474,7,113537,113677,'01:18:50.720','01:18:56.568','He also says that you\'re the one he\ngoes to when the job is, um, sensitive.',-1),(106475,7,113681,113775,'01:18:56.720','01:19:00.645','That\'s the word he used, \"sensitive\n.\" I\'m gonna use \"illegal,\"',-1),(106476,7,113780,113855,'01:19:00.840','01:19:03.969','because that\'s what it was when\nyou hacked into my computer.',-1),(106477,7,113858,113930,'01:19:04.120','01:19:07.090','No, I\'m not gonna do anything about that.\nI could, but I won\'t.',-1),(106478,7,113933,113997,'01:19:07.240','01:19:09.891','What I\'m gonna do is I\'m\ngonna tell you a story,',-1),(106479,7,114000,114091,'01:19:10.040','01:19:13.806','and if it entertains you, maybe you\'ll\ndecide to help me research further.',-1),(106480,7,114095,114170,'01:19:13.960','01:19:17.123','And if not, I\'ll do the washing\nup and you\'ll never see me again.',-1),(106481,7,114197,114244,'01:19:18.240','01:19:20.208','Here, you should eat that.',-1),(106482,7,114262,114298,'01:19:20.920','01:19:22.445','What kind of research?',-1),(106483,7,114311,114362,'01:19:22.960','01:19:25.088','Lisbeth...\nOh, can I call you Lisbeth?',-1),(106484,7,114407,114460,'01:19:26.960','01:19:29.167','I want you to help me\ncatch a killer of women.',-1),(106485,7,114502,114590,'01:19:30.920','01:19:34.606','I\'ve got R.J. Rebecka Jacobsson.\nI\'ve got absolutely no idea',-1),(106486,7,114594,114656,'01:19:34.760','01:19:37.366','who the rest of these are\nor how they\'re connected',-1),(106487,7,114660,114732,'01:19:37.520','01:19:40.524','to the death of a 16-year-old\ngirl, but they must be somehow.',-1),(106488,7,114736,114816,'01:19:40.680','01:19:44.002','What we\'ve gotta do is find out who\nthey are, what happened to them,',-1),(106489,7,114819,114891,'01:19:44.160','01:19:47.164','and what these Leviticus verses\nhave to do with anything.',-1),(106490,7,114973,115015,'01:19:50.560','01:19:52.324','What are you doing?\nGetting started.',-1),(106491,7,115019,115104,'01:19:52.480','01:19:56.041','You can keep talking if you want.\nDon\'t you need to look over these?',-1),(106492,7,115108,115150,'01:19:56.200','01:19:57.929','I got it.',-1),(106493,7,116236,116277,'01:20:43.200','01:20:44.884','Cat!',-1),(106494,7,116988,117035,'01:21:14.520','01:21:16.488','How\'d you get in?',-1),(106495,7,117253,117307,'01:21:25.560','01:21:27.801','No one has asked me about\nMagda in over 40 years.',-1),(106496,7,117349,117418,'01:21:29.560','01:21:32.450','Why would a lady like you want\nto know about an awful murder?',-1),(106497,7,117422,117481,'01:21:32.600','01:21:35.080','Does it? It interests me.',-1),(106498,7,117558,117606,'01:21:38.280','01:21:40.282','<i>Her husband\nwas the first suspect.</i>',-1),(106499,7,117610,117687,'01:21:40.440','01:21:43.649','<i>The husband is always the first\nsuspect and usually the last.</i>',-1),(106500,7,117691,117774,'01:21:43.800','01:21:47.282','But not this time.\nWe moved on to a neighbor.',-1),(106501,7,117778,117822,'01:21:47.440','01:21:49.283','Then a vagrant.',-1),(106502,7,117826,117889,'01:21:49.440','01:21:52.046','Once you get to strangers,\nit\'s only a matter of time',-1),(106503,7,117892,117978,'01:21:52.200','01:21:55.761','before you get to gypsies and you\nknow you\'re never going to solve it.',-1),(106504,7,117982,118036,'01:21:55.920','01:21:58.207','How exactly was she killed?',-1),(106505,7,118056,118083,'01:21:59.040','01:22:00.166','Miss...? Salander.',-1),(106506,7,118087,118179,'01:22:00.320','01:22:04.166','Miss Salander. I hope you don\'t mind\nme asking, but when did you last eat?',-1),(106507,7,118183,118244,'01:22:04.320','01:22:06.846','I have a high metabolism.\nI can\'t put on weight.',-1),(106508,7,118248,118359,'01:22:07.000','01:22:11.642','I\'m asking because it is better to\nlook at what I am about to show you',-1),(106509,7,118363,118395,'01:22:11.800','01:22:13.131','on an empty stomach.',-1),(106510,7,118474,118587,'01:22:16.440','01:22:21.128','<i>If a man\'s offering is a lamb,\nit shall be a female without blemish.</i>',-1),(106511,7,118590,118639,'01:22:21.280','01:22:23.328','<i>He should lay his\nhand upon its head,</i>',-1),(106512,7,118643,118720,'01:22:23.480','01:22:26.689','<i>slaughter it, empty its blood\non the base of the altar,</i>',-1),(106513,7,118724,118773,'01:22:26.840','01:22:28.888','<i>and he shall be forgiven.</i>',-1),(106514,7,118893,118939,'01:22:33.880','01:22:35.803','How is he? He needs surgery,',-1),(106515,7,118943,119032,'01:22:35.960','01:22:39.681','but there\'s no DNR in place.\nSo it\'s up to the family to decide,',-1),(106516,7,119036,119104,'01:22:39.840','01:22:42.684','should the occasion arise,\nwhether to resuscitate or not.',-1),(106517,7,119116,119184,'01:22:43.200','01:22:46.010','And they\'re not\ngood at decisions.',-1),(106518,7,119187,119225,'01:22:46.160','01:22:47.730','So how was it with\nMiss Salander?',-1),(106519,7,119229,119301,'01:22:47.880','01:22:50.884','She said yes. Do you think I\nmight be able to see him?',-1),(106520,7,119305,119376,'01:22:51.080','01:22:54.004','He was asleep the last time\nI looked, but let me check.',-1),(106521,7,119379,119416,'01:22:54.160','01:22:55.685','Thank you. Don\'t check.',-1),(106522,7,119425,119475,'01:22:56.080','01:22:58.162','Tell him to pack his\nthings and leave.',-1),(106523,7,119479,119536,'01:22:58.320','01:23:00.687','Mother, please.\nDon\'t use that tone with me.',-1),(106524,7,119540,119604,'01:23:00.840','01:23:03.525','Isabella, Mr. Blomkvist\nworks for Henrik.',-1),(106525,7,119608,119672,'01:23:03.680','01:23:06.365','- We should put this to a vote.\n- Don\'t be an idiot, Birger.',-1),(106526,7,119676,119732,'01:23:06.520','01:23:08.841','We all know what Henrik wants.\nCan we just do that?',-1),(106527,7,119736,119819,'01:23:09.040','01:23:12.487','Henrik is fighting for his life in there.\nThis is the last thing he needs.',-1),(106528,7,119823,119887,'01:23:12.640','01:23:15.325','Excuse me, Mrs. Vanger, there\nis no smoking in here.',-1),(106529,7,119950,119984,'01:23:17.920','01:23:19.365','Go back to Stockholm.',-1),(106530,7,119988,120087,'01:23:19.520','01:23:23.650','When we need a family chronicle\nwritten by a libelist,',-1),(106531,7,120100,120142,'01:23:24.200','01:23:25.929','we know who to call.',-1),(106532,7,120282,120340,'01:23:31.760','01:23:34.206','All right. Thanks.',-1),(106533,7,120354,120405,'01:23:34.760','01:23:36.888','This way, miss.',-1),(106534,7,120497,120554,'01:23:40.720','01:23:43.087','<i>If a woman\napproaches any beast</i>',-1),(106535,7,120557,120641,'01:23:43.240','01:23:46.722','<i>and lies with it, you shall\nkill the woman and the beast.</i>',-1),(106536,7,120645,120698,'01:23:46.880','01:23:49.087','<i>Their blood shall be upon them.</i>',-1),(106537,7,121021,121066,'01:24:02.560','01:24:04.449','<i>My family\'s impossible.</i>',-1),(10