-1),(107352,11,8872,8931,'00:06:09.703','00:06:12.126','I applied for a job,\nbut Mrs. Stein thought...',-1),(107353,11,8934,8972,'00:06:12.289','00:06:13.836','She said no.',-1),(107354,11,8975,9022,'00:06:13.999','00:06:15.922','Well, until I gain some experience.',-1),(107355,11,9026,9058,'00:06:16.084','00:06:17.427','See? Says right there.',-1),(107356,11,9062,9147,'00:06:17.586','00:06:21.136','\"Great potential. Gain some experience\nand please apply again.\"',-1),(107357,11,9199,9274,'00:06:23.300','00:06:26.429','Oh, Christ. I guess you\'ll do.\nDo you clean?',-1),(107358,11,9287,9335,'00:06:26.970','00:06:28.972','- I\'m sorry. Clean?\n- Clean.',-1),(107359,11,9339,9372,'00:06:29.139','00:06:30.516','Grab that basket.',-1),(107360,11,9407,9491,'00:06:31.975','00:06:35.479','Miss Myrna has gone\nshit-house crazy on us.',-1),(107361,11,9495,9554,'00:06:35.645','00:06:38.114','She drunk hairspray or something.',-1),(107362,11,9558,9612,'00:06:38.273','00:06:40.526','I want you to read her past columns.',-1),(107363,11,9616,9680,'00:06:40.692','00:06:43.366','Then read these letters and you\nanswer them just like she would.',-1),(107364,11,9684,9742,'00:06:43.528','00:06:45.951','Nobody is gonna know\nthe damn difference.',-1),(107365,11,9746,9794,'00:06:46.114','00:06:48.116','You know who Miss Myrna is?',-1),(107366,11,9812,9852,'00:06:48.867','00:06:50.540','I read her articles all the time.',-1),(107367,11,9856,9936,'00:06:50.702','00:06:54.002','Articles? Miss Phelan,\nit\'s a cleaning advice column.',-1),(107368,11,9939,10007,'00:06:54.164','00:06:56.963','Eight bucks a week.\nCopy is due on Thursday.',-1),(107369,11,10011,10075,'00:06:57.125','00:06:59.799','Hello?',-1),(107370,11,10107,10195,'00:07:01.129','00:07:04.804','Lou Ann, honey, I can\'t talk right now.\nI\'m at work.',-1),(107371,11,10199,10280,'00:07:04.966','00:07:08.345','What? Shut that goddamn door.',-1),(107372,11,10653,10704,'00:07:23.902','00:07:26.030','Mama, we\'re late for bridge!',-1),(107373,11,10708,10769,'00:07:26.196','00:07:28.745','Miss Hilly was the first\nof the babies to have a baby.',-1),(107374,11,10773,10810,'00:07:28.907','00:07:30.454','...Three...',-1),(107375,11,10814,10880,'00:07:30.617','00:07:33.336','And it must have come out of her like\nthe 11th Commandment,',-1),(107376,11,10883,10937,'00:07:33.495','00:07:35.748','\'cause once Miss Hilly had a baby,',-1),(107377,11,10941,11011,'00:07:35.914','00:07:38.793','every girl at the bridge table\nhad to have one, too.',-1),(107378,11,11029,11073,'00:07:39.542','00:07:41.385','Minny, go get Mama!',-1),(107379,11,11218,11266,'00:07:47.425','00:07:49.427','Missus Walters,\nyou need help coming down?',-1),(107380,11,11270,11305,'00:07:49.594','00:07:51.062','- I\'m down.\n- Ooh.',-1),(107381,11,11309,11366,'00:07:51.221','00:07:53.599','- I been down.\n- Give me a heart attack.',-1),(107382,11,11370,11445,'00:07:53.765','00:07:56.894','Whoa, whoa, whoa, Missus Walters.\nHere, let me help you.',-1),(107383,11,11449,11520,'00:07:57.060','00:08:00.030','Take that off.\nIt\'s 98 degrees out there.',-1),(107384,11,11524,11559,'00:08:00.188','00:08:01.656','- Is it?\n- Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107385,11,11563,11603,'00:08:01.815','00:08:03.488','Well, let\'s put my coat on then.',-1),(107386,11,11607,11656,'00:08:03.650','00:08:05.698','- Come on, Minny.\n- All right.',-1),(107387,11,11660,11695,'00:08:05.860','00:08:07.328','- Here\'s your pocketbook.\n- Thank you.',-1),(107388,11,11699,11738,'00:08:07.487','00:08:09.114','OK, let me get the pie.',-1),(107389,11,11742,11801,'00:08:09.280','00:08:11.749','Hold on, Missus Walters. Hold on.',-1),(107390,11,11850,11952,'00:08:13.785','00:08:18.006','Once Missus Walters\' arteries went hard,\nMiss Hilly moved her into her house',-1),(107391,11,11955,12019,'00:08:18.164','00:08:20.792','and fired the maid she had\nto make room for Minny too.',-1),(107392,11,12047,12118,'00:08:21.960','00:08:24.930','See, Minny about the best cook\nin Mississippi,',-1),(107393,11,12122,12160,'00:08:25.088','00:08:26.681','and Miss Hilly wanted her.',-1),(107394,11,12223,12297,'00:08:29.300','00:08:32.395','I lost my own boy, Treelore,\nfour years ago.',-1),(107395,11,12328,12384,'00:08:33.680','00:08:36.024','After that, I just didn\'t want\nto live no more.',-1),(107396,11,12418,12478,'00:08:37.434','00:08:39.937','It took God and Minny\nto get me through it.',-1),(107397,11,12502,12610,'00:08:40.937','00:08:45.443','Minn y my best friend.\nOld lady like me lucky to have her.',-1),(107398,11,12708,12829,'00:08:49.529','00:08:54.581','After my boy died, a bitter seed\nwas planted inside of me.',-1),(107399,11,12855,12924,'00:08:55.660','00:08:58.539','And I just didn\'t feel\nso accepting any more.',-1),(107400,11,13251,13277,'00:09:12.135','00:09:13.227','No.',-1),(107401,11,13281,13361,'00:09:13.386','00:09:16.731','You drunk up two glasses of grape juice.\nI know you got to tee-tee.',-1),(107402,11,13365,13387,'00:09:16.890','00:09:17.812','No.',-1),(107403,11,13391,13446,'00:09:17.974','00:09:20.272','I\'ll give you two cookies if you go.',-1),(107404,11,13543,13604,'00:09:24.314','00:09:26.863','Mae Mobley, you\'re going!',-1),(107405,11,13617,13685,'00:09:27.400','00:09:30.244','Aibileen, the girls are\npulling up, and the table isn\'t set.',-1),(107406,11,13689,13749,'00:09:30.403','00:09:32.906','Mae Mobley go, Mama.',-1),(107407,11,13753,13805,'00:09:33.073','00:09:35.246','Get in your room right now.',-1),(107408,11,13847,13895,'00:09:36.993','00:09:38.995','Set out the dessert forks. Please.',-1),(107409,11,13984,14047,'00:09:42.707','00:09:45.301','Put Mama in a chair\nbefore she breaks a hip.',-1),(107410,11,14051,14101,'00:09:45.460','00:09:47.554','I\'m not deaf yet, Hilly.',-1),(107411,11,14105,14160,'00:09:47.712','00:09:50.010','Hey, girls.',-1),(107412,11,14164,14296,'00:09:50.173','00:09:55.680','Oh. Minny. Will you see if Aibileen\nhas some of that ambrosia?',-1),(107413,11,14424,14466,'00:10:01.017','00:10:02.769','Hold on. Those are Miss Hilly\'s.',-1),(107414,11,14470,14545,'00:10:02.936','00:10:06.065','She looks like the winning\nhorse at the Kentucky Derby.',-1),(107415,11,14549,14597,'00:10:06.231','00:10:08.233','All flowers and bows.',-1),(107416,11,14601,14637,'00:10:08.399','00:10:09.901','Got to have paprika on them.',-1),(107417,11,14641,14678,'00:10:10.068','00:10:11.615','Ooh.',-1),(107418,11,14682,14763,'00:10:11.778','00:10:15.157','Forgive me, Lord, but I\'m gonna have\nto kill that woman, Aibileen.',-1),(107419,11,14767,14836,'00:10:15.323','00:10:18.202','Now she gone to putting pencil marks\non my toilet paper.',-1),(107420,11,14869,14905,'00:10:19.577','00:10:21.079','- Did she?\n- Mm-hm.',-1),(107421,11,14909,14998,'00:10:21.246','00:10:24.921','But I carry paper in from my own\ndamn house. That fool don\'t know.',-1),(107422,11,15068,15118,'00:10:27.836','00:10:29.930','Miss Leefolt got so much hairspray\non her head',-1),(107423,11,15122,15175,'00:10:30.088','00:10:32.307','she gonna blow us all up\nif she light a cigarette.',-1),(107424,11,15197,15247,'00:10:33.216','00:10:35.310','And you know she will!',-1),(107425,11,15415,15459,'00:10:42.308','00:10:44.151','- You got some ambrosia?\n- You know I do.',-1),(107426,11,15463,15500,'00:10:44.310','00:10:45.857','All right, I\'ll be back.',-1),(107427,11,15504,15551,'00:10:46.020','00:10:47.988','Minny, cord, girl.',-1),(107428,11,15568,15593,'00:10:48.690','00:10:49.737','Shut up.',-1),(107429,11,15625,15681,'00:10:51.067','00:10:53.411','The Guiding Light.',-1),(107430,11,15757,15799,'00:10:56.573','00:10:58.325','Hi, Missus Walters.',-1),(107431,11,15813,15859,'00:10:58.908','00:11:00.831','I\'m watching my story.',-1),(107432,11,15880,15906,'00:11:01.703','00:11:02.750','OK.',-1),(107433,11,15909,15951,'00:11:02.912','00:11:04.664','Isn\'t it gorgeous?',-1),(107434,11,15955,15979,'00:11:04.831','00:11:05.832','Sorry I\'m late.',-1),(107435,11,16055,16083,'00:11:08.960','00:11:10.132','You\'re home!',-1),(107436,11,16099,16137,'00:11:10.795','00:11:12.388','I missed you all, too.',-1),(107437,11,16193,16272,'00:11:14.716','00:11:18.016','Well, if it isn\'t \"Long Haul\" Skeeter.',-1),(107438,11,16276,16329,'00:11:18.178','00:11:20.397','We didn\'t ever think\nyou\'d leave Ole Miss.',-1),(107439,11,16333,16389,'00:11:20.555','00:11:22.899','Well, it does take four years, Jolene.',-1),(107440,11,16420,16507,'00:11:24.184','00:11:27.814','I\'ve got a great summer planned for you.',-1),(107441,11,16511,16540,'00:11:27.979','00:11:29.196','Great.',-1),(107442,11,16544,16619,'00:11:29.355','00:11:32.484','I went ahead and I picked up my black\ndress from the cleaners this morning.',-1),(107443,11,16689,16713,'00:11:35.403','00:11:36.404','What?',-1),(107444,11,16737,16795,'00:11:37.405','00:11:39.828','- About supper club tonight.\n- What?',-1),(107445,11,16838,16890,'00:11:41.618','00:11:43.791','Honey, Stuart had to cancel.',-1),(107446,11,16894,16927,'00:11:43.953','00:11:45.330','Again?',-1),(107447,11,16931,16997,'00:11:45.496','00:11:48.215','He got held up on the oil rig, Skeeter.',-1),(107448,11,17000,17056,'00:11:48.374','00:11:50.672','It\'s... It\'s offshore.',-1),(107449,11,17060,17151,'00:11:50.835','00:11:54.635','I\'m starting to think this Stuart\nis a figment of your imagination,',-1),(107450,11,17155,17185,'00:11:54.797','00:11:56.049','so just forget it.',-1),(107451,11,17202,17234,'00:11:56.758','00:11:58.101','I\'m just gonna go get a plate.',-1),(107452,11,17238,17291,'00:11:58.259','00:12:00.478','- Shh!\n- Sorry!',-1),(107453,11,17458,17490,'00:12:07.435','00:12:08.778','I got a job today.',-1),(107454,11,17541,17579,'00:12:10.897','00:12:12.490','At The Jackson Journal.',-1),(107455,11,17636,17686,'00:12:14.859','00:12:16.953','They\'d be a fool not to hire you.',-1),(107456,11,17690,17768,'00:12:17.111','00:12:20.365','To Skeeter and her job.',-1),(107457,11,17772,17814,'00:12:20.531','00:12:22.283','Last stop till marriage.',-1),(107458,11,17828,17847,'00:12:22.867','00:12:23.663','Oh!',-1);
INSERT INTO `subtitles` VALUES (107459,11,17946,17998,'00:12:27.789','00:12:29.917','- It\'s for the Miss Myrna column.\n- Hmm.',-1),(107460,11,18001,18052,'00:12:30.083','00:12:32.177','Elizabeth, can I talk to Aibileen?',-1),(107461,11,18070,18146,'00:12:32.919','00:12:36.093','Just to help me with some of the letters\ntill I get a knack for it.',-1),(107462,11,18184,18216,'00:12:37.674','00:12:39.017','My Aibileen?',-1),(107463,11,18238,18296,'00:12:39.926','00:12:42.349','Why can\'t you just\nget Constantine to help?',-1),(107464,11,18421,18480,'00:12:47.558','00:12:50.027','Constantine quit us.',-1),(107465,11,18484,18544,'00:12:50.186','00:12:52.689','Oh, my gosh. Skeeter, I\'m so sorry.',-1),(107466,11,18548,18650,'00:12:52.855','00:12:57.110','Anyway, I just, um... I don\'t really\nknow how to answer these letters.',-1),(107467,11,18666,18757,'00:12:57.777','00:13:01.577','Well, I mean, as long as it doesn\'t\ninterfere with her work.',-1),(107468,11,18761,18805,'00:13:01.739','00:13:03.582','I don\'t see why not.',-1),(107469,11,18999,19027,'00:13:11.666','00:13:12.792','Leefolt residence.',-1),(107470,11,19031,19078,'00:13:12.959','00:13:14.927','Hello. Is Elizabeth in?',-1),(107471,11,19082,19141,'00:13:15.086','00:13:17.555','She having bridge club right now.\nMay I take a message?',-1),(107472,11,19145,19238,'00:13:17.714','00:13:21.594','Yes, please tell her Celia Foote\ncalled again.',-1),(107473,11,19266,19307,'00:13:22.760','00:13:24.478','I\'ll call back tomorrow.',-1),(107474,11,19311,19360,'00:13:24.637','00:13:26.685','- Yes, ma\'am.\n- Uh...',-1),(107475,11,19364,19410,'00:13:26.848','00:13:28.771','Miss?',-1),(107476,11,19414,19518,'00:13:28.933','00:13:33.279','I\'m looking for some help at my house.\nDo you know any maids looking?',-1),(107477,11,19522,19550,'00:13:33.438','00:13:34.610','No, ma\'am.',-1),(107478,11,19554,19614,'00:13:34.772','00:13:37.275','OK. It\'s Celia Foote.',-1),(107479,11,19618,19706,'00:13:37.442','00:13:41.117','Emerson-684.\nBye now.',-1),(107480,11,19849,19912,'00:13:47.076','00:13:49.704','You scared the daylights out of me!',-1),(107481,11,19932,20017,'00:13:50.538','00:13:54.042','It is lunchtime,\nand I am suddenly hungry.',-1),(107482,11,20102,20147,'00:13:57.587','00:13:59.464','Honestly!',-1),(107483,11,20275,20307,'00:14:04.802','00:14:06.145','Oh.',-1),(107484,11,20311,20353,'00:14:06.304','00:14:08.056','I\'m still working on it, Aibileen.',-1),(107485,11,20439,20471,'00:14:11.642','00:14:12.985','Who was that on the phone?',-1),(107486,11,20475,20525,'00:14:13.144','00:14:15.238','Miss Celia Foote called again.',-1),(107487,11,20557,20602,'00:14:16.564','00:14:18.441','I\'ve never called her back, Hilly.',-1),(107488,11,20641,20693,'00:14:20.068','00:14:22.241','She can\'t take a hint, can she?',-1),(107489,11,20697,20735,'00:14:22.403','00:14:23.996','Who\'s Celia Foote?',-1),(107490,11,20739,20787,'00:14:24.155','00:14:26.157','That tacky girl Johnny married.',-1),(107491,11,20791,20836,'00:14:26.324','00:14:28.167','From Sugar Ditch.',-1),(107492,11,20839,20876,'00:14:28.326','00:14:29.873','It could have been you, Hilly.',-1),(107493,11,20880,21009,'00:14:30.036','00:14:35.384','And live 30 minutes outside of town?\nNo, thank you.',-1),(107494,11,21012,21131,'00:14:35.541','00:14:40.468','Anyway, I ran into her at the beauty\nparlor, and she had the nerve to ask',-1),(107495,11,21135,21184,'00:14:40.630','00:14:42.678','if she could help with\nthe Children\'s Benefit Ball.',-1),(107496,11,21188,21264,'00:14:42.840','00:14:46.014','Aren\'t we taking non-members?\nThe benefit has gotten so big.',-1),(107497,11,21268,21342,'00:14:46.177','00:14:49.272','Yes, but we\'re not telling her.',-1),(107498,11,21407,21445,'00:14:51.974','00:14:53.567','Thank you, Aibileen.',-1),(107499,11,21576,21620,'00:14:59.023','00:15:00.866','Hilly, I wish you\'d just\ngo use the bathroom.',-1),(107500,11,21624,21660,'00:15:01.025','00:15:02.527','I\'m fine.',-1),(107501,11,21664,21706,'00:15:02.693','00:15:04.445','Oh, she\'s just upset',-1),(107502,11,21710,21776,'00:15:04.612','00:15:07.365','because the nigra uses the guest bath\nand so do we.',-1),(107503,11,21860,21911,'00:15:10.868','00:15:12.996','Aibileen, go check on Mae Mobley.',-1),(107504,11,21915,21942,'00:15:13.162','00:15:14.254','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107505,11,21970,22011,'00:15:15.456','00:15:17.129','Just go use mine and Raleigh\'s.',-1),(107506,11,22014,22103,'00:15:17.291','00:15:20.966','If Aibileen uses the guest bath,\nI\'m sure she uses yours, too.',-1),(107507,11,22107,22139,'00:15:21.129','00:15:22.472','She does not.',-1),(107508,11,22161,22238,'00:15:23.381','00:15:26.601','Wouldn\'t you rather them\ntake their business outside?',-1),(107509,11,22280,22340,'00:15:28.344','00:15:30.847','Have you all seen the cover\nof Life this week?',-1),(107510,11,22344,22377,'00:15:31.013','00:15:32.390','Jackie\'s never looked more regal.',-1),(107511,11,22381,22448,'00:15:32.557','00:15:35.356','Tell Raleigh every penny he spends\non a colored\'s bathroom',-1),(107512,11,22452,22520,'00:15:35.518','00:15:38.362','he\'ll get back in spades\nwhen y\'all sell.',-1),(107513,11,22555,22653,'00:15:39.814','00:15:43.910','it\'s just plain dangerous. They carry\ndifferent diseases than we do.',-1),(107514,11,22676,22700,'00:15:44.861','00:15:45.862','Pass.',-1),(107515,11,22704,22779,'00:15:46.028','00:15:49.157','That\'s why I\'ve drafted\nthe Home Health Sanitation Initiative.',-1),(107516,11,22783,22814,'00:15:49.323','00:15:50.620','The what?',-1),(107517,11,22818,22864,'00:15:50.783','00:15:52.706','A disease-preventative bill',-1),(107518,11,22868,22975,'00:15:52.869','00:15:57.295','that requires every white home to have a\nseparate bathroom for the colored help.',-1),(107519,11,22995,23052,'00:15:58.166','00:16:00.510','It\'s been endorsed\nby the White Citizens\' Council.',-1),(107520,11,23146,23220,'00:16:04.422','00:16:07.517','Maybe we should just build you\na bathroom outside, Hilly.',-1),(107521,11,23224,23308,'00:16:07.675','00:16:11.179','You ought not to joke\nabout the colored situation.',-1),(107522,11,23340,23404,'00:16:12.513','00:16:15.187','I\'ll do whatever it takes\nto protect our children.',-1),(107523,11,23449,23494,'00:16:17.059','00:16:18.936','Your lead, Elizabeth.',-1),(107524,11,23776,23812,'00:16:30.698','00:16:32.200','- Aibileen?\n- Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107525,11,23864,23935,'00:16:34.368','00:16:37.292','Do you think you\'d be willing to help me\nwith those Miss Myrna letters?',-1),(107526,11,23981,24045,'00:16:39.248','00:16:41.876','Miss Myrna get it wrong a lot of times.\nBe good to get it right.',-1),(107527,11,24113,24147,'00:16:44.712','00:16:46.134','Thank you, Aibileen.',-1),(107528,11,24205,24243,'00:16:48.549','00:16:50.142','All that talk in there today...',-1),(107529,11,24277,24307,'00:16:51.552','00:16:52.804','Hilly\'s talk?',-1),(107530,11,24324,24370,'00:16:53.513','00:16:55.436','I\'m sorry you had to hear that.',-1),(107531,11,24591,24641,'00:17:04.649','00:17:06.743','Is that Preacher Green\'s sermon?',-1),(107532,11,24645,24695,'00:17:06.901','00:17:08.995','Yes, ma\'am, it is.',-1),(107533,11,24699,24769,'00:17:09.153','00:17:12.077','That reminds me so much of my maid,\nConstantine.',-1),(107534,11,24800,24881,'00:17:13.366','00:17:16.745','I know Constantine.\nWe\'re in church circle together.',-1),(107535,11,24898,24928,'00:17:17.453','00:17:18.705','Have you seen her lately?',-1),(107536,11,24959,24991,'00:17:19.997','00:17:21.294','No, ma\'am.',-1),(107537,11,24994,25032,'00:17:21.457','00:17:23.004','Did you know that she had quit us?',-1),(107538,11,25036,25060,'00:17:23.167','00:17:24.168','Quit?',-1),(107539,11,25064,25143,'00:17:24.335','00:17:27.635','I got home from school a week ago,\nand my mama told me she had quit.',-1),(107540,11,25147,25238,'00:17:27.797','00:17:31.597','Back in March, she went to live with\nher daughter, Rachel. In Chicago.',-1),(107541,11,25265,25314,'00:17:32.718','00:17:34.766','Did you hear that?\nDo you have her phone number?',-1),(107542,11,25318,25368,'00:17:34.929','00:17:37.023','There you are, Skeeter.',-1),(107543,11,25419,25476,'00:17:39.141','00:17:41.519','Hilly wants you to put her initiative\nin the League newsletter.',-1),(107544,11,25480,25504,'00:17:41.686','00:17:42.687','OK.',-1),(107545,11,25542,25580,'00:17:44.272','00:17:45.865','I\'ll be back tomorrow, Aibileen,',-1),(107546,11,25584,25646,'00:17:46.023','00:17:48.617','to get started on those\nMiss Myrna letters.',-1),(107547,11,25650,25678,'00:17:48.776','00:17:49.948','Y\'all make it quick.',-1),(107548,11,25682,25738,'00:17:50.111','00:17:52.455','Tomorrow is silver-polishing day. OK?',-1),(107549,11,26196,26229,'00:18:11.507','00:18:12.884','Hi, Jameso.',-1),(107550,11,26233,26263,'00:18:13.050','00:18:14.302','How you, Miss Eugenia?',-1),(107551,11,26313,26337,'00:18:16.387','00:18:17.388','Mama?',-1),(107552,11,26433,26467,'00:18:21.392','00:18:22.814','Mama.',-1),(107553,11,26482,26527,'00:18:23.436','00:18:25.313','Yoo-hoo.',-1),(107554,11,26782,26811,'00:18:35.948','00:18:37.165','Mama?',-1),(107555,11,26815,26845,'00:18:37.325','00:18:38.542','Back here, honey!',-1),(107556,11,26969,27011,'00:18:43.748','00:18:45.466','Is this a little too young?',-1),(107557,11,27030,27075,'00:18:46.250','00:18:48.127','That\'s a little too everything.',-1),(107558,11,27109,27149,'00:18:49.545','00:18:51.218','Oh, hell. You\'re right.',-1),(107559,11,27526,27551,'00:19:06.937','00:19:07.984','OK.',-1),(107560,11,27617,27649,'00:19:10.733','00:19:12.076','Much better.',-1),(107561,11,27673,27730,'00:19:13.069','00:19:15.447','Your daddy bought me this dress in \'58.',-1),(107562,11,27748,27792,'00:19:16.197','00:19:18.040','Mama, I want to ask you\nabout Constantine.',-1),(107563,11,27796,27862,'00:19:18.199','00:19:20.918','Right after Ole Miss won the Sugar Bowl.\nCome on. You try it on.',-1),(107564,11,27865,27892,'00:19:21.077','00:19:22.203','What really happened?',-1),(107565,11,27896,27967,'00:19:22.370','00:19:25.294','Skeeter, your mother is sick.\nShe wants to see you in this dress.',-1),(107566,11,27970,27994,'00:19:25.456','00:19:26.457','Unzip me.',-1),(107567,11,28035,28060,'00:19:28.125','00:19:29.172','Come on.',-1),(107568,11,28117,28177,'00:19:31.545','00:19:34.048','Did I tell you Fanny Peatrow\ngot engaged?',-1),(107569,11,28203,28246,'00:19:35.132','00:19:36.930','After she got that teller job,',-1),(107570,11,28250,28299,'00:19:37.093','00:19:39.141','her mother said she was swimming\nin proposals.',-1),(107571,11,28303,28348,'00:19:39.303','00:19:41.180','Good for fair Fanny Peatrow.',-1),(107572,11,28352,28430,'00:19:41.347','00:19:44.601','Eugenia, your eggs are dying.\nWould it kill you to go on a date?',-1),(107573,11,28448,28546,'00:19:45.351','00:19:49.447','Just show a little gumption.\nCareful now, careful.',-1),(107574,11,28550,28605,'00:19:49.605','00:19:51.903','Oh, now look at this.',-1),(107575,11,28621,28699,'00:19:52.566','00:19:55.820','This dress is just precious on you.',-1),(107576,11,28703,28799,'00:19:55.986','00:19:59.991','Just take it in a little here.\nLittle there.',-1),(107577,11,28856,28922,'00:20:02.368','00:20:05.121','- Get your hair fixed.\n- I got a job today.',-1),(107578,11,28926,28950,'00:20:05.287','00:20:06.288','Where?',-1),(107579,11,28966,29017,'00:20:06.956','00:20:09.050','Writing for The Jackson Journal.',-1),(107580,11,29049,29104,'00:20:10.376','00:20:12.674','Great.',-1),(107581,11,29122,29174,'00:20:13.421','00:20:15.594','You can write my obituary!',-1),(107582,11,29178,29277,'00:20:15.756','00:20:19.886','\"Charlotte Phelan, dead!\nHer daughter, still single.\"',-1),(107583,11,29281,29341,'00:20:20.052','00:20:22.555','Mother, would it really be so bad\nif I never met a husband?',-1),(107584,11,29345,29411,'00:20:22.722','00:20:25.475','Skeeter! Skeeter!',-1),(107585,11,29436,29470,'00:20:26.517','00:20:27.939','Skeeter!',-1),(107586,11,29583,29616,'00:20:32.648','00:20:34.025','I need to ask you something.',-1),(107587,11,29732,29826,'00:20:38.863','00:20:42.788','I read the other day about how\nsome girls get unbalanced.',-1),(107588,11,29842,29875,'00:20:43.451','00:20:44.794','They start thinking these...',-1),(107589,11,29915,29963,'00:20:46.495','00:20:48.463','...unnatural thoughts.',-1),(107590,11,29966,29999,'00:20:48.622','00:20:49.965','Are you...',-1),(107591,11,30042,30157,'00:20:51.751','00:20:56.552','Do you, uh... find men attractive?',-1),(107592,11,30171,30286,'00:20:57.131','00:21:01.932','Are you having unnatural thoughts\nabout girls or women?',-1),(107593,11,30328,30354,'00:21:03.679','00:21:04.771','Oh, my God.',-1),(107594,11,30358,30470,'00:21:04.930','00:21:09.606','Because this article says there\'s\na cure. A special root tea!',-1),(107595,11,30474,30603,'00:21:09.769','00:21:15.151','Mother, I want to be with girls as much\nas you want to be with Jameso.',-1),(107596,11,30607,30659,'00:21:15.316','00:21:17.489','- Eugenia!\n- Unless, of course, you do!',-1),(107597,11,30663,30696,'00:21:17.651','00:21:19.028','Oh!',-1),(107598,11,30747,30831,'00:21:21.155','00:21:24.625','Carlton\'s bringing Rebecca to dinner.\nTry to look presentable!',-1),(107599,11,30934,30985,'00:21:28.954','00:21:31.082','What the hell you know\nabout cleaning a house, Skeeter?',-1),(107600,11,30989,31055,'00:21:31.248','00:21:33.967','It\'s a start, Carlton.',-1),(107601,11,31059,31142,'00:21:34.126','00:21:37.596','If you say so.\nI thought you wanted to write books.',-1),(107602,11,31146,31220,'00:21:37.755','00:21:40.850','Now, y\'all leave Sister alone.',-1),(107603,11,31224,31293,'00:21:41.008','00:21:43.887','- I\'m proud of you, sweetheart.\n- The irony of it all.',-1),(107604,11,31297,31352,'00:21:44.053','00:21:46.351','Giving advice on how to keep up a home\nwhen she doesn\'t even...',-1),(107605,11,31356,31438,'00:21:46.514','00:21:49.939','Oh, no, Pascagoula. You couldn\'t have\nknown this, but I\'m allergic to almonds.',-1),(107606,11,31442,31507,'00:21:50.100','00:21:52.819','Sorry, Miss Eugenia,\nI\'ll get you another one.',-1),(107607,11,31511,31572,'00:21:52.978','00:21:55.527','You know, last time I had an almond,\nI stopped liking men.',-1),(107608,11,31576,31613,'00:21:55.689','00:21:57.236','Oh, my Lord.',-1),(107609,11,31617,31707,'00:21:57.399','00:22:01.154','Oh, no, Rebecca, it\'s fine. There\'s\na special root tea for that now.',-1),(107610,11,31711,31743,'00:22:01.320','00:22:02.663','You have pushed it, young lady.',-1),(107611,11,31760,31835,'00:22:03.364','00:22:06.493','Daddy. What happened to Constantine?',-1),(107612,11,31839,31894,'00:22:06.659','00:22:08.957','Uh, well...',-1),(107613,11,31912,31993,'00:22:09.703','00:22:13.048','Constantine went to live in Chicago\nwith her family.',-1),(107614,11,31996,32057,'00:22:13.207','00:22:15.710','People move on, Skeeter.',-1),(107615,11,32061,32118,'00:22:15.876','00:22:18.254','But I do wish that she\'d\nstayed down here with us.',-1),(107616,11,32238,32279,'00:22:23.259','00:22:24.977','I don\'t believe you.',-1),(107617,11,32322,32380,'00:22:26.762','00:22:29.185','She would\'ve written and told me.',-1),(107618,11,32604,32643,'00:22:38.524','00:22:40.151','Did you fire her?',-1),(107619,11,32659,32758,'00:22:40.818','00:22:44.948','We were just a job to her, honey.\nWith them, it\'s all about money.',-1),(107620,11,32762,32846,'00:22:45.114','00:22:48.618','You\'ll understand that once you\'ve\nhired help of your own.',-1),(107621,11,32865,32934,'00:22:49.410','00:22:52.254','- She raised me.\n- She did not!',-1),(107622,11,32937,33000,'00:22:52.413','00:22:55.007','She worked here for 29 years!',-1),(107623,11,33003,33057,'00:22:55.165','00:22:57.384','It was a colored thing\nand I put it behind me!',-1),(107624,11,33075,33166,'00:22:58.127','00:23:01.927','Excuse me a moment, Rebecca. My daughter\nhas upset my cancerous ulcers.',-1),(107625,11,34288,34346,'00:23:48.677','00:23:51.100','What you doing hiding out here, girl?',-1),(107626,11,34386,34467,'00:23:52.765','00:23:56.144','I couldn\'t tell Mama I didn\'t\nget asked to the dance.',-1),(107627,11,34471,34498,'00:23:56.310','00:23:57.436','It\'s all right.',-1),(107628,11,34527,34611,'00:23:58.646','00:24:02.150','Some things we just got to\nkeep to ourselves, right?',-1),(107629,11,34637,34681,'00:24:03.233','00:24:05.076','All the boys say I\'m ugly.',-1),(107630,11,34726,34825,'00:24:06.946','00:24:11.042','Mama was third runner-up in\nthe Miss South Carolina pageant.',-1),(107631,11,34828,34917,'00:24:11.200','00:24:14.875','I wish you\'d quit\nfeeling sorry for yourself.',-1),(107632,11,34920,34971,'00:24:15.037','00:24:17.165','Now, that\'s ugly.',-1),(107633,11,34996,35082,'00:24:18.207','00:24:21.757','Ugly is something that\ngoes up inside you.',-1),(107634,11,35086,35169,'00:24:21.919','00:24:25.389','It\'s mean and hurtful, like them boys.',-1),(107635,11,35201,35244,'00:24:26.715','00:24:28.513','Now you\'re not one of them, is you?',-1),(107636,11,35269,35315,'00:24:29.551','00:24:31.474','I didn\'t think so, honey.',-1),(107637,11,35440,35464,'00:24:36.684','00:24:37.685','Every day...',-1),(107638,11,35512,35579,'00:24:39.687','00:24:42.486','Every day you\'re not\ndead in the ground,',-1),(107639,11,35583,35693,'00:24:42.648','00:24:47.245','when you wake up in the morning, you\'re\ngonna have to make some decisions.',-1),(107640,11,35728,35786,'00:24:48.696','00:24:51.119','Got to ask yourself this question:',-1),(107641,11,35803,35842,'00:24:51.824','00:24:53.417','\"Am I gonna believe',-1),(107642,11,35845,35958,'00:24:53.575','00:24:58.251','all them bad things them fools\nsay about me today?\"',-1),(107643,11,36004,36031,'00:25:00.207','00:25:01.299','You hear me?',-1),(107644,11,36034,36110,'00:25:01.458','00:25:04.587','\"Am I gonna believe all them bad things',-1),(107645,11,36114,36174,'00:25:04.753','00:25:07.256','them fools say about me today\'?\"',-1),(107646,11,36243,36270,'00:25:10.134','00:25:11.260','All right?',-1),(107647,11,36346,36438,'00:25:14.430','00:25:18.276','As for your mama,\nshe didn\'t pick her life.',-1),(107648,11,36473,36505,'00:25:19.727','00:25:21.070','It picked her.',-1),(107649,11,36572,36599,'00:25:23.856','00:25:24.982','But you...',-1),(107650,11,36665,36753,'00:25:27.735','00:25:31.410','...you\'re gonna do\nsomething big with yours.',-1),(107651,11,36780,36818,'00:25:32.531','00:25:34.124','You wait and see.',-1),(107652,11,36875,36947,'00:25:36.493','00:25:39.463','Come on, go home with me\ntill the dance over. Come on.',-1),(107653,11,37459,37530,'00:26:00.809','00:26:03.779','Miss Stein, you said in your letter\nto write about what disturbs me,',-1),(107654,11,37534,37565,'00:26:03.937','00:26:05.234','particularly if it bothers no one else.',-1),(107655,11,37569,37593,'00:26:05.397','00:26:06.398','Come on.',-1),(107656,11,37597,37640,'00:26:06.565','00:26:08.363','And I understand that now.',-1),(107657,11,37674,37702,'00:26:09.777','00:26:10.949','Continue.',-1),(107658,11,37728,37793,'00:26:12.029','00:26:14.748','I\'d like to write something\nfrom the point of view of the help.',-1),(107659,11,37830,37891,'00:26:16.283','00:26:18.832','These colored women\nraise white children,',-1),(107660,11,37895,37975,'00:26:18.994','00:26:22.294','and in 20 years,\nthose children become the boss.',-1),(107661,11,37978,38044,'00:26:22.456','00:26:25.175','We love them and they love us,',-1),(107662,11,38048,38103,'00:26:25.334','00:26:27.632','but they can\'t even use the toilets\nin our houses.',-1),(107663,11,38107,38145,'00:26:27.795','00:26:29.388','Don\'t you find that ironic, Miss Stein?',-1),(107664,11,38149,38173,'00:26:29.546','00:26:30.547','I\'m listening.',-1),(107665,11,38210,38272,'00:26:32.091','00:26:34.685','Margaret Mitchell glorified\nthe mammy figure,',-1),(107666,11,38276,38316,'00:26:34.843','00:26:36.516','who dedicates her whole life',-1),(107667,11,38320,38345,'00:26:36.678','00:26:37.725','to a white family.',-1),(107668,11,38349,38430,'00:26:37.888','00:26:41.267','But nobody ever asked Mammy\nhow she felt about it.',-1),(107669,11,38434,38500,'00:26:41.433','00:26:44.186','So, a side to this never before heard?',-1),(107670,11,38504,38550,'00:26:44.353','00:26:46.276','Yes.',-1),(107671,11,38554,38622,'00:26:46.438','00:26:49.282','\'Cause nobody ever really\ntalks about it down here.',-1),(107672,11,38690,38733,'00:26:52.111','00:26:53.909','Skeeter, who are you\ntalking to in there?',-1),(107673,11,38758,38790,'00:26:54.947','00:26:56.290','Go away!',-1),(107674,11,38877,38949,'00:26:59.910','00:27:02.880','- Who was that?\n- My mother.',-1),(107675,11,38952,38990,'00:27:03.038','00:27:04.585','Look.',-1),(107676,11,38993,39077,'00:27:04.748','00:27:08.218','No maid in her right mind is ever gonna\ntell you the truth.',-1),(107677,11,39081,39166,'00:27:08.377','00:27:11.927','That\'s a hell of a risk to take in\na place like Jackson, Mississippi.',-1),(107678,11,39170,39203,'00:27:12.089','00:27:13.466','I already have a maid.',-1),(107679,11,39251,39335,'00:27:15.467','00:27:18.971','Really? A Negro maid has already agreed\nto speak with you?',-1),(107680,11,39355,39392,'00:27:19.805','00:27:21.352','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107681,11,39484,39556,'00:27:25.185','00:27:28.189','Well... I guess I can read\nwhat you come up with.',-1),(107682,11,39560,39612,'00:27:28.355','00:27:30.528','The book biz could use\na little rattling.',-1),(107683,11,39616,39649,'00:27:30.691','00:27:32.068','Thank you, Miss Stein.',-1),(107684,11,39653,39695,'00:27:32.234','00:27:33.986','Hey, hey, hey, all I\'m saying',-1),(107685,11,39699,39770,'00:27:34.153','00:27:37.123','is that I\'ll let you know\nif it\'s even worth pursuing.',-1),(107686,11,39774,39856,'00:27:37.281','00:27:40.706','And for God\'s sake, you\'re\na 23-year-old educated woman.',-1),(107687,11,39860,39912,'00:27:40.868','00:27:43.041','Go get yourself an apartment.',-1),(107688,11,40016,40057,'00:27:47.374','00:27:49.047','\"Dear Miss Myrna:',-1),(107689,11,40080,40144,'00:27:50.002','00:27:52.676','When I\'m chopping onions, how do I\nkeep tears out of my eyes?\"',-1),(107690,11,40148,40234,'00:27:52.838','00:27:56.433','Shoot, that\'s easy. You tell\nher hold a matchstick between her teeth.',-1),(107691,11,40269,40306,'00:27:57.885','00:27:59.432','Is it lit?',-1),(107692,11,40310,40349,'00:27:59.595','00:28:01.222','No, ma\'am.',-1),(107693,11,40405,40478,'00:28:03.557','00:28:06.606','Miss Leefolt said\nyou could start right away.',-1),(107694,11,40482,40601,'00:28:06.768','00:28:11.740','Build it just like the bathroom\nat my house. Let\'s see.',-1),(107695,11,40605,40692,'00:28:11.899','00:28:15.529','- Right there. That will be nice.\n- Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107696,11,40824,40881,'00:28:21.033','00:28:23.377','My goodness, we got to run back\nto the car. Come on.',-1),(107697,11,40893,40926,'00:28:23.911','00:28:25.288','Bye, Skeeter!',-1),(107698,11,41012,41051,'00:28:28.874','00:28:30.467','Aibileen.',-1),(107699,11,41055,41142,'00:28:30.626','00:28:34.256','There\'s something else I want to\nwrite about. I would need your help.',-1),(107700,11,41221,41316,'00:28:37.549','00:28:41.520','I want to interview you about\nwhat it\'s like to work as a maid.',-1),(107701,11,41320,41399,'00:28:41.678','00:28:44.978','I\'d like to do a book of interviews\nabout working for white families.',-1),(107702,11,41419,41508,'00:28:45.807','00:28:49.528','And we could show what it\'s like\nto work for, say, Elizabeth?',-1),(107703,11,41512,41590,'00:28:49.686','00:28:52.940','You know what Miss Leefolt do to me if\nshe knew I was telling stories on her?',-1),(107704,11,41594,41669,'00:28:53.106','00:28:56.235','I was thinking that we wouldn\'t\nhave to tell her.',-1),(107705,11,41673,41742,'00:28:56.401','00:28:59.280','The other maids would have\nto keep it a secret, too.',-1),(107706,11,41746,41778,'00:28:59.446','00:29:00.789','Other maids?',-1),(107707,11,41813,41870,'00:29:02.241','00:29:04.619','I was hoping to get four or five.',-1),(107708,11,41915,41983,'00:29:06.495','00:29:09.294','To show what it\'s really like\nin Jackson.',-1),(107709,11,42058,42175,'00:29:12.417','00:29:17.298','Show what y\'all get paid,\nand the babies and the bathrooms.',-1),(107710,11,42179,42208,'00:29:17.464','00:29:18.681','The good and the bad.',-1),(107711,11,42236,42293,'00:29:19.841','00:29:22.219','I bought you this damn house.\nI put up with your new clothes',-1),(107712,11,42297,42358,'00:29:22.386','00:29:24.935','and trips to New Orleans,\nbut this takes the goddamn cake.',-1),(107713,11,42362,42391,'00:29:25.097','00:29:26.314','Hilly spoke to the surgeon general,',-1),(107714,11,42395,42460,'00:29:26.473','00:29:29.192','and she also said it\'ll add value\nto our home.',-1),(107715,11,42464,42532,'00:29:29.351','00:29:32.195','I guess Mae Mobley can go to college\nin that damn bathroom!',-1),(107716,11,42536,42566,'00:29:32.354','00:29:33.606','Hilly\'s covering the cost and said',-1),(107717,11,42570,42614,'00:29:33.772','00:29:35.615','you could just do William\'s taxes\nto pay her back.',-1),(107718,11,42618,42667,'00:29:35.774','00:29:37.822','We don\'t take orders\nfrom the Holbrooks.',-1),(107719,11,42737,42782,'00:29:40.737','00:29:42.614','Skeeter, how you doing?',-1),(107720,11,42817,42841,'00:29:44.074','00:29:45.075','Fine.',-1),(107721,11,42948,42984,'00:29:49.538','00:29:51.006','Fix me a sandwich, Aibileen.',-1),(107722,11,43064,43118,'00:29:54.334','00:29:56.587','Aibileen, Mae Mobley\'s\ncrying her eyes out.',-1),(107723,11,43219,43258,'00:30:00.799','00:30:02.426','Skeeter.',-1),(107724,11,43273,43342,'00:30:03.051','00:30:05.930','I\'m sorry, but I think it\'s best\nif you leave now.',-1),(107725,11,43346,43389,'00:30:06.096','00:30:07.894','Oh, sure, sure.',-1),(107726,11,43393,43483,'00:30:08.056','00:30:11.811','And this Miss Myrna thing isn\'t going\nto work out with Aibileen.',-1),(107727,11,43512,43553,'00:30:13.020','00:30:14.738','I\'m sorry.',-1),(107728,11,43807,43892,'00:30:25.324','00:30:28.874','You\'re making it hotter,\nflapping your arms like that, Minny.',-1),(107729,11,44116,44178,'00:30:38.170','00:30:40.764','Look how big the waves are, Minny.',-1),(107730,11,44216,44294,'00:30:42.341','00:30:45.595','Let\'s go to the beach.\nRun, get Mr. Walters!',-1),(107731,11,44298,44339,'00:30:45.761','00:30:47.479','He loves riding these waves!',-1),(107732,11,44343,44398,'00:30:47.637','00:30:49.935','You know we went to Biloxi\non our honeymoon?',-1),(107733,11,44402,44437,'00:30:50.098','00:30:51.566','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107734,11,44459,44529,'00:30:52.476','00:30:55.400','Are we in Biloxi, Minny?',-1),(107735,11,44557,44629,'00:30:56.563','00:30:59.567','No, ma\'am. We ain\'t.',-1),(107736,11,44710,44805,'00:31:02.944','00:31:06.915','Why don\'t you sit down here for a spell.',-1),(107737,11,44834,44948,'00:31:08.116','00:31:12.872','And then me and you will go on down\nto the beach in a little while.',-1),(107738,11,44952,44985,'00:31:13.038','00:31:14.381','How about that?',-1),(107739,11,45284,45318,'00:31:26.843','00:31:28.265','Uh...',-1),(107740,11,45340,45364,'00:31:29.179','00:31:30.180','Miss Hilly?',-1),(107741,11,45368,45406,'00:31:30.347','00:31:31.940','Mm-hm?',-1),(107742,11,45467,45498,'00:31:34.476','00:31:35.773','Never mind.',-1),(107743,11,45502,45571,'00:31:35.936','00:31:38.815','You go on ahead and use\nthe inside bath, Minny, it\'s all right.',-1),(107744,11,45575,45645,'00:31:38.980','00:31:41.904','Oh, for crying out loud,\nit\'s just a little rain.',-1),(107745,11,45667,45734,'00:31:42.818','00:31:45.617','She can go on up and get an umbrella\nfrom William\'s study.',-1),(107746,11,45750,45840,'00:31:46.279','00:31:50.034','I believe she was working for me\nbefore you dragged us both here.',-1),(107747,11,45926,45979,'00:31:53.620','00:31:55.793','Daddy ruined you.',-1),(107748,11,46062,46107,'00:31:59.251','00:32:01.128','I\'m just gonna get your tea.',-1),(107749,11,46802,46831,'00:32:30.115','00:32:31.332','Minny?',-1),(107750,11,46864,46904,'00:32:32.701','00:32:34.374','Minny, are you in there?',-1),(107751,11,46953,46986,'00:32:36.413','00:32:37.756','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107752,11,47005,47060,'00:32:38.582','00:32:40.835','And just what are you doing?',-1),(107753,11,47249,47289,'00:32:48.717','00:32:50.390','Get off my toilet!',-1),(107754,11,47414,47476,'00:32:55.599','00:32:58.193','You are fired, Minny Jackson!',-1),(107755,11,47759,47801,'00:33:09.988','00:33:11.740','Go on!',-1),(107756,11,48029,48094,'00:33:21.249','00:33:23.923','Eighteen people\ndied in Jackson that day.',-1),(107757,11,48125,48172,'00:33:25.212','00:33:27.180','Ten white and eight black.',-1),(107758,11,48270,48375,'00:33:31.259','00:33:35.639','God don\'t pay no mind to color once\nHe decide to set a tornado loose.',-1),(107759,11,48379,48449,'00:33:35.805','00:33:38.729','Aibee\'s here, honey.',-1),(107760,11,48453,48490,'00:33:38.892','00:33:40.439','Aibee\'s here.',-1),(107761,11,49013,49090,'00:34:02.249','00:34:05.423','Hurry, Aibileen! Mae Mobley\nis up, and I\'m off to the doctor!',-1),(107762,11,49208,49309,'00:34:10.340','00:34:14.561','That\'s Aibee\'s bathroom, Mama.\nHey, Aibee!',-1),(107763,11,49313,49372,'00:34:14.719','00:34:17.188','No, no, no, honey.\nPromise me you won\'t go in there, OK?',-1),(107764,11,49376,49407,'00:34:17.347','00:34:18.644','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107765,11,49420,49456,'00:34:19.182','00:34:20.684','I\'m right here, Baby Girl.',-1),(107766,11,49505,49562,'00:34:22.727','00:34:25.105','Isn\'t it so nice\nto have your own, Aibileen?',-1),(107767,11,49566,49593,'00:34:25.272','00:34:26.398','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107768,11,49963,50050,'00:34:41.830','00:34:45.425','You\'re my real mama, Aibee.',-1),(107769,11,50662,50718,'00:35:10.942','00:35:13.286','- Is that Minny?\n- Minny.',-1),(107770,11,50736,50780,'00:35:14.029','00:35:15.872','Hey, Aibileen!',-1),(107771,11,50797,50821,'00:35:16.573','00:35:17.574','Hey, Minny!',-1),(107772,11,50825,50870,'00:35:17.741','00:35:19.584','Mm-hmm.',-1),(107773,11,50873,50901,'00:35:19.743','00:35:20.915','Where you headed?',-1),(107774,11,50934,51008,'00:35:22.287','00:35:25.336','I got some business to tend to,\nso y\'all just mind your own.',-1),(107775,11,51035,51071,'00:35:26.499','00:35:27.967','All right, then. Well, bye!',-1),(107776,11,51075,51118,'00:35:28.126','00:35:29.924','Bye!',-1),(107777,11,51122,51186,'00:35:30.086','00:35:32.760','Now is she mad at me \'cause I got\nthat job at Miss Hilly\'s?',-1),(107778,11,51190,51254,'00:35:32.922','00:35:35.596','Don\'t worry about her.\nShe always mad about something.',-1),(107779,11,51303,51337,'00:35:37.636','00:35:39.058','Aibileen.',-1),(107780,11,51423,51471,'00:35:42.641','00:35:44.643','Yes, ma\'am. Everything OK?',-1),(107781,11,51475,51526,'00:35:44.809','00:35:46.937','Yeah, I just wanted to talk to you.',-1),(107782,11,51549,51603,'00:35:47.896','00:35:50.149','You got some more\nMiss Myrna questions for me?',-1),(107783,11,51607,51647,'00:35:50.315','00:35:51.988','Oh, no, I just wanted to talk about...',-1),(107784,11,51740,51798,'00:35:55.862','00:35:58.285','We never finished our conversation\nat Elizabeth\'s.',-1),(107785,11,51802,51856,'00:35:58.448','00:36:00.667','About that book I want to write?',-1),(107786,11,52213,52281,'00:36:15.548','00:36:18.392','I\'d really like\nto interview you, Aibileen.',-1),(107787,11,52305,52336,'00:36:19.386','00:36:20.683','I know it\'s scary.',-1),(107788,11,52440,52503,'00:36:25.016','00:36:27.644','They set my cousin\nShinelle\'s car on fire,',-1),(107789,11,52507,52556,'00:36:27.811','00:36:29.859','just \'cause she went down\nto the voting station.',-1),(107790,11,52560,52614,'00:36:30.021','00:36:32.274','A book like this has never\nbeen written before.',-1),(107791,11,52618,52658,'00:36:32.440','00:36:34.113','\'Cause there\'s a reason.',-1),(107792,11,52662,52730,'00:36:34.275','00:36:37.119','I do this with you, I might as well\nburn my own house down.',-1),(107793,11,52734,52765,'00:36:37.278','00:36:38.575','I promise we\'ll be careful.',-1),(107794,11,52769,52828,'00:36:38.738','00:36:41.207','This already ain\'t careful,\nMiss Skeeter!',-1),(107795,11,52954,53020,'00:36:46.454','00:36:49.173','You not knowing that is what\'s\nscaring me the most.',-1),(107796,11,53023,53074,'00:36:49.332','00:36:51.426','Scare me more than Jim Crow.',-1),(107797,11,53143,53171,'00:36:54.295','00:36:55.467','All right.',-1),(107798,11,53190,53229,'00:36:56.256','00:36:57.883','Here\'s my phone number.',-1),(107799,11,53316,53395,'00:37:01.511','00:37:04.811','- My car\'s here. I could take you home.\n- No, ma\'am.',-1),(107800,11,53672,53763,'00:37:16.359','00:37:20.159','\"No person shall\nrequire any white female',-1),(107801,11,53767,53873,'00:37:20.321','00:37:24.747','to nurse in wards or rooms\nin which Negro men are placed.',-1),(107802,11,53921,54050,'00:37:26.745','00:37:32.093','Books shall not be interchangeable\nbetween the white and colored schools,',-1),(107803,11,54079,54175,'00:37:33.293','00:37:37.298','but shall continue to be used\nby the race first using them.',-1),(107804,11,54231,54358,'00:37:39.632','00:37:44.934','No colored barber shall serve as\na barber to white women or girls.',-1),(107805,11,54405,54461,'00:37:46.890','00:37:49.234','Any person printing, publishing',-1),(107806,11,54465,54509,'00:37:49.392','00:37:51.235','or circulating written matter',-1),(107807,11,54513,54639,'00:37:51.394','00:37:56.651','urging for public acceptance or social\nequality between whites and Negroes',-1),(107808,11,54643,54694,'00:37:56.816','00:37:58.944','is subject to imprisonment. \"',-1),(107809,11,54723,54748,'00:38:00.153','00:38:01.200','Hello?',-1),(107810,11,54752,54828,'00:38:01.362','00:38:04.536','Aibileen, I done went and did it now.',-1),(107811,11,54853,54902,'00:38:05.575','00:38:07.623','I went to Miss Hilly\'s house\nthis afternoon.',-1),(107812,11,54912,54942,'00:38:08.036','00:38:09.288','Why Minny?',-1),(107813,11,54946,55026,'00:38:09.454','00:38:12.754','She done told every white woman\nin town I\'m a thief',-1),(107814,11,55029,55089,'00:38:12.916','00:38:15.385','Said I stole a candelabra.',-1),(107815,11,55141,55180,'00:38:17.545','00:38:19.172','But I got her back.',-1),(107816,11,55184,55224,'00:38:19.339','00:38:21.012','What you did?',-1),(107817,11,55256,55288,'00:38:22.342','00:38:23.685','I can\'t tell you.',-1),(107818,11,55321,55369,'00:38:25.053','00:38:27.055','I ain \'t telling nobody.',-1),(107819,11,55474,55566,'00:38:31.434','00:38:35.280','I done something terrible awful\nto that woman,',-1),(107820,11,55570,55632,'00:38:35.438','00:38:38.032','and now she know what I done.',-1),(107821,11,55636,55667,'00:38:38.191','00:38:39.488','Sorry.',-1),(107822,11,55770,55794,'00:38:43.780','00:38:44.781','Minny.',-1),(107823,11,55798,55846,'00:38:44.948','00:38:46.950','She got what she deserved, Aibileen.',-1),(107824,11,55878,55941,'00:38:48.284','00:38:50.912','But now I ain\'t gonna never get\nno job again.',-1),(107825,11,55988,56044,'00:38:52.872','00:38:55.170','Oh, Lord, Leroy gonna kill me.',-1),(107826,11,56193,56217,'00:39:01.381','00:39:02.382','Leroy?',-1),(107827,11,56273,56315,'00:39:04.717','00:39:06.469','What you done did now, Minny?',-1),(107828,11,56353,56409,'00:39:08.054','00:39:10.398','- Get off that phone, woman!\n- Leroy, please!',-1),(107829,11,56413,56474,'00:39:10.557','00:39:13.106','Minny? Minny!',-1),(107830,11,56478,56531,'00:39:13.268','00:39:15.487','Please! Please!',-1),(107831,11,56535,56562,'00:39:15.645','00:39:16.771','Come here!',-1),(107832,11,56761,56855,'00:39:25.071','00:39:28.996','Please open your Bibles to Exodus.',-1),(107833,11,56871,56937,'00:39:29.659','00:39:32.412','Chapter four, verse ten.',-1),(107834,11,56949,57059,'00:39:32.912','00:39:37.463','God, having asked Moses\nto free the Israelites...',-1),(107835,11,57102,57140,'00:39:39.252','00:39:40.845','...Moses answered:',-1),(107836,11,57173,57277,'00:39:42.213','00:39:46.559','\"Oh, my Lord. I am not eloquent.',-1),(107837,11,57298,57400,'00:39:47.427','00:39:51.682','I am slow of speech and slow of tongue.\"',-1),(107838,11,57461,57566,'00:39:54.225','00:39:58.605','See, courage isn\'t just\nabout being brave.',-1),(107839,11,57570,57595,'00:39:58.771','00:39:59.818','Amen!',-1),(107840,11,57599,57652,'00:39:59.981','00:40:02.200','Courage is daring to do what is right',-1),(107841,11,57658,57726,'00:40:02.442','00:40:05.286','in spite of the weakness of our flesh.',-1),(107842,11,57730,57787,'00:40:05.445','00:40:07.823','And God tells us,',-1),(107843,11,57804,57870,'00:40:08.531','00:40:11.284','commands us, compels us,',-1),(107844,11,57874,57928,'00:40:11.451','00:40:13.704','- to love. Amen?\n- Amen.',-1),(107845,11,57988,58021,'00:40:16.205','00:40:17.582','See, love,',-1),(107846,11,58025,58113,'00:40:17.749','00:40:21.379','as exemplified\nby our Lord Jesus Christ,',-1),(107847,11,58117,58209,'00:40:21.544','00:40:25.390','is to be prepared to put yourself\nin harm\'s way',-1),(107848,11,58213,58260,'00:40:25.548','00:40:27.516','...for your fellow man.',-1),(107849,11,58264,58319,'00:40:27.675','00:40:29.973','And by your fellow man,\nI mean your brother,',-1),(107850,11,58328,58439,'00:40:30.345','00:40:34.976','your sister, your neighbor,\nyour friend and your enemy.',-1),(107851,11,58443,58539,'00:40:35.141','00:40:39.146','If you can love your enemy,\nyou already have the victory.',-1),(107852,11,58543,58593,'00:40:39.312','00:40:41.406','Let\'s stand. All right.',-1),(107853,11,59112,59143,'00:41:03.002','00:41:04.299','Quick. Come quick.',-1),(107854,11,59147,59225,'00:41:04.462','00:41:07.716','I parked way up on State Street and\ncaught a cab here, like you asked.',-1),(107855,11,59229,59265,'00:41:07.882','00:41:09.384','Got dropped two streets over?',-1),(107856,11,59269,59304,'00:41:09.550','00:41:11.018','Mm-hm.',-1),(107857,11,59642,59722,'00:41:25.108','00:41:28.453','I know now that it\'s against the law,\nwhat we\'re doing.',-1),(107858,11,59903,59947,'00:41:35.994','00:41:37.792','I\'ve never seen you\nout of uniform before.',-1),(107859,11,59986,60030,'00:41:39.455','00:41:41.253','You look really nice.',-1),(107860,11,60057,60086,'00:41:42.375','00:41:43.592','Thank you.',-1),(107861,11,60525,60593,'00:42:01.894','00:42:04.738','I ain\'t never had no white person\nin my house before.',-1),(107862,11,60644,60680,'00:42:06.858','00:42:08.360','Miss Skeeter...',-1),(107863,11,60746,60858,'00:42:11.112','00:42:15.788','...what if you don\'t like what I\ngot to say... about white people?',-1),(107864,11,60897,60939,'00:42:17.410','00:42:19.128','This isn\'t about me.',-1),(107865,11,60978,61017,'00:42:20.788','00:42:22.381','It doesn\'t matter how I feel.',-1),(107866,11,61218,61294,'00:42:30.757','00:42:33.931','You gonna have to change my name.\nMine, Miss Leefolt\'s. Everybody.',-1),(107867,11,61330,61379,'00:42:35.428','00:42:37.476','Do you have other maids\nthat are interested?',-1),(107868,11,61425,61473,'00:42:39.390','00:42:41.392','That gonna be hard.',-1),(107869,11,61477,61517,'00:42:41.559','00:42:43.232','What about Minny?',-1),(107870,11,61521,61559,'00:42:43.394','00:42:44.987','Minny got her some stories,\nsure enough,',-1),(107871,11,61563,61655,'00:42:45.146','00:42:48.992','but she ain\'t real keen on talking\nto white peoples right now.',-1),(107872,11,61731,61793,'00:42:52.153','00:42:54.747','What does it feel like\nto raise a white child',-1),(107873,11,61797,61866,'00:42:54.906','00:42:57.785','when your own child\'s at home being\nlooked after by somebody else?',-1),(107874,11,61934,61972,'00:43:00.620','00:43:02.167','It feel...',-1),(107875,11,62269,62298,'00:43:14.550','00:43:15.767','Is that your son?',-1),(107876,11,62422,62467,'00:43:20.932','00:43:22.809','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107877,11,62471,62523,'00:43:22.975','00:43:25.148','Can we move on to the next question?',-1),(107878,11,62527,62596,'00:43:25.311','00:43:28.190','You don\'t have to call me ma\'am.',-1),(107879,11,62610,62658,'00:43:28.773','00:43:30.775','Not here.',-1),(107880,11,62801,62826,'00:43:36.739','00:43:37.786','Uh...',-1),(107881,11,62830,62888,'00:43:37.949','00:43:40.372','Do you want to talk about the bathroom?',-1),(107882,11,62908,62980,'00:43:41.202','00:43:44.172','Or anything about Miss Leefolt?',-1),(107883,11,63003,63115,'00:43:45.164','00:43:49.795','How she pays you, or has she ever\nyelled at you in front of Mae Mobley?',-1),(107884,11,63221,63301,'00:43:54.215','00:43:57.560','I thought I might write my stories down\nand read them to you.',-1),(107885,11,63318,63368,'00:43:58.261','00:44:00.355','Ain\'t no different than writing down\nmy prayers.',-1),(107886,11,63463,63497,'00:44:04.308','00:44:05.730','OK.',-1),(107887,11,63534,63559,'00:44:07.270','00:44:08.317','Sure.',-1),(107888,11,63736,63795,'00:44:15.695','00:44:18.164','I don\'t say my prayers out loud.',-1),(107889,11,63799,63875,'00:44:18.322','00:44:21.496','I can get my point across\na lot better writing them down.',-1),(107890,11,63879,64001,'00:44:21.659','00:44:26.711','I write an hour,\nsometimes two, every night.',-1),(107891,11,64004,64117,'00:44:26.873','00:44:31.549','And after my prayers last night,\nI got some stories down, too.',-1),(107892,11,64196,64227,'00:44:34.839','00:44:36.136','Go ahead.',-1),(107893,11,64458,64532,'00:44:45.766','00:44:48.861','\"My first white baby to ever look after',-1),(107894,11,64536,64613,'00:44:49.020','00:44:52.240','was named Alton Carrington Speers.',-1),(107895,11,64617,64714,'00:44:52.398','00:44:56.448','It was 1925, and I had just turned 14.',-1),(107896,11,64730,64803,'00:44:57.111','00:45:00.160','I dropped out of school\nto help Mama with the bills.',-1),(107897,11,64807,64870,'00:45:00.323','00:45:02.917','Alton\'s mama died of lung disease.\"',-1),(107898,11,64956,65051,'00:45:06.537','00:45:10.462','I loved that baby. And he loved me.',-1),(107899,11,65110,65184,'00:45:12.919','00:45:16.014','That\'s when I learned I could make\nchildren feel proud of theyself.',-1),(107900,11,65249,65332,'00:45:18.716','00:45:22.186','Alton used to always be asking me\nhow come I was black.',-1),(107901,11,65336,65385,'00:45:22.345','00:45:24.393','Just ate him up.',-1),(107902,11,65389,65482,'00:45:24.555','00:45:28.435','And one time, I told him it was because\nI drank too much coffee.',-1),(107903,11,65584,65647,'00:45:32.688','00:45:35.316','You should have seen his face.',-1),(107904,11,65944,66007,'00:45:47.703','00:45:50.297','This was just so great.',-1),(107905,11,66054,66134,'00:45:52.291','00:45:55.591','I can\'t tell you how much I appreciate\nyour doing this with me.',-1),(107906,11,66164,66205,'00:45:56.837','00:45:58.555','What changed your mind?',-1),(107907,11,66246,66273,'00:46:00.258','00:46:01.384','God.',-1),(107908,11,66325,66372,'00:46:03.552','00:46:05.520','And Miss Hilly Holbrook.',-1),(107909,11,66689,66801,'00:46:18.734','00:46:23.410','Miss Hilly, I would like to ask you\nand Mr. William something.',-1),(107910,11,66884,66982,'00:46:26.867','00:46:30.917','My twin boys graduated from high school,\nboth on the honor roll.',-1),(107911,11,66997,67081,'00:46:31.580','00:46:35.050','Me and my husband, we been saving\nfor years to send them to Tougaloo.',-1),(107912,11,67129,67204,'00:46:37.044','00:46:40.173','We\'re short about $75\non one of the tuitions.',-1),(107913,11,67253,67372,'00:46:42.216','00:46:47.188','Whoo! I am late. I gotta get going.',-1),(107914,11,67443,67472,'00:46:50.141','00:46:51.358','See you tonight, honey.',-1),(107915,11,67476,67501,'00:46:51.517','00:46:52.564','OK.',-1),(107916,11,67559,67586,'00:46:54.979','00:46:56.105','Go on.',-1),(107917,11,67670,67739,'00:46:59.608','00:47:02.487','Well, now we\'re...',-1),(107918,11,67743,67808,'00:47:02.653','00:47:05.372','...faced with having to choose',-1),(107919,11,67812,67875,'00:47:05.531','00:47:08.159','which son can go if we don\'t\ncome up with the money.',-1),(107920,11,67904,67967,'00:47:09.368','00:47:11.996','Would you consider giving us a loan?',-1),(107921,11,67985,68111,'00:47:12.747','00:47:17.969','I\'d work every day for free\ntill it was paid off.',-1),(107922,11,68115,68211,'00:47:18.127','00:47:22.132','That\'s not working for free.\nThat\'s paying off a debt.',-1),(107923,11,68271,68307,'00:47:24.633','00:47:26.135','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107924,11,68401,68503,'00:47:30.056','00:47:34.311','As a Christian, I\'m doing you a favor.',-1),(107925,11,68545,68646,'00:47:36.062','00:47:40.283','See, God don\'t give charity to those\nwho are well and able.',-1),(107926,11,68674,68765,'00:47:41.442','00:47:45.242','You need to come up with this money\non your own. OK?',-1),(107927,11,68818,68867,'00:47:47.448','00:47:49.496','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(107928,11,68871,68907,'00:47:49.658','00:47:51.126','You\'ll thank me one day.',-1),(107929,11,68967,69048,'00:47:53.662','00:47:57.007','You cooking white food,\nyou taste it with a different spoon.',-1),(107930,11,69066,69117,'00:47:57.750','00:47:59.878','If they see you put the tasting spoon\nback in the pot,',-1),(107931,11,69121,69153,'00:48:00.044','00:48:01.387','might as well throw it all out.',-1),(107932,11,69157,69185,'00:48:01.545','00:48:02.717','Spoon, too.',-1),(107933,11,69189,69266,'00:48:02.880','00:48:06.100','And you use the same cup, same fork,\nsame plate every day.',-1),(107934,11,69270,69308,'00:48:06.258','00:48:07.851','And you put it up in the cabinet.',-1),(107935,11,69312,69377,'00:48:08.010','00:48:10.729','You tell that white woman that\'s where\nyou\'re gonna keep it from now on out.',-1),(107936,11,69381,69424,'00:48:10.888','00:48:12.686','Don\'t do it and see what happens.',-1),(107937,11,69428,69468,'00:48:12.848','00:48:14.521','Morning, ladies.',-1),(107938,11,69472,69512,'00:48:14.683','00:48:16.356','When you\'re sewing white folks coffee,',-1),(107939,11,69516,69547,'00:48:16.519','00:48:17.816','set it down in front of them.',-1),(107940,11,69551,69615,'00:48:17.978','00:48:20.652','Don\'t hand it to them,\n\'cause your hands can\'t touch.',-1),(107941,11,69634,69699,'00:48:21.440','00:48:24.159','And don\'t hit on they children.',-1),(107942,11,69703,69764,'00:48:24.318','00:48:26.867','White folks like to do\nthey own spanking.',-1),(107943,11,69795,69855,'00:48:28.155','00:48:30.658','And last thing. Come here.',-1),(107944,11,69886,69916,'00:48:31.951','00:48:33.168','Look at me.',-1),(107945,11,69919,69976,'00:48:33.327','00:48:35.671','No Sass-mouthing.',-1),(107946,11,70026,70084,'00:48:37.790','00:48:40.168','No Sass-mouthing.',-1),(107947,11,70088,70129,'00:48:40.334','00:48:42.052','I mean it.',-1),(107948,11,70254,70286,'00:48:47.258','00:48:48.601','Give your mama a kiss.',-1),(107949,11,70350,70458,'00:48:51.262','00:48:55.768','Leroy had made Sugar quit\nschool to help him with the bills.',-1),(107950,11,70551,70633,'00:48:59.645','00:49:03.070','And every day Minny\nwent without a job,',-1),(107951,11,70637,70703,'00:49:03.232','00:49:05.985','might have been a day Leroy\ntook her from our world.',-1),(107952,11,70810,70852,'00:49:10.448','00:49:12.200','Good morning, everybody.',-1),(107953,11,71017,71049,'00:49:19.081','00:49:20.378','But I knew.',-1),(107954,11,71052,71156,'00:49:20.541','00:49:24.842','I knew the only white lady Miss Hilly\nhadn\'t gotten to with her lies.',-1),(107955,11,71357,71398,'00:49:33.220','00:49:34.938','Hey!',-1),(107956,11,71402,71475,'00:49:35.097','00:49:38.146','Come on!',-1),(107957,11,71479,71586,'00:49:38.309','00:49:42.780','No sass-mouthing, Minny Jackson.\nNo Sass-mouthing.',-1),(107958,11,71632,71695,'00:49:44.690','00:49:47.318','Aibileen said you\'d be on time.',-1),(107959,11,71797,71842,'00:49:51.572','00:49:53.449','I\'m Celia Rae Foote.',-1),(107960,11,71846,71886,'00:49:53.616','00:49:55.289','I\'m Minny Jackson.',-1),(107961,11,71925,71999,'00:49:56.911','00:49:59.960','You, uh... cooking something?',-1),(107962,11,72027,72110,'00:50:01.165','00:50:04.590','One of those upside-down cakes\nfrom a magazine.',-1),(107963,11,72114,72204,'00:50:04.752','00:50:08.507','It ain\'t working out too good.\nCome on, let\'s get you a cold Coca-Cola.',-1),(107964,11,72269,72293,'00:50:11.217','00:50:12.218','Come on.',-1),(107965,11,72344,72393,'00:50:14.345','00:50:16.393','This here is the kitchen.',-1),(107966,11,72423,72478,'00:50:17.640','00:50:19.938','What in the hell?',-1),(107967,11,72559,72617,'00:50:23.312','00:50:25.735','I guess I got some learning to do.',-1),(107968,11,72635,72708,'00:50:26.482','00:50:29.531','You sure do.',-1),(107969,11,72712,72785,'00:50:29.693','00:50:32.742','Johnny\'s grandmama left him this house\nwhen she died.',-1),(107970,11,72789,72861,'00:50:32.905','00:50:35.909','And then Johnny\'s mama\nwouldn\'t let me change a thing.',-1),(107971,11,72865,72913,'00:50:36.075','00:50:38.077','But if I had it my way,',-1),(107972,11,72917,73035,'00:50:38.244','00:50:43.125','this place would be wall-to-wall\nwhite carpet with gold trim.',-1),(107973,11,73038,73091,'00:50:43.290','00:50:45.463','None of this old stuff.',-1),(107974,11,73095,73150,'00:50:45.626','00:50:47.924','The main house has\nfive beds and baths,',-1),(107975,11,73154,73257,'00:50:48.087','00:50:52.388','and then the pool house has\ntwo more beds and baths.',-1),(107976,11,73261,73313,'00:50:52.550','00:50:54.723','When y\'all gonna start\nhaving some children,',-1),(107977,11,73317,73367,'00:50:54.885','00:50:56.979','filling up all these empty beds?',-1),(107978,11,73419,73482,'00:50:59.139','00:51:01.767','- I\'m pregnant now.\n- Oh.',-1),(107979,11,73486,73570,'00:51:01.934','00:51:05.438','Gonna be eating for two.\nThat\'s double the cooking.',-1),(107980,11,73595,73664,'00:51:06.480','00:51:09.359','I know. It\'s an awful lotto do.',-1),(107981,11,73689,73763,'00:51:10.401','00:51:1