8,11,154927,154988,'01:47:35.324','01:47:37.873','It\'s my fault she pounced on you.',-1),(108699,11,155048,155096,'01:47:40.371','01:47:42.373','If you leave Mr. Johnny...',-1),(108700,11,155152,155227,'01:47:44.708','01:47:47.803','...then Miss Hilly done won\nthe whole ball game.',-1),(108701,11,155279,155323,'01:47:49.964','01:47:51.807','Then she done beaten me...',-1),(108702,11,155357,155407,'01:47:53.217','01:47:55.311','...and she done beat you.',-1),(108703,11,155576,155637,'01:48:02.351','01:48:04.900','Thank you for telling me that.',-1),(108704,11,155817,155904,'01:48:12.403','01:48:16.033','Lord, look at all these pages. 266.',-1),(108705,11,155915,155960,'01:48:16.490','01:48:18.367','Mm-mm!',-1),(108706,11,155990,156059,'01:48:19.618','01:48:22.497','So we just send it off?\nJust wait and see?',-1),(108707,11,156063,156105,'01:48:22.663','01:48:24.381','Hope Miss Stein gonna publish it?',-1),(108708,11,156108,156208,'01:48:24.540','01:48:28.670','Well, I have one more story to type\nbefore I put it in the mail,',-1),(108709,11,156212,156248,'01:48:28.836','01:48:30.338','but other than that, we\'re done.',-1),(108710,11,156252,156290,'01:48:30.504','01:48:32.097','Which one you got left?',-1),(108711,11,156350,156378,'01:48:34.591','01:48:35.763','Uh, mine.',-1),(108712,11,156633,156692,'01:48:46.395','01:48:48.864','I need to talk to you about Constantine.',-1),(108713,11,156704,156800,'01:48:49.356','01:48:53.361','Oh, Eugenia, that was so long ago.',-1),(108714,11,156813,156841,'01:48:53.902','01:48:55.074','What happened?',-1),(108715,11,156845,156902,'01:48:55.237','01:48:57.615','Oh.',-1),(108716,11,156921,156966,'01:48:58.407','01:49:00.250','What happened?',-1),(108717,11,157079,157131,'01:49:04.997','01:49:07.125','She didn\'t give me a choice.',-1),(108718,11,157254,157372,'01:49:12.254','01:49:17.181','The Daughters of America had just\nappointed me state regent.',-1),(108719,11,157439,157519,'01:49:19.970','01:49:23.315','Grace Higginbotham, our esteemed\npresident, came all the way down',-1),(108720,11,157523,157618,'01:49:23.474','01:49:27.445','from Washington, D.C.,\nto our house for the ceremony.',-1),(108721,11,157657,157753,'01:49:29.063','01:49:33.068','That\'s just beautiful. Look at that.',-1),(108722,11,157837,157926,'01:49:36.570','01:49:40.291','She\'d gotten so old and slow, Skeeter.',-1),(108723,11,158015,158045,'01:49:43.994','01:49:45.211','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(108724,11,158108,158191,'01:49:47.873','01:49:51.298','It\'s such an honor\nthat you came all this way.',-1),(108725,11,158400,158425,'01:50:00.010','01:50:01.057','That\'s all right.',-1),(108726,11,158541,158605,'01:50:05.891','01:50:08.565','- Hello, Miss Charlotte.\n- Rachel.',-1),(108727,11,158654,158705,'01:50:10.604','01:50:12.732','We were expecting you next week.',-1),(108728,11,158709,158752,'01:50:12.898','01:50:14.696','I decided to come early\nand surprise Mama.',-1),(108729,11,158756,158802,'01:50:14.858','01:50:16.781','Oh.',-1),(108730,11,158827,158860,'01:50:17.820','01:50:19.197','I\'m entertaining.',-1),(108731,11,158864,158921,'01:50:19.363','01:50:21.741','Why don\'t you go around back.\nWait in the kitchen.',-1),(108732,11,159057,159089,'01:50:27.412','01:50:28.709','Go on now.',-1),(108733,11,159165,159201,'01:50:31.875','01:50:33.377','I am sorry.',-1),(108734,11,159272,159335,'01:50:36.338','01:50:38.966','Rachel, what are you doing?',-1),(108735,11,159339,159417,'01:50:39.133','01:50:42.387','I\'m just doing as I was told,\nMiss Charlotte.',-1),(108736,11,159421,159457,'01:50:42.553','01:50:44.055','Going to the kitchen.',-1),(108737,11,159461,159511,'01:50:44.221','01:50:46.315','But I\'m going to see my mama first.',-1),(108738,11,159546,159612,'01:50:47.766','01:50:50.519','Hello, Mama.',-1),(108739,11,159616,159681,'01:50:50.686','01:50:53.405','Go on to the kitchen, baby.\nI\'ll be there directly.',-1),(108740,11,159685,159785,'01:50:53.564','01:50:57.740','You may put up with this kind\nof nonsense, but I do not.',-1),(108741,11,159946,159983,'01:51:04.449','01:51:05.996','Get out of this house, Rachel.',-1),(108742,11,160082,160140,'01:51:10.122','01:51:12.500','You heard her. Go on, girl.',-1),(108743,11,160143,160243,'01:51:12.666','01:51:16.796','Miss Charlotte, let me take her to\nthe kitchen. Come on, baby. Let\'s go.',-1),(108744,11,160288,160322,'01:51:18.672','01:51:20.094','Charlotte.',-1),(108745,11,160428,160474,'01:51:24.511','01:51:26.434','Both of you.',-1),(108746,11,160478,160541,'01:51:26.597','01:51:29.225','Leave. Now.',-1),(108747,11,160641,160673,'01:51:33.395','01:51:34.738','Come on, Mama.',-1),(108748,11,161454,161491,'01:52:07.262','01:52:08.809','Come on now.',-1),(108749,11,161818,161878,'01:52:22.444','01:52:24.947','Constantine didn\'t do anything wrong.',-1),(108750,11,161919,161965,'01:52:26.657','01:52:28.580','And you love Rachel. I know you do.',-1),(108751,11,161969,162045,'01:52:28.742','01:52:31.916','She was our president.\nWhat was I supposed to do?',-1),(108752,11,162069,162174,'01:52:32.913','01:52:37.259','She did you the biggest favor of\nyour life. She taught me everything.',-1),(108753,11,162178,162254,'01:52:37.417','01:52:40.591','Well, you idolized her too much.\nYou always have.',-1),(108754,11,162258,162309,'01:52:40.754','01:52:42.882','I needed someone to look up to.',-1),(108755,11,162391,162424,'01:52:46.301','01:52:47.678','Well, I...',-1),(108756,11,162444,162532,'01:52:48.512','01:52:52.187','I went to her house the next day,\nbut she had already gone.',-1),(108757,11,163270,163307,'01:53:22.921','01:53:24.468','How could you not tell me all this?',-1),(108758,11,163311,163395,'01:53:24.631','01:53:28.135','Because I didn\'t want to upset you\nduring your final exams.',-1),(108759,11,163399,163464,'01:53:28.302','01:53:31.021','I knew you\'d blame me,\nand it wasn\'t my fault!',-1),(108760,11,163468,163506,'01:53:31.179','01:53:32.772','I have to go find her. She needs me.',-1),(108761,11,163510,163541,'01:53:32.931','01:53:34.228','- Eugenia.\n- What?',-1),(108762,11,163587,163670,'01:53:36.143','01:53:39.613','We sent your brother up to Chicago\nto bring Constantine home.',-1),(108763,11,163884,163918,'01:53:48.530','01:53:49.952','When he got there...',-1),(108764,11,164016,164053,'01:53:54.036','01:53:55.583','...she had died.',-1),(108765,11,164441,164491,'01:54:11.720','01:54:13.814','You broke her heart.',-1),(108766,11,164625,164743,'01:54:19.394','01:54:24.321','- I\'m...\n- I\'m sorry. I\'m so sorry!',-1),(108767,11,164817,164856,'01:54:27.402','01:54:29.029','I\'m sorry.',-1),(108768,11,166196,166243,'01:55:24.835','01:55:26.803','They printed a few thousand copies',-1),(108769,11,166247,166327,'01:55:26.962','01:55:30.307','with the worst advance Miss Stein\nhad ever seen.',-1),(108770,11,166331,166394,'01:55:30.465','01:55:33.093','Baby, what you doing with Alicia book?\nYou can\'t read.',-1),(108771,11,166420,166548,'01:55:34.177','01:55:39.525','They sent Miss Skeeter $600. She broke\nthat money up and gave it to each of us.',-1),(108772,11,166568,166686,'01:55:40.350','01:55:45.277','Divided 13 ways,\nthat came to about $46 each.',-1),(108773,11,166832,166864,'01:55:51.361','01:55:52.704','Y\'all finish your homework.',-1),(108774,11,166988,167051,'01:55:57.868','01:56:00.462','Aibileen. Aibileen!',-1),(108775,11,167070,167135,'01:56:01.288','01:56:03.962','We just got this from Miss Skeeter.\nLook at it.',-1),(108776,11,167138,167176,'01:56:04.124','01:56:05.671','Look at it.',-1),(108777,11,167180,167221,'01:56:05.834','01:56:07.552','Look at it!',-1),(108778,11,167225,167272,'01:56:07.711','01:56:09.679','Minny, we\'re rich!',-1),(108779,11,167318,167401,'01:56:11.590','01:56:15.060','\"She fired me\nfor using her inside toilet.',-1),(108780,11,167405,167519,'01:56:15.218','01:56:19.974','Put me out in a storm and told me never\nto come back. But I did come back.',-1),(108781,11,167523,167623,'01:56:20.140','01:56:24.316','I came back with a 