,'00:27:26.560','00:27:27.600','Now, that\'s good.',-1),(109545,12,39545,39596,'00:27:27.720','00:27:29.850','Wardo, it\'s like a final club,\nexcept we\'re the president.',-1),(109546,12,39609,39674,'00:27:30.390','00:27:33.100','I told him I thought it sounded great.',-1),(109547,12,39692,39725,'00:27:33.860','00:27:35.230','It was a great idea.',-1),(109548,12,39728,39752,'00:27:35.360','00:27:36.360','There was nothing to hack.',-1),(109549,12,39754,39827,'00:27:36.440','00:27:39.490','People were gonna provide\ntheir own pictures, their own information.',-1),(109550,12,39829,39944,'00:27:39.570','00:27:44.370','And people had the ability to invite,\nor not invite, their friends to join.',-1),(109551,12,39960,40043,'00:27:45.030','00:27:48.490','See, in a world where\nsocial structure was everything,',-1),(109552,12,40058,40089,'00:27:49.120','00:27:50.410','that was the thing.',-1),(109553,12,40103,40134,'00:27:50.960','00:27:52.290','It was a big project,',-1),(109554,12,40138,40212,'00:27:52.420','00:27:55.540','and he was going to have to write\ntens of thousands of lines of code,',-1),(109555,12,40215,40278,'00:27:55.630','00:27:58.250','so I wondered why he was\ncoming to me and not his roommates,',-1),(109556,12,40280,40344,'00:27:58.340','00:28:01.010','Dustin Moskovitz and Chris Hughes.\nThey were programmers.',-1),(109557,12,40347,40427,'00:28:01.130','00:28:04.470','We\'re gonna need a little start-up cash\nto rent the servers and get it online.',-1),(109558,12,40455,40480,'00:28:05.640','00:28:06.680','So that was why.',-1),(109559,12,40482,40521,'00:28:06.760','00:28:08.390','- Did he offer terms?\n- Yes.',-1),(109560,12,40523,40570,'00:28:08.470','00:28:10.430','We\'ll split it, 70/30.',-1),(109561,12,40574,40633,'00:28:10.600','00:28:13.060','70 for me, 30 for you\nfor putting up the $1,000',-1),(109562,12,40635,40689,'00:28:13.140','00:28:15.400','and for handling everything\non the business end. You\'re CFO.',-1),(109563,12,40691,40716,'00:28:15.480','00:28:16.520','And you said?',-1),(109564,12,40718,40757,'00:28:16.610','00:28:18.230','I said, \"Let\'s do it.\"',-1),(109565,12,40759,40804,'00:28:18.320','00:28:20.190','Okay. Did he add anything else?',-1),(109566,12,40814,40839,'00:28:20.610','00:28:21.650','Yes.',-1),(109567,12,40928,40990,'00:28:25.370','00:28:27.950','It probably was a diversity thing.',-1),(109568,12,41019,41047,'00:28:29.160','00:28:30.330','But so what?',-1),(109569,12,41052,41082,'00:28:30.500','00:28:31.790','Why do you think he said that?',-1),(109570,12,41084,41137,'00:28:31.870','00:28:34.080','Gretchen, excuse me for interrupting,\nbut whose discovery is this?',-1),(109571,12,41140,41182,'00:28:34.170','00:28:35.920','Sy, if you\'ll let me continue\nwith my line of questioning.',-1),(109572,12,41184,41209,'00:28:36.000','00:28:37.080','What are you suggesting?',-1),(109573,12,41212,41264,'00:28:37.170','00:28:39.340','That I was jealous of Eduardo\nfor getting punched by the Phoenix',-1),(109574,12,41267,41304,'00:28:39.460','00:28:41.000','and began a plan\nto screw him out of a company',-1),(109575,12,41307,41347,'00:28:41.130','00:28:42.800','- I hadn\'t even invented yet.\n- Were you?',-1),(109576,12,41349,41379,'00:28:42.880','00:28:44.130','- Gretchen.\n- Jealous of Eduardo?',-1),(109577,12,41381,41411,'00:28:44.220','00:28:45.470','Stop typing. We\'re off the record.',-1),(109578,12,41413,41438,'00:28:45.550','00:28:46.590','Ma\'am, I know you\'ve done your homework,',-1),(109579,12,41440,41478,'00:28:46.680','00:28:48.260','and so you know that money\nisn\'t a big part of my life.',-1),(109580,12,41480,41528,'00:28:48.350','00:28:50.350','But at the moment,\nI could buy Mount Auburn Street,',-1),(109581,12,41531,41607,'00:28:50.470','00:28:53.640','take the Phoenix Club\nand turn it into my ping-pong room.',-1),(109582,12,41708,41756,'00:28:57.860','00:28:59.860','I\'ll let you know how the party is.',-1),(109583,12,41896,41975,'00:29:05.700','00:29:08.990','We recognize that you\'re a plaintiff\nin one suit involving Facebook,',-1),(109584,12,41979,42011,'00:29:09.160','00:29:10.490','and a witness in another.',-1),(109585,12,42013,42039,'00:29:10.580','00:29:11.660','Yes, sir.',-1),(109586,12,42042,42114,'00:29:11.750','00:29:14.750','At any time in the weeks\nprior to Mark\'s telling you his idea,',-1),(109587,12,42115,42175,'00:29:14.830','00:29:17.330','did he mention Tyler Winklevoss,\nCameron Winklevoss,',-1),(109588,12,42178,42233,'00:29:17.420','00:29:19.710','Divya Narendra or Harvard Connection?',-1),(109589,12,42236,42299,'00:29:19.840','00:29:22.460','Yes. He said they\'d asked him\nto work on their site,',-1),(109590,12,42301,42395,'00:29:22.550','00:29:26.470','but that he looked at what they had\nand decided it wasn\'t worth his time.',-1),(109591,12,42397,42435,'00:29:26.550','00:29:28.140','He said even his most pathetic friends',-1),(109592,12,42437,42530,'00:29:28.220','00:29:32.100','knew more about getting people\ninterested in a website than these guys.',-1),(109593,12,42532,42578,'00:29:32.180','00:29:34.100','\"These guys,\" meaning my clients.',-1),(109594,12,42580,42675,'00:29:34.180','00:29:38.150','Yes. He resented...\nMark resented that your clients thought',-1),(109595,12,42677,42735,'00:29:38.230','00:29:40.650','that he needed to rehabilitate\nhis image after Facemash.',-1),(109596,12,42737,42787,'00:29:40.730','00:29:42.820','But Mark didn\'t want\nto rehabilitate anything.',-1),(109597,12,42789,42856,'00:29:42.900','00:29:45.690','With Facemash, he\'d hacked into\nthe Harvard computers,',-1),(109598,12,42858,42921,'00:29:45.780','00:29:48.410','he\'d thumbed his nose at the Ad Board,\nhe\'d gotten a lot of notoriety.',-1),(109599,12,42924,42986,'00:29:48.530','00:29:51.120','Facemash did exactly\nwhat he wanted it to do.',-1),(109600,12,42988,43047,'00:29:51.200','00:29:53.660','Were you aware that while Mr. Zuckerberg\nwas building The Facebook,',-1),(109601,12,43050,43092,'00:29:53.750','00:29:55.540','he was also communicating\nwith the plaintiffs?',-1),(109602,12,43094,43146,'00:29:55.620','00:29:57.790','Not at the time, I wasn\'t. But...',-1),(109603,12,43193,43260,'00:29:59.710','00:30:02.500','It really didn\'t have much to do\nwith the Winklevosses\' dating site.',-1),(109604,12,43262,43287,'00:30:02.590','00:30:03.630','How would you know?\nYou weren\'t even there.',-1),(109605,12,43289,43315,'00:30:03.710','00:30:04.800','Ty.',-1),(109606,12,43323,43397,'00:30:05.130','00:30:08.220','Were you aware that while Mr. Zuckerberg\nwas building The Facebook,',-1),(109607,12,43399,43482,'00:30:08.300','00:30:11.760','he was leading the plaintiffs to believe\nhe was building Harvard Connection?',-1),(109608,12,43485,43519,'00:30:11.890','00:30:13.310','You\'re offering a conclusion\nnot found in evidence.',-1),(109609,12,43521,43585,'00:30:13.390','00:30:16.060','We are about to find it in evidence.',-1),(109610,12,43598,43655,'00:30:16.600','00:30:18.980','From Mark Zuckerberg to Tyler Winklevoss.',-1),(109611,12,43657,43703,'00:30:19.060','00:30:20.980','November 30th, 2003.',-1),(109612,12,43705,43772,'00:30:21.060','00:30:23.860','\"I read over all the stuff you sent me\nre: Harvard Connection.',-1),(109613,12,43774,43835,'00:30:23.940','00:30:26.490','\"And it seems like it shouldn\'t\ntake too long to implement.',-1),(109614,12,43837,43950,'00:30:26.570','00:30:31.280','\"So we can talk about it after I get all\nthe basic functionality up tomorrow night.\"',-1),(109615,12,43953,44058,'00:30:31.410','00:30:35.790','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Cameron Winklevoss. December 1 st, 2003.',-1),(109616,12,44061,44144,'00:30:35.910','00:30:39.370','\"Sorry I was unreachable tonight.\nI just got about three of your missed calls.',-1),(109617,12,44147,44214,'00:30:39.460','00:30:42.290','\"I was working on a problem set\nfor my systems class.\"',-1),(109618,12,44218,44272,'00:30:42.420','00:30:44.670','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Tyler and Cameron Winklevoss.',-1),(109619,12,44274,44326,'00:30:44.750','00:30:46.920','December 10, 2003.',-1),(109620,12,44340,44404,'00:30:47.510','00:30:50.180','\"This week has been pretty busy\nthus far with classes and work,',-1),(109621,12,44406,44481,'00:30:50.260','00:30:53.390','\"so I think it\'s probably best\nto postpone the meeting.\"',-1),(109622,12,44483,44534,'00:30:53.470','00:30:55.600','\"I\'m also really busy tomorrow.\"',-1),(109623,12,44536,44617,'00:30:55.680','00:30:59.060','Okay, anybody else feel like\nthere\'s something up with this guy?',-1),(109624,12,44619,44644,'00:30:59.140','00:31:00.190','Tell him okay,',-1),(109625,12,44646,44712,'00:31:00.270','00:31:03.020','but we do have to make sure that\nwe meet up before we all go off for break.',-1),(109626,12,44726,44792,'00:31:03.610','00:31:06.360','I know, I know. Yeah, watch out.',-1),(109627,12,45535,45564,'00:31:37.310','00:31:38.520','Hey, Mark.',-1),(109628,12,45567,45636,'00:31:38.640','00:31:41.520','I need a dedicated Linux box\nrunning Apache with a MySQL back end.',-1),(109629,12,45639,45674,'00:31:41.640','00:31:43.100','It\'s gonna cost a little more money.',-1),(109630,12,45676,45733,'00:31:43.190','00:31:45.560','- How much more?\n- About 200 more.',-1),(109631,12,45737,45795,'00:31:45.730','00:31:48.150','- Do we need it?\n- Gotta handle the traffic.',-1),(109632,12,45875,45920,'00:31:51.490','00:31:53.360','- Do it.\n- I already did.',-1),(109633,12,46024,46051,'00:31:57.700','00:31:58.830','Hey, guess what?',-1),(109634,12,46092,46131,'00:32:00.540','00:32:02.160','I made the second cut.',-1),(109635,12,46148,46174,'00:32:02.870','00:32:03.920','That\'s good.',-1),(109636,12,46176,46264,'00:32:04.000','00:32:07.670','You should be proud of that right there.\nDon\'t worry if you don\'t make it any further.',-1),(109637,12,46380,46415,'00:32:12.510','00:32:13.970','I\'ll get out of here.',-1),(109638,12,46417,46473,'00:32:14.050','00:32:16.390','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Tyler and Cameron Winklevoss',-1