ogize to anyone\nfor losing a race like that.',-1),(110791,12,125658,125702,'01:27:15.770','01:27:17.600','- Boys.\n- Mr. Kenwright.',-1),(110792,12,125718,125782,'01:27:18.270','01:27:20.940','Dad, this is Mr. Kenwright,\nhead of the host family for this week.',-1),(110793,12,125784,125826,'01:27:21.020','01:27:22.770','- Pleasure to meet you.\n- Good to meet you.',-1),(110794,12,125828,125862,'01:27:22.860','01:27:24.270','I\'ve just had a phone chat with my daughter.',-1),(110795,12,125864,125935,'01:27:24.360','01:27:27.320','She told me that she and her friends\nare already talking about the race,',-1),(110796,12,125938,125992,'01:27:27.450','01:27:29.700','which they\'ve just seen via their computers.',-1),(110797,12,125995,126087,'01:27:29.820','01:27:33.660','A new website called Facebook.\nDo you have this in America?',-1),(110798,12,126119,126171,'01:27:34.990','01:27:37.160','I\'m gonna find your mother.',-1),(110799,12,126209,126234,'01:27:38.710','01:27:39.750','Have I said something wrong?',-1),(110800,12,126235,126281,'01:27:39.830','01:27:41.710','Your daughter doesn\'t go\nto school in the States?',-1),(110801,12,126283,126315,'01:27:41.830','01:27:43.130','No, no. Cambridge.',-1),(110802,12,126317,126383,'01:27:43.210','01:27:45.960','Majoring in French literature, though\nI wasn\'t aware there was such a thing.',-1),(110803,12,126385,126411,'01:27:46.050','01:27:47.130','And they have Facebook at Cambridge?',-1),(110804,12,126413,126463,'01:27:47.220','01:27:49.300','And apparently Oxford and\nthe London School of Economics.',-1),(110805,12,126465,126491,'01:27:49.380','01:27:50.470','That\'s where her friends are.',-1),(110806,12,126505,126541,'01:27:51.050','01:27:52.550','That\'s awesome.',-1),(110807,12,126552,126636,'01:27:53.010','01:27:56.520','Good race, boys.\nTake the bitter with the better, eh?',-1),(110808,12,126692,126725,'01:27:58.850','01:28:00.230','I\'m gonna go watch the race film.',-1),(110809,12,126805,126860,'01:28:03.560','01