39,16109,16181,'00:11:11.221','00:11:14.224','<i>You know, the nobility of the band\nplaying to the very end and all that.</i>',-1),(112946,39,16187,16246,'00:11:14.474','00:11:16.935','<i>But what I\'m interested in\nare the untold stories.</i>',-1),(112947,39,16247,16295,'00:11:16.977','00:11:18.979','<i>The secrets locked deep inside\nthe hull of Titanic.</i>',-1),(112948,39,16301,16397,'00:11:19.229','00:11:23.233','<i>And we\'re out here using robot technology\nto go further into the wreck...</i>',-1),(112949,39,16403,16443,'00:11:23.483','00:11:25.152','<i>...than anybody\nhas ever done before.</i>',-1),(112950,39,16451,16527,'00:11:25.485','00:11:28.655','<i>REPORTER: Your expedition is at the\ncenter of a storm of controversy...</i>',-1),(112951,39,16533,16581,'00:11:28.906','00:11:30.908','<i>...over salvage rights\nand even ethics.</i>',-1),(112952,39,16582,16629,'00:11:30.949','00:11:32.910','<i>Many are calling you\na graverobber.</i>',-1),(112953,39,16635,16679,'00:11:33.160','00:11:34.995','<i>Well, nobody ever called the\nrecovery of the artifacts...</i>',-1),(112954,39,16685,16709,'00:11:35.245','00:11:36.246','What is it?',-1),(112955,39,16715,16755,'00:11:36.496','00:11:38.165','Turn that up, dear.',-1),(112956,39,16763,16828,'00:11:38.498','00:11:41.168','<i>I</i> have museum-trained experts\nsent out here making sure...',-1),(112957,39,16834,16898,'00:11:41.418','00:11:44.087','<i>...that these relics are preserved\nand catalogued properly.</i>',-1),(112958,39,16902,16970,'00:11:44.254','00:11:47.090','<i>Take a look at this drawing\nthat we found just today.</i>',-1),(112959,39,16976,17060,'00:11:47.341','00:11:50.844','<i>A piece of paper that\'s been\nunderwater for 84 years.</i>',-1),(112960,39,17068,17128,'00:11:51.178','00:11:53.680','<i>And my team are able to\npreserve it intact.</i>',-1),(112961,39,17140,17178,'00:11:54.181','00:11:55.766','<i>Should this have remained unseen</i>',-1),(112962,39,17179,17216,'00:11:55.807','00:11:57.351',