:28:53.241','00:28:54.492','He won\'t, trust me.',-1),(113275,39,41634,41688,'00:28:54.784','00:28:57.036','- ROSE: Let\'s put the Degas in the bedroom.\n- At least they were cheap.',-1),(113276,39,41706,41750,'00:28:57.787','00:28:59.622','Put it in the wardrobe.',-1),(113277,39,41883,41987,'00:29:05.127','00:29:09.465','<i>OLD ROSE: At Cherbourg, a woman\ncame aboard named Margaret Brown.</i>',-1),(113278,39,41995,42035,'00:29:09.799','00:29:11.467','<i>We all called her Molly.</i>',-1),(113279,39,42043,42119,'00:29:11.801','00:29:14.971','<i>History would call her\nthe Unsinkable Molly Brown.</i>',-1),(113280,39,42127,42178,'00:29:15.304','00:29:17.431','Well, I wasn\'t about to\nwait all day for you, sonny.',-1),(113281,39,42181,42232,'00:29:17.556','00:29:19.684','Here, if you think\nyou can manage.',-1),(113282,39,42247,42319,'00:29:20.309','00:29:23.312','<i>OLD ROSE: Her husband had\nstruck gold someplace out west.</i>',-1),(113283,39,42327,42394,'00:29:23.646','00:29:26.440','<i>And she was what Mother\ncalled \"new money.\"</i>',-1),(113284,39,42423,42454,'00:29:27.650','00:29:28.943','<i>By the next afternoon...</i>',-1),(113285,39,42456,42521,'00:29:29.026','00:29:31.737','...we were steaming west\nfrom the <i>coast</i> of Ireland...',-1),(113286,39,42542,42626,'00:29:32.613','00:29:36.117','<i>...with nothing out ahead\nof us but ocean.</i>',-1),(113287,39,42775,42828,'00:29:42.331','00:29:44.500','Take her to sea,\nMr. Murdoch.',-1),(113288,39,42850,42879,'00:29:45.418','00:29:46.627','Let\'s stretch her legs.',-1),(113289,39,42890,42914,'00:29:47.086','00:29:48.087','Yes sir.',-1),(113290,39,42968,42993,'00:29:50.339','00:29:51.382','All ahead full, Mr. Moody.',-1),(113291,39,43011,43036,'00:29:52.133','00:29:53.175','Very good, sir.',-1),(113292,39,43043,43089,'00:29:53.467','00:29:55.386','(ENGINE TELEGRAPH RINGING)',-1),(113293,39,43106,43130,'00:29:56.095','00:29:57.096','(CHIMES)',-1),(113294,39,43167,43192,'00:29:58.639','00:29:59.682','All ahead full.',-1),(113295,39,43193,43219,'00:29:59.724','00:30:00.808','(RINGING)',-1),(113296,39,43221,43255,'00:30:00.891','00:30:02.310','All ahead full!',-1),(113297,39,43265,43294,'00:30:02.727','00:30:03.936','ENGINEER BELL: Come on lads,\nstep lively!',-1),(113298,39,43414,43460,'00:30:08.941','00:30:10.860','(ENGINEERS SHOUTING)',-1),(113299,39,43738,43789,'00:30:22.455','00:30:24.582','All right! Let\'s stoke\nher right up!',-1),(113300,39,43794,43824,'00:30:24.790','00:30:26.000','We go full ahead!',-1),(113301,39,43832,43880,'00:30:26.334','00:30:28.336','Come on, put your backs into it!',-1),(113302,39,44418,44452,'00:30:50.775','00:30:52.193','<i>(WIND HOWLS)</i>',-1),(113303,39,45194,45238,'00:31:23.099','00:31:24.934','21 knots, sir.',-1),(113304,39,45452,45476,'00:31:33.859','00:31:34.860','JACK: Hey, look,\nlook, look!',-1),(113305,39,45554,45586,'00:31:38.114','00:31:39.448','See it?',-1),(113306,39,45666,45714,'00:31:42.785','00:31:44.787','There\'s another\none! See him?',-1),(113307,39,45964,46007,'00:31:55.172','00:31:56.966','Look at that one!\nLook at him jump!',-1),(113308,39,46041,46068,'00:31:58.384','00:31:59.510','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113309,39,46380,46414,'00:32:12.523','00:32:13.941','(STOKERS GRUNTING)',-1),(113310,39,46586,46615,'00:32:21.115','00:32:22.324','Whoo!',-1),(113311,39,46645,46699,'00:32:23.576','00:32:25.828','I can see the Statue\nof Liberty already.',-1),(113312,39,46707,46741,'00:32:26.162','00:32:27.580','Very small, of course.',-1),(113313,39,46828,46896,'00:32:31.167','00:32:34.003','I\'m the king of the world!',-1),(113314,39,46900,46958,'00:32:34.170','00:32:36.589','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113315,39,46960,47020,'00:32:36.672','00:32:39.175','(BOTH WHOOPING)',-1),(113316,39,47033,47067,'00:32:39.717','00:32:41.135','Yee-hah!',-1),(113317,39,47101,47137,'00:32:42.553','00:32:44.054','(HOWLING)',-1),(113318,39,48001,48038,'00:33:20.049','00:33:21.592','<i>She is the largest moving object</i>',-1),(113319,39,48039,48073,'00:33:21.634','00:33:23.052','<i>ever made by the hand of man...</i>',-1),(113320,39,48079,48127,'00:33:23.302','00:33:25.304','...in all history.',-1),(113321,39,48135,48186,'00:33:25.638','00:33:27.765','And our master shipbuilder,\nMr. Andrews here...',-1),(113322,39,48188,48233,'00:33:27.848','00:33:29.725','...designed her from the\nkeel plates up.',-1),(113323,39,48239,48286,'00:33:29.975','00:33:31.936','I may have knocked\nher together, but...',-1),(113324,39,48290,48340,'00:33:32.102','00:33:34.188','...the idea was\nMr.Ismay\'s.',-1),(113325,39,48351,48408,'00:33:34.647','00:33:37.024','He envisioned a steamer\nso grand in scale...',-1),(113326,39,48410,48435,'00:33:37.107','00:33:38.150','...and so luxurious in...',-1),(113327,39,48437,48462,'00:33:38.234','00:33:39.276','...its appointments...',-1),(113328,39,48464,48515,'00:33:39.360','00:33:41.487','...that its supremacy\nwould never be challenged.',-1),(113329,39,48519,48555,'00:33:41.654','00:33:43.155','And here she is.',-1),(113330,39,48561,48640,'00:33:43.405','00:33:46.700','- Willed into solid reality.\n- CAL: Hear, hear.',-1),(113331,39,48668,48705,'00:33:47.868','00:33:49.411','I\'ll have the salmon.',-1),(113332,39,48777,48838,'00:33:52.414','00:33:54.917','You know I don\'t\nlike that, Rose.',-1),(113333,39,48922,48954,'00:33:58.420','00:33:59.755','She knows.',-1),(113334,39,49022,49058,'00:34:02.591','00:34:04.093','Hm. We\'ll both have\nthe lamb.',-1),(113335,39,49060,49112,'00:34:04.176','00:34:06.345','Rare, with very\nlittle mint sauce.',-1),(113336,39,49138,49176,'00:34:07.429','00:34:09.014','Hm. You like lamb,\nright sweet pea?',-1),(113337,39,49240,49292,'00:34:11.684','00:34:13.852','You gonna out her meat for her\ntoo there, Cal? (CHUCKLES)',-1),(113338,39,49354,49422,'00:34:16.438','00:34:19.275','Hey, who thought of\nthe name Titanic?',-1),(113339,39,49442,49466,'00:34:20.109','00:34:21.110','Was it you, Bruce?',-1),(113340,39,49470,49502,'00:34:21.277','00:34:22.611','Yes, actually.',-1),(113341,39,49522,49622,'00:34:23.445','00:34:27.616','I wanted to convey sheer size.\nAnd size means stability...',-1),(113342,39,49634,49706,'00:34:28.117','00:34:31.120','...luxury, and above\nall, strength.',-1),(113343,39,49726,49786,'00:34:31.954','00:34:34.456','Do you know of\nDr. Freud, Mr. Ismay?',-1),(113344,39,49792,49848,'00:34:34.707','00:34:37.001','His ideas about the male\npreoccupation with size',-1),(113345,39,49850,49897,'00:34:37.084','00:34:39.044','might be of particular\ninterest to you.',-1),(113346,39,49931,49963,'00:34:40.462','00:34:41.797','(WHISPERS)\nWhat\'s gotten into you?',-1),(113347,39,49969,50001,'00:34:42.047','00:34:43.382','Excuse me.',-1),(113348,39,50111,50143,'00:34:47.970','00:34:49.305','I do apologize.',-1),(113349,39,50149,50198,'00:34:49.555','00:34:51.599','She\'s a pistol, Cal.\nHope you can handle her.',-1),(113350,39,50219,50254,'00:34:52.474','00:34:53.934','Well, I may have\nto start minding',-1),(113351,39,50256,50309,'00:34:54.018','00:34:56.228','what she reads from\nnow on, won\'t I, Mrs. Brown?',-1),(113352,39,50319,50385,'00:34:56.645','00:34:59.398','Freud? Who is he?\nIs he a passenger?',-1),(113353,39,50680,50724,'00:35:11.702','00:35:13.537','FABRIZIO:\nThe ship is nice, huh?',-1),(113354,39,50748,50772,'00:35:14.538','00:35:15.539','MAN: (IRISH ACCENT)\nYeah. It\'s an Irish ship.',-1),(113355,39,50775,50799,'00:35:15.664','00:35:16.665','FABRIZIO: Is English, no?',-1),(113356,39,50802,50826,'00:35:16.790','00:35:17.791','No, it was built in Ireland.',-1),(113357,39,50829,50873,'00:35:17.875','00:35:19.710','15,000 Irishmen built this ship.',-1),(113358,39,50877,50941,'00:35:19.877','00:35:22.546','Solid as a rock.\nBig Irish hands.',-1),(113359,39,50957,50981,'00:35:23.213','00:35:24.214','That\'s typical.',-1),(113360,39,50984,51057,'00:35:24.340','00:35:27.384','First-class dogs come down\nhere to take a shite.',-1),(113361,39,51075,51124,'00:35:28.135','00:35:30.179','Lets us know where we rank\nin the scheme of things.',-1),(113362,39,51129,51169,'00:35:30.387','00:35:32.056','Like we could forget?',-1),(113363,39,51170,51195,'00:35:32.097','00:35:33.140','(JACK LAUGHS)',-1),(113364,39,51209,51237,'00:35:33.724','00:35:34.892','I\'m Tommy Ryan.',-1),(113365,39,51244,51293,'00:35:35.184','00:35:37.227','Jack Dawson.\nFabrizio.',-1),(113366,39,51343,51380,'00:35:39.313','00:35:40.856','Do you make any money\nwith your drawings?',-1),(113367,39,51645,51685,'00:35:51.909','00:35:53.577','Ah, forget it, boyo.',-1),(113368,39,51687,51741,'00:35:53.661','00:35:55.913','You\'d as like have angels fly out\nof your arse as get next to...',-1),(113369,39,51745,51781,'00:35:56.080','00:35:57.581','...the likes of her.',-1),(113370,39,52054,52087,'00:36:08.926','00:36:10.302','(FABRIZIO LAUGHS)',-1),(113371,39,52133,52170,'00:36:12.221','00:36:13.764','(INDISTINCT EXCHANGE)',-1),(113372,39,52342,52438,'00:36:20.938','00:36:24.942','<i>OLD ROSE: I saw my whole life\nas if I\'d already lived it.</i>',-1),(113373,39,52446,52530,'00:36:25.275','00:36:28.779','<i>An endless parade\nof parties and cotillions...</i>',-1),(113374,39,52538,52586,'00:36:29.113','00:36:31.115','<i>...yachts and polo matches.</i>',-1),(113375,39,52602,52714,'00:36:31.782','00:36:36.453','<i>Always the same narrow people,\nthe same mindless chatter.</i>',-1),(113376,39,52726,52818,'00:36:36.954','00:36:40.791','<i>I felt like I was standing\nat a great precipice...</i>',-1),(113377,39,52834,52935,'00:36:41.458','00:36:45.629','<i>...with no one to pull me back.\nNo one who cared...</i>',-1),(113378,39,52943,52995,'00:36:45.963','00:36:48.132','<i>...or even noticed.</i>',-1),(113379,39,53062,53095,'00:36:50.926','00:36:52.302','(PANTING)',-1),(113380,39,53196,53234,'00:36:56.515','00:36:58.100','(ROSE SOBBING)',-1),(113381,39,53701,53736,'00:37:17.578','00:37:19.037','(RUNNING FOOTSTEPS)',-1),(113382,39,53746,53779,'00:37:19.455','00:37:20.831','(ROSE PANTING)',-1),(113383,39,54195,54232,'00:37:38.140','00:37:39.683','(OCEAN ROARING)',-1),(113384,39,55350,55375,'00:38:26.271','00:38:27.314','(GASPS)',-1),(113385,39,55541,55584,'00:38:34.238','00:38:36.031','(BREATHING HEAVILY)',-1),(113386,39,55648,55672,'00:38:38.700','00:38:39.701','Don\'t do it.',-1),(113387,39,55697,55729,'00:38:40.744','00:38:42.079','Stay back.',-1),(113388,39,55753,55777,'00:38:43.080','00:38:44.081','Don\'t come any closer.',-1),(113389,39,55819,55845,'00:38:45.833','00:38:46.875','Come on.',-1),(113390,39,55846,55880,'00:38:46.917','00:38:48.335','Just give me your hand.\nI\'ll pull you back over.',-1),(113391,39,55885,55914,'00:38:48.544','00:38:49.753','No!\nStay where you are.',-1),(113392,39,55946,55970,'00:38:51.088','00:38:52.089','I mean it.',-1),(113393,39,55986,56026,'00:38:52.756','00:38:54.424','I\'ll let go.',-1),(113394,39,56290,56326,'00:39:05.435','00:39:06.937','No, you won\'t.',-1),(113395,39,56362,56406,'00:39:08.438','00:39:10.274','What do you mean, no I won\'t?',-1),(113396,39,56413,56477,'00:39:10.566','00:39:13.235','Don\'t presume to tell me\nwhat I will and will not do.',-1),(113397,39,56480,56506,'00:39:13.360','00:39:14.444','You don\'t know me.',-1),(113398,39,56510,56562,'00:39:14.611','00:39:16.780','Well, you would\nhave done it already.',-1),(113399,39,56578,56630,'00:39:17.447','00:39:19.616','You\'re distracting me.\nGo away.',-1),(113400,39,56638,56666,'00:39:19.950','00:39:21.118','I can\'t.',-1),(113401,39,56670,56700,'00:39:21.285','00:39:22.536','I\'m involved now.',-1),(113402,39,56722,56802,'00:39:23.453','00:39:26.790','You let go, and I\'m going to\nhave to jump in there after you-',-1),(113403,39,56847,56883,'00:39:28.625','00:39:30.127','Don\'t be absurd.',-1),(113404,39,56891,56943,'00:39:30.460','00:39:32.629','- You\'ll be killed.\n- I\'m a good swimmer.',-1),(113405,39,56951,56995,'00:39:32.963','00:39:34.798','The fall alone will kill you.',-1),(113406,39,57003,57079,'00:39:35.132','00:39:38.302','It would hurt. I\'m not\nsaying it wouldn\'t.',-1),(113407,39,57095,57122,'00:39:38.969','00:39:40.095','Tell you the truth...',-1),(113408,39,57134,57197,'00:39:40.596','00:39:43.223','...I\'m a lot more concerned\nabout that water being so cold-',-1),(113409,39,57367,57398,'00:39:50.314','00:39:51.607','How cold?',-1),(113410,39,57407,57483,'00:39:51.982','00:39:55.152','Freezing.\nMaybe a couple degrees over.',-1),(113411,39,57591,57615,'00:39:59.656','00:40:00.657','You ever, uh...',-1),(113412,39,57623,57665,'00:40:00.991','00:40:02.743','...ever been\nto Wisconsin?',-1),(113413,39,57743,57771,'00:40:05.996','00:40:07.164','What?',-1),(113414,39,57778,57831,'00:40:07.456','00:40:09.666','Well, they have some of\nthe coldest winters around.',-1),(113415,39,57844,57908,'00:40:10.167','00:40:12.836','I grew up there,\nnear Chippewa Falls.',-1),(113416,39,57916,58004,'00:40:13.170','00:40:16.840','I remember when I was a kid, me and\nmy father, we went ice fishing...',-1),(113417,39,58012,58056,'00:40:17.174','00:40:19.009','...out on Lake Wissota.',-1),(113418,39,58070,58100,'00:40:19.593','00:40:20.844','Ice fishing is,\nyou know, where you...',-1),(113419,39,58108,58146,'00:40:21.178','00:40:22.763','I know what ice fishing is!',-1),(113420,39,58176,58204,'00:40:24.014','00:40:25.182','Sorry.',-1),(113421,39,58232,58320,'00:40:26.350','00:40:30.020','You just seem like, you know,\nkind of an indoor girl.',-1),(113422,39,58368,58400,'00:40:32.022','00:40:33.357','Anyway, I...',-1),(113423,39,58432,58472,'00:40:34.691','00:40:36.360','...fell through some thin ice.',-1),(113424,39,58484,58516,'00:40:36.860','00:40:38.195','And I\'m telling you...',-1),(113425,39,58556,58588,'00:40:39.863','00:40:41.198','...water that cold,',-1),(113426,39,58591,58636,'00:40:41.323','00:40:43.200','like right down there...',-1),(113427,39,58655,58735,'00:40:43.992','00:40:47.329','...it hits you like 1000 knives\nstabbing you all over your body.',-1),(113428,39,58771,58803,'00:40:48.830','00:40:50.165','You can\'t breathe.',-1),(113429,39,58828,58936,'00:40:51.208','00:40:55.671','You can\'t think. Least not\nabout anything but the pain.',-1),(113430,39,59009,59087,'00:40:58.715','00:41:01.969','Which is why I\'m not looking forward\nto jumping in there after you.',-1),(113431,39,59113,59137,'00:41:03.053','00:41:04.054','Like I said...',-1),(113432,39,59181,59221,'00:41:05.889','00:41:07.557','...I don\'t have a choice.',-1),(113433,39,59321,59389,'00:41:11.728','00:41:14.564','I guess I\'m kind of hoping you\'ll\ncome back over the rail and...',-1),(113434,39,59391,59425,'00:41:14.648','00:41:16.066','...and get me off\nthe hook here.',-1),(113435,39,59445,59477,'00:41:16.900','00:41:18.235','You\'re crazy.',-1),(113436,39,59509,59561,'00:41:19.569','00:41:21.738','That\'s what\neverybody says but...',-1),(113437,39,59597,59637,'00:41:23.240','00:41:24.908','...with all due\nrespect, miss...',-1),(113438,39,59639,59705,'00:41:24.992','00:41:27.744','...I\'m not the one hanging off\nthe back of a ship here.',-1),(113439,39,59725,59757,'00:41:28.578','00:41:29.913','Come on.',-1),(113440,39,59773,59813,'00:41:30.580','00:41:32.249','Come on, give me your hand.',-1),(113441,39,59835,59866,'00:41:33.166','00:41:34.418','You don\'t want to do this.',-1),(113442,39,60197,60225,'00:41:48.223','00:41:49.391','Phew.',-1),(113443,39,60250,60286,'00:41:50.434','00:41:51.935','I\'m Jack Dawson.',-1),(113444,39,60322,60362,'00:41:53.437','00:41:55.105','Rose DeWitt Bukater.',-1),(113445,39,60369,60410,'00:41:55.397','00:41:57.107','I\'ll have to get you to\nwrite that one down.',-1),(113446,39,60413,60442,'00:41:57.232','00:41:58.442','(ROSE LAUGHS)',-1),(113447,39,60470,60498,'00:41:59.609','00:42:00.777','Come on.',-1),(113448,39,60545,60575,'00:42:02.738','00:42:03.989','(ROSE SCREAMS)',-1),(113449,39,60592,60623,'00:42:04.698','00:42:05.991','(JACK GRUNTING)',-1),(113450,39,60625,60649,'00:42:06.074','00:42:07.075','(SCREAMING)\nI got you.',-1),(113451,39,60661,60685,'00:42:07.576','00:42:08.577','Come on.',-1),(113452,39,60694,60726,'00:42:08.952','00:42:10.287','Come on.',-1),(113453,39,60794,60822,'00:42:13.123','00:42:14.291','(SCREAMING)',-1),(113454,39,60834,60866,'00:42:14.750','00:42:16.084','Help, please!',-1),(113455,39,60873,60911,'00:42:16.376','00:42:17.961','(SCREAMING) Help!',-1),(113456,39,60946,60971,'00:42:19.421','00:42:20.464','Please, help me!\nListen. Listen to me.',-1),(113457,39,60974,61011,'00:42:20.589','00:42:22.132','Listen. Listen to me.',-1),(113458,39,61015,61055,'00:42:22.299','00:42:23.967','I\'ve got you.\nI won\'t let go.',-1),(113459,39,61062,61110,'00:42:24.259','00:42:26.261','Now pull yourself up.\nCome on!',-1),(113460,39,61115,61167,'00:42:26.470','00:42:28.638','(BOTH GRUNTING)',-1),(113461,39,61183,61207,'00:42:29.306','00:42:30.307','Come on.',-1),(113462,39,61213,61238,'00:42:30.557','00:42:31.600','That\'s right.',-1),(113463,39,61251,61277,'00:42:32.142','00:42:33.226','You can do it.',-1),(113464,39,61367,61394,'00:42:36.980','00:42:38.106','(ROSE GRUNTS)',-1),(113465,39,61395,61427,'00:42:38.148','00:42:39.483','I got you.',-1),(113466,39,61437,61467,'00:42:39.900','00:42:41.151','(BOTH GRUNTING)',-1),(113467,39,61563,61599,'00:42:45.155','00:42:46.656','What\'s all this?',-1),(113468,39,61662,61706,'00:42:49.284','00:42:51.119','(ROSE GASPING)',-1),(113469,39,61739,61767,'00:42:52.496','00:42:53.663','You stand back and...',-1),(113470,39,61775,61809,'00:42:53.997','00:42:55.415','...don\'t move an inch!',-1),(113471,39,61866,61893,'00:42:57.751','00:42:58.877','Fetch the Master at Arms.',-1),(113472,39,61956,61994,'00:43:01.505','00:43:03.090','This is completely unacceptable!',-1),(113473,39,61996,62064,'00:43:03.173','00:43:06.009','What made you think that you could\nput your hands on my fianoe?!',-1),(113474,39,62104,62132,'00:43:07.677','00:43:08.845','Look at me, you filth!',-1),(113475,39,62140,62164,'00:43:09.179','00:43:10.180','Cal.',-1),(113476,39,62168,62195,'00:43:10.347','00:43:11.473','What do you think\nyou were doing?',-1),(113477,39,62200,62260,'00:43:11.681','00:43:14.184','Cal, stop.\nIt was an accident.',-1),(113478,39,62276,62316,'00:43:14.851','00:43:16.520','An accident?',-1),(113479,39,62324,62356,'00:43:16.853','00:43:18.188','It was.',-1),(113480,39,62380,62408,'00:43:19.189','00:43:20.357','Stupid, really.',-1),(113481,39,62428,62488,'00:43:21.191','00:43:23.693','I was leaning over\nand I slipped.',-1),(113482,39,62548,62632,'00:43:26.196','00:43:29.699','I was leaning far over\nto see the, uh...',-1),(113483,39,62640,62696,'00:43:30.033','00:43:32.369','...uh, uh, the uh...',-1),(113484,39,62716,62772,'00:43:33.203','00:43:35.539','- Propellers?\n- Propellers, and I slipped.',-1),(113485,39,62780,62845,'00:43:35.872','00:43:38.542','And I would have gone overboard\nbut Mr-Dawson here...',-1),(113486,39,62853,62929,'00:43:38.875','00:43:42.045','...saved me\n- And almost went over himself.',-1),(113487,39,62951,62977,'00:43:42.963','00:43:44.047','You wanted to see the... She\nwanted to see the propellers.',-1),(113488,39,62985,63061,'00:43:44.381','00:43:47.551','Like I said, women and\nmachinery do not mix.',-1),(113489,39,63081,63129,'00:43:48.385','00:43:50.387','Was that the way of it?',-1),(113490,39,63189,63237,'00:43:52.889','00:43:54.891','Yeah. Yeah, that\nwas pretty much it.',-1),(113491,39,63245,63281,'00:43:55.225','00:43:56.726','Well, the boy\'s a hero then.',-1),(113492,39,63297,63327,'00:43:57.394','00:43:58.645','Good for you, son.\nWell done.',-1),(113493,39,63333,63381,'00:43:58.895','00:44:00.897','So, it\'s all\'s well and back\nto our brandy, eh?',-1),(113494,39,63445,63525,'00:44:03.567','00:44:06.903','Look at you. You must be\nfreezing. Let\'s get you inside-',-1),(113495,39,63541,63597,'00:44:07.571','00:44:09.906','Perhaps a little something\nfor the boy?',-1),(113496,39,63649,63681,'00:44:12.075','00:44:13.410','Of course.',-1),(113497,39,63688,63773,'00:44:13.702','00:44:17.247','Mr. Lovejoy,\nI think a 20 should do it.',-1),(113498,39,63789,63854,'00:44:17.914','00:44:20.584','ROSE: Is that the going rate for\nsaving the woman you love?',-1),(113499,39,63894,63938,'00:44:22.252','00:44:24.087','CAL: Rose is displeased.',-1),(113500,39,63950,63990,'00:44:24.588','00:44:26.256','What to do?',-1),(113501,39,64001,64025,'00:44:26.715','00:44:27.716','I know.',-1),(113502,39,64078,64166,'00:44:29.926','00:44:33.597','Perhaps you could join us for\ndinner tomorrow evening...',-1),(113503,39,64174,64210,'00:44:33.930','00:44:35.432','...to regale our group...',-1),(113504,39,64218,64270,'00:44:35.765','00:44:37.934','...with your heroic tale.',-1),(113505,39,64326,64378,'00:44:40.270','00:44:42.439','JACK: Sure.\nCount me in.',-1),(113506,39,64386,64442,'00:44:42.772','00:44:45.108','Good.\nIt\'s settled then.',-1),(113507,39,64466,64498,'00:44:46.109','00:44:47.444','This should be interesting.',-1),(113508,39,64631,64657,'00:44:52.991','00:44:54.075','(WHISTLES)',-1),(113509,39,64722,64786,'00:44:56.786','00:44:59.456','Can I bum a smoke?',-1),(113510,39,64999,65027,'00:45:08.298','00:45:09.466','You\'ll want to tie those.',-1),(113511,39,65091,65117,'00:45:12.135','00:45:13.220','It\'s interesting...',-1),(113512,39,65131,65173,'00:45:13.803','00:45:15.555','...the young lady slipped\nso suddenly...',-1),(113513,39,65178,65259,'00:45:15.764','00:45:19.142','...and you still had time to\nremove your jacket and your shoes...',-1),(113514,39,65433,65459,'00:45:26.399','00:45:27.484','(TUNE PLAYS ON MUSIC BOX)',-1),(113515,39,65461,65487,'00:45:27.567','00:45:28.652','(KNOCKING)',-1),(113516,39,65647,65695,'00:45:35.325','00:45:37.327','I know you\'ve been melancholy.',-1),(113517,39,65719,65767,'00:45:38.328','00:45:40.330','I don\'t pretend to know why.',-1),(113518,39,65831,65884,'00:45:42.999','00:45:45.168','I intended to save this...',-1),(113519,39,65896,66008,'00:45:45.669','00:45:50.340','...until the engagement\ngala next week...',-1),(113520,39,66040,66096,'00:45:51.675','00:45:54.010','...but, I thought...',-1),(113521,39,66104,66136,'00:45:54.344','00:45:55.679','...tonight.',-1),(113522,39,66171,66200,'00:45:57.138','00:45:58.348','- Good gracious.\n(CHUCKLES)',-1),(113523,39,66222,66288,'00:45:59.266','00:46:02.018','Perhaps as a reminder\nof my feelings for you.',-1),(113524,39,66308,66339,'00:46:02.852','00:46:04.145','- Is it a...\n- Diamond. Yes. (LAUGHS)',-1),(113525,39,66400,66476,'00:46:06.690','00:46:09.859','56 carats to be exact.',-1),(113526,39,66524,66580,'00:46:11.861','00:46:14.197','It was worn by Louis XVI.',-1),(113527,39,66600,66656,'00:46:15.031','00:46:17.367','And they called\nit <i>Le Coeur de la Mer</i>.',-1),(113528,39,66668,66712,'00:46:17.867','00:46:19.703','- The Heart of the Ocean.\n- The Heart of the Ocean.Yes. (LAUGHS)',-1),(113529,39,66869,66909,'00:46:26.209','00:46:27.877','It\'s overwhelming.',-1),(113530,39,66920,66960,'00:46:28.336','00:46:30.005','Well, it\'s for royalty.',-1),(113531,39,66989,67041,'00:46:31.214','00:46:33.383','We are royalty, Rose.',-1),(113532,39,67137,67193,'00:46:37.387','00:46:39.723','You know, there\'s\nnothing I couldn\'t give you.',-1),(113533,39,67213,67261,'00:46:40.557','00:46:42.559','There\'s nothing I\'d deny you...',-1),(113534,39,67277,67329,'00:46:43.226','00:46:45.395','...if you would not deny me.',-1),(113535,39,67429,67485,'00:46:49.566','00:46:51.901','Open your heart to me, Rose.',-1),(113536,39,67858,67951,'00:47:07.417','00:47:11.296','JACK: VVell, I\'ve been on my own since\nI was 15, since my folks died.',-1),(113537,39,67978,68074,'00:47:12.422','00:47:16.426','And I had no brothers or sisters or close\nkin in that part of the country...',-1),(113538,39,68085,68165,'00:47:16.885','00:47:20.221','...so I lit on out of there and\nI haven\'t been back since.',-1),(113539,39,68170,68221,'00:47:20.430','00:47:22.557','You could just call me a\nturnbleweed blowing in the wind.',-1),(113540,39,68222,68253,'00:47:22.599','00:47:23.892','(BOTH CHUCKLE)',-1),(113541,39,68282,68382,'00:47:25.101','00:47:29.272','Well, Rose, we\'ve walked about a\nmile around this boat deck and...',-1),(113542,39,68389,68461,'00:47:29.564','00:47:32.567','...chewed over how great the\nweather\'s been and how I grew up...',-1),(113543,39,68466,68554,'00:47:32.776','00:47:36.446','...but I reckon that\'s not why\nyou came to talk to me, is it?',-1),(113544,39,68602,68650,'00:47:38.448','00:47:40.450','(SIGHS) - Mr. Dawson, I...\n- Jack.',-1),(113545,39,68684,68708,'00:47:41.868','00:47:42.869','Jack.',-1),(113546,39,68718,68796,'00:47:43.286','00:47:46.539','I want to thank you\nfor what you did.',-1),(113547,39,68798,68911,'00:47:46.623','00:47:51.294','Not just for pulling me back,\nbut for your discretion.',-1),(113548,39,68919,68951,'00:47:51.628','00:47:52.962','You\'re welcome.',-1),(113549,39,68963,68987,'00:47:53.463','00:47:54.464','Look.',-1),(113550,39,69013,69077,'00:47:55.548','00:47:58.218','I know what you\nmust be thinking.',-1),(113551,39,69083,69122,'00:47:58.468','00:48:00.095','Poor little rich girl.',-1),(113552,39,69126,69177,'00:48:00.261','00:48:02.389','What does she know about misery?',-1),(113553,39,69183,69207,'00:48:02.639','00:48:03.640','No.',-1),(113554,39,69231,69283,'00:48:04.641','00:48:06.810','No, that\'s not\nwhat I was thinking.',-1),(113555,39,69291,69321,'00:48:07.143','00:48:08.395','What I was thinking was...',-1),(113556,39,69325,69407,'00:48:08.561','00:48:11.981','...what could have happened to this girl\nto make her think she had no way out?',-1),(113557,39,69471,69495,'00:48:14.651','00:48:15.652','Well I...',-1),(113558,39,69513,69610,'00:48:16.403','00:48:20.448','It was everything.\nIt was my whole world and...',-1),(113559,39,69615,69641,'00:48:20.657','00:48:21.741','...all the people in it.',-1),(113560,39,69657,69733,'00:48:22.409','00:48:25.578','And the inertia of my life,\nplunging ahead and me...',-1),(113561,39,69738,69782,'00:48:25.787','00:48:27.622','...powerless to stop it.',-1),(113562,39,69787,69835,'00:48:27.831','00:48:29.833','God, look at that thing.',-1),(113563,39,69843,69895,'00:48:30.125','00:48:32.293','You would have gone\nstraight to the bottom.',-1),(113564,39,69936,69996,'00:48:34.003','00:48:36.506','500 invitations have gone out.',-1),(113565,39,70004,70068,'00:48:36.840','00:48:39.509','All of Philadelphia\nsociety will be there.',-1),(113566,39,70075,70123,'00:48:39.801','00:48:41.803','And all the while I feel I\'m...',-1),(113567,39,70132,70178,'00:48:42.178','00:48:44.097','...standing in the middle\nof a crowded room...',-1),(113568,39,70180,70220,'00:48:44.180','00:48:45.849','...screaming at the\ntop of my lungs...',-1),(113569,39,70223,70252,'00:48:45.974','00:48:47.183','...and no one\neven looks up.',-1),(113570,39,70296,70320,'00:48:49.018','00:48:50.019','Do you love him?',-1),(113571,39,70352,70376,'00:48:51.354','00:48:52.355','Pardon me?',-1),(113572,39,70384,70419,'00:48:52.689','00:48:54.149','Do you love him?',-1),(113573,39,70432,70504,'00:48:54.691','00:48:57.694','You\'re being very rude. You\nshouldn\'t be asking me this.',-1),(113574,39,70515,70576,'00:48:58.153','00:49:00.697','Well, it\'s a simple question.\nDo you love the guy or not?',-1),(113575,39,70604,70632,'00:49:01.865','00:49:03.032','(SCOFFS)',-1),(113576,39,70635,70684,'00:49:03.158','00:49:05.201','This is not\na suitable conversation.',-1),(113577,39,70691,70720,'00:49:05.493','00:49:06.703','Why can\'t you just\nanswer the question?',-1),(113578,39,70723,70761,'00:49:06.828','00:49:08.413','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113579,39,70784,70831,'00:49:09.372','00:49:11.332','This is absurd.',-1),(113580,39,70846,70873,'00:49:11.958','00:49:13.042','You don\'t know me\nand I don\'t know you...',-1),(113581,39,70880,70952,'00:49:13.334','00:49:16.337','...and we are not having this\nconversation at all. You are rude...',-1),(113582,39,70957,71037,'00:49:16.546','00:49:19.883','...and uncouth and presumptuous\nand I am leaving now...',-1),(113583,39,71045,71113,'00:49:20.216','00:49:23.052','...Jack. Mr. Dawson.\nIt\'s been a pleasure.',-1),(113584,39,71117,71159,'00:49:23.219','00:49:24.971','I sought you out to thank you\nand now I have thanked you.',-1),(113585,39,71164,71212,'00:49:25.180','00:49:27.182','And you\'ve insulted me.',-1),(113586,39,71217,71256,'00:49:27.390','00:49:29.017','Well, you deserved it.',-1),(113587,39,71261,71289,'00:49:29.225','00:49:30.393','- Right.\n- Right.',-1),(113588,39,71361,71400,'00:49:33.396','00:49:35.023','I thought you were leaving.',-1),(113589,39,71405,71437,'00:49:35.231','00:49:36.566','I am.',-1),(113590,39,71489,71521,'00:49:38.735','00:49:40.069','You are so annoying.',-1),(113591,39,71524,71553,'00:49:40.195','00:49:41.404','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113592,39,71557,71581,'00:49:41.571','00:49:42.572','Wait.',-1),(113593,39,71587,71689,'00:49:42.822','00:49:47.076','I don\'t have to leave. This is\nmy part of the ship. You leave.',-1),(113594,39,71697,71769,'00:49:47.410','00:49:50.413','Oh-ho-ho-ho-well, well, well.\nNow who\'s being rude?',-1),(113595,39,71813,71844,'00:49:52.248','00:49:53.500','(ROSE LAUGHS)',-1),(113596,39,71862,71930,'00:49:54.250','00:49:57.086','What is this stupid thing\nyou\'re carrying around?',-1),(113597,39,71958,72014,'00:49:58.254','00:50:00.590','So, what are you,\nan artist or something?',-1),(113598,39,72055,72079,'00:50:02.300','00:50:03.301','Well...',-1),(113599,39,72114,72158,'00:50:04.761','00:50:06.596','These are rather good.',-1),(113600,39,72238,72314,'00:50:09.933','00:50:13.102','They\'re very good, actually.',-1),(113601,39,72490,72530,'00:50:20.443','00:50:22.111','Jack, this is exquisite work.',-1),(113602,39,72538,72602,'00:50:22.445','00:50:25.114','Ah, they didn\'t think too\nmuch of them in old Paree.',-1),(113603,39,72606,72638,'00:50:25.281','00:50:26.616','Paris?',-1),(113604,39,72669,72733,'00:50:27.909','00:50:30.578','You do get around for a p...',-1),(113605,39,72774,72866,'00:50:32.288','00:50:36.084','Well, a... a\nperson of limited means.',-1),(113606,39,72871,72919,'00:50:36.292','00:50:38.294','Go on. A poor guy.\nYou can say it.',-1),(113607,39,72999,73039,'00:50:41.631','00:50:43.299','Well, well, well.',-1),(113608,39,73143,73182,'00:50:47.637','00:50:49.264','And these were drawn from life?',-1),(113609,39,73267,73315,'00:50:52.809','00:50:54.811','Well, that\'s one of the\ngood things about Paris.',-1),(113610,39,73327,73361,'00:50:55.311','00:50:56.729','Lots of girls are willing\nto take their clothes off.',-1),(113611,39,73390,73419,'00:50:57.939','00:50:59.148','(ROSE LAUGHS)',-1),(113612,39,73518,73551,'00:51:03.278','00:51:04.654','You liked this woman.',-1),(113613,39,73571,73623,'00:51:05.488','00:51:07.657','You used her several times.',-1),(113614,39,73651,73675,'00:51:08.825','00:51:09.826','Well.',-1),(113615,39,73693,73739,'00:51:10.577','00:51:12.495','She had beautiful\nhands, you see?',-1),(113616,39,73799,73855,'00:51:14.998','00:51:17.333','I think you must have\nhad a love affair with her.',-1),(113617,39,73868,73916,'00:51:17.834','00:51:19.836','No, no, no.\nJust with her hands.',-1),(113618,39,73924,73988,'00:51:20.169','00:51:22.839','She was a\none-legged prostitute.',-1),(113619,39,74015,74039,'00:51:23.965','00:51:24.966','See?',-1),(113620,39,74096,74124,'00:51:27.343','00:51:28.511','Oh.',-1),(113621,39,74144,74176,'00:51:29.345','00:51:30.680','(BOTH LAUGH)',-1),(113622,39,74196,74244,'00:51:31.514','00:51:33.516','She had a good\nsense of humor though.',-1),(113623,39,74304,74328,'00:51:36.019','00:51:37.020','Oh, and this lady...',-1),(113624,39,74372,74444,'00:51:38.855','00:51:41.858','She used to sit at\nthis bar every night...',-1),(113625,39,74448,74488,'00:51:42.025','00:51:43.693','...wearing every piece\nof jewelry she owned...',-1),(113626,39,74494,74550,'00:51:43.943','00:51:46.279','...just waiting for\nher long, lost love.',-1),(113627,39,74568,74624,'00:51:47.030','00:51:49.365','We called her Madame Bijoux.',-1),(113628,39,74636,74680,'00:51:49.866','00:51:51.701','See, her clothes\nare all moth-eaten.',-1),(113629,39,74720,74788,'00:51:53.369','00:51:56.205','Well, you have a gift, Jack.',-1),(113630,39,74796,74828,'00:51:56.539','00:51:57.874','You do.',-1),(113631,39,74836,74873,'00:51:58.207','00:51:59.709','You see people.',-1),(113632,39,74880,74917,'00:52:00.001','00:52:01.544','I see you.',-1),(113633,39,74975,75007,'00:52:03.963','00:52:05.298','And?',-1),(113634,39,75040,75081,'00:52:06.674','00:52:08.384','You wouldn\'t have jumped.',-1),(113635,39,75185,75272,'00:52:12.722','00:52:16.351','But the purpose of university\nis to find a suitable husband.',-1),(113636,39,75277,75317,'00:52:16.559','00:52:18.227','Rose has already done that.',-1),(113637,39,75325,75393,'00:52:18.561','00:52:21.397','Look, here comes that\nvulgar Brown woman.',-1),(113638,39,75401,75465,'00:52:21.731','00:52:24.400','Quickly, get up before\nshe sits with us.',-1),(113639,39,75489,75552,'00:52:25.401','00:52:28.029','Hello, girls. I was hoping\nI\'d catch you at tea.',-1),(113640,39,75557,75593,'00:52:28.237','00:52:29.739','We\'re awfully sorry,\nyou missed it.',-1),(113641,39,75597,75679,'00:52:29.906','00:52:33.326','The Countess and I were just off\nto take the air on the boat deck.',-1),(113642,39,75684,75757,'00:52:33.534','00:52:36.579','What a lovely idea. I need\nto catch up on my gossip.',-1),(113643,39,75841,75870,'00:52:40.083','00:52:41.250','Countess.',-1),(113644,39,75906,75974,'00:52:42.752','00:52:45.588','So, you\'ve not yet lit the\nlast four boilers?',-1),(113645,39,75986,76021,'00:52:46.089','00:52:47.548','No, I don\'t see the need.',-1),(113646,39,76041,76066,'00:52:48.383','00:52:49.425','We are making excellent time.',-1),(113647,39,76102,76154,'00:52:50.927','00:52:53.096','The press knows\nthe size of Titanic.',-1),(113648,39,76156,76206,'00:52:53.179','00:52:55.264','Now, I want them\nto marvel at her speed.',-1),(113649,39,76213,76266,'00:52:55.556','00:52:57.767','We must give them\nsomething new to print.',-1),(113650,39,76314,76362,'00:52:59.769','00:53:01.771','This maiden voyage\nof Titanic must...',-1),(113651,39,76374,76412,'00:53:02.271','00:53:03.856','...make headlines.',-1),(113652,39,76418,76514,'00:53:04.107','00:53:08.111','Mr.Ismay, I would prefer\nnot to push the engines...',-1),(113653,39,76522,76582,'00:53:08.444','00:53:10.947','...until they\'ve been\nproperly run in.',-1),(113654,39,76614,76645,'00:53:12.281','00:53:13.574','Of course I\'m just a passenger.',-1),(113655,39,76646,76704,'00:53:13.616','00:53:16.035','I leave it to your good offioes\nto decide what\'s best.',-1),(113656,39,76718,76782,'00:53:16.619','00:53:19.288','But what a glorious end\nto your final crossing...',-1),(113657,39,76786,76824,'00:53:19.455','00:53:21.040','...if we were to get into New\nYork on Tuesday night...',-1),(113658,39,76829,76891,'00:53:21.249','00:53:23.793','...and surprise them all.\nMake the morning papers.',-1),(113659,39,76910,76958,'00:53:24.585','00:53:26.587','Retire with a bang, eh, E.J.?',-1),(113660,39,77047,77079,'00:53:30.299','00:53:31.634','Good man.',-1),(113661,39,77113,77173,'00:53:33.052','00:53:35.555','After that, I worked\non a squid boat in Monterey...',-1),(113662,39,77183,77243,'00:53:35.972','00:53:38.474','...then I went to\nLos Angeles to the...',-1),(113663,39,77249,77325,'00:53:38.725','00:53:41.894','...Santa Monica pier and did\nportraits for 10 cents each.',-1),(113664,39,77343,77387,'00:53:42.645','00:53:44.480','Why can\'t I be like you?',-1),(113665,39,77395,77479,'00:53:44.814','00:53:48.317','Just head out for the horizon\nwhenever I feel like it.',-1),(113666,39,77527,77593,'00:53:50.319','00:53:53.072','Say we\'ll go there\nsometime, to that pier...',-1),(113667,39,77599,77651,'00:53:53.322','00:53:55.491','...only if we\njust talk about it.',-1),(113668,39,77659,77727,'00:53:55.825','00:53:58.661','No, we\'ll do it.\nWe\'ll drink cheap beer.',-1),(113669,39,77735,77779,'00:53:58.995','00:54:00.830','Ride on the roller coaster\ntill we throw up.',-1),(113670,39,77780,77805,'00:54:00.872','00:54:01.914','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113671,39,77807,77884,'00:54:01.998','00:54:05.168','We\'ll ride horses\non the beach, in the surf.',-1),(113672,39,77892,77988,'00:54:05.501','00:54:09.505','But you have to do it like a real\ncowboy. No sidesaddle stuff.',-1),(113673,39,78000,78063,'00:54:10.006','00:54:12.633','You mean with one\nleg on each side?',-1),(113674,39,78064,78088,'00:54:12.675','00:54:13.676','Yeah.',-1),(113675,39,78096,78120,'00:54:14.010','00:54:15.011','Can you show me?',-1),(113676,39,78126,78170,'00:54:15.261','00:54:17.096','Sure, if you like.',-1),(113677,39,78208,78248,'00:54:18.681','00:54:20.349','Teach me to ride like a man.',-1),(113678,39,78254,78286,'00:54:20.600','00:54:21.934','(WESTERN U.S. ACCENT)\nChew tobacco like a man.',-1),(113679,39,78324,78376,'00:54:23.519','00:54:25.688','(WESTERN U.S. ACCENT)\nAnd spit like a man.',-1),(113680,39,78384,78426,'00:54:26.022','00:54:27.774','You didn\'t learn\nin finishing school?',-1),(113681,39,78432,78460,'00:54:28.024','00:54:29.192','No. (LAUGHS)',-1),(113682,39,78468,78512,'00:54:29.525','00:54:31.360','Come on, I\'ll show you.',-1),(113683,39,78536,78560,'00:54:32.361','00:54:33.362','I\'ll show you how.',-1),(113684,39,78566,78636,'00:54:33.613','00:54:36.532','Jack! No, Jack, no. Wait.',-1),(113685,39,78668,78716,'00:54:37.867','00:54:39.869','I couldn\'t possibly, Jack.',-1),(113686,39,78724,78764,'00:54:40.203','00:54:41.871','Watch closely.',-1),(113687,39,78765,78798,'00:54:41.913','00:54:43.289','(HAWKING PHLEGM)',-1),(113688,39,78804,78848,'00:54:43.539','00:54:45.374','That\'s disgusting.',-1),(113689,39,78852,78877,'00:54:45.541','00:54:46.542','Your turn.',-1),(113690,39,78883,78912,'00:54:46.793','00:54:48.002','(ROSE SNIFFS)',-1),(113691,39,78933,79005,'00:54:48.878','00:54:51.881','That was pitiful. You really\nhave to hawk it back.',-1),(113692,39,79013,79085,'00:54:52.215','00:54:55.218','Get some leverage. Use your\narms. (SNORTS) Arc your neck.',-1),(113693,39,79086,79115,'00:54:55.259','00:54:56.469','(HAWKING)\n(ROSE CLEARS THROAT)',-1),(113694,39,79117,79165,'00:54:56.552','00:54:58.554','<i>You see the range on that thing?\nMm-hm.</i>',-1),(113695,39,79185,79213,'00:54:59.388','00:55:00.556','JACK: Okay, go.',-1),(113696,39,79297,79417,'00:55:04.060','00:55:09.065','That was better. You have to work\non it. Really try to hawk it up.',-1),(113697,39,79418,79453,'00:55:09.106','00:55:10.566','(SNORTS)',-1),(113698,39,79562,79591,'00:55:15.112','00:55:16.322','(JACK GULPS)',-1),(113699,39,79607,79639,'00:55:16.989','00:55:18.324','ROSE: Mother.',-1),(113700,39,79769,79825,'00:55:23.746','00:55:26.082','May I introduce Jack Dawson?',-1),(113701,39,79854,79898,'00:55:27.250','00:55:29.085','Charmed, I\'m sure.',-1),(113702,39,80010,80066,'00:55:33.756','00:55:36.092','OLD ROSE: The others\nwere gracious and curious',-1),(113703,39,80067,80122,'00:55:36.133','00:55:38.427','<i>about the man\nwho\'d saved my life.</i>',-1),(113704,39,80150,80222,'00:55:39.595','00:55:42.598','<i>But my mother\nlooked at him like an insect.</i>',-1),(113705,39,80234,80330,'00:55:43.099','00:55:47.103','<i>A dangerous insect which\nmust be squashed quickly.</i>',-1),(113706,39,80338,80430,'00:55:47.436','00:55:51.274','Sounds like you\'re a good man to\nhave around in a sticky spot.',-1),(113707,39,80454,80499,'00:55:52.275','00:55:54.151','(FANFARE PLAYING)',-1),(113708,39,80502,80590,'00:55:54.277','00:55:57.947','Why do they always insist on announcing\ndinner like a damn cavalry charge?',-1),(113709,39,80592,80620,'00:55:58.030','00:55:59.198','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113710,39,80622,80662,'00:55:59.282','00:56:00.950','Shall we go dress, Mother?',-1),(113711,39,80686,80730,'00:56:01.951','00:56:03.786','See you at dinner, Jack.',-1),(113712,39,80778,80802,'00:56:05.788','00:56:06.789','Uh, son?',-1),(113713,39,80814,80842,'00:56:07.290','00:56:08.457','Son!',-1),(113714,39,80854,80911,'00:56:08.958','00:56:11.294','Do you have any idea\nwhat you\'re doing?',-1),(113715,39,80935,80959,'00:56:12.295','00:56:13.296','Not really.',-1),(113716,39,80967,81027,'00:56:13.629','00:56:16.132','You\'re about to go\ninto the snake pit.',-1),(113717,39,81085,81125,'00:56:18.551','00:56:20.219','What are you going to wear?',-1),(113718,39,81199,81247,'00:56:23.306','00:56:25.308','(SCOFFS) I figured. Come on.',-1),(113719,39,81311,81415,'00:56:27.977','00:56:32.315','I was right. You and my son\nare just about the same size.',-1),(113720,39,81423,81463,'00:56:32.648','00:56:34.317','Pretty close.',-1),(113721,39,81515,81548,'00:56:36.485','00:56:37.862','(WHISTLES)',-1),(113722,39,81551,81607,'00:56:37.987','00:56:40.323','You shine up like a new penny.',-1),(113723,39,81616,81643,'00:56:40.698','00:56:41.824','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113724,39,81892,81932,'00:56:52.168','00:56:53.836','Good evening, sir.',-1),(113725,39,82093,82156,'00:57:00.551','00:57:03.179','<i>(ORCHESTRA PLAYS\nTHE BLUE DANUBE)</i>',-1),(113726,39,83475,83541,'00:57:58.150','00:58:00.903','CAL: Thousands of tons of Hockley\nsteel are in this ship.',-1),(113727,39,83547,83597,'00:58:01.153','00:58:03.239','- RUTH: Which part?\n- CAL: All the right ones.',-1),(113728,39,83603,83679,'00:58:03.489','00:58:06.659','Then you\'re accountable if there\'s\na problem. Where\'s Rose?',-1),(113729,39,83685,83717,'00:58:06.909','00:58:08.244','She\'ll be along.',-1),(113730,39,83725,83773,'00:58:08.577','00:58:10.579','There is the Countess.',-1),(113731,39,84466,84550,'00:58:39.442','00:58:42.945','I saw that in a nickelodeon\nand always wanted to do it.',-1),(113732,39,84558,84588,'00:58:43.279','00:58:44.530','(BOTH LAUGH)',-1),(113733,39,84897,84925,'00:58:57.376','00:58:58.544','Darling...',-1),(113734,39,84939,84991,'00:58:59.128','00:59:01.297','...surely you remember\nMr. Dawson.',-1),(113735,39,85059,85145,'00:59:04.133','00:59:07.720','(LAUGHS) It\'s amazing. You could\nalmost pass for a gentleman.',-1),(113736,39,85175,85203,'00:59:08.971','00:59:10.139','Almost.',-1),(113737,39,85211,85245,'00:59:10.473','00:59:11.891','This is extraordinary.',-1),(113738,39,85595,85635,'00:59:26.489','00:59:28.157','This is a remarkable voyage.',-1),(113739,39,85641,85675,'00:59:28.407','00:59:29.825','- Mad.\n- Completely lunatic.',-1),(113740,39,85717,85765,'00:59:31.577','00:59:33.579','There\'s the Countess of Rothes.',-1),(113741,39,85815,85888,'00:59:35.664','00:59:38.667','That\'s John Jacob Astor...',-1),(113742,39,85904,85944,'00:59:39.335','00:59:41.003','...the richest man on board.',-1),(113743,39,85950,86044,'00:59:41.253','00:59:45.174','His little wifey, Madeleine, is rny\nage and in a delicate condition.',-1),(113744,39,86064,86112,'00:59:46.008','00:59:48.010','See how she tries to hide it.',-1),(113745,39,86118,86152,'00:59:48.260','00:59:49.678','- Quite the scandal.\n- Hmm.',-1),(113746,39,86164,86272,'00:59:50.179','00:59:54.683','Benjamin Guggenheim and his mistress,\nMadame Aubert. Mrs-Guggenheim...',-1),(113747,39,86278,86366,'00:59:54.934','00:59:58.604','...is at home with the children,\nof course- And over here...',-1),(113748,39,86372,86412,'00:59:58.854','01:00:00.523','...Sir Cosmo and Lucile,\nLady Duff-Gordon.',-1),(113749,39,86418,86498,'01:00:00.773','01:00:04.110','She designs naughty lingerie,\namong her many talents.',-1),(113750,39,86504,86560,'01:00:04.360','01:00:06.695','Very popular with the royals.',-1),(113751,39,86584,86628,'01:00:07.696','01:00:09.532','Congratulations.\nShe\'s splendid.',-1),(113752,39,86636,86672,'01:00:09.865','01:00:11.367','Why, thank you.',-1),(113753,39,86692,86726,'01:00:12.201','01:00:13.619','Escort a lady to dinner?',-1),(113754,39,86732,86768,'01:00:13.869','01:00:15.371','Certainly.\n(LAUGHS)',-1),(113755,39,86772,86797,'01:00:15.538','01:00:16.580','(RUTH LAUGHS)',-1),(113756,39,86800,86848,'01:00:16.705','01:00:18.707','Sweet pea, sweet pea.',-1),(113757,39,86869,86903,'01:00:19.542','01:00:20.960','Ain\'t nothing to it.',-1),(113758,39,86921,87029,'01:00:21.710','01:00:26.215','They love money. Pretend like you own\na gold mine and you\'re in the club.',-1),(113759,39,87081,87121,'01:00:28.384','01:00:30.052','Hey, Astor.',-1),(113760,39,87141,87205,'01:00:30.886','01:00:33.556','Hello, Molly.\nNice to see you.',-1),(113761,39,87211,87281,'01:00:33.806','01:00:36.725','J.J., Madeleine, I\'d like\nyou to meet Jack Dawson.',-1),(113762,39,87315,87347,'01:00:38.144','01:00:39.478','Well, Jack...',-1),(113763,39,87357,87397,'01:00:39.895','01:00:41.564','...are you of the\nBoston Dawsons?',-1),(113764,39,87421,87483,'01:00:42.565','01:00:45.151','No, the Chippewa Falls\nDawsons, actually.',-1),(113765,39,87489,87521,'01:00:45.401','01:00:46.735','Oh, yes.',-1),(113766,39,87569,87665,'01:00:48.737','01:00:52.741','<i>OLD ROSE: He must have been\nnervous, but he never faltered.</i>',-1),(113767,39,87685,87737,'01:00:53.576','01:00:55.744','<i>They assumed he was one of them.</i>',-1),(113768,39,87745,87821,'01:00:56.078','01:00:59.248','<i>Heir to a railroad\nfortune, perhaps.</i>',-1),(113769,39,87829,87930,'01:00:59.582','01:01:03.752','<i>New money, obviously, but\nstill a member of the club.</i>',-1),(113770,39,87946,88028,'01:01:04.420','01:01:07.840','<i>Mother, of course,\ncould always be counted upon.</i>',-1),(113771,39,88042,88160,'01:01:08.424','01:01:13.345','Tell us of the accommodations in steerage,\nMr. Dawson. I hear they\'re quite good.',-1),(113772,39,88196,88272,'01:01:14.847','01:01:18.017','The best I\'ve seen, ma\'am.\nHardly any rats.',-1),(113773,39,88278,88312,'01:01:18.267','01:01:19.685','(LAUGHTER)',-1),(113774,39,88346,88414,'01:01:21.103','01:01:23.939','Mr. Dawson is joining us\nfrom third class.',-1),(113775,39,88420,88476,'01:01:24.190','01:01:26.525','He was of help to\nmy fiance last night.',-1),(113776,39,88482,88550,'01:01:26.775','01:01:29.612','It happens Mr. Dawson\nis quite a fine artist.',-1),(113777,39,88558,88618,'01:01:29.945','01:01:32.448','He showed me\nsome of his work today.',-1),(113778,39,88630,88746,'01:01:32.948','01:01:37.786','Rose and I differ in our definition of\nfine art. Not to impugn your work, sir.',-1),(113779,39,88778,88802,'01:01:39.121','01:01:40.122','(ROSE CLEARS THROAT)',-1),(113780,39,88804,88830,'01:01:40.206','01:01:41.290','(MOUTHS)',-1),(113781,39,89007,89031,'01:01:48.631','01:01:49.632','(HUSHED)\nAre all these mine?',-1),(113782,39,89037,89087,'01:01:49.882','01:01:51.967','Start from the outside\nand work in.',-1),(113783,39,89093,89141,'01:01:52.218','01:01:54.220','He knows every rivet in her.',-1),(113784,39,89147,89203,'01:01:54.470','01:01:56.805','Your ship is a wonder,\nMr. Andrews.',-1),(113785,39,89209,89241,'01:01:57.056','01:01:58.390','Thank you, Rose.',-1),(113786,39,89317,89355,'01:02:01.560','01:02:03.145','How do you take\nyour caviar, sir?',-1),(113787,39,89361,89439,'01:02:03.395','01:02:06.649','No caviar for me, thanks.\nNever did like it much.',-1),(113788,39,89483,89547,'01:02:08.484','01:02:11.153','Where exactly do\nyou live, Mr. Dawson?',-1),(113789,39,89557,89629,'01:02:11.570','01:02:14.573','Right now, my address\nis the RMS Titanic.',-1),(113790,39,89635,89683,'01:02:14.823','01:02:16.825','<i>After that,\nI\'m on God\'s good humor.</i>',-1),(113791,39,89695,89741,'01:02:17.326','01:02:19.245','How do you have means to travel?',-1),(113792,39,89763,89815,'01:02:20.162','01:02:22.331','I work my way\nfrom place to place.',-1),(113793,39,89817,89863,'01:02:22.414','01:02:24.333','Tramp steamers and such.',-1),(113794,39,89872,89960,'01:02:24.667','01:02:28.337','I won my ticket on Titanic\nat a lucky hand at poker.',-1),(113795,39,89966,90002,'01:02:28.587','01:02:30.089','A very lucky hand.',-1),(113796,39,90024,90072,'01:02:31.006','01:02:33.008','All life is a game of luck.',-1),(113797,39,90100,90170,'01:02:34.176','01:02:37.096','Hmm. A real man makes his\nown luck. Right, Dawson?',-1),(113798,39,90183,90208,'01:02:37.638','01:02:38.681','Mmm.',-1),(113799,39,90210,90302,'01:02:38.764','01:02:42.601','And you find that sort of\nrootless existence appealing?',-1),(113800,39,90376,90414,'01:02:45.688','01:02:47.273','Yes, ma\'am, I do.',-1),(113801,39,90432,90504,'01:02:48.023','01:02:51.026','I\'ve got everything I need\nright here with me.',-1),(113802,39,90510,90578,'01:02:51.277','01:02:54.113','I have air in my lungs\nand blank sheets of paper.',-1),(113803,39,90612,90718,'01:02:55.531','01:02:59.952','I love waking up, not knowing what\nwill happen or who I\'ll meet.',-1),(113804,39,90740,90774,'01:03:00.869','01:03:02.288','Where I\'ll wind up.',-1),(113805,39,90784,90838,'01:03:02.705','01:03:04.957','One night I\'m sleeping\nunder a bridge...',-1),(113806,39,90844,90947,'01:03:05.207','01:03:09.461','...now I\'m on the grandest ship in\nthe world, with you fine people.',-1),(113807,39,90953,90977,'01:03:09.712','01:03:10.713','I\'ll take more of that.',-1),(113808,39,91009,91081,'01:03:12.047','01:03:15.050','Life\'s a gift.\nI don\'t intend on wasting it.',-1),(113809,39,91113,91173,'01:03:16.385','01:03:18.887','You never know what\nhand you\'ll get dealt.',-1),(113810,39,91181,91245,'01:03:19.221','01:03:21.890','You take life as it comes\nat you. Here, Cal.',-1),(113811,39,91307,91347,'01:03:24.476','01:03:26.145','Make each day count.',-1),(113812,39,91367,91391,'01:03:26.979','01:03:27.980','Well said, Jack.',-1),(113813,39,91397,91423,'01:03:28.230','01:03:29.315','Hear, hear.',-1),(113814,39,91447,91485,'01:03:30.316','01:03:31.900','To making it count.',-1),(113815,39,91525,91565,'01:03:33.569','01:03:35.237','ALL: To making it count.',-1),(113816,39,91577,91601,'01:03:35.738','01:03:36.739','COL. ARCHIBALD: Bravo.',-1),(113817,39,91716,91749,'01:03:41.535','01:03:42.911','(MOLLY LAUGHING)',-1),(113818,39,91767,91845,'01:03:43.662','01:03:46.915','But Mr. Brown didn\'t know I\'d\nhidden the money in the stove.',-1),(113819,39,91846,91884,'01:03:46.957','01:03:48.500','(LAUGHTER)',-1),(113820,39,91890,91974,'01:03:48.751','01:03:52.254','He comes home drunk as a pig\ncelebrating and lights a fire.',-1),(113821,39,91976,92005,'01:03:52.338','01:03:53.547','(LAUGHTER)',-1),(113822,39,92070,92122,'01:03:56.258','01:03:58.427','(HUSHED) Next is brandy\nin the smoking room.',-1),(113823,39,92174,92224,'01:04:00.596','01:04:02.681','Join me in a brandy, gentlemen?',-1),(113824,39,92270,92331,'01:04:04.600','01:04:07.144','(HUSHED) Now they retreat\nto congratulate each other',-1),(113825,39,92333,92376,'01:04:07.227','01:04:09.021','on being masters\nof the universe.',-1),(113826,39,92382,92430,'01:04:09.271','01:04:11.273','Ladies, thank you\nfor your company.',-1),(113827,39,92456,92496,'01:04:12.358','01:04:14.026','May I escort you to the cabin?',-1),(113828,39,92502,92526,'01:04:14.276','01:04:15.277','No, I\'ll stay here.',-1),(113829,39,92546,92570,'01:04:16.111','01:04:17.112','Here, Molly.',-1),(113830,39,92594,92642,'01:04:18.113','01:04:20.115','COL. ARCHIBALD:\nJoining us, Dawson?',-1),(113831,39,92650,92706,'01:04:20.449','01:04:22.785','You don\'t want to stay\nwith the women. (CHUCKLES)',-1),(113832,39,92718,92751,'01:04:23.285','01:04:24.661','No, thanks.\nI have to head back.',-1),(113833,39,92753,92780,'01:04:24.745','01:04:25.871','COL. ARCHIBALD: Ah.',-1),(113834,39,92782,92895,'01:04:25.954','01:04:30.626','That\'s best. It\'ll be all business and\npolitics. Wouldn\'t interest you.',-1),(113835,39,92921,92985,'01:04:31.710','01:04:34.380','But Dawson, good of you to come.',-1),(113836,39,93119,93151,'01:04:39.968','01:04:41.303','Must you go?',-1),(113837,39,93157,93213,'01:04:41.553','01:04:43.889','Time for me to row\nwith the other slaves.',-1),(113838,39,93218,93248,'01:04:44.098','01:04:45.349','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113839,39,93299,93331,'01:04:47.476','01:04:48.811','Good night, Rose.',-1),(113840,39,93980,94018,'01:05:15.838','01:05:17.423','(CLOCK CHIMING)',-1),(113841,39,94043,94072,'01:05:18.465','01:05:19.675','(EXHALES)',-1),(113842,39,94292,94352,'01:05:28.851','01:05:31.353','Want to go to a real party?',-1),(113843,39,94372,94403,'01:05:32.187','01:05:33.480','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113844,39,94412,94452,'01:05:33.856','01:05:35.524','(PLAYING IRISH JIG)',-1),(113845,39,94530,94561,'01:05:38.777','01:05:40.070','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113846,39,94564,94596,'01:05:40.195','01:05:41.530','(CLAPPING)',-1),(113847,39,94602,94654,'01:05:41.780','01:05:43.949','Is okay I put my hand here?',-1),(113848,39,94994,95028,'01:05:58.088','01:05:59.506','(SPEAKING SWEDISH)',-1),(113849,39,95065,95108,'01:06:01.049','01:06:02.843','(SPEAKING SWEDISH)',-1),(113850,39,95125,95173,'01:06:03.552','01:06:05.554','I can\'t understand you.',-1),(113851,39,95405,95437,'01:06:15.230','01:06:16.565','(GLASS SMASHING)',-1),(113852,39,95557,95588,'01:06:21.570','01:06:22.863','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113853,39,95715,95750,'01:06:28.160','01:06:29.620','(FABRIZIO LAUGHING)',-1),(113854,39,95769,95809,'01:06:30.412','01:06:32.080','(MUSIC ENDS)\n(CHEERING)',-1),(113855,39,95813,95845,'01:06:32.247','01:06:33.582','FABRIZIO: Bravo!',-1),(113856,39,95948,96004,'01:06:37.836','01:06:40.172','I\'m going to dance with her now.',-1),(113857,39,96008,96032,'01:06:40.339','01:06:41.340','Come on.',-1),(113858,39,96046,96094,'01:06:41.924','01:06:43.926','Come on. Come with me.',-1),(113859,39,96102,96146,'01:06:44.259','01:06:46.094','Jack. Jack, wait.',-1),(113860,39,96202,96226,'01:06:48.430','01:06:49.431','I can\'t do this.',-1),(113861,39,96232,96276,'01:06:49.681','01:06:51.517','We\'ll have to get a bit closer.',-1),(113862,39,96282,96310,'01:06:51.767','01:06:52.935','- Like this.\n(GASPS)',-1),(113863,39,96334,96386,'01:06:53.936','01:06:56.104','(IRISH JIG PLAYING)',-1),(113864,39,96390,96430,'01:06:56.271','01:06:57.940','You\'re still my best girl, Cora.',-1),(113865,39,96508,96565,'01:07:01.193','01:07:03.570','I don\'t know the steps.\nMe, either. Just go with it.',-1),(113866,39,96566,96592,'01:07:03.612','01:07:04.696','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113867,39,96594,96628,'01:07:04.780','01:07:06.198','Don\'t think.\n(EXCLAIMS)',-1),(113868,39,96634,96670,'01:07:06.448','01:07:07.950','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113869,39,96717,96748,'01:07:09.910','01:07:11.203','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113870,39,96750,96801,'01:07:11.286','01:07:13.413','(JACK WHOOPING)',-1),(113871,39,96876,96916,'01:07:16.500','01:07:18.168','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113872,39,97087,97151,'01:07:25.300','01:07:27.970','Wait! Jack! Wait!\nStop, Jack!',-1),(113873,39,97275,97302,'01:07:33.141','01:07:34.268','Bom, bom, bom.',-1),(113874,39,97303,97343,'01:07:34.309','01:07:35.978','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113875,39,97387,97423,'01:07:37.813','01:07:39.314','What? Wait!',-1),(113876,39,97904,97944,'01:07:59.334','01:08:01.003','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113877,39,98128,98159,'01:08:08.677','01:08:09.970','JACK: Whoo-hoo!',-1),(113878,39,98224,98256,'01:08:12.681','01:08:14.016','(ROSE LAUGHING)',-1),(113879,39,98332,98384,'01:08:17.185','01:08:19.354','JACK: Whoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo!',-1),(113880,39,98412,98452,'01:08:20.522','01:08:22.190','Jack, no.',-1),(113881,39,98478,98511,'01:08:23.275','01:08:24.651','Wow!',-1),(113882,39,98513,98538,'01:08:24.735','01:08:25.777','(SCREAMS)',-1),(113883,39,98540,98583,'01:08:25.861','01:08:27.654','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113884,39,98592,98680,'01:08:28.030','01:08:31.700','...beyond the jurisdiction\nof the Sherman Act.',-1),(113885,39,98688,98778,'01:08:32.034','01:08:35.787','That\'s what Rockefeller said...\nSupreme Court didn\'t swallow it.',-1),(113886,39,98781,98823,'01:08:35.912','01:08:37.664','(SHOUTS OF ENCOURAGEMENT)',-1),(113887,39,98897,98931,'01:08:40.709','01:08:42.127','(SPEAKING SWEDISH)',-1),(113888,39,99265,99341,'01:08:56.058','01:08:59.227','What? You think a first-class\ngirl can\'t drink?',-1),(113889,39,99344,99368,'01:08:59.353','01:09:00.354','(LAUGHS)',-1),(113890,39,99376,99402,'01:09:00.687','01:09:01.772','ROSE: Oh!\n(SCREAMS)',-1),(113891,39,99407,99431,'01:09:01.980','01:09:02.981','Get out of here.',-1),(113892,39,99445,99477,'01:09:03.565','01:09:04.900','- Are you all right?\n(LAUGHS)',-1),(113893,39,99525,99549,'01:09:06.902','01:09:07.903','I\'m fine.\n(BJORN ROARS)',-1),(113894,39,99555,99592,'01:09:08.153','01:09:09.696','Two out of three.',-1),(113895,39,99593,99623,'01:09:09.738','01:09:10.989','(SPEAKING SWEDISH)',-1),(113896,39,99625,99657,'01:09:11.073','01:09:12.407','So...',-1),(113897,39,99685,99733,'01:09:13.575','01:09:15.577','...you think you\'re tough?',-1),(113898,39,99765,99801,'01:09:16.912','01:09:18.413','Let\'s see you do this.',-1),(113899,39,99857,99922,'01:09:20.749','01:09:23.418','Hold this for me, Jack.\nHold it up.',-1),(113900,39,100260,100296,'01:09:37.516','01:09:39.017','- Ow! (LAUGHS)\n- Whoa!',-1),(113901,39,100346,100372,'01:09:41.103','01:09:42.187','Jesus!',-1),(113902,39,100378,100406,'01:09:42.437','01:09:43.605','You okay?',-1),(113903,39,100412,100450,'01:09:43.855','01:09:45.440','I haven\'t done that in years.',-1),(113904,39,100594,100639,'01:09:51.446','01:09:53.323','(ROSE LAUGHING)\n(MUSIC ENDS)',-1),(113905,39,100644,100710,'01:09:53.532','01:09:56.284','Come on, lads.\nGive it all you got. Let\'s go.',-1),(113906,39,100712,100752,'01:09:56.368','01:09:58.036','(WHOOPING)',-1),(113907,39,101335,101367,'01:10:22.310','01:10:23.645','Coffee, sir?',-1),(113908,39,101605,101645,'01:10:33.572','01:10:35.240','You didn\'t come\nto me last night.',-1),(113909,39,101699,101735,'01:10:37.492','01:10:38.994','I was tired.',-1),(113910,39,101795,101859,'01:10:41.496','01:10:44.166','Your exertions below deck\nwere no doubt exhausting.',-1),(113911,39,101936,102020,'01:10:47.335','01:10:50.839','I see you had that undertaker\nof a manservant follow me.',-1),(113912,39,102028,102098,'01:10:51.173','01:10:54.092','You will never\nbehave like that again.',-1),(113913,39,102184,102256,'01:10:57.679','01:11:00.682','I\'m not one of your mill\nforemen who you can command.',-1),(113914,39,102292,102332,'01:11:02.184','01:11:03.852','I\'m your fiance.',-1),(113915,39,102372,102420,'01:11:05.520','01:11:07.522','(QUIETLY) My fiance.\n(SHOUTING) My fiance!',-1),(113916,39,102428,102476,'01:11:07.856','01:11:09.858','Yes, you are! And my wife!',-1),(113917,39,102508,102616,'01:11:11.193','01:11:15.697','My wife in practice, if not yet\nby law, so you will honor me!',-1),(113918,39,102624,102690,'01:11:16.031','01:11:18.784','You will honor me the way\na wife honors her husband.',-1),(113919,39,102696,102750,'01:11:19.034','01:11:21.286','Because I will not\nbe made a fool of.',-1),(113920,39,102770,102814,'01:11:22.120','01:11:23.955','Is this in any way unclear?',-1),(113921,39,102836,102864,'01:11:24.873','01:11:26.041','No.',-1),(113922,39,102872,102929,'01:11:26.374','01:11:28.710','Good. Excuse me.',-1),(113923,39,103022,103060,'01:11:32.589','01:11:34.174','(ROSE GASPING)',-1),(113924,39,103065,103105,'01:11:34.382','01:11:36.051','Oh, Miss Rose.',-1),(113925,39,103145,103183,'01:11:37.719','01:11:39.304','(PANTING)\nWe had a little accident.',-1),(113926,39,103189,103241,'01:11:39.554','01:11:41.723','- That\'s all right.\n- I\'m sorry.',-1),(113927,39,103251,103275,'01:11:42.140','01:11:43.141','Let me help you.',-1),(113928,39,103281,103321,'01:11:43.391','01:11:45.060','It\'s all right, miss.',-1),(113929,39,103381,103421,'01:11:47.562','01:11:49.231','<i>(SOBS)</i>',-1),(113930,39,103477,103511,'01:11:51.566','01:11:52.984','It\'s all right, miss.',-1),(113931,39,103645,103677,'01:11:58.573','01:11:59.908','Tea, Trudy.',-1),(113932,39,104098,104174,'01:12:17.425','01:12:20.595','You\'re not to see that boy\nagain. You understand?',-1),(113933,39,104206,104262,'01:12:21.930','01:12:24.266','Rose, I forbid it.',-1),(113934,39,104286,104358,'01:12:25.267','01:12:28.270','Stop it, Mother. You\'ll\ngive yourself a nosebleed.',-1),(113935,39,104366,104406,'01:12:28.603','01:12:30.272','This is not a game.',-1),(113936,39,104420,104506,'01:12:30.856','01:12:34.442','Our situation is precarious.\nYou know the money\'s gone.',-1),(113937,39,104514,104618,'01:12:34.776','01:12:39.114','Of course I know.\nYou remind me every day.',-1),(113938,39,104644,104760,'01:12:40.198','01:12:45.036','Your father left us nothing but a legacy\nof bad debts hidden by a good name.',-1),(113939,39,104766,104830,'01:12:45.287','01:12:47.956','That name is the only\ncard we have to play.',-1),(113940,39,104846,104887,'01:12:48.623','01:12:50.292','I don\'t understand you.',-1),(113941,39,104903,104944,'01:12:50.959','01:12:52.669','It is a fine match with Hockley.',-1),(113942,39,104946,104999,'01:12:52.752','01:12:54.963','It will ensure our survival.',-1),(113943,39,105031,105071,'01:12:56.298','01:12:57.966','How can you put this on me?',-1),(113944,39,105077,105113,'01:12:58.216','01:12:59.718','Why are you being so selfish?',-1),(113945,39,105125,105169,'01:13:00.218','01:13:02.053','I\'m being selfish?',-1),(113946,39,105253,105323,'01:13:05.557','01:13:08.476','Do <i>you want to see me\nworking as</i> a <i>seamstress?</i>',-1),(113947,39,105367,105411,'01:13:10.312','01:13:12.147','Is that what you want?',-1),(113948,39,105475,105543,'01:13:14.816','01:13:17.652','To see our fine things\nsold at auction?',-1),(113949,39,105583,105627,'01:13:19.321','01:13:21.156','Our memories scattered?',-1),(113950,39,105896,105936,'01:13:32.334','01:13:34.002','(SIGHS) It\'s so unfair.',-1),(113951,39,105968,106012,'01:13:35.337','01:13:37.172','Of course it\'s unfair.',-1),(113952,39,106044,106076,'01:13:38.506','01:13:39.841','We\'re women.',-1),(113953,39,106136,106188,'01:13:42.344','01:13:44.512','Our choices are never easy.',-1),(113954,39,106360,106395,'01:13:51.686','01:13:53.146','Mmm?',-1),(113955,39,106712,106804,'01:14:06.368','01:14:10.205','ALL: <i>Protect them\nby Thy guiding hand</i>',-1),(113956,39,106812,106929,'01:14:10.538','01:14:15.377','<i>From every peril on the land</i>',-1),(113957,39,106977,107073,'01:14:17.379','01:14:21.383','<i>O, spirit whom the Father sent</i>',-1),(113958,39,107089,107189,'01:14:22.050','01:14:26.221','<i>To spread abroad the firmament</i>',-1),(113959,39,107197,107301,'01:14:26.554','01:14:30.892','<i>O, wind of heaven, by Thy might</i>',-1),(113960,39,107309,107425,'01:14:31.226','01:14:36.064','<i>Save all who dare\nthe eagle\'s flight</i>',-1),(113961,39,107433,107525,'01:14:36.398','01:14:40.235','<i>And keep them by\nThy watchful care...</i>',-1),(113962,39,107589,107629,'01:14:42.904','01:14:44.572','Hello, Mr. Andrews.',-1),(113963,39,107780,107821,'01:14:50.870','01:14:52.580','(SINGING CONTINUES WITHIN)',-1),(113964,39,107875,107910,'01:14:54.833','01:14:56.251','I need to talk to someone.',-1),(113965,39,107916,107970,'01:14:56.501','01:14:58.753','You\'re not supposed\nto be in here.',-1),(113966,39,108082,108120,'01:15:03.425','01:15:05.010','I was here last night, remember?',-1),(113967,39,108126,108166,'01:15:05.260','01:15:06.928','No. Now please turn around.',-1),(113968,39,108172,108240,'01:15:07.178','01:15:10.015','He\'ll tell you.\nI just need to talk...',-1),(113969,39,108246,108322,'01:15:10.265','01:15:13.435','Mr. Hockley and\nMrs. DeWitt Bukater...',-1),(113970,39,108330,108398,'01:15:13.768','01:15:16.604','...are still appreciative\nof your assistance.',-1),(113971,39,108406,108490,'01:15:16.938','01:15:20.442','They asked me to give\nyou this in gratitude...',-1),(113972,39,108496,108534,'01:15:20.692','01:15:22.277','I don\'t want your money.',-1),(113973,39,108542,108634,'01:15:22.610','01:15:26.448','...And remind you you are in third\nclass and your presence here...',-1),(113974,39,108640,108682,'01:15:26.698','01:15:28.450','...is no longer appropriate.',-1),(113975,39,108688,108720,'01:15:28.700','01:15:30.035','Let me speak to Rose.',-1),(113976,39,108726,108822,'01:15:30.285','01:15:34.289','Gentlemen, please see Mr. Dawson\nreturns to where he belongs...',-1),(113977,39,108830,108870,'01:15:34.622','01:15:36.291','...and that he stays there?',-1),(113978,39,108891,108915,'01:15:37.125','01:15:38.126','Yes, sir.',-1),(113979,39,108921,108949,'01:15:38.376','01:15:39.544','Come along, you.',-1),(113980,39,108999,109075,'01:15:41.629','01:15:44.799','<i>Hear us when we cry to Thee</i>',-1),(113981,39,109083,109191,'01:15:45.133','01:15:49.637','<i>For those in peril on the sea</i>',-1),(113982,39,109215,109259,'01:15:50.638','01:15:52.474','RUTH: Why are there\ntwo steering wheels?',-1),(113983,39,109265,109301,'01:15:52.724','01:15:54.225','We use this one near shore.',-1),(113984,39,109307,109395,'01:15:54.476','01:15:58.146','Excuse me, sir. Another ice\nwarning, from the Noordam.',-1),(113985,39,109401,109433,'01:15:58.396','01:15:59.731','CAPT. SMITH:\nThank you, Sparks.',-1),(113986,39,109487,109567,'01:16:01.983','01:16:05.320','Not to worry. Quite normal\nfor this time of year.',-1),(113987,39,109591,109633,'01:16:06.321','01:16:08.073','In fact, we\'re speeding up.',-1),(113988,39,109635,109687,'01:16:08.156','01:16:10.325','I\'ve ordered\nthe last boilers lit.',-1),(113989,39,109703,109731,'01:16:10.992','01:16:12.160','(GRUNTING)',-1),(113990,39,109784,109819,'01:16:14.370','01:16:15.830','MAN: Okay, son,\nwind it up tight',-1),(113991,39,109821,109855,'01:16:15.914','01:16:17.332','like I showed you.\nThat\'s right.',-1),(113992,39,109860,109900,'01:16:17.540','01:16:19.167','Okay, now let it go.',-1),(113993,39,109973,110021,'01:16:22.212','01:16:24.214','It was good, wasn\'t it? Quite\nnice. That\'s excellent.',-1),(113994,39,110189,110261,'01:16:31.221','01:16:34.224','ROSE: Mr. Andrews...\nForgive me.',-1),(113995,39,110276,110310,'01:16:34.849','01:16:36.267','I did the sum in my head...',-1),(113996,39,110325,110409,'01:16:36.893','01:16:40.396','...and with the number of lifeboats\ntimes the capacity you mentioned...-',-1),(113997,39,110417,110501,'01:16:40.730','01:16:44.234','Forgive me, but it seems that there\nare not enough for everyone aboard.',-1),(113998,39,110520,110561,'01:16:45.026','01:16:46.736','About half, actually.',-1),(113999,39,110581,110617,'01:16:47.570','01:16:49.072','Rose, you miss nothing, do you?',-1),(114000,39,110637,110689,'01:16:49.906','01:16:52.075','In fact, I put in these\nnew type davits...',-1),(114001,39,110697,110760,'01:16:52.408','01:16:55.036','...which can take an extra row\nof boats inside this one.',-1),(114002,39,110777,110824,'01:16:55.745','01:16:57.705','But it was thought, by some...',-1),(114003,39,110828,110866,'01:16:57.872','01:16:59.457','...the deck would look\ntoo cluttered.',-1),(114004,39,110877,110934,'01:16:59.916','01:17:02.252','So, I was overruled.',-1),(114005,39,110946,111018,'01:17:02.752','01:17:05.755','It\'s a waste of deck space as\nit is on an unsinkable ship.',-1),(114006,39,111026,111066,'01:17:06.089','01:17:07.757','Sleep soundly, young Rose.',-1),(114007,39,111069,111131,'01:17:07.882','01:17:10.468','I have built you a good\nship, strong and true.',-1),(114008,39,111138,111178,'01:17:10.760','01:17:12.428','She\'s all the lifeboat you need.',-1),(114009,39,111186,111258,'01:17:12.762','01:17:15.765','Just keep heading aft. The next\nstop will be the engine room.',-1),(114010,39,111386,111490,'01:17:21.104','01:17:25.441','Jack, this is impossible.\nI can\'t see you.',-1),(114011,39,111497,111566,'01:17:25.733','01:17:28.611','I need to talk to you.\nNo, Jack. No.',-1),(114012,39,111602,111658,'01:17:30.113','01:17:32.448','Jack.\nI\'m engaged.',-1),(114013,39,111682,111726,'01:17:33.449','01:17:35.285','I\'m marrying Cal.',-1),(114014,39,111746,111773,'01:17:36.119','01:17:37.245','I love Cal.',-1),(114015,39,111834,111866,'01:17:39.789','01:17:41.124','Rose...',-1),(114016,39,111878,111987,'01:17:41.624','01:17:46.129','...you\'re no picnic. All right?\nYou\'re a spoiled little brat even.',-1),(114017,39,111995,112103,'01:17:46.462','01:17:50.967','But under that, you\'re the\nmost amazingly, astounding...',-1),(114018,39,112111,112151,'01:17:51.301','01:17:52.969','...wonderful girl...',-1),(114019,39,112166,112210,'01:17:53.595','01:17:55.430','...woman,\nthat I\'ve ever known.',-1),(114020,39,112212,112238,'01:17:55.513','01:17:56.598','Jack, I...',-1),(114021,39,112239,112304,'01:17:56.639','01:17:59.350','No, let me try and get\nthis out. You\'re ama...',-1),(114022,39,112306,112330,'01:17:59.434','01:18:00.435','(SIGHS)',-1),(114023,39,112363,112435,'01:18:01.811','01:18:04.814','I\'m not an idiot. I know\nhow the world works.',-1),(114024,39,112443,112488,'01:18:05.148','01:18:07.025','I\'ve got ten bucks in my pocket.',-1),(114025,39,112491,112558,'01:18:07.150','01:18:09.944','I have nothing to offer\nyou and I know that.',-1),(114026,39,112563,112603,'01:18:10.153','01:18:11.821','I understand.',-1),(114027,39,112626,112666,'01:18:12.780','01:18:14.449','But I\'m too involved now.',-1),(114028,39,112675,112723,'01:18:14.824','01:18:16.826','You jump, I jump.\nRemember?',-1),(114029,39,112731,112791,'01:18:17.160','01:18:19.662','I can\'t turn away without\nknowing you\'ll be all right.',-1),(114030,39,112834,112858,'01:18:21.456','01:18:22.457','That\'s all that I want.',-1),(114031,39,112891,112928,'01:18:23.833','01:18:25.335','Well, I\'m fine.',-1),(114032,39,112956,113016,'01:18:26.502','01:18:29.005','I\'ll be fine. Really.',-1),(114033,39,113040,113068,'01:18:30.006','01:18:31.174','Really?',-1),(114034,39,113120,113156,'01:18:33.343','01:18:34.844','I don\'t think so.',-1),(114035,39,113180,113231,'01:18:35.845','01:18:37.972','They\'ve got you trapped, Rose.',-1),(114036,39,113235,113268,'01:18:38.139','01:18:39.515','And you\'re gonna die\nif you don\'t break free.',-1),(114037,39,113271,113296,'01:18:39.641','01:18:40.683','Maybe not right away...',-1),(114038,39,113299,113339,'01:18:40.808','01:18:42.477','...because you\'re strong...',-1),(114039,39,113372,113452,'01:18:43.853','01:18:47.190','...but sooner or later that fire\nthat I love about you, Rose...',-1),(114040,39,113460,113520,'01:18:47.523','01:18:50.026','...that fire is gonna\nburn out.',-1),(114041,39,113636,113679,'01:18:54.864','01:18:56.658','It\'s not up to you\nto save me, Jack.',-1),(114042,39,113739,113768,'01:18:59.160','01:19:00.370','You\'re right.',-1),(114043,39,113800,113840,'01:19:01.704','01:19:03.373','Only you can do that.',-1),(114044,39,113985,114021,'01:19:09.379','01:19:10.880','I\'m going back.',-1),(114045,39,114029,114065,'01:19:11.214','01:19:12.715','Leave me alone.',-1),(114046,39,114134,114161,'01:19:15.593','01:19:16.719','(DOOR SHUTS)',-1),(114047,39,114341,114417,'01:19:24.227','01:19:27.397','Tell Lucile about the disaster\nyou had with the Stationers.',-1),(114048,39,114424,114488,'01:19:27.689','01:19:30.358','Well, of course the invitations\nhad to be sent back, twice.',-1),(114049,39,114493,114521,'01:19:30.566','01:19:31.734','Oh, my dear.',-1),(114050,39,114528,114565,'01:19:32.026','01:19:33.569','And the dreadful\nbridesmaids\' gowns.',-1),(114051,39,114568,114624,'01:19:33.695','01:19:36.030','Let me tell you what an\nodyssey that has been.',-1),(114052,39,114629,114684,'01:19:36.239','01:19:38.533','Rose decided she\nwanted lavender.',-1),(114053,39,114702,114730,'01:19:39.284','01:19:40.451','She knows I detest the color.',-1),(114054,39,114741,114772,'01:19:40.910','01:19:42.203','So, she did it only to spite me.',-1),(114055,39,114777,114825,'01:19:42.412','01:19:44.414','LADY GORDON: If only\nyou\'d come to me sooner.',-1),(114056,39,114832,114901,'01:19:44.706','01:19:47.542','<i>Ruth saw some of my designs\nin La Mode lllustre.</i>',-1),(114057,39,114906,114986,'01:19:47.750','01:19:51.087','hey were for the trousseau of the Duchess\nof Marlborough\'s youngest daughter.',-1),(114058,39,114989,115013,'01:19:51.212','01:19:52.213','They were quite charming.',-1),(114059,39,115015,115063,'01:19:52.297','01:19:54.299','But, I think you\'ll agree,\nmy dear, that together...',-1),(114060,39,115070,115133,'01:19:54.590','01:19:57.218','...we\'ve created something\nof a phoenix from the ashes.',-1),(114061,39,115134,115161,'01:19:57.260','01:19:58.386','(LAUGHTER)',-1),(114062,39,115501,115525,'01:20:12.567','01:20:13.568','Hello, Jack.',-1),(114063,39,115662,115706,'01:20:19.282','01:20:21.117','I changed my mind.',-1),(114064,39,115849,115877,'01:20:27.081','01:20:28.249','They said you might be up here.',-1),(114065,39,115879,115906,'01:20:28.333','01:20:29.417','Shh.',-1),(114066,39,115951,115983,'01:20:31.294','01:20:32.628','Give me your hand.',-1),(114067,39,116163,116195,'01:20:40.136','01:20:41.471','Now close your eyes.',-1),(114068,39,116227,116259,'01:20:42.805','01:20:44.140','Go on.',-1),(114069,39,116339,116375,'01:20:47.477','01:20:48.978','Now, step up.',-1),(114070,39,116467,116498,'01:20:52.815','01:20:54.108','Now, hold onto the railing.',-1),(114071,39,116500,116548,'01:20:54.192','01:20:56.194','Keep your eyes closed.\nDon\'t peek.',-1),(114072,39,116554,116578,'01:20:56.444','01:20:57.445','I\'m not.',-1),(114073,39,116611,116659,'01:20:58.821','01:21:00.823','Now, step up onto the rail.',-1),(114074,39,116755,116803,'01:21:04.827','01:21:06.829','Hold on. Hold on.',-1),(114075,39,116815,116844,'01:21:07.330','01:21:08.539','Keep your eyes closed.',-1),(114076,39,116846,116870,'01:21:08.623','01:21:09.624','(LAUGHS)',-1),(114077,39,116871,116904,'01:21:09.665','01:21:11.000','JACK: Do you trust me?',-1),(114078,39,116916,116948,'01:21:11.501','01:21:12.835','I trust you.',-1),(114079,39,117184,117208,'01:21:22.678','01:21:23.679','All right...',-1),(114080,39,117217,117253,'01:21:24.055','01:21:25.556','...open your eyes.',-1),(114081,39,117287,117327,'01:21:26.974','01:21:28.643','(ROSE GASPS)',-1),(114082,39,117423,117447,'01:21:32.647','01:21:33.648','I\'m flying.',-1),(114083,39,117459,117483,'01:21:34.148','01:21:35.149','Jack.',-1),(114084,39,118086,118185,'01:22:00.258','01:22:04.387','<i>(SINGING) Come, Josephine, in\nmy flying machine. Going up.</i>',-1),(114085,39,118205,118285,'01:22:05.221','01:22:08.558','<i>...she goes. Up she goes.</i>',-1),(114086,39,119239,119279,'01:22:48.306','01:22:49.974','(MUFFLED RADIO CHATTER)',-1),(114087,39,119430,119502,'01:22:56.272','01:22:59.275','That was the last time\nTitanic ever saw daylight.',-1),(114088,39,119537,119587,'01:23:00.735','01:23:02.820','We\'re up to dusk the\nnight of the sinking.',-1),(114089,39,119607,119637,'01:23:03.654','01:23:04.906','6 hours to go.',-1),(114090,39,119642,119713,'01:23:05.114','01:23:08.075','Incredible. There\'s Smith and\nhe\'s standing there and...',-1),(114091,39,119715,119755,'01:23:08.159','01:23:09.827','...he\'s got the iceberg warning\nin his fucking hand...',-1),(114092,39,119761,119833,'01:23:10.077','01:23:13.080','...excuse me... his hand,\nand he\'s ordering more speed.',-1),(114093,39,119838,119915,'01:23:13.289','01:23:16.459','26 years of experience\nworking against him.',-1),(114094,39,119922,119970,'01:23:16.751','01:23:18.753','He figures anything big\nenough to sink, the ship...',-1),(114095,39,119974,120016,'01:23:18.920','01:23:20.671','...they\'re gonna see\nin time to turn.',-1),(114096,39,120023,120082,'01:23:20.963','01:23:23.424','But the ship\'s too big\nwith too small a rudder.',-1),(114097,39,120086,120135,'01:23:23.591','01:23:25.635','Doesn\'t corner worth a damn.',-1),(114098,39,120163,120219,'01:23:26.802','01:23:29.138','Everything he knows is wrong.',-1),(114099,39,120523,120570,'01:23:41.817','01:23:43.778','(LAUGHING) It\'s quite\nproper, I assure you.',-1),(114100,39,120571,120615,'01:23:43.819','01:23:45.655','This is the sitting room.',-1),(114101,39,120663,120699,'01:23:47.657','01:23:49.158','- Will this light do?\n- What?',-1),(114102,39,120731,120763,'01:23:50.493','01:23:51.827','Don\'t artists need good light?',-1),(114103,39,120770,120823,'01:23:52.119','01:23:54.330','(FRENCH ACCENT) That is true, but\nI\'m not used to working in...',-1),(114104,39,120842,120880,'01:23:55.12