630','What?\n(LAUGHS)',-1),(114196,39,133172,133212,'01:32:28.844','01:32:30.512','MAN: More coal for\nnumber one, mate.',-1),(114197,39,133219,133279,'01:32:30.804','01:32:33.307','Hold up? What are you two\ndoing down here?',-1),(114198,39,133292,133316,'01:32:33.849','01:32:34.850','You shouldn\'t be down here.',-1),(114199,39,133324,133349,'01:32:35.184','01:32:36.226','It could be dangerous! Oi!',-1),(114200,39,133455,133479,'01:32:40.647','01:32:41.648','Carry on!',-1),(114201,39,133488,133533,'01:32:42.024','01:32:43.901','Don\'t mind us. You\'re\ndoing a great job!',-1),(114202,39,133537,133573,'01:32:44.068','01:32:45.569','Keep up the good work!',-1),(114203,39,133965,134012,'01:33:01.877','01:33:03.837','JACK: Ah. Look at\nwhat we have here, huh?',-1),(114204,39,134013,134053,'01:33:03.879','01:33:05.547','(JACK CHUCKLES)',-1),(114205,39,134282,134318,'01:33:15.099','01:33:16.600','(ROSE CLEARS THROAT)',-1),(114206,39,134372,134412,'01:33:18.852','01:33:20.521','<i>(JACK CLEARS THROAT)</i>',-1),(114207,39,134449,134481,'01:33:22.064','01:33:23.398','Thank you.',-1),(114208,39,134724,134759,'01:33:33.534','01:33:34.993','(HONKS HORN)\n(LAUGHS)',-1),(114209,39,134761,134805,'01:33:35.077','01:33:36.912','Where to, miss?',-1),(114210,39,134833,134873,'01:33:38.080','01:33:39.748','To the stars.',-1),(114211,39,134937,134969,'01:33:42.376','01:33:43.710','(JACK LAUGHS)',-1),(114212,39,135330,135366,'01:33:58.767','01:34:00.269','You nervous?',-1),(114213,39,135425,135453,'01:34:02.729','01:34:03.897','(QUIETLY) No.',-1),(114214,39,135858,135906,'01:34:20.789','01:34:22.791','Put your hands on me, Jack.',-1),(114215,39,136483,136519,'01:34:46.815','01:34:48.317','<i>It\'s bloody cold.</i>',-1),(114216,39,136531,136615,'01:34:48.817','01:34:52.321','You know, I can smell ice,\nyou know. When it\'s near.',-1),(114217,39,136647,136679,'01:34:53.655','01:34:54.990','Bollocks!',-1),(114218,39,136687,136727,'01:34:55.324','01:34:56.992','Well, I can, all right?',-1),(114219,39,136735,136786,'01:34:57.326','01:34:59.453','Did you ever find those\nbinoculars for the lookouts?',-1),(114220,39,136791,136835,'01:34:59.661','01:35:01.496','Haven\'t seen them\nsince Southampton.',-1),(114221,39,136851,136883,'01:35:02.164','01:35:03.498','Well, I\'ll be on my rounds.',-1),(114222,39,136906,136931,'01:35:04.458','01:35:05.459','Cheerio.',-1),(114223,39,137371,137411,'01:35:23.810','01:35:25.479','(JACK BREATHING HEAVILY)',-1),(114224,39,137680,137712,'01:35:36.698','01:35:38.033','You\'re trembling.',-1),(114225,39,137771,137796,'01:35:40.494','01:35:41.536','Don\'t worry.',-1),(114226,39,137799,137841,'01:35:41.662','01:35:43.413','I\'ll be all right.',-1),(114227,39,138353,138397,'01:36:04.726','01:36:06.561','They ran down there.\nRight.',-1),(114228,39,138631,138671,'01:36:16.321','01:36:17.990','LOVEJOY: Anything missing?',-1),(114229,39,139272,139316,'01:36:43.015','01:36:44.850','I have a better idea.',-1),(114230,39,139504,139544,'01:36:52.691','01:36:54.359','(CLICKS FINGERS)',-1),(114231,39,139624,139652,'01:36:57.696','01:36:58.864','Got you!',-1),(114232,39,139696,139736,'01:37:00.699','01:37:02.367','(BOTH LAUGHING)',-1),(114233,39,139874,139943,'01:37:08.123','01:37:10.959','Did you see those guys\' faces?',-1),(114234,39,139957,140001,'01:37:11.543','01:37:13.378','Did you see them?',-1),(114235,39,140153,140197,'01:37:19.718','01:37:21.553','When the ship docks...',-1),(114236,39,140229,140271,'01:37:22.888','01:37:24.639','...I\'m getting off with you.',-1),(114237,39,140297,140329,'01:37:25.724','01:37:27.059','This is crazy.',-1),(114238,39,140333,140401,'01:37:27.225','01:37:30.062','I know. It doesn\'t\nmake any sense.',-1),(114239,39,140437,140473,'01:37:31.563','01:37:33.065','(SIGHS)\nThat\'s why I trust it.',-1),(114240,39,140689,140753,'01:37:42.074','01:37:44.743','Oh, yes.\nHere, look at this.',-1),(114241,39,140773,140821,'01:37:45.577','01:37:47.579','Look at that, would you?',-1),(114242,39,140829,140865,'01:37:47.913','01:37:49.414','They\'re warmer than we are.',-1),(114243,39,140875,140980,'01:37:49.831','01:37:54.169','If that\'s what it takes for us\nto get warm, I\'d rather not.',-1),(114244,39,140982,141016,'01:37:54.252','01:37:55.670','(CHUCKLES)',-1),(114245,39,141274,141310,'01:38:06.431','01:38:07.933','Bugger me!',-1),(114246,39,141311,141339,'01:38:07.974','01:38:09.142','(BELL RINGING)',-1),(114247,39,141398,141433,'01:38:11.603','01:38:13.063','(TELEPHONE RINGING)',-1),(114248,39,141438,141473,'01:38:13.271','01:38:14.731','Pick up, you bastards!',-1),(114249,39,141475,141520,'01:38:14.815','01:38:16.691','(TELEPHONE CONTINUES RINGING)',-1),(114250,39,141562,141586,'01:38:18.443','01:38:19.444','FLEET: Is anyone there?!',-1),(114251,39,141592,141620,'01:38:19.694','01:38:20.862','What do you see?',-1),(114252,39,141626,141660,'01:38:21.113','01:38:22.531','Iceberg, right ahead!',-1),(114253,39,141666,141692,'01:38:22.781','01:38:23.865','Thank you.',-1),(114254,39,141748,141772,'01:38:26.201','01:38:27.202','Iceberg ahead!',-1),(114255,39,141776,141824,'01:38:27.369','01:38:29.371','Hard a\' starboard!',-1),(114256,39,141991,142045,'01:38:36.294','01:38:38.547','Turn! Turn! Smartly!',-1),(114257,39,142095,142144,'01:38:40.632','01:38:42.676','(ENGINE TELEGRAPH RINGS)',-1),(114258,39,142171,142195,'01:38:43.802','01:38:44.803','Full astern!',-1),(114259,39,142251,142275,'01:38:47.139','01:38:48.140','Hard over.',-1),(114260,39,142279,142319,'01:38:48.306','01:38:49.975','MOODY: Helm\'s hard over, sir.',-1),(114261,39,142364,142404,'01:38:51.852','01:38:53.520','(ENGINE TELEGRAPH RINGING)',-1),(114262,39,142407,142443,'01:38:53.645','01:38:55.147','Go, lads, go!',-1),(114263,39,142501,142567,'01:38:57.566','01:39:00.318','ENGINEER BELL: Bring that steam down!\nBring it down!',-1),(114264,39,142611,142678,'01:39:02.154','01:39:04.948','Shut all the dampers!\nShut them!',-1),(114265,39,142680,142720,'01:39:05.031','01:39:06.700','(DOORS SLAMMING)',-1),(114266,39,142795,142819,'01:39:09.828','01:39:10.829','Hold it.',-1),(114267,39,142863,142887,'01:39:12.664','01:39:13.665','Hold it!',-1),(114268,39,142921,142963,'01:39:15.083','01:39:16.793','Now! Engage\nreversing engine!',-1),(114269,39,142965,143007,'01:39:16.877','01:39:18.628','(OVERLAPPING SHOUTS)',-1),(114270,39,143301,143354,'01:39:30.891','01:39:33.101','(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)',-1),(114271,39,143660,143696,'01:39:45.864','01:39:47.365','Why ain\'t they turning?',-1),(114272,39,143702,143730,'01:39:47.616','01:39:48.783','Is it hard over?!',-1),(114273,39,143736,143784,'01:39:49.034','01:39:51.036','It is, sir. Hard over.',-1),(114274,39,143880,143981,'01:39:55.040','01:39:59.211','(QUIETLY) Come on,\ncome on, come on. Turn.',-1),(114275,39,144249,144281,'01:40:10.388','01:40:11.723','Yes.',-1),(114276,39,144405,144445,'01:40:16.895','01:40:18.563','It\'s going to hit!',-1),(114277,39,144719,144755,'01:40:29.991','01:40:31.493','Jesus Christ!',-1),(114278,39,144780,144830,'01:40:32.536','01:40:34.621','(CREAKING)',-1),(114279,39,144874,144910,'01:40:36.456','01:40:37.958','(METALLIC SCRAPING)',-1),(114280,39,145128,145161,'01:40:47.008','01:40:48.385','(GLASS TINKLING)',-1),(114281,39,145254,145282,'01:40:52.264','01:40:53.431','Jesus!',-1),(114282,39,145288,145312,'01:40:53.682','01:40:54.683','Hard to port!',-1),(114283,39,145318,145350,'01:40:54.933','01:40:56.268','MOODY: Hard to port!',-1),(114284,39,145442,145483,'01:41:00.105','01:41:01.815','(SCREAMING)',-1),(114285,39,145586,145621,'01:41:06.111','01:41:07.571','JACK: Get back!',-1),(114286,39,145623,145648,'01:41:07.654','01:41:08.697','(MEN GRUNT)',-1),(114287,39,145814,145852,'01:41:15.620','01:41:17.205','(SCREAMS)',-1),(114288,39,146080,146107,'01:41:26.673','01:41:27.799','(SCREAMING)',-1),(114289,39,146278,146323,'01:41:34.931','01:41:36.808','(ALARM RINGING)',-1),(114290,39,146329,146361,'01:41:37.058','01:41:38.393','Let\'s go!',-1),(114291,39,146367,146447,'01:41:38.643','01:41:41.980','They\'re closing the doors!\nGet out!',-1),(114292,39,146603,146659,'01:41:48.486','01:41:50.822','Get out the door! Go!',-1),(114293,39,146667,146739,'01:41:51.156','01:41:54.159','Go! Come on, lads!\nGo, lads, go!',-1),(114294,39,146972,147012,'01:42:03.835','01:42:05.503','Go! Go!',-1),(114295,39,147024,147072,'01:42:06.004','01:42:08.006','Out! Out!',-1),(114296,39,147171,147211,'01:42:12.135','01:42:13.803','(ALARM RINGING)',-1),(114297,39,147424,147464,'01:42:22.687','01:42:24.356','Oh, my God.',-1),(114298,39,147484,147516,'01:42:25.190','01:42:26.524','That was a close shave.',-1),(114299,39,147524,147594,'01:42:26.858','01:42:29.778','Smell ice, can you?\nBleedin\' Christ!',-1),(114300,39,147692,147760,'01:42:33.865','01:42:36.701','Note the time.\nEnter it in the log.',-1),(114301,39,147898,147939,'01:42:42.457','01:42:44.125','What was that,\nMr. Murdoch?',-1),(114302,39,147961,147995,'01:42:45.043','01:42:46.461','An iceberg, sir.',-1),(114303,39,148021,148105,'01:42:47.545','01:42:51.049','I put her hard to starboard,\nbut it was too close.',-1),(114304,39,148113,148165,'01:42:51.383','01:42:53.551','I tried to port round it, but...',-1),(114305,39,148173,148249,'01:42:53.885','01:42:57.055','- CAPT-SMITH: Close the watertight doors.\n- They\'re closed, sir.',-1),(114306,39,148325,148353,'01:43:00.225','01:43:01.393','All stop.',-1),(114307,39,148441,148482,'01:43:05.063','01:43:06.773','(ENGINE TELEGRAPH RINGING)',-1),(114308,39,148577,148629,'01:43:10.735','01:43:12.904','Have the carpenter\nsound the ship.',-1),(114309,39,148731,148766,'01:43:17.158','01:43:18.618','(SPLASHING)\n(EXCLAIMS IN ITALIAN)',-1),(114310,39,148767,148807,'01:43:18.660','01:43:20.328','(SPEAKING SWEDISH)',-1),(114311,39,148909,148990,'01:43:24.582','01:43:27.919','Come on, let\'s get\nthe hell out of here!',-1),(114312,39,149106,149174,'01:43:32.757','01:43:35.593','Why have the engines stopped?\nI felt a shudder.',-1),(114313,39,149180,149244,'01:43:35.844','01:43:38.513','Not to worry.\nWe threw a propeller blade.',-1),(114314,39,149250,149318,'01:43:38.763','01:43:41.599','That\'s the shudder you felt.\nDo you need anything?',-1),(114315,39,149338,149364,'01:43:42.434','01:43:43.518','No, thank you.',-1),(114316,39,149482,149542,'01:43:48.440','01:43:50.942','MAN 1:\nThere\'s talk of an iceberg.',-1),(114317,39,149548,149590,'01:43:51.192','01:43:52.944','MAN 2: I don\'t see\nanything. Do you?',-1),(114318,39,149642,149718,'01:43:55.113','01:43:58.283','If this is where the rats\nare going, I am, too.',-1),(114319,39,149886,149926,'01:44:05.290','01:44:06.958','You.\nThere is no emergency.',-1),(114320,39,149932,150001,'01:44:07.208','01:44:10.044','There is. I\'ve been robbed.\nGet the Master at Arms.',-1),(114321,39,150015,150055,'01:44:10.628','01:44:12.297','Now, you moron!',-1),(114322,39,150072,150112,'01:44:13.006','01:44:14.674','(MEN LAUGHING)',-1),(114323,39,150167,150199,'01:44:16.968','01:44:18.303','Did I miss the fun?',-1),(114324,39,150227,150315,'01:44:19.471','01:44:23.141','Did you see what happened?\nNo. I guess it hit over there.',-1),(114325,39,150343,150445,'01:44:24.309','01:44:28.563','Boiler room six is flooded eight\nfeet and the mail hold is worse-',-1),(114326,39,150451,150509,'01:44:28.813','01:44:31.232','Can you shore up? Not\nunless the pumps get ahead-',-1),(114327,39,150515,150591,'01:44:31.483','01:44:34.652','- Have you seen the mail hold?\n- HUTCHINSON: It\'s already underwater.',-1),(114328,39,150605,150645,'01:44:35.236','01:44:36.905','This is bad.',-1),(114329,39,150701,150739,'01:44:39.240','01:44:40.825','We should tell Mother and Cal.',-1),(114330,39,150765,150815,'01:44:41.910','01:44:43.995','I think they\'re very good, sir.',-1),(114331,39,150883,150956,'01:44:46.831','01:44:49.834','Don\'t touch anything.\nI want the room photographed.',-1),(114332,39,151076,151128,'01:44:54.839','01:44:57.008','We\'ve been looking\nfor you, miss.',-1),(114333,39,151244,151270,'01:45:01.846','01:45:02.931','ROSE: Here we go.',-1),(114334,39,151412,151446,'01:45:08.853','01:45:10.271','Something serious has happened.',-1),(114335,39,151484,151520,'01:45:11.856','01:45:13.358','Yes, it has.',-1),(114336,39,151556,151638,'01:45:14.859','01:45:18.279','Indeed. Two things dear\nto me have disappeared.',-1),(114337,39,151644,151744,'01:45:18.530','01:45:22.700','Now that one is back, I know where\nto find the other. Search him.',-1),(114338,39,151750,151794,'01:45:22.951','01:45:24.786','Take your coat off.\nNow what?',-1),(114339,39,151822,151918,'01:45:25.954','01:45:29.958','What are you doing? We\'re in\nthe middle of an emergency.',-1),(114340,39,151924,151975,'01:45:30.208','01:45:32.293','- Is this it?\n- That\'s it.',-1),(114341,39,151989,152033,'01:45:32.877','01:45:34.712','This is horseshit!',-1),(114342,39,152065,152097,'01:45:36.047','01:45:37.382','Don\'t you believe it.',-1),(114343,39,152105,152185,'01:45:37.715','01:45:41.052','- He couldn\'t have.\n- Easy enough for a professional.',-1),(114344,39,152191,152251,'01:45:41.302','01:45:43.805','I was with him the entire time.',-1),(114345,39,152257,152329,'01:45:44.055','01:45:47.058','Perhaps he did it while you were\nputting your clothes back on, dear.',-1),(114346,39,152369,152423,'01:45:48.726','01:45:50.979','Real slick.\nThey put it in my pocket.',-1),(114347,39,152429,152497,'01:45:51.229','01:45:54.065','- Shut up.\n- LOVEJOY: It isn\'t even your pocket.',-1),(114348,39,152503,152539,'01:45:54.315','01:45:55.817','\"Property of A.L. Ryerson.\"',-1),(114349,39,152643,152679,'01:46:00.154','01:46:01.656','That was reported stolen.',-1),(114350,39,152685,152723,'01:46:01.906','01:46:03.491','I just borrowed it.',-1),(114351,39,152729,152785,'01:46:03.741','01:46:06.077','Oh, we have an honest thief.',-1),(114352,39,152793,152845,'01:46:06.411','01:46:08.580','You know I didn\'t do this, Rose.',-1),(114353,39,152865,152913,'01:46:09.414','01:46:11.416','Don\'t believe them.\nYou know it.',-1),(114354,39,152919,152944,'01:46:11.666','01:46:12.667','Let\'s go, son.',-1),(114355,39,152950,152994,'01:46:12.917','01:46:14.752','You know I didn\'t do it!',-1),(114356,39,153002,153074,'01:46:15.086','01:46:18.089','There\'s a good lad.\nCome on.',-1),(114357,39,153082,153138,'01:46:18.423','01:46:20.758','You know I didn\'t do it!\nYou know me!',-1),(114358,39,153184,153238,'01:46:22.677','01:46:24.929','ISMAY: This is most\nunfortunate, Captain.',-1),(114359,39,153322,153404,'01:46:28.433','01:46:31.853','Water fourteen feet above\nthe keel in ten minutes...',-1),(114360,39,153410,153490,'01:46:32.103','01:46:35.440','...in the forepeak, all three\nholds and boiler room six.',-1),(114361,39,153496,153520,'01:46:35.690','01:46:36.691','That\'s right.',-1),(114362,39,153526,153558,'01:46:36.941','01:46:38.276','When can we get underway?',-1),(114363,39,153564,153612,'01:46:38.526','01:46:40.528','That\'s five compartments.',-1),(114364,39,153658,153754,'01:46:42.447','01:46:46.451','She can float with four compartments\nbreached, but not five.',-1),(114365,39,153770,153858,'01:46:47.118','01:46:50.788','Not five. As she goes down,\nthe water will spill...',-1),(114366,39,153864,153965,'01:46:51.039','01:46:55.209','...over the tops of the bulkheads\nat E deck, one to the next...',-1),(114367,39,153971,154035,'01:46:55.460','01:46:58.129','...back and back.\nThere\'s no stopping it.',-1),(114368,39,154043,154073,'01:46:58.463','01:46:59.714','The pumps.',-1),(114369,39,154079,154155,'01:46:59.964','01:47:03.134','The pumps buy you time,\nbut minutes only.',-1),(114370,39,154171,154225,'01:47:03.801','01:47:06.054','As of now,\nno matter what we do...',-1),(114371,39,154247,154299,'01:47:06.971','01:47:09.140','...Titanic will founder.',-1),(114372,39,154355,154387,'01:47:11.476','01:47:12.810','But this ship can\'t sink.',-1),(114373,39,154393,154461,'01:47:13.061','01:47:15.897','She\'s made of iron.\nI assure you, she can.',-1),(114374,39,154475,154499,'01:47:16.481','01:47:17.482','And she will.',-1),(114375,39,154519,154569,'01:47:18.316','01:47:20.401','It\'s a mathematical certainty.',-1),(114376,39,154675,154711,'01:47:24.822','01:47:26.324','How much time?',-1),(114377,39,154891,154952,'01:47:33.831','01:47:36.334','An hour. Two, at most.',-1),(114378,39,155096,155146,'01:47:42.340','01:47:44.425','How many aboard,\nMr. Murdoch?',-1),(114379,39,155156,155224,'01:47:44.842','01:47:47.679','Two thousand,\ntwo hundred souls, sir.',-1),(114380,39,155384,155468,'01:47:54.352','01:47:57.855','Well, I believe you may\nget your headlines, Mr. lsmay.',-1),(114381,39,155634,155668,'01:48:04.779','01:48:06.197','(SIGHS)',-1),(114382,39,155888,155941,'01:48:15.373','01:48:17.542','Oh, it is a little slut,\nisn\'t it?',-1),(114383,39,155961,155990,'01:48:18.376','01:48:19.585','Look at me when\nI\'m talking to you!',-1),(114384,39,155992,156018,'01:48:19.669','01:48:20.753','(KNOCKING)',-1),(114385,39,156019,156071,'01:48:20.795','01:48:22.964','- Mr. Hockley?\n- Not now. We\'re busy.',-1),(114386,39,156077,156159,'01:48:23.214','01:48:26.634','You\'ve been asked to put on\nlifebelts and go to the boat deck.',-1),(114387,39,156165,156189,'01:48:26.884','01:48:27.885','I said, not now.',-1),(114388,39,156195,156315,'01:48:28.136','01:48:33.141','I\'m sorry, Mr. Hockley, but it\'s\nCaptain\'s orders. Dress warmly.',-1),(114389,39,156321,156373,'01:48:33.391','01:48:35.560','It\'s quite cold out.',-1),(114390,39,156381,156449,'01:48:35.893','01:48:38.730','May I suggest topcoats and hats?',-1),(114391,39,156457,156501,'01:48:39.063','01:48:40.898','This is ridiculous.',-1),(114392,39,156517,156605,'01:48:41.566','01:48:45.236','Not to worry, miss. I\'m\nsure it\'s just a precaution.',-1),(114393,39,156613,156661,'01:48:45.570','01:48:47.572','Everybody up! Lifebelts on!',-1),(114394,39,156701,156739,'01:48:49.240','01:48:50.825','What\'s he on about?',-1),(114395,39,156761,156805,'01:48:51.743','01:48:53.578','Put your lifebelts on!\nWhat is it?',-1),(114396,39,156811,156843,'01:48:53.828','01:48:55.163','Just put them on.',-1),(114397,39,156873,156901,'01:48:56.414','01:48:57.582','C.Q.D.?',-1),(114398,39,156917,156946,'01:48:58.249','01:48:59.417','Sir?',-1),(114399,39,156986,157078,'01:49:01.085','01:49:04.922','That\'s right, C.Q.D. The distress\ncal. That\'s our position.',-1),(114400,39,157178,157203,'01:49:09.093','01:49:10.136','(SIGHS)',-1),(114401,39,157212,157314,'01:49:10.511','01:49:14.766','Tell whoever responds we\'re going\ndown and need immediate assistance.',-1),(114402,39,157542,157574,'01:49:24.275','01:49:25.610','Blimey.',-1),(114403,39,157818,157862,'01:49:35.787','01:49:37.622','Keep lowering!',-1),(114404,39,157870,157918,'01:49:37.955','01:49:39.957','Keep lowering!',-1),(114405,39,157948,157982,'01:49:41.167','01:49:42.585','(CREWMEN SHOUTING)',-1),(114406,39,158011,158103,'01:49:43.795','01:49:47.632','Steady! Make it taut!\nAnd winch out!',-1),(114407,39,158195,158291,'01:49:51.469','01:49:55.473','Uncover this boat!\nUncover all the boats aft!',-1),(114408,39,158299,158339,'01:49:55.807','01:49:57.475','LIGHTOLLER:\nRelease those ties!',-1),(114409,39,158347,158413,'01:49:57.809','01:50:00.561','Roll back that cover!\nSmartly now!',-1),(114410,39,158427,158463,'01:50:01.145','01:50:02.647','Where are the passengers?',-1),(114411,39,158469,158549,'01:50:02.897','01:50:06.234','They went inside.\nToo cold and noisy for them.',-1),(114412,39,158555,158659,'01:50:06.484','01:50:10.822','You there! Get down here\nand help with these lines!',-1),(114413,39,158824,158864,'01:50:17.703','01:50:19.372','(CHATTER)',-1),(114414,39,159000,159044,'01:50:25.002','01:50:26.838','Care for a drink, sir?',-1),(114415,39,159104,159151,'01:50:29.340','01:50:31.300','Sonny, what\'s doing?',-1),(114416,39,159153,159222,'01:50:31.384','01:50:34.262','You get us all trussed up and\nnow we\'re cooling our heels.',-1),(114417,39,159228,159288,'01:50:34.512','01:50:37.014','Sorry, ma\'am.\nLet me go find out.',-1),(114418,39,159304,159360,'01:50:37.682','01:50:40.017','Nobody knows what\'s going on.',-1),(114419,39,159366,159436,'01:50:40.268','01:50:43.187','Just like the damn English...\neverything by the book.',-1),(114420,39,159442,159508,'01:50:43.437','01:50:46.190','No need for language,\nMr. Hockley.',-1),(114421,39,159512,159569,'01:50:46.357','01:50:48.734','Go back and turn on\nthe heaters in our rooms.',-1),(114422,39,159570,159628,'01:50:48.776','01:50:51.195','I want a cup of tea\nwhen I return.',-1),(114423,39,159888,159912,'01:51:02.039','01:51:03.040','Mr. Andrews.',-1),(114424,39,159961,160041,'01:51:05.042','01:51:08.379','I saw the iceberg.\nAnd I see it in your eyes.',-1),(114425,39,160049,160089,'01:51:08.713','01:51:10.381','Please tell me the truth.',-1),(114426,39,160285,160329,'01:51:18.556','01:51:20.391','The ship will sink.',-1),(114427,39,160371,160395,'01:51:22.143','01:51:23.144','You\'re certain?',-1),(114428,39,160421,160537,'01:51:24.228','01:51:29.066','In an hour or so, all this will\nbe at the bottom of the Atlantic.',-1),(114429,39,160601,160650,'01:51:31.736','01:51:33.779','Please, tell only who you must.',-1),(114430,39,160652,160705,'01:51:33.863','01:51:36.073','I don\'t want to cause a panic.',-1),(114431,39,160713,160781,'01:51:36.407','01:51:39.243','And get to a boat.\nQuickly. Don\'t wait.',-1),(114432,39,160797,160873,'01:51:39.911','01:51:43.080','You remember what\nI told you about the boats?',-1),(114433,39,160929,160962,'01:51:45.416','01:51:46.751','Yes.',-1),(114434,39,161006,161042,'01:51:48.586','01:51:50.087','I understand.',-1),(114435,39,161234,161266,'01:51:58.095','01:51:59.430','Over here, son.',-1),(114436,39,161290,161366,'01:52:00.431','01:52:03.601','Sir, there\'s a big mob at the\nSecond Class Purser\'s office.',-1),(114437,39,161374,161416,'01:52:03.935','01:52:05.686','Go on. I\'ll watch him.',-1),(114438,39,161434,161482,'01:52:06.437','01:52:08.439','Aye. Right.',-1),(114439,39,161810,161930,'01:52:22.119','01:52:27.124','Sir, Carpathia says they\'re making\n17 knots. Full steam for them, sir.',-1),(114440,39,161975,162009,'01:52:28.960','01:52:30.378','She\'s the only one responding?',-1),(114441,39,162015,162101,'01:52:30.628','01:52:34.215','The only one close.\nThey\'ll be here in four hours.',-1),(114442,39,162119,162159,'01:52:34.966','01:52:36.634','Four hours?!',-1),(114443,39,162279,162315,'01:52:41.639','01:52:43.140','Thank you, Bride.',-1),(114444,39,162419,162459,'01:52:47.478','01:52:49.146','My God.',-1),(114445,39,162687,162735,'01:52:58.656','01:53:00.658','We are swung out and ready, sir.',-1),(114446,39,162771,162865,'01:53:02.159','01:53:06.080','Hadn\'t we better get the women\nand children into the boats?',-1),(114447,39,162911,162936,'01:53:07.999','01:53:09.000','(QUIETLY) Yes.',-1),(114448,39,163036,163112,'01:53:13.170','01:53:16.340','Women and children first, yes.',-1),(114449,39,163148,163180,'01:53:17.842','01:53:19.176','Yes, sir.',-1),(114450,39,163248,163312,'01:53:22.013','01:53:24.682','LIGHTOLLER: Ladies and\ngentlemen, attention, please!',-1),(114451,39,163324,163384,'01:53:25.182','01:53:27.685','Step this way, please.\nThat\'s right.',-1),(114452,39,163392,163460,'01:53:28.019','01:53:30.855','Come towards me.\nThank you.',-1),(114453,39,163484,163508,'01:53:31.856','01:53:32.857','Good.',-1),(114454,39,163514,163616,'01:53:33.107','01:53:37.361','For the time being, I require\nonly women and children.',-1),(114455,39,163628,163656,'01:53:37.862','01:53:39.030','MAN: Right here.',-1),(114456,39,163672,163768,'01:53:39.697','01:53:43.701','Like the Captain said, nice and\ncheery, so there\'s no panic.',-1),(114457,39,163792,163824,'01:53:44.702','01:53:46.037','\"Wedding Dance.\"',-1),(114458,39,164026,164089,'01:53:54.420','01:53:57.048','Lifebelts on.\nPut your lifebelts on.',-1),(114459,39,164097,164161,'01:53:57.381','01:54:00.051','Put your lifebelts on.\nLifebelt on.',-1),(114460,39,164169,164241,'01:54:00.384','01:54:03.387','Here, put that lifebelt on.\nTurn it around.',-1),(114461,39,164369,164425,'01:54:08.726','01:54:11.062','It isn\'t time to go\nto the boats yet!',-1),(114462,39,164433,164473,'01:54:11.395','01:54:13.064','Please, stay calm.',-1),(114463,39,164481,164557,'01:54:13.397','01:54:16.567','Make sure you have\nyour lifebelts on.',-1),(114464,39,164565,164623,'01:54:16.901','01:54:19.320','Let women and children\nthrough to the front.',-1),(114465,39,164629,164661,'01:54:19.570','01:54:20.905','What are we doing?',-1),(114466,39,164667,164741,'01:54:21.155','01:54:24.241','Waiting. Once first-class\npeople are in the boats...',-1),(114467,39,164747,164827,'01:54:24.492','01:54:27.828','...they\'ll start with us\nand we want to be ready.',-1),(114468,39,164855,164909,'01:54:28.996','01:54:31.248','Pushing won\'t get\nyou out any faster.',-1),(114469,39,164917,164950,'01:54:31.582','01:54:32.917','Go get help.',-1),(114470,39,164958,165054,'01:54:33.250','01:54:37.254','Lower it away, left and\nright together! Steady.',-1),(114471,39,165070,165142,'01:54:37.922','01:54:40.925','Both sides together!\nSteady!',-1),(114472,39,165150,165178,'01:54:41.258','01:54:42.426','Steady!',-1),(114473,39,165186,165218,'01:54:42.760','01:54:44.095','Steady!',-1),(114474,39,165254,165302,'01:54:45.596','01:54:47.598','Stop, stop, stop!',-1),(114475,39,165322,165350,'01:54:48.432','01:54:49.600','Hold the left!',-1),(114476,39,165358,165418,'01:54:49.934','01:54:52.436','Right side only!\nRight side only!',-1),(114477,39,165426,165454,'01:54:52.770','01:54:53.938','Right side!',-1),(114478,39,165462,165554,'01:54:54.271','01:54:58.109','Hold the left! Right side down!\nLower away together!',-1),(114479,39,165606,165646,'01:55:00.277','01:55:01.946','Steady, lads!',-1),(114480,39,165741,165785,'01:55:05.908','01:55:07.743','(FLARE EXPLODES)\n(ALL GASP)',-1),(114481,39,166783,166867,'01:55:49.326','01:55:52.830','You know, I do believe\nthis ship may sink.',-1),(114482