:06:04.373','00:06:08.386','To know me is to fly with me.\nThis is where I live.',-1),(115472,14,8911,8938,'00:06:11.333','00:06:12.454','When I run my card,',-1),(115473,14,8940,9057,'00:06:12.540','00:06:17.376','the system automatically prompts the desk clerk\nto greet me with this exact statement:',-1),(115474,14,9061,9102,'00:06:17.559','00:06:19.252','Pleasure to see you again,\nMr Bingham.',-1),(115475,14,9104,9210,'00:06:19.338','00:06:23.782','It\'s these kinds of systemized friendly\ntouches that keep my world in orbit.',-1),(115476,14,10053,10110,'00:06:58.897','00:07:01.252','All the things you probably hate\nabout travelling -',-1),(115477,14,10112,10207,'00:07:01.338','00:07:05.328','the recycled air, the artificial lighting,\nthe digital juice dispensers,',-1),(115478,14,10209,10323,'00:07:05.414','00:07:10.146','the cheap sushi -\nare warm reminders that I\'m home.',-1),(115479,14,10622,10678,'00:07:22.595','00:07:24.928','Do you want the cancer?',-1),(115480,14,10727,10789,'00:07:26.963','00:07:29.558','The what?\n- Do you want the cancer?',-1),(115481,14,10791,10837,'00:07:29.644','00:07:31.558','The cancer?',-1),(115482,14,10840,10982,'00:07:31.705','00:07:37.586','The can...sir?\n- Oh, no. I\'m fine, thank you.',-1),(115483,14,11494,11566,'00:07:58.940','00:08:01.920','How much does your life weigh?',-1),(115484,14,11588,11655,'00:08:02.863','00:08:05.658','Imagine for a second\nthat you\'re carrying a backpack.',-1),(115485,14,11657,11788,'00:08:05.744','00:08:11.172','I want you to feel the straps\non your shoulders. Feel \'em?',-1),(115486,14,11795,11878,'00:08:11.495','00:08:14.944','Now I want you to pack it with\nall the stuff that you have in your life.',-1),(115487,14,11880,11923,'00:08:15.030','00:08:16.792','You start with the little things,',-1),(115488,14,11925,12029,'00:08:16.878','00:08:21.223','the things on shelves and in drawers\nthe knick-knacks, the collectibles.',-1),(115489,14,12031,12087,'00:08:21.309','00:08:23.641','Feel t