le this time.',-1),(115636,14,28981,29075,'00:20:07.580','00:20:11.465','I\'m thrilled that everyone\'s back\nunder one roof. Welcome home, boys.',-1),(115637,14,29077,29148,'00:20:11.551','00:20:14.515','I know there\'s been a lot of whispering about\nwhy we\'re here, so let me jump right in.',-1),(115638,14,29150,29234,'00:20:14.601','00:20:18.111','Retailers are down 20%.',-1),(115639,14,29236,29346,'00:20:18.197','00:20:22.767','Auto industry is in the dump.\nHousing market doesn\'t have a heartbeat.',-1),(115640,14,29348,29452,'00:20:22.853','00:20:27.204','It is one of the worst times on record\nfor America.',-1),(115641,14,29458,29538,'00:20:27.431','00:20:30.757','This is our moment.',-1),(115642,14,29558,29665,'00:20:31.601','00:20:36.065','Now, last summer, we received\na dynamite young woman here from Cornell.',-1),(115643,14,29667,29759,'00:20:36.151','00:20:39.977','And she had some pretty big ideas\nthat she challenged me with.',-1),(115644,14,29761,29817,'00:20:40.063','00:20:42.387','And my first reaction was,\n\"Who does this kid think that she is?\"',-1),(115645,14,29819,29885,'00:20:42.473','00:20:45.219','But after I gave it a listen,\nshe really knocked me out. So...',-1),(115646,14,29887,30002,'00:20:45.305','00:20:50.110','With a peek into our future,\nNatalie Keener.',-1),(115647,14,30043,30155,'00:20:51.809','00:20:56.467','If there\'s one word I want to\nleave you with today, it\'s this.',-1),(115648,14,30188,30245,'00:20:57.856','00:21:00.215','Glocal?',-1),(115649,14,30257,30294,'00:21:00.730','00:21:02.260','Glocal.',-1),(115650,14,30296,30398,'00:21:02.346','00:21:06.584','Our global must become local.',-1),(115651,14,30400,30533,'00:21:06.670','00:21:12.222','This company keeps 23 people\non the road at least 250 days a year.',-1),(115652,14,30535,30606,'00:21:12.308','00:21:15.278','It\'s expensive and it\'s inefficient',-1),(115653,14,30608,30667,'00:21:15.364','00:21:17.825','When I came to Craig\nthree months ago with this,',-1),(115654,14,30669,30787,'00:21:17.911','00:21:22.813','he told me, and quite astutely, it\'s only\na problem if you have a solution.',-1),(115655,14,30789,30876,'00:21:22.899','00:21:26.529','Well, today I stand before you\nwith just that.',-1),(115656,14,30900,31007,'00:21:27.525','00:21:31.962','You all know Ned in reception.\nToday I\'m gonna fire Ned.',-1),(115657,14,31011,31095,'00:21:32.134','00:21:35.633','Sorry, Ned. I\'m sure HR\nwill hire you back this afternoon.',-1),(115658,14,31097,31152,'00:21:35.719','00:21:38.032','We\'ll see about that.',-1),(115659,14,31158,31265,'00:21:38.262','00:21:42.743','Now Ned could be any employee in any one\nof our clients\' locations worldwide.',-1),(115660,14,31267,31315,'00:21:42.829','00:21:44.823','Strategy packets\nwill be shipped in advance.',-1),(115661,14,31317,31423,'00:21:44.909','00:21:49.321','Ned will be given a seat and find one\nof our transition specialists waiting for him.',-1),(115662,14,31430,31466,'00:21:49.622','00:21:51.124','Mr Laskin,',-1),(115663,14,31469,31559,'00:21:51.210','00:21:54.965','the reason we\'re having this conversation\nis your position is no longer available.',-1),(115664,14,31561,31613,'00:21:55.051','00:21:57.210','I don\'t understand. I\'m fired?',-1),(115665,14,31615,31668,'00:21:57.296','00:21:59.507','Hearing the words\n\"You\'ve been let go\" is never easy.',-1),(115666,14,31670,31733,'00:21:59.593','00:22:02.245','Change is always scary,\nbut consider the following:',-1),(115667,14,31735,31822,'00:22:02.331','00:22:05.953','anybody who ever built an empire or\nchanged the world sat where you are now.',-1),(115668,14,31824,31906,'00:22:06.039','00:22:09.445','And it\'s because they sat there\nthat they were able to do it.',-1),(115669,14,31908,31937,'00:22:09.531','00:22:10.722','That\'s my fucking line.',-1),(115670,14,31939,31985,'00:22:10.808','00:22:12.738','But what happens now?',-1),(115671,14,31987,32075,'00:22:12.824','00:22:16.493','This is the first step of a process that\nwill end with you in a new job that fulfills you.',-1),(115672,14,32077,32113,'00:22:16.579','00:22:18.044','Yeah, but how does it work?',-1),(115673,14,32115,32163,'00:22:18.130','00:22:20.129','Take the packet in front of you.',-1),(115674,14,32165,32241,'00:22:20.215','00:22:23.409','Review it - all the answers\nyou\'re looking for are inside.',-1),(115675,14,32243,32347,'00:22:23.495','00:22:27.816','Start filling out the necessary information and\nbefore you know it you will be on your way to new opportunities.',-1),(115676,14,32349,32448,'00:22:27.902','00:22:32.000','Now Ned, I need you to go back to your desk\nand start putting together your things.',-1),(115677,14,32450,32544,'00:22:32.086','00:22:36.007','As a favour to me, I\'d appreciate it\nif you didn\'t spread the news just yet.',-1),(115678,14,32546,32589,'00:22:36.093','00:22:37.879','Panic doesn\'t help anyone.',-1),(115679,14,32591,32652,'00:22:37.965','00:22:40.519','I understand.',-1),(115680,14,32654,32714,'00:22:40.605','00:22:43.098','Give it up for Ned.',-1),(115681,14,32805,32894,'00:22:46.904','00:22:50.610','You can start the morning in Boston,\nstop in Dallas over lunch,',-1),(115682,14,32896,32995,'00:22:50.696','00:22:54.827','and finish the day in San Francisco.\nAll for the price of a T1 line.',-1),(115683,14,32997,33076,'00:22:54.913','00:22:58.197','Our inflated travel budget\nis eviscerated by 85%.',-1),(115684,14,33078,33167,'00:22:58.283','00:23:01.988','And more importantly,\nto you guys on the road,',-1),(115685,14,33169,33278,'00:23:02.074','00:23:06.624','no more Christmases in a hotel in Tulsa,\nno more hours lost to weather delays.',-1),(115686,14,33281,33357,'00:23:06.710','00:23:09.894','You get to come home.',-1),(115687,14,33405,33462,'00:23:11.902','00:23:14.272','Tell me you\'re not taking this seriously.',-1),(115688,14,33464,33515,'00:23:14.358','00:23:16.495','That\'s why I brought the entire company in\nfrom the road,',-1),(115689,14,33517,33554,'00:23:16.581','00:23:18.112','because we\'re not taking it seriously.',-1),(115690,14,33556,33632,'00:23:18.198','00:23:21.360','There is a methodology to what I do.\nThere is a reason why it works.',-1),(115691,14,33634,33723,'00:23:21.446','00:23:25.146','Coke and IBM have been doing this\nfor years. Are you familiar with them?',-1),(115692,14,33725,33840,'00:23:25.232','00:23:30.020','Like anything else, it\'ll take a few months\nto sort of transition and everybody will settle in.',-1),(115693,14,33842,33899,'00:23:30.106','00:23:32.464','Who are you taking off the road?\n- How are you not getting this?',-1),(115694,14,33901,33980,'00:23:32.550','00:23:35.837','You are grounded.\nEverybody\'s grounded. It\'s done.',-1),(115695,14,33982,34067,'00:23:35.923','00:23:39.459','What we do here is brutal\nand it does leave people devastated.',-1),(115696,14,34069,34128,'00:23:39.545','00:23:42.015','But there is a dignity to the way I do it.',-1),(115697,14,34130,34205,'00:23:42.101','00:23:45.229','By stabbing them in the chest\ninstead of the back. Is that right?',-1),(115698,14,34207,34263,'00:23:45.315','00:23:47.651','You wanted to see me?\n- Well, uhm...',-1),(115699,14,34265,34345,'00:23:47.737','00:23:51.074','You know what? Yeah, come on in.\n- Great job out there.',-1),(115700,14,34347,34427,'00:23:51.160','00:23:54.481','Thank you. How\'s everyone taking it?\n- Great.',-1),(115701,14,34429,34566,'00:23:54.567','00:24:00.280','Listen, I admire your...zeal.\nAnd I think you have some very good ideas.',-1),(115702,14,34568,34648,'00:24:00.366','00:24:03.673','But you know nothing\nabout the realities of my industry.',-1),(115703,14,34650,34739,'00:24:03.759','00:24:07.463','You can set up an iChat,\nbut you don\'t know how people think.',-1),(115704,14,34741,34826,'00:24:07.549','00:24:11.104','Actually I minored in psychology.\n- Nice.',-1),(115705,14,34862,34924,'00:24:12.621','00:24:15.198','OK, kiddo, fire me.\n- Ryan...',-1),(115706,14,34926,34999,'00:24:15.284','00:24:18.296','If she\'s gonna do this regular basis, don\'t\nyou wanna know if she can fire somebody?',-1),(115707,14,35001,35062,'00:24:18.382','00:24:20.921','She\'s fired Ned.\n- My dog can fire Ned. Fire me.',-1),(115708,14,35064,35155,'00:24:21.007','00:24:24.833','You don\'t need to do this.\n- No, it\'s OK. I got this.',-1),(115709,14,35170,35215,'00:24:25.452','00:24:27.329','Mr Bingham,',-1),(115710,14,35217,35319,'00:24:27.415','00:24:31.646','I regret to inform you that your position\nat this company is no longer available.',-1),(115711,14,35321,35345,'00:24:31.732','00:24:32.748','Hm. Who the hell are you?',-1),(115712,14,35348,35409,'00:24:32.834','00:24:35.413','My name is Miss Keener. I\'m here\ntoday to discuss your future.',-1),(115713,14,35411,35471,'00:24:35.499','00:24:37.995','My future? The only one who can fire me\nis Craig Gregory.',-1),(115714,14,35473,35542,'00:24:38.081','00:24:40.933','Mr Gregory hired me to handle this for him.\n- Handle what? Handle Me?',-1),(115715,14,35544,35610,'00:24:41.019','00:24:43.791','Mr. Gregory hired me,\nhe\'s the only one who can fire me.',-1),(115716,14,35613,35695,'00:24:43.877','00:24:47.293','You know what? I\'m gonna go talk to him.\n- Mr Bingham...',-1),(115717,14,35697,35761,'00:24:47.379','00:24:50.069','No, no, no. You can\'t follow me.\nYou\'re on a computer screen, remember?',-1),(115718,14,35763,35818,'00:24:50.155','00:24:52.438','Right.\n- Let\'s try this again. Fire me again.',-1),(115719,14,35820,35872,'00:24:52.524','00:24:54.697','I just did.\n- Actually, you didn\'t. Fire me.',-1),(115720,14,35874,35913,'00:24:54.783','00:24:56.385','That\'s enough. I think we get it.',-1),(115721,14,35915,36019,'00:24:56.471','00:25:00.815','Mr Bingham, I\'m here to inform you\nyour position is no longer available.',-1),(115722,14,36030,36074,'00:25:01.290','00:25:03.088','I\'m fired?\n- Yes, you\'re fired.',-1),(115723,14,36076,36124,'00:25:03.174','00:25:05.195','Never say fired.\n- You\'ve been let go